NK093(ge)002:3049: na rnam rig gi semas dapara ltung bar 'gyur ba
NK093(ge)002:3050: yin no // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK093(ge)002:3051: rtog pa'i skyon bcos thabs bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:3052: sgrib pa'i skyon bcos thabs bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3055: dbu mar nges pa'i zhes pa nas /
NK093(ge)002:3057: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3058: de dag bsal ba'i thabs gang snyam pa la /
NK093(ge)002:3059: rab tu 'byed pa mngon du byed pas bcos thabs bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3060: skyes bu gang su zhig gis rnam par mi rtog
NK093(ge)002:3061: pa'i ye shes gsang ba'i dbu mar ngesa pa'i lam
NK093(ge)002:3062: gyi don gnyer nas yang dag par tshola bar zhugs
NK093(ge)002:3063: te phyi nang gi dgona pa 'du 'dzi dang bya
NK093(ge)002:3064: byed gnyis dang bral ba'i gnas kyi rgyud du rang
NK093(ge)002:3065: nyid gcig pur dben par bzung ste mngon sum dang
NK093(ge)002:3066: rjes dpag gam lung dang rigs pa'i tshad ma gnyis
NK093(ge)002:3067: kyis thun mong dang thun mong ma yin par gazhala
NK093(ge)002:3068: te nges pa'i gdeng yod pa'i shes rab kyi blos
NK093(ge)002:3069: sgom skyon du gyur pa'i rnam par rtog pa'i yid
NK093(ge)002:3070: la byed pa dag rjes gcoda pa'am rtsad gcad par
NK093(ge)002:3072: chos rnams la yod pa dang med pa dang sngona
NK093(ge)002:3073: gyi rtog pa dang phyis kyi rtog pa la sogs
NK093(ge)002:3074: pa rnam par rtog pa rnams gang lasa byung ba'i
NK093(ge)002:3076: ngo bo ma grub par nan gyis brtagas pasa skad
NK093(ge)002:3077: cig snga ma'i rtog pa nyid mthu brtas pa las
NK093(ge)002:3078: byung bar shes pa'i tshes bcos pa'i thabs kyang de
NK093(ge)002:3079: lta bur rgyu 'khrul rtog brtan pa'i rtog pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:3080: snang la rang bzhin ma grub par bden med sgyu
NK093(ge)002:3081: mar rab tu shesa par gyur na /
NK093(ge)002:3082: rtog pa'i ri bo phra rags dag rab tu zhi nas yongs su dag para 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:3083: de ltar zhi ba des ni 'bras bu ngan 'gro'i
NK093(ge)002:3084: gansa ngan gsum du nam yang ltung ba mina no
NK093(ge)002:3085: // de bzhin du mtshan ma bcos pa'i thabs kyang /
NK093(ge)002:3086: rtog pa brtas pa'ang rgyu ganga las byung ba yin zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:3087: de yang lung dang man ngag la brten nas nges par brtags shing dpyad pas /
NK093(ge)002:3088: yul la mtshan mara 'dzin pa'am chos nyid la bzung ba nyid lasa byung ba yina par shes pas /
NK093(ge)002:3089: yul du zhen pa'i matshana ma yang bshad pa ltar
NK093(ge)002:3090: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i sgyu mara rab tu
NK093(ge)002:3091: shesa pa na matshana ma'i chos rnams mi ldang bar
NK093(ge)002:3093: desa ni 'doda pa'i khamsa kyi mtho ris kyi gnas tha ma mi'i 'gro bar ltung ba mina no //
NK093(ge)002:3094: matshana ma de yang rgyu ji ltar yin dpyad na /
NK093(ge)002:3095: de yang dran pa rgyu ba ni gting thog tu
NK093(ge)002:3096: byung bas 'byung ba zhes bya bas na 'byung ba
NK093(ge)002:3097: dag lasa byung bar shes te dran pa'i shes pa
NK093(ge)002:3098: phyi nang du rgyu ba na skyon dang /
NK093(ge)002:3099: de ltar dran pa'i rgyu ba ring thung rnams snang
NK093(ge)002:3100: la rang bzhin med par sgyu ma lta bur rab
NK093(ge)002:3101: tu zhira zhes zhi bar shesa na /
NK093(ge)002:3102: thabs des rgyu ba'i skyon kun sela zhing chang para byed pas /
NK093(ge)002:3103: 'doda khamsa lha'i gnas rgyal chen rigs bzhi dang sum
NK093(ge)002:3104: cu rtsa gsum gnyis longs spyod mtshungs pas gcig para
NK093(ge)002:3105: brtsis te rtogs pa de dang ldan pa dag zhes
NK093(ge)002:3106: pa'am gnas ris de dag tu ltung ba mina no
NK093(ge)002:3107: // gong ma ltar rgyu ba de yang gang las byung zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:3108: de ltar rtsad bcad pas snga ma de bzhina du
NK093(ge)002:3109: de yang de ltar bde sdug myong ba'i tshor ba
NK093(ge)002:3110: las byung ba yin par shes te /
NK093(ge)002:3111: tshor ba de nyid snga ma de ltar snang la
NK093(ge)002:3112: med pa sgyu mar lta bur shesa par gyur na
NK093(ge)002:3113: / skyon gyi tshor ba sel bar byed de mi 'byung bas /
NK093(ge)002:3114: 'doda khamas kyi lha gnas gsum par 'thab bral de ru yonga ye ltung ba min no //
NK093(ge)002:3115: tshor ba de nyida kyang de ltar gang las byung ba de nyid rtsad bcad nas brtags pa na /
NK093(ge)002:3116: ganga de yang byung tshor phyi nang nyid du 'byung
NK093(ge)002:3117: 'jug byed pa'i rgyu kho na las byung bar shes
NK093(ge)002:3118: te byung tshor ngos zin nas /
NK093(ge)002:3119: byung tshor de nyid skyon tu gyur pa'ang sgyu ma
NK093(ge)002:3120: lta bur rang byung rang zhir raba tu shes pas
NK093(ge)002:3121: na dagga pa dang skye ba'am ldang ba yang ga
NK093(ge)002:3122: la yod de med pas na de ni 'doda khamas
NK093(ge)002:3123: bzhi pa dga' ba dang ldan par ltung ba min
NK093(ge)002:3124: no // byung tshor de yanga gang las skye zhing mched na /
NK093(ge)002:3125: de'i rgyu semsa kyi chosa shes rig gis 'dzin pa lasa byung bar gyur pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:3126: de bas na semas nyid kyang snang stong gi mtha'
NK093(ge)002:3127: dang bral bar sgyu ma lta bur raba tu shes
NK093(ge)002:3128: shing rtogs na / semas kyi chos su gyur pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3129: dran rtog gis 'dzin pa rnams mi ldang bar zhi
NK093(ge)002:3130: shing rtogs na / bar 'gyur ro // de ltar
NK093(ge)002:3131: rtogs na lus su snang ba'i gzugs kyi phung po
NK093(ge)002:3132: ni snang la rang bzhin ma grub pas gzugsa brnyan
NK093(ge)002:3134: semsa dang sems byung ni skad cig ma'i rgyun du
NK093(ge)002:3135: brang breng snang yang dngos po med pa smig rgyu
NK093(ge)002:3136: lta bur 'doda pa nyid de yoda pa dang meda
NK093(ge)002:3137: pa gnyis kyi mtha'a lasa ma spangs par grol ba'i
NK093(ge)002:3138: ngo bor gsal bas na de ltar shes shing rtogs
NK093(ge)002:3139: pa des / 'phrul dga' dang gzhan 'phrul dbang byed
NK093(ge)002:3140: gnyis longs spyod 'phrul tshul spyir mtshungs pas gcig tu
NK093(ge)002:3141: pa des / brtsis te / 'doda khamsa kyi lha gnas lnga par ltung ba mina no //
NK093(ge)002:3142: de dag ni 'bras bu nas dpyad pas rgyu ngos
NK093(ge)002:3143: zin nas de nyid kyang dgag pa med par shes
NK093(ge)002:3144: pas mi ldang bar grol ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:3145: nyon mongs pa rab tu 'byed de don mngon du byed pas spong ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:3146: gzhan gnyen pos spangs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3147: rab tu 'byed pa med par mngon du mi byed
NK093(ge)002:3148: pas spongs ba ni snga ma blo chung ba dang
NK093(ge)002:3149: / phyi ma gcig char 'jug pa'i thabs so //
NK093(ge)002:3150: gzhan yang semsa nyid snang stong gi mtha' las grol
NK093(ge)002:3151: bar rtogs pas rtag pa bdag dang bdag gir yod
NK093(ge)002:3152: pa'i dngos po'am chad pa snga phyi rgyu 'bras med
NK093(ge)002:3153: ces bya bar mi lta bar mtha' la mi 'dzin
NK093(ge)002:3154: pas / 'dir rtag chad du lta ba spyi la
NK093(ge)002:3155: bsting ba'i tshig gis ya mtshan can mu stegs byed
NK093(ge)002:3161: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3162: byings rmugsa kyis 'thibs pa can du ma gyur te rang rig pa ye shes su gsal bas /
NK093(ge)002:3163: 'du shes med pa dang bsam gtan bzhi'i skyon du de nyid ltung bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:3164: sems cir yang mi rtog pa nyid 'du shes kyi
NK093(ge)002:3165: rjes su ma 'brangsa pas tha mal gyi 'du shes
NK093(ge)002:3166: dang skye mched mu bzhi'i 'du shes su mi gol
NK093(ge)002:3167: bas semsa can phal pa dang gzugs med rgyun bzhi'i
NK093(ge)002:3168: gnas su de nyid ltung ba yong ye min no
NK093(ge)002:3169: // de gnyis kyi snga ma ni byings rmugs kyis 'thibs pa bcos thabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:3170: phyi ma ni lus med sems kyi g.yo ba bcos pa'i thabs so //
NK093(ge)002:3171: chos thams cad pa'i rtsa ba kun 'byung kun gzhi
NK093(ge)002:3172: nyid rtogs te chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong bas
NK093(ge)002:3173: / zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i myang 'das nyan thos
NK093(ge)002:3174: 'gog pa'i gansa su yong ye ltung ba ma yin
NK093(ge)002:3175: / no // 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' gnyis med par rtogs pa la /
NK093(ge)002:3176: rten 'brel lugs 'byung du 'dzin pa zhi basa 'khor ba'i skyon ched du zhi bar mi lta bas /
NK093(ge)002:3177: rang rgyal gyi gansa su'ang ga la yin te mi ltung ngo //
NK093(ge)002:3178: de gnyis kyi snga ma ni /
NK093(ge)002:3179: 'dzin chags kyi dbang gis 'gog pa bcos thabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:3180: phyi ma ni phyal bas med pa bcos pa'i thabs so //
NK093(ge)002:3181: ril sems kyi chos nyid du shes pa la /
NK093(ge)002:3182: nyams myong gis 'thas te sems snang ba'i rnam riga
NK093(ge)002:3183: tsam du'nga mi lta zhing 'dzin pa mina pasa na
NK093(ge)002:3184: semsa dapa'a semas tsam pa de la yang skabs dera
NK093(ge)002:3186: de nyid ther zug dbang gis rtog pa bcos thabs so //
NK093(ge)002:3187: stong nyid mnyam pa'i ngo bo mtha' gnyis bral ba'i
NK093(ge)002:3188: dbu ma chen po'i don la mtha' dbus 'byed cing
NK093(ge)002:3189: gong 'og dang mnyam rjes so sora tha dada kyi
NK093(ge)002:3190: ris dang bral te bden gnyis dbyer med mnyam pa
NK093(ge)002:3192: dang po nas bcu pa'i bar gyi sa yi rima
NK093(ge)002:3193: pa'ang sbyong ste kun tu 'od la bgrod du yod
NK093(ge)002:3195: rgyu mtshan 'dis na tshul 'di yang sngags kyi rtsol
NK093(ge)002:3196: ba'i rnal 'byor rim gyis 'jug pa la'ang sbyar bar
NK093(ge)002:3201: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3202: bden gnyis phyogsa ris su lta ba'i mtha'a thams cad
NK093(ge)002:3203: las 'adsa pa'i dbu ma chen po gsang ba'i chos
NK093(ge)002:3204: nyid rang bzhina 'di 'drar med pas stong pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:3205: gang du'ang mi zin pa yi de kho na nyid
NK093(ge)002:3206: kyi don la / rang rig pa'i semsa nyid gyi
NK093(ge)002:3207: na 'ad'a bas bsgom pa'ang lus sems khong klod bag
NK093(ge)002:3208: bdal te yang bgas su bzhag la ched du grims
NK093(ge)002:3209: phyung ba med par btang snyoms kyi skad ciga mas
NK093(ge)002:3210: ma bral ma shor tsam du blo mi g.yo bar
NK093(ge)002:3211: dal ba'i ngang la cir yang mi bsam par rgyun
NK093(ge)002:3212: du dran par byas te bzhag par bya ste de
NK093(ge)002:3213: la yun je ring du 'bad do //
NK093(ge)002:3216: ye shes bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3224: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3225: de ltar bsgom pa'i ngo bo bshad pa'i tshul de
NK093(ge)002:3226: kho na la blo yun ring du mnyam par bazhaga
NK093(ge)002:3228: don la nye ba'i rtagsa kyi tshor ba rnam pa lnga nyid 'di ltar 'byung ste /
NK093(ge)002:3230: drod dang rtagsa dang cho 'phrul dang mngona shesa dang
NK093(ge)002:3231: ni rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes rnams
NK093(ge)002:3236: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3237: de yang drod la ni mgo g.yo ba dang legs par thob pa gnyis dang /
NK093(ge)002:3238: dang sgra'i zur gyis brtan pa dang gsum du 'gyur la /
NK093(ge)002:3239: rtagas ni mgo byung ba dang mi 'gyur bar brtan pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3240: dang sgra'i zur gyis thob pa dang gsum du 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:3241: cho 'phrul ni mgo 'byung ba dang yongs su rdzogsa par thob pa dang gnyis so //
NK093(ge)002:3242: de nas mngon par shes pa yul drug po ganga
NK093(ge)002:3243: du yang riga pa gsal te sngon gyi gnas dang
NK093(ge)002:3245: lkog gyur gyi sgra la sogs pa kun gsal bar
NK093(ge)002:3246: mthong ste ye shes chen po nyid la ltos nas
NK093(ge)002:3247: phra ba'o // de nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen
NK093(ge)002:3248: pa'i ye shes kyis ji lta ba dang ji snyed
NK093(ge)002:3249: pa thamsa cad gsal bar mkhyen to //
NK093(ge)002:3250: lnga po desa ni drod rtags kyi dona rnams yongs
NK093(ge)002:3251: su rdzogsa te bsgrub bya mthar phyin pa yin pas
NK093(ge)002:3252: skyed du bya ba med par gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3253: de dag 'byung ba'i tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:3254: de yang gzung ba la rags pa dang phra ba
NK093(ge)002:3255: dang 'dzin pa la rags pa dang phra ba dang
NK093(ge)002:3256: bag la nyal ba'i rim pas dag pa'i snang ba
NK093(ge)002:3257: ni / dper bya na mun pa sangsa nas gsal ba lta bu drod dang /
NK093(ge)002:3258: skya rengs shar nas snang ba byung ba lta bu'i rtags dang /
NK093(ge)002:3259: nam mkha' shin tu dwangs pa la nyi ma shar ba lta bu'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK093(ge)002:3260: yul khams kun tu mthong ba lta bu'i mngon shes dang /
NK093(ge)002:3261: rdzas ril la ma khyab cing mi gsal ba med
NK093(ge)002:3262: par thamsa cad gasla bar snang ba'i nyi ma shar
NK093(ge)002:3264: rtog pa grol te mun pa sangs pa skya rengs dang po lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:3265: mtshan ma dang bral bas snang ba byung ba skya rengs tha ma lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:3266: rgyu ba sangs pas nam mkha' gsal ba nam langs pa lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:3267: tshor ba dag pas kun tu mthong ba nyi ma ma shar gong lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:3268: byung tshor zhi bas thams cad gsal ba nyi ma shar ba lta bu'o //
NK093(ge)002:3271: ye shes shar ba'i yon tan /
NK093(ge)002:3273: ma rtogs par gzhan la bstan pa'i skyon bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3278: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3279: de ltar drod rtags byung nas ye shes shar bas sgrib pa 'dag pa'i tshul ni /
NK093(ge)002:3280: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob pa desa na
NK093(ge)002:3281: yon tan lnga skyes pa de yi mthu dang rtsal
NK093(ge)002:3283: kun gzhi'i khams ganga du sems la yod pa'i ma rig pa'i bag chagas dang /
NK093(ge)002:3284: de'i dbang gi 'khrul bar snang ba'i mun pas sgrib
NK093(ge)002:3285: pa'i tshogs kyi dri ma mtha' dag bsal bar byas
NK093(ge)002:3286: te dag par byed pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3288: drag po'i 'thor rlung gisa sprin phyagsa pa ltar du
NK093(ge)002:3289: bya ba rdzogs pa'i skad cig ma tsam gyi bar
NK093(ge)002:3290: du yang dag pa'i don la rnal du 'byor ba'i
NK093(ge)002:3292: sgrib par gyur pa'i mun pa'i khamsa de dag thams
NK093(ge)002:3293: cad rang bzhin med pa'i dbyings kyi ngang du phyagsa
NK093(ge)002:3295: des na don du gnyer ba'i dgos pa yang dpe
NK093(ge)002:3296: ji ltar na mar mesa mun pa basla bar byas
NK093(ge)002:3297: na / mun pa de nyid snang bar 'gyur ba bzhina du /
NK093(ge)002:3298: sems skad cig ma yi rang bzhin de nyid ye
NK093(ge)002:3299: nas chos nyid yin pa'i don du rtogs pa'i rig
NK093(ge)002:3300: pa ye shes gsal bar gyur pa na /
NK093(ge)002:3301: sngona thog ma med pa nas kyi log par zhena pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3302: lam la bslab nas yang dag par zhen pa'i bag
NK093(ge)002:3303: chags kyi mun pa'i mthar snang ma lus pa kun
NK093(ge)002:3304: sel te dag par byed do //
NK093(ge)002:3307: de ltar sems kyis sems mthong na //
NK093(ge)002:3308: ye shes kyis ni chos nyid mthong //
NK093(ge)002:3309: dus kun tu ni skye 'gag med //
NK093(ge)002:3310: sngon ma mthong ba'i don mthong 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:3311: de yang dngos po cang mi mthong //
NK093(ge)002:3312: thams cad rang bzhin med pa zhig /blo la 'gyus pa kho nar zad //
NK093(ge)002:3313: de lta bu yi don mthong na //
NK093(ge)002:3314: mtshan mar mthong ba ci yang med //
NK093(ge)002:3315: sgyu ma tsam du tshul shes na //
NK093(ge)002:3316: nam mkhar mnyam pa'i don snang 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:3318: de nas de ma thag tu yang //
NK093(ge)002:3319: yid kyi rgyu ba rgyun chad nas //
NK093(ge)002:3320: sngar 'khrul mtshan ma'i chos bral te //
NK093(ge)002:3321: des ni bden pa mthong ba yin //
NK093(ge)002:3323: de nyid rtogs pa'i rtags ni /
NK093(ge)002:3324: de lta bu'i chos nyid kyi don ganga yin pa
NK093(ge)002:3325: de nyid nges par riga cing rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:3327: don de kho na nyid de yi sgo rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3328: rig pa de yis phye zhing de bzhina nyid mthong
NK093(ge)002:3329: ba'i shes rab kyi miga gam spyan dang dam pa
NK093(ge)002:3331: mthonga thos kyi chos ji snyed pa thams cad tshig
NK093(ge)002:3332: gi lam gyi le'u bzhira bsdebsa nas tshig bzhi pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3333: tshigs su bcad pa'i sgo nas lta sgom spyod 'bras
NK093(ge)002:3334: kun gyi gnad don gsal bar byed pa dang sbyar
NK093(ge)002:3335: te smra zhing ston pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3336: gtan tshigs zab mo rnams kyang tshig la ma bslabs par rigs pa'i rtsal gyis 'byin par nus te /
NK093(ge)002:3337: de lta bu'i rtogs pa dang ldan pa de ni /
NK093(ge)002:3338: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po'am
NK093(ge)002:3339: rig pa 'dzin pa'i skyes bu dam pa yin pasa
NK093(ge)002:3340: na / de ltar don chen po de la yang dag par ltos la rtogs par gyis shig pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3345: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3346: de ltar don ma go ba'i skyon ni /
NK093(ge)002:3347: bshad ma thag pa de lta bu'i chos nyid rtogs
NK093(ge)002:3348: pa'i shes rab de yi spyan miga dang ma ldan
NK093(ge)002:3349: par rtogs pa'i gdeng dang bral na /
NK093(ge)002:3350: don gyi mtshon thabs mu mtha'a yas pa ji snyed pa'i tshiga gi lam gyi brjod pa rnams kyis /
NK093(ge)002:3351: don de la mtshon pa'i tha snyad sna tshogs pa ji ltar brjod de bstan kyang /
NK093(ge)002:3352: ji bzhin du ngesa sam ma ngesa pa'i khyad par
NK093(ge)002:3353: dbye nas nor ma nor gyi dmigas gnad mi phyed
NK093(ge)002:3354: pas yang dag par dpogs par mi nus so //
NK093(ge)002:3359: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3360: de'i phyir don ma nges par tshiga gam sgra'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:3361: blo 'brangsa pas blo gros rtsing zhing rnam par g.yeng
NK093(ge)002:3362: ba'i dmu rgod dag /nges pa'i don la goms par
NK093(ge)002:3363: bya ba'i gsang ba mchog gi bslab pa'i sa dang
NK093(ge)002:3364: lam la gnas pa ma yin te /
NK093(ge)002:3365: tshig tsam shes kyang don ma nges pas so //
NK093(ge)002:3366: de lta bu'i gang zag des gsang don mtshon pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3367: tshig gi lam gyi rjod byed 'bum phraga tu gyur
NK093(ge)002:3368: pa stong phrag brgya lta bu ji ltar brjod kyang
NK093(ge)002:3369: / de dag gazhana la ston zhing smra bar bya
NK093(ge)002:3370: ba ma yina pas gsang bar bya ste smra bar
NK093(ge)002:3371: ma byed cig /gal te gang zag ganga zhig rang
NK093(ge)002:3372: gis ma rtogs par gzhan snod ma yin pa gang
NK093(ge)002:3373: la gsang don smra ba dang bshad par byed na
NK093(ge)002:3374: / / chos min chos su smra bas log par
NK093(ge)002:3375: smra ba rdo rje gsang ba'i theg pa chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:3376: bka'a rkun byed po de nyid /
NK093(ge)002:3377: thar pa'i dus med par rdo rje dmyal ba'i gnas
NK093(ge)002:3378: dera ltung nas sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag pa'i nyes
NK093(ge)002:3383: rdo rjer grags pa'i dmyal ba der log smra de nyid ltung bar 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:3386: gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i don nges par ma
NK093(ge)002:3387: go bar dora ram g.yo sgyu dang tshul 'chosa makhana
NK093(ge)002:3388: dag gisa / don ji bzhin du nges pa'i blo
NK093(ge)002:3389: shed ma bye bar khyad par mtshon pa'i tshiga lam
NK093(ge)002:3390: sgra phyir 'brangs pa'i ming tshig gnyis kyi rten yi
NK093(ge)002:3392: ganga don ma ngesa te mi shes par the tshom
NK093(ge)002:3393: za bzhin du gzhan la gsang sngags kyi tshig lam
NK093(ge)002:3395: khams gsum gyi sems can srog chagsa pa kun gyi srog phrogsa te bsad pa'i sdig pa bas kyang /
NK093(ge)002:3396: rang gis ma rtogs te ngesa pa ma rnyed par
NK093(ge)002:3397: gzhan la chosa smra ba ni de bas kyang sdig
NK093(ge)002:3399: des ni log lam du btsud pas bdag gzhan la
NK093(ge)002:3400: thar pa'i skabs med par 'khor ba'i gting rdo byas
NK093(ge)002:3401: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa la lnga ste /
NK093(ge)002:3403: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:3406: la bzla ba'i thabs bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3409: bsam du med pa'i chos nyid /
NK093(ge)002:3412: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3413: de dag gi rjes su theg pa chen po gcig char ba'i 'jug thabs bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:3414: de bas na blo mchog gcig char ba rnams kyis blo bzhag thabs ni /
NK093(ge)002:3415: gnas lugs rang bzhin gyi snang ba bsam du med pa'i chos nyid ji bzhin pa 'di ni /
NK093(ge)002:3416: sems kyis gang du'ang bsam dpyad med par rig pa'ang
NK093(ge)002:3417: de nyid kyi phyir rtog pa'i blos cir yang mi
NK093(ge)002:3418: bsam pa kho nar chos nyid ma bcos pa'i de
NK093(ge)002:3419: bzhina nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang du ma
NK093(ge)002:3420: g.yos par bazhaga na rtsol bas ma bslad pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:3425: thams cad mi rtog skye med cing //
NK093(ge)002:3426: rtog pa'i mtha' spangs nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK093(ge)002:3428: de ltar bzhag na yid kyi bya bas mi 'khyud
NK093(ge)002:3429: pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK093(ge)002:3430: rnams ji snyed pa kuna gyi don yang bsam du
NK093(ge)002:3431: med pa'i chos nyid gza' gtad dang bral ba'i de
NK093(ge)002:3432: bzhina nyid kyi ngang du 'dus pas /
NK093(ge)002:3433: de las gzhan du gyur pa'i chos gang yang med
NK093(ge)002:3434: pas de ltar g.yo ba med par mi gnas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3435: gnas pa chen po ni rang snang lhun grub kyi
NK093(ge)002:3436: ngang du rig pa rang gsal du gdal ba kho
NK093(ge)002:3438: gong nas mtha' dang dbus bral /
NK093(ge)002:3441: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3442: 'o na lta ba'i don ma nor ba gsang sngags gcig char ba gang ltar 'dod ce na /
NK093(ge)002:3443: mtha'a dang dbus kyi tha snyad dang ye nas bral
NK093(ge)002:3444: ba'i gsang ba'i chos nyid de kho na nyid ji
NK093(ge)002:3445: bzhin pa'i de bzhin nyid ji lta bar khong du
NK093(ge)002:3447: blo ci la yang rten bcas te /
NK093(ge)002:3448: mi gnas par dbu ma'am chos nyid kyang dang du mi lena la /
NK093(ge)002:3449: bzang ngan la sogs pa'i ris su mi 'byed cinga /
NK093(ge)002:3450: ngo bo'am mtshan nyid med pa'i chos nyid ci yanga
NK093(ge)002:3451: ma yina pa la mthonga thosa la sogs pa ma
NK093(ge)002:3452: 'gags la bral bas mtshan ma'i tha snyad gang yang
NK093(ge)002:3453: meda par don gyi dngos po gang ci yanga mngon
NK093(ge)002:3455: sems mi rtog pa nyid ched du bya ba'i rtsol ba tsam dang yang brala ba nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:3456: de lta bu'i don ni mtha' gang du'ang 'byung ma
NK093(ge)002:3457: myong bas snang ba med pa'i chos nyid dbus su
NK093(ge)002:3458: snang ba'i tha snyad dang yang bral bas /
NK093(ge)002:3459: mtha' med do zhes pa'i btags pa'ang med pas dmigs
NK093(ge)002:3460: bsam brjod pa kun las 'das pa'i rang rig pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3461: ngo bo rjen par mthong nas dgongs pa mi g.yo
NK093(ge)002:3463: rgyud kyi rgyal po sems lung chen po'i mdo las /
NK093(ge)002:3464: chos nyid mtshan ma med pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:3465: chos nyid dmigs pa'i yul med pas //
NK093(ge)002:3466: dbang pos mthong bar bya ba min //
NK093(ge)002:3467: yul med khyab pas de bzhin nyid //
NK093(ge)002:3469: gleng bral 'di la gnas pa yis //
NK093(ge)002:3471: chos nyid gter ldan nam mkha'i tshul //
NK093(ge)002:3472: rnal 'byor chos nyid yin pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:3473: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK093(ge)002:3475: las dang dus la rag ma las par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:3476: yon tan bzhi dang ldan par bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3482: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3483: rim gyis pas yun ring mos chos lnga thob pa'i tshul des na /
NK093(ge)002:3484: mtha' dbus dang bral bas mnyam nyid chen po'i don la /
NK093(ge)002:3485: rim pa med par spyi blugs su btud de gcig
NK093(ge)002:3486: char du gang 'juga pa yi rnal 'byor rab mchog
NK093(ge)002:3487: de dag gi bzhag thabs ni bshad zin te bsam
NK093(ge)002:3489: de ltar gsang sngags kyi don go nas bsgom pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3490: 'bras bu nyid la zhugs pa yin pas brtson pa
NK093(ge)002:3491: che na bsgom gnas yun ringa thung la rag ma
NK093(ge)002:3492: las pa dang de bzhin du yang ganga las 'phro
NK093(ge)002:3493: yoda pa dang med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3494: dus nam zhig na 'grub par 'gyur snyam pa'i khar
NK093(ge)002:3495: yang rag ma lus te gol sgrib med pa'i snying
NK093(ge)002:3496: po la gnas pas las 'phro che chung dang re
NK093(ge)002:3497: rtsol la ltos pa med do //
NK093(ge)002:3502: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3504: de yang chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i ngang la rig
NK093(ge)002:3505: pa de yang ji bzhina par spyi blugs su ma
NK093(ge)002:3506: bzhag par bzhag pa ltar mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang
NK093(ge)002:3507: dera bazhaga na / dus skad cig tsam las mi
NK093(ge)002:3508: thogs par de ma thag tu rang byung gi ye
NK093(ge)002:3509: shes de nyid rang la snang ste /
NK093(ge)002:3510: rang rig pa mnyam pa'i klong du gsal bar 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:3511: de lta bu la re dogs med pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:3512: de bas na 'dir gsang sngags nyid kyi rim gyis pa'ang /
NK093(ge)002:3513: zab mo gcig char ba la ltos pas ring ba lta bur snang yang /
NK093(ge)002:3514: rgyu 'bras gnyis med la sbyor bas rag lus par mi byed do //
NK093(ge)002:3515: gol sa rnams kyang gzhig dpyad med par khegs te /
NK093(ge)002:3517: gcig char bas mnyam pa chen po byang chub sems
NK093(ge)002:3518: kyi klong de las don de bzhina du ma g.yos
NK093(ge)002:3519: te 'du shes gang du'ang ma zhugs pas na gzugs
NK093(ge)002:3520: khams kyi grong khyer snang bar gol ba dera mi
NK093(ge)002:3521: 'gro'o // chags na lha la chags kyang 'ching ba'i rgyu dang /
NK093(ge)002:3522: rtog na don du rtog kyang bdud yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:3523: mnyam pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ro de
NK093(ge)002:3524: la de ltar ma chagsa pas na gzugs med kyi
NK093(ge)002:3525: khams snang ba med par ga la 'gro ste mi
NK093(ge)002:3527: sems kyi de nyid mngona du gyur te mnyam pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3528: ye shes rang gsal bas na nyan thos zhi ba
NK093(ge)002:3529: phyogs gcig pa'i gnas su de daga gol ba mina
NK093(ge)002:3530: pas 'gog par ltung ba'ang med do //
NK093(ge)002:3538: spyod pa'i gol sa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3543: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3544: nges par bzung ba'i skyon gyis dbu mar gol ba'i tshul 'chad pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3545: sems kyi chos nyid la yod pa snang ba dang
NK093(ge)002:3546: med pa stong pa'i mtha' gnyis dang bral bar thag
NK093(ge)002:3547: choda de chos thams cad chos nyid spros bral du
NK093(ge)002:3548: rtogs nas ngang las ma g.yos na mtha'a las 'adsa
NK093(ge)002:3549: pa'i rnal 'byor gyi don zab mo ma nor bar
NK093(ge)002:3551: sems lung chen po'i mdo las /
NK093(ge)002:3552: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' ba //
NK093(ge)002:3553: zab cing phra la rtogs par dka' //chos nyid mi rnyed sgyu mar bstan //
NK093(ge)002:3554: ji ltar sgyu ma snang gyur yang //
NK093(ge)002:3555: de la dngos po ga la yod //
NK093(ge)002:3557: btsal du med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK093(ge)002:3558: ma btsal bzhag pas bsgom pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:3559: chos nyid ji bzhin mnyam pa'i tshul //
NK093(ge)002:3560: dmigs pa med pas kun tu bzang //
NK093(ge)002:3562: des na gsang sngags gcig char ba'i lta bas skabs ganga 'dira /
NK093(ge)002:3563: don ma nor ba'i dngos po ni 'di ltar ngesa
NK093(ge)002:3564: pa dam pa de kho na 'o zhes zhe bas
NK093(ge)002:3565: 'dod de nges par gzung ba gang dag 'di ltar
NK093(ge)002:3566: nges so zhes dbu ma pa ltar dam 'acha'a ba
NK093(ge)002:3567: ni / gsang ba chen po'i ting nge 'dzin rang
NK093(ge)002:3568: gsal ba ganga la rtags mtshan dang gol ba la
NK093(ge)002:3569: re ba dang dogsa pa med pa yi don las
NK093(ge)002:3570: 'khrul pas gola sgrib nyid du nges par snang ste
NK093(ge)002:3571: don mthong du mi ster ba kho na'o //
NK093(ge)002:3572: de ltar zhe la 'dzin pa nyid skyon yin pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK093(ge)002:3573: ci yi phyir mngon na don la dbus mtha' 'byed cing mtha' bsal te dbus sgrub pas na /
NK093(ge)002:3574: dbu ma'i chos nyid du nges pa'i dbus yod na
NK093(ge)002:3575: de la ltos pa'i mtha' yang rang bzhina gyis 'byung
NK093(ge)002:3576: la / ye nyid nas mtha' dang bral bas dbus
NK093(ge)002:3577: med pa la mtha' yi snang ba yang ngang gis
NK093(ge)002:3578: med pas mtha' dbus su 'dzin pa'i rtog zhen gyis
NK093(ge)002:3579: don dang mi mthun pa'i sel ba'i 'du shes gang
NK093(ge)002:3581: chos nyid don du gnyer ba'ang med na mtha' ga la 'byung ste /
NK093(ge)002:3582: rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs kyis gsal lo //
NK093(ge)002:3583: de bas na dbus mthar dbye ba de nyid de
NK093(ge)002:3584: ltar don las nyams pa'i phyir gsang ba chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:3585: nada yin no // gnyis pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3590: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3591: de bas na bsgom pa gol ba'i phyir rgyu'i spyod pa 'dir 'dus te /
NK093(ge)002:3592: pha rol tu phyin pa'i sa yi rim pa bcu dang /
NK093(ge)002:3593: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang gsum la sogas pa
NK093(ge)002:3594: zhes bsdu ba'i don gyis byang chub phyogs kyi chos
NK093(ge)002:3595: sum cu rtsa bdun lta bu 'bras bu chosa kyi
NK093(ge)002:3596: sku yi byang chub chen po thob par byed pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3597: dakara po'i phyogsa su bzhag pa'i las ji snyed pa
NK093(ge)002:3598: kun kyang yid kyis bsam du med pa yi chos
NK093(ge)002:3599: nyid bya rtsol dang bral ba'i don gyi ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:3600: mthong du mi ster ba'i gola sgrib kyi g.yang sa
NK093(ge)002:3601: dang gegs chen por gyur pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:3603: rig pa cir yang ma bsam na ma g.yos pa
NK093(ge)002:3604: la bsam dpyad byas pas rig pa'i rgya mtsho rnyogs
NK093(ge)002:3605: te / rtog dpyod kyi rnyog ma ma sangs na mi mthong ba'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:3610: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3611: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi dam tshig 'ad'a daka'a chena po'i daka'a thub dam pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3612: sems kyi chos nyid thig le chen po ye nas
NK093(ge)002:3613: ma bcos pa'i de bzhina nyid ji bzhin pa'i de
NK093(ge)002:3614: kho na nyid kyi ngang de la 'da' nyams dang
NK093(ge)002:3615: bsrung ba med pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:3616: dpag tu med pa'i rgyal ba dam pa 'dren mchog
NK093(ge)002:3617: bde bar gshegs pa ji snyed pa kun kyang de
NK093(ge)002:3618: las 'ad'a bar daka'a bas thugs dam chen po de'i
NK093(ge)002:3619: ngang las mi 'da' bar bzhugs pa kho na'o //
NK093(ge)002:3620: de lta bu'i ngang la bsrung mtshams gang yang gzung
NK093(ge)002:3621: du med pa la rnal 'byor pa gang gis phyogs
NK093(ge)002:3622: ris su phye nas sdom pa gang gi bsrung mtshams
NK093(ge)002:3623: 'dzina pa ni chos nyid kyi dam tshig bsrung du
NK093(ge)002:3624: med pa las gol ba yin pas don las 'khrul
NK093(ge)002:3629: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3630: khams gsum thams cad gadla khyab chen po'i chos kyi
NK093(ge)002:3631: skus bsnums pa'i gnyis med ye shes bla ma'i sa
NK093(ge)002:3632: mchog 'di nyid ni ye nas rim pas ma bgrod
NK093(ge)002:3633: par 'gro ba drug kun sangs rgyas kyi sa la
NK093(ge)002:3634: rang bzhin gyis bkoda de ma bcos rdzogs pa'i sa
NK093(ge)002:3635: chen po nyid non pas sems kyi chos nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:3636: klong 'dira ma chub pa gang yang med pas sangs
NK093(ge)002:3637: rgyas kyi sa ma yin pa'i chos gang yang mi
NK093(ge)002:3638: rnyed la / des na klong chen po gang 'dira
NK093(ge)002:3639: stong gsum thams cad sangs rgyas kyi sa la ma
NK093(ge)002:3640: bkoda par ye non pa lags pas gang sa bcu'i
NK093(ge)002:3641: rim pa rtsol bas bgrod par 'dod pa ni ched
NK093(ge)002:3642: du byas pa'i gol sa ste nor ba'i lam yin
NK093(ge)002:3643: rnyed la / no // lnga pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3644: de nyid de rig /ces pa nas /
NK093(ge)002:3646: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3647: sems kyi chos nyid mnyam pa chen po de bzhin
NK093(ge)002:3648: nyida de nyid rang riga pa de ni rang byung
NK093(ge)002:3649: gi ye shes 'byung 'jug dang bral ba'i ngo bor
NK093(ge)002:3650: bgrod du med par gdod nas grol ba yin pa
NK093(ge)002:3651: la / su dag lam gyi ye shes bsgom nas
NK093(ge)002:3652: rig pa la bogs dang skyed kyi khyad par rim
NK093(ge)002:3653: par skyes nas mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu 'byung bar
NK093(ge)002:3655: gcig char ba'i don chen po ganga 'dira rmongsa pas gol ba kho na'o //
NK093(ge)002:3656: des na sems kyi chos nyid rgyu rkyen med pas
NK093(ge)002:3657: rang byung gi snying po ye nas gnas pa'i don
NK093(ge)002:3658: shes pa'i rang rig pa de lasa ngesa par gol
NK093(ge)002:3659: ba la the tshom yang med do //
NK093(ge)002:3664: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3665: sgo gsum bcos pa'i skyon 'chad pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3666: 'dir ye shes chen po bsgom bsam spyod yul dmigsa
NK093(ge)002:3667: su med pa'i rang gsal rig pa gnyis med chen
NK093(ge)002:3668: po la dus gsum du dmigs pa'i 'du shes med
NK093(ge)002:3669: par btang snyomsa chena po'i rnal 'byor pa nyid ni
NK093(ge)002:3670: gang du'ang ma g.yos pas ma bcos rnal ma ji
NK093(ge)002:3671: bzhina pa nyid dang bral ba med par ye nas
NK093(ge)002:3672: yin bzhina du / de nyid yang dag par ma
NK093(ge)002:3673: rnyed pas rgyu ba dang ma bral bar lusa dgon
NK093(ge)002:3674: par 'dug nas dbena par byas te semsa kyi byung
NK093(ge)002:3675: tshor 'chos bgegs kyi rtog dpyod 'dzin pa dag ni
NK093(ge)002:3676: chos nyid dang mtshan ma ris su byed pa dang
NK093(ge)002:3677: ma bral bas gol sar zhugas te lam 'og mar
NK093(ge)002:3678: yin bzhina du / chud pa'o // bdun pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3682: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3683: chos kun sems nyid du rang grol bas gnas lugs
NK093(ge)002:3684: chen po de nyid la ye nas bcingsa pa ma
NK093(ge)002:3685: dmigs pas mthar grol bar 'dod pa'i 'du shes yang
NK093(ge)002:3686: med par lhun mnyam rdzogs pa'i ngo bor ngesa bzhina
NK093(ge)002:3687: du / 'og ma pa gang 'dira ldong pa dag
NK093(ge)002:3688: de ltar blor ma chud pas rang rang gi srung
NK093(ge)002:3689: bar bya ba rtsa ba dang yan lag gi daka'a
NK093(ge)002:3690: thub la rtoga pas sgo gsum bcingas nas blang dor
NK093(ge)002:3691: byed pa'i kun spyod la gnas pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3692: shin tu rnam par grol ba'i rnal 'byor chena po
NK093(ge)002:3693: nyid lasa gola te bcings grol med pa'i don ma
NK093(ge)002:3699: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3700: ye gdod ma nas ma bcos ma bslad pa'i chos
NK093(ge)002:3701: nyid de kho nar dbyings dang rig pa gnyis su
NK093(ge)002:3702: med par gang gansa te sgrib med mkhyen pa'i ye
NK093(ge)002:3703: shes de nyid rang shar ba la bsam pa'i 'du
NK093(ge)002:3704: shes gang yang med par de kho na nyid du
NK093(ge)002:3705: gsal ba la / thams cad chos nyid gdal bas na /
NK093(ge)002:3706: gsang sngags gsang ba'i snying po de la skyon gyi gol sa ga la yoda de /
NK093(ge)002:3707: gol sgrib nyid kyang de kho na nyid de'i ngo
NK093(ge)002:3708: bo yin par rtogs pas skyon yon tan du shar
NK093(ge)002:3709: te thig le nyag gcig gi klong la sel med
NK093(ge)002:3710: pas gol sgrib kyi ming yang med de /
NK093(ge)002:3712: de bas 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs //
NK093(ge)002:3713: sems ni yang dag lam nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:3714: mkha' la bya lam rjes med bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:3715: gol med lam zhes 'dren pas bshad //
NK093(ge)002:3721: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3722: de skad ces bgros te bka' stsal pasa /
NK093(ge)002:3723: 'khor langa ka'i badga po la sogas pa damna pa'i lus kyi semsa dapa'a rnams kyis /
NK093(ge)002:3724: 'khrul pa'i rtog pa gang dang gang gis bcingsa pa rnams lasa yongas su grol te /
NK093(ge)002:3725: 'bras bu gzhan la re rtsol gyi the tshoma chad nas nges pa'i gdengs rnyeda para gyur to //
NK093(ge)002:3726: de lta bu'i rtogs pa ni bshad pa ltar rnal 'byor dbu ma'i don te /
NK093(ge)002:3727: de la rnam grangs bcu las yang thog gi yul du gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3729: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chena po las /
NK093(ge)002:3730: don gyi gtso bo las chosa thamsa cad kyi me
NK093(ge)002:3731: longa nam mkha' mtha' dang bral ba bzhin chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:3732: mtha' bral du bstan pa'i le'u ste lnga bcu rtsa
NK093(ge)002:3733: bzhi pa nyid gsal bar 'grel te bstan pa'o ////gnyis
NK093(ge)002:3734: pa mi mthun pa skyon gyi rtsa ba bshad pa
NK093(ge)002:3735: la bzhi ste / mdor bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:3737: rgyud lung man ngag gi dpes mun pa'i the tshom bsal ba /
NK093(ge)002:3742: mun snang gnyis su snang ba yin te /
NK093(ge)002:3743: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3744: le'u 'dis drang don 'ba' zhig ston no //
NK093(ge)002:3745: mtshon pa dpe'i rtsa ba bstan pa de nasa yanga
NK093(ge)002:3746: sdud pa po langa ka'i mang'a badga byang chub sems
NK093(ge)002:3747: dapa'a semas dapa'a chen po des /
NK093(ge)002:3748: ston pa gasnga ba pa'i badga po la lde'u mig
NK093(ge)002:3749: tha ma rtsa ba gsum gyi don las bar ma
NK093(ge)002:3750: chos thams cad kyi mun pa ganga gi rtsa ba'i
NK093(ge)002:3751: rnam grangs chen po'i don gyi dri ba yongsa su
NK093(ge)002:3752: drisa pa / kye gasnga ba pa'i badga po /
NK093(ge)002:3753: chosa thams cad kyi rtsa ba zhes bgyi ba de yi ngo bo gang lagas /
NK093(ge)002:3754: de nyid thabs gang gis ji ltar yongsa su shes par bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:3755: de skad ces rnam grangs gnyis dris pa las /
NK093(ge)002:3756: ston pa gasnga ba pa'i badga posa lan smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK093(ge)002:3758: zhes bos nas dri ba gnyis dris pa la legs pa gnyis gnang ste /
NK093(ge)002:3759: ganga du dri ba dam pa 'di ni rang don du yang legas so //
NK093(ge)002:3760: gzhan don du'ang shina tu rab tu legsa so //
NK093(ge)002:3761: ganga chos thamsa cad kyi rtsa ba zhes bgyi ba
NK093(ge)002:3762: de ni rtogs na 'das pa dang ma rtogs na
NK093(ge)002:3763: 'khor ba 'byung ba'i rtsa ba chos nyid byang chub
NK093(ge)002:3766: de nyid ji ltar shes par bya ba'i lan bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3767: byang chub kyi sems de ni 'di ltar nye bar
NK093(ge)002:3768: bstan pa'i thabs kyi sgo nas yongsa su shes para
NK093(ge)002:3769: bya ste / gang sangsa rgyas kun gyi thugsa kyi chosa nyid dang /
NK093(ge)002:3770: semsa can kun gyi semas kyi chos nyid gnyis tha
NK093(ge)002:3771: snyad so sor dbye yang ngo bos dbyer med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3772: spros pa dang bral ba'i rang bzhin de nyid du
NK093(ge)002:3773: shes par bya'o // chos nyid de ni rtogs ma
NK093(ge)002:3774: rtogs kyi rtsa bas mun pa 'khor ba'i sems can
NK093(ge)002:3775: shes par bya'o // dang / snang ba mya ngan
NK093(ge)002:3776: las 'das pa'i sangs rgyas gnyis su snang ba yin
NK093(ge)002:3777: shes par bya'o // dang / te / tshig lhag
NK093(ge)002:3778: ma dang bcas pa ni don de nyid rgyas par
NK093(ge)002:3781: mun pa'i gzhi chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba'i dris lan bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:3782: mun pa'i khams kyi ngo bo'i dris lan bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3787: ston pa gsang ba'i sku'i lo rgyus bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:3792: the tshom chad nas slar dong ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:3793: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3795: zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:3796: gnas lugs de yanga gsang ba'i sku las thos pa'i
NK093(ge)002:3797: tshul 'di ltar rten 'dzom pa'i rig pa skad cig
NK093(ge)002:3798: gis rtogs pa gsang ba'i sku'i lo rgyus nyid ston
NK093(ge)002:3799: te / tshul 'di nyid ji ltar snang lugs ni /
NK093(ge)002:3800: gsang ba rmad du byung ba'i thabs chen pos skad
NK093(ge)002:3801: cig gis rtog pa bag chags dang bcas pa bcom
NK093(ge)002:3802: zhing yon tan rdzogs par ldan kyang mtha' kun las
NK093(ge)002:3803: 'adsa pa'i ston pa gsang ba'i sku gsang sngags kyi
NK093(ge)002:3804: rgyal po thams cad la khyab kyang rtogs par dka'
NK093(ge)002:3805: bas gasnga ba mchog gi badga po 'khor 'das dbyer
NK093(ge)002:3806: med kyi ngo bo mtha' gang yang snang ba med
NK093(ge)002:3807: pa de nyid / rgyu yi theg pas mi rtogs
NK093(ge)002:3808: pas gasnga ba'i gnas nyes pas mi gos pas pad+mo
NK093(ge)002:3809: can zhes bya ba thabs kyi mchog gi rdo rje'i
NK093(ge)002:3810: gtsuga tor gyi rtog pa gcod pa'i 'khora los bde
NK093(ge)002:3811: stong la dbang bsgyur ba'i cho 'phrul gyis sprul pa
NK093(ge)002:3812: thams cad gnas pa'i lhumsa yum gyi mkha' gasnga ba
NK093(ge)002:3814: yun dus mtha'i skad cig la bzhugs te chos ston pa de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK093(ge)002:3815: gang de nyid kyi 'khor rang bzhin gyi skyes bu
NK093(ge)002:3816: dam pa rdo rje myur ba la sogs pa dapaga
NK093(ge)002:3817: tu med pa mang po dag /rdo rje'i rtse mor
NK093(ge)002:3818: lhan cig skyes pa'i ngo bo de kho na nyid
NK093(ge)002:3819: gasnga ba dam pa'i don la sngar nges pa ma
NK093(ge)002:3820: rnyed pa'i the tshom dag dga' ba bzhi'i sgo nas
NK093(ge)002:3821: gcoda pa dang / sbyor ba'i bstan bcos ltar da
NK093(ge)002:3822: lta rdo rje'i lam nas yongsa su zhu ba dang
NK093(ge)002:3823: gcoda pa dang / / rtsa gnas rnams nas g.yo zhing da gdod zhu bar bsdog pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3824: ye shes skyes pas the tshom chad nasa slar rtsa
NK093(ge)002:3825: gnas su donga ba dang ldan te longs spyod rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:3826: pa chen po'i gsang ba'i thabs mchog gi phun sum
NK093(ge)002:3832: zhes pa'i bar gyi bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3833: gang de'i tshe sdud pa po gsang ba'i bdag po
NK093(ge)002:3834: phyag na rdo rje kho bo gsang ba'i sku'i 'khora
NK093(ge)002:3836: bcoma ldan 'das gsang ba'i sku de la 'di skad ces gsola to //
NK093(ge)002:3837: zhes zhu ba brjod pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3838: spyir dri ba lnga las 'dir dgos pa gzhan don du the tshom dang mi shes pa dris pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3839: 'o na skabs 'dir gsang ba'i sku kho na la dri ba 'byung ba ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:3840: thabs dang ldan mi ldan gyis 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i rtsa bar gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:3842: zhes ston pa la bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:3844: don chen po byang chub kyi snying po zhes bgyi
NK093(ge)002:3845: ba 'khor 'das kyi chos thamsa cad kyi rtsa bar
NK093(ge)002:3847: ma rig pas sgrib pas ma rtogs te ngo bo ma mthong /
NK093(ge)002:3849: yul du byed pas yang daga par ma rnyed /
NK093(ge)002:3850: the tshom med par ngesa par ma 'atshala lagsa so //
NK093(ge)002:3851: zab cing dpag par dka' bas blo yis bsnyagsa pas ma slebsa /
NK093(ge)002:3852: bgrod kyang yangs pas ma khyab lagsa na /
NK093(ge)002:3858: zhes pa'i dri ba bcu gcig dris pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3859: bcom ldan 'adsa thabs kyi sgo nas ye shes skye
NK093(ge)002:3860: ba'i dus kyi skad cig ma 'di nyid du bstan
NK093(ge)002:3861: du gsol / dus de la nan tan brnan nas bde bar gshegas pa 'di nyid bstan du gsola /
NK093(ge)002:3862: zhes bdag dang gzhan don gnyis kyi phyir yang gsungs te /
NK093(ge)002:3863: de ltar tshig tu zhu ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:3864: ting nge 'dzin gyis zhu ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:3866: thabs kyis zhu ba rnams las tha ma gnyis kyis zhus pa las /
NK093(ge)002:3868: 'o na 'di rgyu mtshan nyid kyang yin pa la
NK093(ge)002:3869: gsang ba'i sku'i gleng gzhir byung ba 'gal snyam na
NK093(ge)002:3870: / spyir theg pa chen po kun la grags kyang /
NK093(ge)002:3871: 'dir gsang ba'i lam du lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes skyes na sangs rgya /
NK093(ge)002:3872: thun mong 'dod chags su gol na 'khor bar snang
NK093(ge)002:3873: ba'i don dpe de bzhin du kun gzhi nyid kyang
NK093(ge)002:3874: rtogs na 'tshang rgya la ma rtogs na 'khor bar
NK093(ge)002:3875: snang ba'i phyir lung chen po'i thabs chen gsang ba'i
NK093(ge)002:3876: sgo dam pa ste ma h+aa man chad kun las
NK093(ge)002:3881: de skad ces bka' stsal ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:3882: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:3883: spyir mun pa'i spyod yul 'di la sa bcad lugs gnyis te /
NK093(ge)002:3884: lha rje yang khyed kyi lugs su sa bcad na /
NK093(ge)002:3886: rgyas pa la gnyis te mun pa'i gleng gzhi chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba'i dris lan dang /
NK093(ge)002:3891: lang ka'i bdag po de yang 'di ltar bcom ldan 'das gsang ba mchog gi bdag po de /
NK093(ge)002:3893: bde bar gshegs pa 'di bstan du gsol /
NK093(ge)002:3898: bcom ldan 'das des 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NK093(ge)002:3899: sems dpa' chen po byang chub kyi snying po /
NK093(ge)002:3901: gang mun pa'i khams pa dang cha gcig tu shes par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:3902: de skad ces bka' stsal pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3906: tshan gnyis lhag tsam gyi 'og na /
NK093(ge)002:3907: bcom ldan 'das des bka' stsal pa sems dpa' chen
NK093(ge)002:3908: po mun pa dang snang bas bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK093(ge)002:3909: cad kyi rtsa ba ni gzhi dang rtsa ba med
NK093(ge)002:3912: blun po'i ched du shes par gyis /
NK093(ge)002:3918: yan lag mdo dang rtsa ba ste //
NK093(ge)002:3922: mun pa 'byed pa'i yan lag drug dang /
NK093(ge)002:3925: de la gzhi'i mdo kun gzhi la /
NK093(ge)002:3926: dris pa dang lan dang mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:3927: dris pa ni gong du bzhag pa'i kho bos 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK093(ge)002:3928: bcom ldan 'das mun pa 'di ci las byung /
NK093(ge)002:3929: la sogs pa don bco lnga dris pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3931: lang ka'i bdag po de la gzhi'i mdo ni 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:3932: zhes pa nas mar lan 'debs so //
NK093(ge)002:3933: de la skyon du bya ba kun gzhi la dri ba'i mkhan po yang gsang bdag yin la /
NK093(ge)002:3934: lan 'debs pa yang gsang bdag yin pas mi 'thad do zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:3935: de ni gsang bdag gis dris pa las /
NK093(ge)002:3936: sngon byung du ston pa gsang ba mchog gi bdag pos lan don gyis btabs te /
NK093(ge)002:3937: rjes 'jug tu rim la yar gsang bdag gis dam pa'i rigs can la gsungs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:3938: ston pas lan btabs pa cis mngon zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:3939: de skad gsang ba mchog des bshad //
NK093(ge)002:3942: stod kyi 'khrugs med par byas la /
NK093(ge)002:3943: mun pa'i gzhi chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba'i dris lan la /
NK093(ge)002:3947: de'ang dri ba bco lnga la lan bcu gnyis su bsdus nas 'debs te /
NK093(ge)002:3951: zhes pa la lan gcig tu 'debs /
NK093(ge)002:3955: zhes pa la lan gcig tu 'debs /
NK093(ge)002:3956: mun pa zhes ci'i phyir bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:3959: zhes pa la lan gcig tu 'debs so //
NK093(ge)002:3963: mun pa'ang de nyid de las byung //
NK093(ge)002:3964: mun pa'i rang bzhin ngo bo dang //
NK093(ge)002:3965: mtshan nyid yan lag rtsa ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:3966: gnas dang sgrib pa bye brag chos //
NK093(ge)002:3967: gang du gang gis gang phyir gang //
NK093(ge)002:3968: de dag de bas dbye bar bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:3969: zhes pa de yar blang la /
NK093(ge)002:3972: lang ka'i bdag po de la gzhi'i mdo ni 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:3974: ces pa nas mar bco lngas ston to //
NK093(ge)002:3975: 'on kyang 'dir ni kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches mdzad pa'i bsdus don ltar te /
NK093(ge)002:3976: ston pa bcoma ldan 'das gsang ba mchog gi bdag po desa 'di skad ces bka'a stsal to //
NK093(ge)002:3978: byin gyis brlabs kyis lan stsal ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:3979: dgongs pa brda yis lan 'debs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3980: tshig tu brjod pas lan gdab pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3981: thabs dang brda yis lan 'debs pa thun mong ba rnams las /
NK093(ge)002:3982: 'dir dris lan gyis the tshom bcad pa spyir bstan pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:3983: bshad pa dang 'chad pa'i dris lan la'ang nye bar sbyar ro //
NK093(ge)002:3984: de bas na 'dir tha ma bka' stsal bar mdzad de /
NK093(ge)002:3985: semas dapa'a chena po zhes bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:3986: chos nyid byang chub kyi snying po zhes bya ba
NK093(ge)002:3987: chos thamsa cad kyi rtsa ba chen po'i don byang
NK093(ge)002:3988: chub kyi sems thig le nyag gcig de ni 'di
NK093(ge)002:3989: ltar dang po'i lan rang ngo ma shes pa'i ma
NK093(ge)002:3990: rig pas bsgribsa pas ma mthonga ba yin la /
NK093(ge)002:3991: de nas rim pa bzhin sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:3992: spyod yul du byar med pas ma dmigas shing /
NK093(ge)002:3993: gting zaba pasa yang dag pa'i don ma rnyed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:3994: blos dpag par daka'a basa nges par ma shesa /
NK093(ge)002:3995: byang chub kyi snying po rang gi ngang ni shin
NK093(ge)002:3996: tu myur bas rtsol bgrod kyis ma slebsa la don
NK093(ge)002:3997: de nyid mu mtha' med de yangas pasa blos ma
NK093(ge)002:3999: des na 'di nyid 'jig rten 'khor ba mun pa'i khamas na yoda pa yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:4000: rtogs par byed nas don tshol na grong khyer gsum du btsal la /
NK093(ge)002:4001: 'di yi rigs kyi rang bzhin gang zhig yin na yana lag drug dang /
NK093(ge)002:4003: rtsa ba gsum nyid yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:4004: de'i ngo bo chos thams cad kyi chos nyid de kho na nyid la bya zhing /
NK093(ge)002:4005: gar stor na ma rig bdag tu rtog pa'i muna pa'i khams su stor ba yin no //
NK093(ge)002:4008: gtan tshigs de lta bas na /
NK093(ge)002:4009: lan gyi don tshul gyis rtsa ba ma rig pa'i mun pa 'di nyid basla ba'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4010: 'di'i ranga bzhina la makhasa para bya zhing mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:4011: ji lta bar rtogs par gyis shig par gdams pa'o
NK093(ge)002:4012: // rtogs par bya ba'i thabs bstan pa'i ched du /
NK093(ge)002:4017: sgo lnga dang shes pa bzhi po'i re re la'ang sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:4021: ji srid du gnas pa'i yun dang /
NK093(ge)002:4024: mtshon byed kyi dpe la sogas pa rnams dang /
NK093(ge)002:4025: mun pa 'di nyid basla ba'i thabsa lam gyi chos
NK093(ge)002:4026: kyi mtshan nyid rig pa rnams la yang makhasa para
NK093(ge)002:4027: bya'o // 'di rnams ma nor bar nges pa la nana tan du 'bad par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:4028: de'ang don gzhan du tshol ba'i zhen pa dgag pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4029: gang blo chung ngu'i theg pa 'dzin pas mun pa'i
NK093(ge)002:4030: khamsa pa dbu sems dag gis 'dod pa'i mun pa'i
NK093(ge)002:4031: khams dang yang byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ni
NK093(ge)002:4032: cha gciga tu bstun te shes par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:4033: zhes ldog pa'i tha dad yod kyang ngo bo mun
NK093(ge)002:4034: pa'i khams dang byang chub snying po dbyer med pa'o
NK093(ge)002:4035: zhes gsungs te de skada ces bka'a stsal bar mdzad
NK093(ge)002:4036: pa dang / gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK093(ge)002:4042: de skad ces gsol ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:4043: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4044: de nyid shes par bya ba'i phyir rgyas par dris pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:4045: gsang bdag chen po phyag na rdo rje kho bos /
NK093(ge)002:4046: ston pa gsang ba'i sku la 'di skada ces gsola to //
NK093(ge)002:4048: de lta bu'i mun pa 'di nyid rgyu ci las byung ba lags /
NK093(ge)002:4049: mun pa 'di'i ranga bzhina ci lta bu /
NK093(ge)002:4050: mun pa 'di'i ngo bo ganga zhig yin /
NK093(ge)002:4051: mun pa 'di'i matshana nyid ci lta bu /
NK093(ge)002:4052: mun pa 'di'i yan lag gi dbye ba du /
NK093(ge)002:4053: mun pa 'di'i rtsa ba gang zhig yin /
NK093(ge)002:4054: mun pa 'di ji srid ciga tu gansa /
NK093(ge)002:4055: mun pa 'disa don ci zhig la sgrib /
NK093(ge)002:4056: mun pa 'di'i bye brag gi rnam grangs du /
NK093(ge)002:4057: mun pa 'di dpe gang dang mthun /
NK093(ge)002:4059: mun pa 'di thabs gang gisa sela /
NK093(ge)002:4060: mun pa zhes nges tshig ci'i phyir bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:4062: 'di nyid rtsa ba ganga du 'dus zhes /
NK093(ge)002:4063: dri ba bco lnga po 'di nyid dus kyi skad cig 'di ru yang dag par bashada du gsola /
NK093(ge)002:4065: bde bar gshegas pa 'di nyid nges par bashada du gsola /
NK093(ge)002:4066: de skad ces gsola te zhus pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:4068: de'ang spyi dang khyad par las /
NK093(ge)002:4069: khyad par du yang mun pa'i yan lag drug dang /
NK093(ge)002:4071: rtsa ba gsum gyi ngo bo las /
NK093(ge)002:4072: mdo bzhi shes pa re re la ldan pa'i bye brag bzhir nyung bsdus nas dris pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4073: de'ang mun pa ni ma rig pa dang mtshungs pa'i shes pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:4074: kun gzhi la 'di dag rgyas par ldan te 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:4077: bye brag gi lan bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4078: dang po la bcu gcig ste /
NK093(ge)002:4079: rtsa ba gang dang gang du 'dus kyi lan byang chub sems su 'dus par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4080: ci'i phyir 'thibs kyi lan rtogs par dka' bas mthar lam pas kyang ma mthong bar bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4081: rang bzhin gyi lan dngos po med pas mi dmigs par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4082: mtshan nyid kyi lan btsal bas mi rnyed pas chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4083: ci srid gnas pa dang ci la sgrib kyi lan byang chub kyi shing la bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4084: mun pa gang du 'thibs kyi lan rtogs par dka' bas khams gsum du 'thibs par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4085: ngo bo'i lan shes pa yul la 'jug cing chos nyid ma rig par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4086: gang dang mthun gyi lan mun khung du gser stor ba ltar bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4087: mun pa zhes ci'i phyir bgyi ba'i lan rtag tu
NK093(ge)002:4088: mun pa'i 'du shes su 'byung bas nges tshig grub
NK093(ge)002:4089: par bstan pa / ci las byung gi lan rgyu'i
NK093(ge)002:4090: theg pa blo chung bas kun tu brtags pa las
NK093(ge)002:4092: yan lag dang bye brag gi lan thun mong du bstan te rnam grangs ngos gzung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:4097: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4098: dri ba'i lan spyi dang khyad par las /
NK093(ge)002:4099: spyi'i dbang du lan tha ma bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:4100: cha gcig tu shes par bya ba'i don bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4101: ston pa bcoma ldana 'adsa desa bka'a stsal pa /
NK093(ge)002:4102: byang chub semas dapa'a chen po /
NK093(ge)002:4104: ma rig pa'i mun pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:4105: ye shes kyi snang bas bsdus pa'i chosa thamsa cad kyi rtsa ba gang nyid ni /
NK093(ge)002:4106: rang gi sems kyi rang bzhin rten pa'i gzhi dang
NK093(ge)002:4107: skyed pa'i rtsa ba med para snying po byang chub
NK093(ge)002:4108: kyi sems nyid du 'dusa pas byang chub kyi sems
NK093(ge)002:4109: rgyu rkyen dang bral bar ngang gcig tu gyur par
NK093(ge)002:4110: shesa para bya'o // des na mun pa'i rtsa ba ma rig pa'i sems kyang der 'dus so //
NK093(ge)002:4111: drug pa'i lan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4112: de ltar ngo bo gnyiis med chen po nyid ma
NK093(ge)002:4113: mthong ba'i don shes par bya ba'i thabs dam pa
NK093(ge)002:4114: ma nor bar ston pa'i mdo ni 'chad pa'i tshul
NK093(ge)002:4115: nye bar bstan pa 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:4116: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kyi byang chub
NK093(ge)002:4117: chen po chos kyi sku'i yon tan thams cad 'byung
NK093(ge)002:4118: ba yi gzhi dang skyed par byed cing rtsa ba'i
NK093(ge)002:4119: bcud du gyur pa'i sems kyi rang bzhin byang chub
NK093(ge)002:4120: kyi snying po de nyid ni /
NK093(ge)002:4121: kun gzhi ma rig pa dang bcas pa'i ngo bo de kho na nyid yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:4122: dper na me tog pad+mo kha 'bus pa'i rgyu yi
NK093(ge)002:4123: rtsa ba'i snying po 'dam la zug nas yod pa
NK093(ge)002:4124: ltar / snying po byang chub chen po'i rtsa ba
NK093(ge)002:4125: yang 'khor ba'i 'adma na chos nyid gnyis med chen
NK093(ge)002:4127: des na kun gzhi 'khrul pa yang lhan cig skyes
NK093(ge)002:4128: pa dang kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa gnyis
NK093(ge)002:4130: nges don 'dus pa ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK093(ge)002:4131: de yang 'dus pa'i snying po nyon //
NK093(ge)002:4132: lhan cig kun brtags gnyis 'dzom pas //
NK093(ge)002:4133: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:4134: des bskyed tshogs brgyad kha tshang bas //
NK093(ge)002:4137: de'i phyir log pa dang ma rig pa'i yang rtsa
NK093(ge)002:4138: ba rtogs ma rtogs kyis 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi
NK093(ge)002:4139: chos thams cad 'byung ba yi dngos gzhi'i rtsa ba
NK093(ge)002:4140: ngo bo 'di 'drar med pa'i sems nyid snying po'i
NK093(ge)002:4141: rtsa ba ni / dngos po gnyis pa'i chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yina pas /
NK093(ge)002:4142: khamsa gsum du snang ba'i mun pa'i chos 'di dag
NK093(ge)002:4143: kun gyi rtsa ba yang rang gi rig pa'i sems
NK093(ge)002:4144: nyid du 'dus par shes par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:4149: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4152: gnyis pa'i lan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4153: rkang pa snga ma gnyis dang /
NK093(ge)002:4154: brgyad pa dang bcu gcig pa'i lan gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:4155: rkang pa phyi ma gnyis kyis bstan par bzhed nas /
NK093(ge)002:4156: de dag gi gtan tshigs tshigs bcad 'og mas bstan par mdzad do //
NK093(ge)002:4159: don ci la sgrib pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:4160: rgyud gang du 'thibs par bstan pa yin kyang /
NK093(ge)002:4162: bcu bzhi pa'i lan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4163: mun pa'i rang bzhin rang rig pa byang chub sems
NK093(ge)002:4164: kyi chos nyid 'di ni dper na nam mkha'i gting
NK093(ge)002:4165: ma rnyed pa bzhin du shin tu zab ste dmigs
NK093(ge)002:4166: pa dang bcas pa'i blos mthong bar daka'a zhing gting
NK093(ge)002:4167: dpag par mi nus pas ngo bo ji bzhin du
NK093(ge)002:4168: rtogsa par dka' ba'i phyir 'di'i rang bzhin yang 'di
NK093(ge)002:4169: 'drar zhes ni mthong bar mi nus te yul dang
NK093(ge)002:4170: dngos por ma grub pas so //
NK093(ge)002:4171: des na slob pa'i sa yi rim pa mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:4172: te sa bcu pa la gansa pa yi byang chub
NK093(ge)002:4173: sems dpa' chen po kun tu 'od la 'jug pa
NK093(ge)002:4174: la'ang kun nas nyon mongs pa med pa'i lhan cig
NK093(ge)002:4175: skyes pa'i ma rig pa yod pas na /
NK093(ge)002:4176: de lta bu'i skyes busa kyang ni rtsa ba chen po mthong ba ma yina te /
NK093(ge)002:4177: bag la nyal ba'i mun pas bsgribs pa'i phyir te /
NK093(ge)002:4178: tshul de'i dbang gis 'thibs pa yin pas kun tu
NK093(ge)002:4179: 'od dang sa bcu man chad la sgrib cing sa
NK093(ge)002:4180: la gnas pa'i skabs sems skyes pa yan chad du
NK093(ge)002:4181: rang rang la sgrib tshab che chung dang phra rags
NK093(ge)002:4182: yod pa'o // de'i phyir sgrib pas ma mthong bar yang gsal lo //
NK093(ge)002:4187: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4189: de ltar rtogs par dka' ba ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:4190: don gyi ngo bo'i rang bzhin spyod yul du meda
NK093(ge)002:4191: pas gnas lugs mtha' thams cad kyis stong pa'i chos
NK093(ge)002:4192: nyid 'di la / blos dmigs pa'i yul dang yul
NK093(ge)002:4193: can gyi mtshan nyid gzhi nas bral bas yoda pa'i
NK093(ge)002:4194: dngosa pora yonga ye mi dmigas pa'i gnyis med chen
NK093(ge)002:4195: po nyid du nges pa yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:4196: de lta bu'i ngang la ye shes chos kyi dbyings
NK093(ge)002:4197: rgyun du skye ba'i tha snyad med par mar me
NK093(ge)002:4198: ltar rang gsal ba nyid la dmigsa pa dang mi
NK093(ge)002:4199: dmigas pa'i tshig lam chad de brjod gzhi dang bral
NK093(ge)002:4200: ba'i ngo bo mtha' dang dbus sam yod med gnyis
NK093(ge)002:4201: dang gnyis med tsam du'ang gzung 'dzin du rnam par
NK093(ge)002:4202: mi rtog pas rang byung rig pa'i ye shes tha
NK093(ge)002:4203: snyad thams cad bral ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4204: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid zab mo bsam brjod
NK093(ge)002:4205: kyi yul las 'das pa nyid du nges pas sa'i
NK093(ge)002:4206: zhen mtha' ma rtogs pa kho nar zad do //
NK093(ge)002:4207: des na med pas ma dmigs par yang nges so //
NK093(ge)002:4212: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4214: 'di nas bzung 'og gi tshigs bcad gcig yan chad /
NK093(ge)002:4215: bdun pa'i lan bstan pa'i phyir gsungs pas /
NK093(ge)002:4216: de ltar mtshan nyid 'di ltar nges te yul du
NK093(ge)002:4217: byed pas dus gsum du ma rnyed pas mun khams
NK093(ge)002:4218: 'khor ba ji snyed pa'i yul du gnas kyang byang
NK093(ge)002:4219: chub snying po'i shing bu mngon du gyur pa na
NK093(ge)002:4220: ldog par bstan pa yin la /
NK093(ge)002:4223: byang chub kyi snying po ni ye nas yul med rang gasla gyi ngo bo nyid yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:4224: dran rig sgrib byed dang bral ba'i sgo nas dus
NK093(ge)002:4225: thog ma dang tha ma bral ba'i mtha' yi tshad
NK093(ge)002:4226: gzung med pa ru gnas khams gsum ma lus par
NK093(ge)002:4227: khyab para kun tu btsal bar byas na yang /
NK093(ge)002:4228: sems kyi ngo bo mtshan nyid 'di ltar nges pa
NK093(ge)002:4229: zhig go zhes bya ba'i dngosa po nges gzung can
NK093(ge)002:4230: zhiga sngar gyi sangs rgyas kun gyis kyang mi rnyed
NK093(ge)002:4231: pa'i ngang de la sems can rnams kyis da yong
NK093(ge)002:4232: btsal yang phyis su rnyed para mi 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:4233: de bzhin du rgyal ba lta bu'i makhasa pa'am sgra
NK093(ge)002:4234: dang tshad ma la mkhas shing goms par byas pas
NK093(ge)002:4235: kyang dus thog mtha'a meda pa ru blo so sor
NK093(ge)002:4236: rtog pa'i shes rab kyis shina tu bsgrimsa te mtha'
NK093(ge)002:4237: bgrangs nas cir zhes ci ltar brtagsa shing dpyad par
NK093(ge)002:4238: byas pas kyang / gang snying po byang chub kyi
NK093(ge)002:4239: mtshan nyid 'dira ngo bo nges pa cir yanga mthong
NK093(ge)002:4240: byas pas kyang / ba meda de / slar yang ched du byas pa'i sgrib par 'gyur bas so //
NK093(ge)002:4241: de bas na yul du byed pas dus gsum du
NK093(ge)002:4242: mi rnyed pas 'khor ba ji snyed pa'i yul du
NK093(ge)002:4245: mnyam pa chen po ma yin pa med pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4246: dpe lta bur mgyogsa pasa dus mtha'a meda pa ru /
NK093(ge)002:4247: nyam thaga chad par brgyugsa te kun tu phyin kyang ni /
NK093(ge)002:4248: da dung de kho na nyid chos kyi dbyingsa 'di
NK093(ge)002:4249: nyid lasa gzhan gara yang ma phyin pas logs su
NK093(ge)002:4250: gyur par sngar yang ma slebs pas na da yang
NK093(ge)002:4251: phyin pa med par gzhi 'di nyid kyi ngang kho
NK093(ge)002:4252: na'o // des nas bgrod du med par mun pa'i rang bzhin dang cha gcig tu gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4256: myur bas ma sleb par nges pa'ang yin no //
NK093(ge)002:4261: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4262: bdun pa dang brgyad pa gnyis kyi lan gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:4263: rnal 'byor gyi dbang gis rgyu'i theg pa las rnam par thar pa gsum du bstan kyang /
NK093(ge)002:4264: 'dir thun mong min pa'i gnas lugs dngos gzhi dang
NK093(ge)002:4265: bral bas skye ba meda pa'i chos nyid kyi sdong
NK093(ge)002:4266: po kun gyi rtsa bar gyur pas dngos po'i de
NK093(ge)002:4268: ma rtogs pa'i dus su 'khor ba'i chos kyi yan lag sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK093(ge)002:4269: mtshan nyid rtogs pas lam pa'i blo la lam gyi chos su snang bas na /
NK093(ge)002:4270: rang bzhin dang mthun par stong pa nyid dang /
NK093(ge)002:4273: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi
NK093(ge)002:4274: rnam par thar ba'i sgo bzhi yi ye shes ma
NK093(ge)002:4275: 'gags par snang bas yal ga 'gel ba'am yan lag
NK093(ge)002:4276: gela pa ni kun nas rgyas pa dang phyogs su
NK093(ge)002:4278: de nyid lam pas don du gnyer nas 'bad pa
NK093(ge)002:4279: byas pas lam gyi rnam thar bzhis 'bras bu'i mtshan
NK093(ge)002:4280: nyid byang chub bla na med pa'i snying por smin
NK093(ge)002:4281: te chos sku chen po nyid du mthar phyin pa'o
NK093(ge)002:4282: // che ba'i yon tan de ltar rgyas pa'i snying
NK093(ge)002:4283: po'i ljon pa bzang po de ni yon tan kun
NK093(ge)002:4284: gyi 'byung gnas byang chub kyi shing bu dam pa
NK093(ge)002:4285: // yin no // de bas na byang chub snying
NK093(ge)002:4286: po'i ngo bo la sgrib cing de nyid mngon du
NK093(ge)002:4288: tshul de'i phyir yangs pas ma khyab par yang gsal lo //
NK093(ge)002:4293: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4294: bsdus don ltar na tshigs bcad 'di nyid bcu gcig pa'i lan te /
NK093(ge)002:4295: shes pa tshogs drug yul drug la 'juga pa dang
NK093(ge)002:4296: bcas te gzugs sgra la sogs pa'i yul dona gyi
NK093(ge)002:4297: dngos po la ma rig pa'i dbang gis zhen cing
NK093(ge)002:4298: chags pa ni 'doda pa'i khamas kyi ma rig pa
NK093(ge)002:4299: yin la / bsam gtan bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin mngona
NK093(ge)002:4300: du byed cing de la nyon yid kyis bdag tu
NK093(ge)002:4301: 'dzina pa'i 'du shes dang ma bral ba nyid gzugsa
NK093(ge)002:4302: kyi khamas kyi ma rig par nges so //
NK093(ge)002:4303: gzugs mngon du snang ba med par kun gzhi'i ngang
NK093(ge)002:4304: la bsam pa'i 'du shes bzhi rgyun ma chad par
NK093(ge)002:4305: snyoms 'jug bzhi la gnas te dmigs pa dang rnam
NK093(ge)002:4306: par rgyu bas yang dag pa'i don ma rnyed pa
NK093(ge)002:4307: gzugsa med pa'i khams kyi ma rig pa nyid de
NK093(ge)002:4308: bye brag gsum gyis chos nyid rtogs par dka' bas
NK093(ge)002:4309: na khams gsum du 'thibs pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:4310: des na ganga shes pa gsum du snang ba de yi rgyu ni /
NK093(ge)002:4311: ji bzhin pa ma rig pa las rang gi yul
NK093(ge)002:4312: dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dmigs pa la ched du
NK093(ge)002:4313: 'dzin pa'i lasa kyi byed pa lasa ma rig pa'i
NK093(ge)002:4314: rgyun gyis khams gsum du snang bar gyur ba yin
NK093(ge)002:4316: rkang pa snga ma gsum dgu pa'i lan te /
NK093(ge)002:4317: ma rig pa'i bye brag gis khams gsum du snang ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:4318: dang po'i lan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4319: rkang pa bzhi pa gsungs te /
NK093(ge)002:4320: ma rig pa'i dbang gis rang yul ched du byed pa las grong khyer gsum du byung bas so //
NK093(ge)002:4321: tshul 'di dag la brten nas btsal ba'i gnas grong khyer gsum yin par shes par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:4326: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4328: dbang po'i yul dang sems kyi yul ting nge 'dzin
NK093(ge)002:4329: du chags pas khams gsum gyi 'gro ba'i yul du
NK093(ge)002:4330: gang gyur pa'i dngos po gang yang rung ba la
NK093(ge)002:4332: yul gang la 'juga kyang rung ste g.yo ba de
NK093(ge)002:4333: nyid khams gsum gyi 'khrul pa'i rnam par shes pa
NK093(ge)002:4334: don la mdongs pa'i ngo bo de nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:4335: des na shes pas zin pa'i yul gang du snang
NK093(ge)002:4336: bar gyur pa na yang 'gro ba de dag gi
NK093(ge)002:4337: spyod yul de ni mun pa'i khamsa su gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:4340: mun pa'i khamas nyid na rang rig pa byang chub
NK093(ge)002:4341: kyi snying po'i ngo bo de nyid snang zhing gnyis
NK093(ge)002:4342: su med par gsal bar yod pas nang shes pa'i
NK093(ge)002:4343: rgyun gsal ba de ni snang ba'i khams yang yin
NK093(ge)002:4344: no // des na byang chub kyi sems 'di ni mun pa'i khams na yod do //
NK093(ge)002:4345: de yang sems dang sems byung du snang ba dang
NK093(ge)002:4346: sems snang ba'i 'od du byung ba'i dngos po gnyis
NK093(ge)002:4347: pa ji snyed pa de dag skye ba bzhi dang
NK093(ge)002:4348: 'byung ba lnga la sogs par snang ba'i yang gzhi
NK093(ge)002:4349: dang rten du gyur pas rtsa ba'i snying po rang
NK093(ge)002:4350: rig pa cir yang snang ba nyid yin pas khams
NK093(ge)002:4351: gsum gyi 'gro ba kun gyis de nyid la kun
NK093(ge)002:4352: gzhi'i khams kyi dngos po'i phyogsa kyi khyad par tsam
NK093(ge)002:4353: du riga cing mthong yang ngesa pa'i don ji bzhin
NK093(ge)002:4354: du ma rig pa yi ngo bo nyid med pas
NK093(ge)002:4355: phyogs ris su gzung du mi btub pa'i shes pa
NK093(ge)002:4356: ma rig pa dang mtshungs pa'i rang rig pa de
NK093(ge)002:4357: nyid yin pas don la mun snang dbyer med kyi
NK093(ge)002:4358: chos nyid bsam brjod las 'das pa nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:4359: des na ngo bo de kho na nyid la bya bar yang gsal lo //
NK093(ge)002:4364: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4366: tshigs bcad 'di nyid bcu pa'i lan te /
NK093(ge)002:4367: de ltar shes pa ma rig pa dang mtshungs par
NK093(ge)002:4368: ldan pas rang gi chos nyid mi mthong ba ni
NK093(ge)002:4369: / dper na mun khung du gsera stor ba ji lta ba bzhina du /
NK093(ge)002:4370: 'khora ba'i gnas mun pa mun nag gi smag rum dang 'dra ba nyid du /
NK093(ge)002:4371: rin chen gsera dang 'dra ba yi chos nyid byang
NK093(ge)002:4372: chub semas kyi don 'di nyid stor bar gyur te
NK093(ge)002:4373: / ma rig pas don mthong du mi ster ba'i phyir dpe don mthun par nges pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4377: dper mun par gser stor ba dang 'dra ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:4378: de nas rkang pa gsum lan bcu gsum pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:4379: 'khor ba'i smag rum du rin chen sems nyid kyi don stor te /
NK093(ge)002:4380: ma rig pas don mthong du mi ster ba'i phyir mun pa zhes bgyi ba'i gtan tshigs so //
NK093(ge)002:4381: des na mun pa'i khams su stor ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:4386: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4389: ma rig pa gnyis kyi mun pa'i khamas su gyur
NK093(ge)002:4390: pa'i 'gro ba sems can gyi gnas skabs dag tu
NK093(ge)002:4391: / dper na mig gis mig mi mthong ba ltar
NK093(ge)002:4392: spyod yul dang bral bas rang gis rang ma mthong
NK093(ge)002:4393: / ste / shes pa ma rig pa'i rgyud du
NK093(ge)002:4394: gyur pa'i phyir mun pa'i 'du shes nyida du 'byung
NK093(ge)002:4395: / ste / bas na / sngags la ltos pa'i
NK093(ge)002:4396: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'ang 'du shes de dang
NK093(ge)002:4398: de'i phyir mun pa zhes bagyi'o //
NK093(ge)002:4401: ma rig pa sha stag tu gyur pa'i 'gro ba rnams /
NK093(ge)002:4402: ma rig pa gnyis kyis non pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:4403: dper mig gis mig ma mthong ba ltar yul bral bas rang gis rang ma mthong ste /
NK093(ge)002:4404: shes pa ma rig pa rgyud du gyur pa'i phyir mun pa nyid du 'thibs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4409: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4412: khams gsum gyi 'gro ba'i mun pa'i shes pa ma
NK093(ge)002:4413: zad gsang sngags bla na med pa la ltos nas
NK093(ge)002:4414: mun pa'i khamas pas grub mtha' smra ba dag gis
NK093(ge)002:4415: gang ltar shesa pa rtog pa'i mtshan nyid phra mo'i
NK093(ge)002:4416: phra mo cha shas tsam gyi dngos po yana chad
NK093(ge)002:4417: thams cad mun pa yin pas de'i dngos don ganga
NK093(ge)002:4418: 'dira blo chung byis pa rgyu'i theg pa chen po
NK093(ge)002:4419: rnams kyi ched du ston pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK093(ge)002:4420: kyis gleng gzhi gang zhig brjod pa de nyid /
NK093(ge)002:4421: 'di na don dang mthun par gsal ba'i phyir gsang
NK093(ge)002:4422: sngags theg pa chen po'i blo dang ldana pa kuna
NK093(ge)002:4423: la yang 'di ltar brjod cing bshad kyis /
NK093(ge)002:4424: sems dpa' chen po khyod kyis kyang gzhan gyi don
NK093(ge)002:4425: phyir blun po'i rigs can drang ba'i cheda du shesa
NK093(ge)002:4426: para byos la rtogs par gyis shig ces gdams par
NK093(ge)002:4427: mdzad pa'o // tshul 'di ltar na mun pa gang
NK093(ge)002:4428: gis sel gyi lan 'dir dngos su ma zin kyang
NK093(ge)002:4432: mun pa'i khams par gyur pas grong khyer gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams kyis /
NK093(ge)002:4433: gang yul gyi bye brag shes par byed pa'i shes
NK093(ge)002:4434: pa dngos po la rig cing rtog pa'i ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:4435: ni mun pa'i mtshan nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:4436: de dag gi mtshan nyid phra mo'i cha shas tsam
NK093(ge)002:4437: yang chad phra rags thams cad ji ltar bsal ba
NK093(ge)002:4438: bcu gnyis pa'i lan gyis gsal bar ston te /
NK093(ge)002:4439: gang 'dir rgyu'i theg pa chen po blo chung zhing
NK093(ge)002:4440: don gyi brda shed ma bye ba rnams kyi ched
NK093(ge)002:4441: du ston pas gleng gzhi gang brjod cing bka' stsal
NK093(ge)002:4442: pa de nyid / 'dir gsal ba'i phyir theg pa
NK093(ge)002:4443: chen po'i blo dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor kun la
NK093(ge)002:4444: yang 'di ltar brjod de bshad kyis /
NK093(ge)002:4445: khyod kyis kyang gzhan blun po rnams drang ba'i ched du shes par gyis shig par gdams pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4450: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4451: bsdus don ltar na lnga pa dang dgu pa'i lan dang /
NK093(ge)002:4452: 'grel chen las lnga pa'i lan dang khyad par gyis
NK093(ge)002:4453: de dag gis lan gdab pa thun mong du bstan
NK093(ge)002:4454: pa'i phyir / ma rig pa'i mun pa mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:4455: pas mthong ba'i don 'di yang yan lag 'byed na
NK093(ge)002:4456: 'di ltar lde mig gsum du yongas su snang ba
NK093(ge)002:4457: pa'i phyir / nyid de / yan lag tshogs drug
NK093(ge)002:4458: dang mdo shes pa bzhi dang rtsa ba lus ngag
NK093(ge)002:4459: pa'i phyir / nyid de / yid gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:4460: lde mig dang pos 'khor ba rnam par 'byed pa
NK093(ge)002:4461: pa'i phyir / nyid de / yid gsum ste / dang / bar mas 'grol ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:4462: tha mas nges par 'byin pa yina te /
NK093(ge)002:4463: shugs kyis bcu gnyis pa'i lan du'ang 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:4464: des na bka'i lung gcig la zhus lan phra men rgyas na rgyud du 'gro ba'i dpe ltar /
NK093(ge)002:4465: rnam par shes pa'i rgyud gcig la dbang po drug
NK093(ge)002:4466: gi rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa tshogs drug dang
NK093(ge)002:4467: dmigs pa'i rnam shes dang bdun rtsa ba'i rnam shes
NK093(ge)002:4468: dang brgyad du byung nas sgo gsum du rgyas shing
NK093(ge)002:4471: mun pa'i yan lag drug bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4473: mun pa'i rtsa ba gsum bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4478: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4479: de la yan lag dang po gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:4480: rnam par shes pa'i rgyud gcig la dbang po drug
NK093(ge)002:4481: gi rkyen gyis yana lag drug tu gang gragsa pa
NK093(ge)002:4482: ni / mig gis mthonga ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:4487: yid kyis kun shes pa dang rnam par shes pa'i tshogs drug ste /
NK093(ge)002:4488: de la'ang rgyu'i yan lag drug dang /
NK093(ge)002:4489: dmigs pa'i yan lag drug dang /
NK093(ge)002:4490: gcod pa'i yan lag drug ste /
NK093(ge)002:4491: yul la phyir 'byung ba lta bu dang dngos su
NK093(ge)002:4492: yul la 'juga cing yul gyi sgro 'dogs yongs su
NK093(ge)002:4493: gcoda pa'i yan lag tu gyur pa rnams yina no
NK093(ge)002:4495: sgo lnga 'jug pa'i mdo dang mthun /
NK093(ge)002:4496: yid shes snang ba'i mdo dang mthun pas 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:4505: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4506: langa ka'i badga po zhes bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:4507: mdo bzhi bstan pa ni ganga zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:4508: lung gi mdo bzhi ni rnam shes bzhi ste /
NK093(ge)002:4509: chos thams cad kyi mdo rnam shes su 'dus pa'i tshul 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:4510: bag chags bsags pa'i gzhi'i mdo kun gzhi dang /
NK093(ge)002:4511: de la bdag tu lta bas dmigsa pa'i mdo nyon yid dang /
NK093(ge)002:4512: phyi nang kun snang ba'i mdo yid kyi shes pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:4513: rang yul thun min la 'juga pa'i mdo sgo lnga'i shes pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4515: mdo bzhi po gzhi yi mdo dang dmigsa pa dang
NK093(ge)002:4516: snang ba dang 'juga pa yi mdo bzhi ston pa
NK093(ge)002:4517: mchog gis drang ba'i lung bzhina du gsal bar bashada
NK093(ge)002:4520: gzhi'i mdo kun gzhi bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4521: dmigs pa'i mdo nyon mongs pa can gyi yid bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4522: snang ba'i mdo yid kyii rnam shes bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4523: 'jug pa'i mdo sgo lnga'i shes pa bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4532: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4533: de la mun pa'i dris lan so so'i bye brag tu phye nas mdo dang po bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4536: de la gzhi'i mdo nye bar ston pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:4537: cha phra ba'i gzhi de ni mtshan nyid theg pa
NK093(ge)002:4538: don la shed ma bye ba'i byis pa rnam rig
NK093(ge)002:4539: pa la sogs pa rnams kun gzhi'i rang bzhin 'di
NK093(ge)002:4540: ltar 'doda de de nyid 'thad par sgrub par byed
NK093(ge)002:4541: do // gnyis pa la bcu gnyis te /
NK093(ge)002:4542: rang bzhin dngos po med cing kun la khyab pas ma bcos par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4543: mtshan nyid shes la mi gsal bas tshor ba btang
NK093(ge)002:4544: snyoms dang ldan te skad cig ma'i rgyun dang bcas
NK093(ge)002:4545: par bstan pa / ngo bo phyogs gcig tu rgya
NK093(ge)002:4546: ma chad pas bag chags thams cad kyi gzhir bstan
NK093(ge)002:4547: par bstan pa / pa / yan lag thun mong
NK093(ge)002:4548: dang khyad par gyi 'khor dang ldan pas bag chags
NK093(ge)002:4550: gnas pa'i yun dang ci la sgrib kun thun mong du bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4551: bye brag 'khor 'das gnyis kyi gzhi rten du gyur par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4552: rtsa ba gang dang gang du 'dus pa thun mong du bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:4553: mun pa'i rgyu ci las byung dang kun gzhi sgrub byed kyi rigs pa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4554: mun pa'i khams kyi kun gzhi nyid dpe gang dang mthun tshul bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4555: mun pa zhes ci'i phyir bgyi ba'i nges tshig bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4556: mun pa nyid ci'i phyir 'thibs pa'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:4557: mun pa gang gis sel ba ye shes rang snang du bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:4562: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4563: spyir kun gzhi dang mun pa gnyis ngo bo gcig yin kyang /
NK093(ge)002:4564: thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pas kun gzhi dang /
NK093(ge)002:4565: de ma rtogs pas 'khor bar snang bas mun pa zhes bstan pa yin la /
NK093(ge)002:4566: de bas na gong gi mun pa'i dris lan dang kun gzhi'i dris lan mthun no //
NK093(ge)002:4567: 'on kyang gong gi mun pa gang gi ched du
NK093(ge)002:4568: lan ma gsungs pa rnams 'dir bstan par mdzad do
NK093(ge)002:4569: // de yang 'chad pa'i don gyi rnam grangs kyis bcu gsum du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:4570: khyad par du mun pa'i rang bzhin nyid 'chad de /
NK093(ge)002:4571: de la sbyor ba'i kun gzhi rang bzhin cha phra
NK093(ge)002:4572: bas gzugsa kyi phung po dngos su snang ba med
NK093(ge)002:4573: par brtags pa'i mtshan nyid kyi ming bzhi'i phung po'i
NK093(ge)002:4574: mtshan ma'i tha snyad tsam la kha bltas te mngona
NK093(ge)002:4575: par zhena cing rtog pa'i ngo bo gsal bar snang
NK093(ge)002:4576: ba med pa de ni gzugs med pa'i khamas la
NK093(ge)002:4577: gnas pa nyid yin pas kun gzhi de yang de
NK093(ge)002:4578: dang cha mthun pa kho na yin zhing /
NK093(ge)002:4579: kun gzhi de'i byed pa'i las kyi khyad par gyis
NK093(ge)002:4580: rnam par shesa pa tshogs brgyad dang drug dang sems
NK093(ge)002:4581: byung dang bcas pa kun gyi rgyu'i ngo bora snang
NK093(ge)002:4582: bas thams cad 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur la /
NK093(ge)002:4583: de bas na kun gzhi de nyid rgyu'i theg pa
NK093(ge)002:4584: sems tsam dang dbu ma'i grub mtha' 'dzin pa phal
NK093(ge)002:4585: che bas snang sems kun gyi gzhi shesa par bya
NK093(ge)002:4586: ba'i chos su bzhed pa nyida de /
NK093(ge)002:4587: des na 'dir yang don gyi shes byar mi bzhed kyang /
NK093(ge)002:4589: rgyan stug po bkod pa las /
NK093(ge)002:4590: ji ltar khab len mthong ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:4591: lcags ni myur bar kun tu 'khor //
NK093(ge)002:4592: 'on kyang de la sems pa med //
NK093(ge)002:4593: sems ldan bzhin du'ang rab tu snang //
NK093(ge)002:4594: de bzhin kun gzhi rnam shes kyang //
NK093(ge)002:4595: sems med sems can ji bzhin du //
NK093(ge)002:4597: sa rnams 'bri bar rab tu byed //
NK093(ge)002:4599: 'di ltar snang ba gang yang rung //
NK093(ge)002:4600: mtshan ma gzugs su snang ba rnams //
NK093(ge)002:4601: bag chags log pa'i kun gzhi ste //
NK093(ge)002:4602: sa rnams kun na gzugs ltar gnas //
NK093(ge)002:4603: ji ltar 'o ma gyur pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:4604: yon tan zho dang dar bar snang //
NK093(ge)002:4605: de bzhin kun gzhi rnam shes kyang //
NK093(ge)002:4606: rnam par gyur nas gzugs ltar gnas //
NK093(ge)002:4608: gzugs kyi yon tan ldan pa'i gzugs //
NK093(ge)002:4609: kun gzhi gzugs ltar gnas pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:4610: byis pa ji ltar brtags pa bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:4611: gzugs ni gud na yod pa min //
NK093(ge)002:4613: brtags pa'i sems can du snang zhing mtshan ma'i don
NK093(ge)002:4614: du snang ba'i gzhir gyur pas phyi rol gyi yul
NK093(ge)002:4615: sna tshogs pa nyid du snang bas na /
NK093(ge)002:4616: dper na dge slong mi gtsang ba bsgom pas spyod
NK093(ge)002:4617: yul thams cad rus pa'i phung por snang ba lta
NK093(ge)002:4618: bur / yul thams cad kyi yang rtsa ba kun
NK093(ge)002:4619: gzhi 'khrul pas phyi rol yul gyi dngos po sna
NK093(ge)002:4620: tshogs su snang zhing sa bon thams cad pa yin
NK093(ge)002:4621: pas 'khor 'das dang dge sdig dang lam pa'i lta
NK093(ge)002:4622: ba la sogs pa kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos
NK093(ge)002:4623: rnams thamsa cad 'byung bar byed pa'i rgyu dang rnam
NK093(ge)002:4624: par byang ba'i rten du gyur pa ni sbyor ba
NK093(ge)002:4626: gzhi don gyi kun gzhi'i rang bzhin ni /
NK093(ge)002:4627: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi rkyen bzhis 'khrul bdo tsam na /
NK093(ge)002:4628: spyil po'am khang pa lta bur rang re rnam par gtses pas spyi 'dus bdo ba tsam med de /
NK093(ge)002:4629: ye thog ma nas rnal ma don gyi ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:4630: rang bzhin nganga gis ma skyes la byed pa pos
NK093(ge)002:4631: ma bcosa par thams cad la khyab cing ngos bzung
NK093(ge)002:4632: dang bral te sgrib byed med par yong gisa 'od
NK093(ge)002:4633: gsal ba rgyu rkyen med par rang snang yang ngo
NK093(ge)002:4634: bo 'dus ma byas pa chos nyid skye ba med
NK093(ge)002:4635: pa'i ngang de'o // de'ang dri bral gyi chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:4636: min par dri ma dang bcas pa'i gnas lugs yin
NK093(ge)002:4637: pa'i ngang de'o // pas / yang 'byed 'phrul gyi lde mig las /
NK093(ge)002:4638: kun gzhi kun gzhi zhes bya ba //
NK093(ge)002:4639: thams cad kun gyi gzhir gyur pas //
NK093(ge)002:4640: de phyir kun gzhi'i ming du btags //
NK093(ge)002:4641: dper na sa la rnyog mi zer //
NK093(ge)002:4642: de bzhin chu la rnyog mi zer //
NK093(ge)002:4643: sa chu 'dres la rnyog mar btags //
NK093(ge)002:4644: de bzhin sems can thams cad la //
NK093(ge)002:4645: chos skus khyab par gnas pa la //
NK093(ge)002:4646: de la kun gzhir ming ma btags //
NK093(ge)002:4647: rnam rtog mtshan mar gnas pa la //
NK093(ge)002:4648: de la kun gzhir ming ma btags //
NK093(ge)002:4649: chos sku chu dang 'dra ba la //
NK093(ge)002:4650: bag chags sa 'dras bslad pa la //
NK093(ge)002:4651: kun gzhi zhes ni ming du btags //
NK093(ge)002:4652: zhes gsungs pas rang bzhin gyi gsang gnad ston pa'i
NK093(ge)002:4653: nges tshig 'di la brten nas mthar thug gi don
NK093(ge)002:4654: la gsang ba snying tig gi dgongs pa ltar kun
NK093(ge)002:4655: mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po dang dgongs pa'i bab so
NK093(ge)002:4661: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:4662: kun gzhi'i dmigs pa'i yul ji lta bu snyam pa la /
NK093(ge)002:4663: bag chags kyi kun gzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:4664: mig gi rnam par shes pas gzugs kho na la dmigs pa'am /
NK093(ge)002:4665: rna ba'i rnam par shes pas sgra kho na la
NK093(ge)002:4666: dmigs pa lta bu ma yin par dmigs pa dang
NK093(ge)002:4667: rnam pa yongsa su ma chad par don dang sems
NK093(ge)002:4668: can dang kun brtags pa'i bag chags thog ma nas
NK093(ge)002:4669: bsags pa'i dbang gis gang du smin kyang de'i phyi
