NK093(ge)002:10760: mi phyed 'byed pa yongs su med //
NK093(ge)002:10761: thams cad rang byung ye shes so //
NK093(ge)002:10762: zhes thun mong min pa'i gleng gzhi'i skabs su gsungs shing /
NK093(ge)002:10763: de nas thun mong gi gleng gzhi rgyas par bstan pa'i mjug tu /
NK093(ge)002:10764: mi 'byed rang bzhin rnam dag pa //
NK093(ge)002:10765: thams cad ngo bo dbyer med par //
NK093(ge)002:10766: brjod cing sgra tshig bde rig ste //
NK093(ge)002:10767: chos kyi sku yang rgyu med pa //
NK093(ge)002:10768: longs sku gdal ba kun khyab par //
NK093(ge)002:10769: sprul sku spros gzhi rdzogs pa las //
NK093(ge)002:10770: dbyer mi phyed pas snyoms zhugs te //
NK093(ge)002:10771: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK093(ge)002:10773: de ltar ngang gcig dbyer med do //
NK093(ge)002:10774: zhes gsungs pa ltar rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi phun
NK093(ge)002:10775: sum tshogs pa 'bras bu rdzogs pa chen po rang
NK093(ge)002:10777: sems phyogs rdzogs pa chen po'i man ngag gi skabs du mar /
NK093(ge)002:10778: 'bad rtsol med par lhun grub chen po'i dkyil 'khor /
NK093(ge)002:10779: lhag lus med par khams gsum dong sprugs kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK093(ge)002:10780: phyi nang med par ye shes rang snang gi dkyil 'khor /
NK093(ge)002:10781: spang blang med par rang grol chen po'i dkyil 'khor /
NK093(ge)002:10782: gtso 'khor med par mnyam pa nyid kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK093(ge)002:10783: mtha' dbus med pa gdal khyab chen po'i dkyil 'khor /
NK093(ge)002:10784: sgrib g.yogs med pa ye shes zang thal gyi dkyil
NK093(ge)002:10785: 'khor zhes pa la sogs pa ji skad gsungs pa
NK093(ge)002:10786: lta bu ste / de ltar khyab bdag ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:10787: nyid sku'i dkyil 'khor du thabs gcig par 'khod pa'i
NK093(ge)002:10788: skabs kyi dgongs pa rang snang ba'i don phul du
NK093(ge)002:10789: byung ba de nyid kho bo sdud pa po phyag
NK093(ge)002:10790: na rdo rje gsang ba'i mnga' bdag chen posa ji
NK093(ge)002:10791: lta ba bzhin du nor ba med cing phyina ci
NK093(ge)002:10792: ma loga para lang ka la sogs pa khyed rnams
NK093(ge)002:10793: la yongas su bgro bar bya'o zhes gsungs nas bshad
NK093(ge)002:10794: par zhal gyis bzhes pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:10796: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos nyid la //
NK093(ge)002:10797: nam mkha' lta bu'i dpe yis mtshon //
NK093(ge)002:10798: dmigs su med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK093(ge)002:10799: dmigs su med par mtshon te bstan //
NK093(ge)002:10800: tshig tu brjod du med pa la //
NK093(ge)002:10801: brjod du med pa'i tshig brjod de //
NK093(ge)002:10802: dmigs med don gyi ngo bor bstan //
NK093(ge)002:10804: 'o na 'dir ngo bo nyid sku kho na'i gleng
NK093(ge)002:10805: gzhi 'ong zhing ston pa dang smos pa ci dgos
NK093(ge)002:10806: gzhan yang yod dam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:10807: de kho na nyid snang ba dam pa dag pa
NK093(ge)002:10808: mthar phyin pa ni ngo bo nyid chos kyi sku
NK093(ge)002:10809: 'khor dang bcas pa kho na'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:10810: des na gnas lugs don gyi rdzogs chen ni ngo bo nyid sku'i bstan pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:10812: 'di yi don gyi rang bzhin las //
NK093(ge)002:10813: rtogs nas byin rlabs 'byung ba ni //
NK093(ge)002:10814: rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin ni //
NK093(ge)002:10815: sangs rgyas rdzogs la sems can rdzogs //
NK093(ge)002:10817: bde dang sdug bsngal gnyis med rdzogs //
NK093(ge)002:10818: theg pa rdzogs la chos nyid rdzogs //
NK093(ge)002:10819: yod pa'i mtha' rdzogs med mtha' rdzogs //
NK093(ge)002:10820: gcig rdzogs kun rdzogs thams cad rdzogs //
NK093(ge)002:10821: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mdo 'di ni //
NK093(ge)002:10822: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK093(ge)002:10823: sngar grub dgongs pa 'di yis grub //
NK093(ge)002:10824: da ltar bzhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK093(ge)002:10825: mi yengs dgongs lam 'di la gnas //
NK093(ge)002:10826: slad nas byon pa'i gdung 'tshob rnams //
NK093(ge)002:10827: dgongs pa'i lung bstan 'di yis mdzad //
NK093(ge)002:10828: gang su 'di la gnas pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:10829: rnal 'byor de ni chen po yin //
NK093(ge)002:10830: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar yin kyang /
NK093(ge)002:10831: mtshon byed sgra rgyud kyi rdzogs pa chen po'i ngos
NK093(ge)002:10832: nas chos sku'i bstan pa gsungs pa'ang gnad mchog tu
NK093(ge)002:10833: gsang ba la brten pa'i nges pa'i gsang sgo rmad
NK093(ge)002:10835: de lta bu ngo bo nyid sku'i gleng gzhi 'di ni /
NK093(ge)002:10836: rin po che rgyan las kyang /
NK093(ge)002:10837: ngo bo nyid skus chos sku la //
NK093(ge)002:10838: dus bzhi mnyam pa'i dus nyid la //
NK093(ge)002:10839: tha dad mi gnas pa yi gnas //
NK093(ge)002:10840: kun 'dus rang grol bstan pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:10841: ma bsgribs mthong thos rang shar ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:10843: chos longs sprul gsum gyi gleng gzhi ni theg pa spyi'i gzhung dang mthun la /
NK093(ge)002:10844: gsang ba'i gleng gzhi ni gdul bya chags can dang
NK093(ge)002:10845: mthun par don la drang ba yin pa'i phyir mthar
NK093(ge)002:10846: thug thun mong min pa ni ngo bo nyid sku'i
NK093(ge)002:10847: gleng gzhi 'di nyid kho na yin pas theg pa
NK093(ge)002:10848: kun gyi gnas dang phun sum tshogs pa kun gyi
NK093(ge)002:10851: dang po gsum ni spyi gzhung la //
NK093(ge)002:10852: gcig ni gdul bya mthun par drangs //
NK093(ge)002:10853: mthar thug tha ma thun mong min //
NK093(ge)002:10854: kun gyi gnas yin kun gyi gtso //
NK093(ge)002:10855: kun grol chen po'i rgyud las grags //
NK093(ge)002:10856: zhes gsungs pa ltar te rgyas par rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud sde rnams las shes par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:10858: don nges pa'i rtsa ba dngos bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:10859: de nyid rtogs ma rtogs kyi khyad par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:10860: ma rtogs pa rnams gtan la phabs te rang gzhung du bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:10861: de ltar ston pa'i bla ma dam pa ji ltar bkur tshul bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:10863: gang gis gsungs pa'i khungs bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:10864: ji ltar bstan pa'i ngo bo bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:10869: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:10870: de yang dper na me long g.yas g.yogs pa nyid dal gyis rim par phyi ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:10871: tsha mar dang nyi ma la gdung ste cig char
NK093(ge)002:10872: phyi ba gnyis dag pa'i tshe gsal ba dang gzugs
NK093(ge)002:10873: brnyan nges par 'char ba ltar 'dir me long cig
NK093(ge)002:10874: char du phyi ba'i dpes sems kyi chos nyid ji
NK093(ge)002:10875: bzhin par rtogs pa'i skad cig gis nyon yid ni
NK093(ge)002:10876: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa yin pas gzhi nas dag
NK093(ge)002:10877: ste tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag pa'i ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:10878: rgyas par bshad pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:10879: langa ka'i badga po zhes bos nas thog mar cig
NK093(ge)002:10880: char du rtogs pa'i thabs kyi khungs nye bar bstan
NK093(ge)002:10882: dper na muna khunga du gsera stor ba nyid snang
NK093(ge)002:10883: gsal sgrona mas rkyen las rnyed pa na byas pa
NK093(ge)002:10884: med par ranga snang ba ltar du 'khor ba'i srid
NK093(ge)002:10885: pa ma riga pa'i muna para rang rig byang chub
NK093(ge)002:10886: semas kyi gser stor ba nyid ranga snang zhing rnyed
NK093(ge)002:10887: par byed pa'i rkyen du gyur pa sgron ma lta
NK093(ge)002:10888: bu'i rgyud chen po rgyal ba thams cad kyi brjod
NK093(ge)002:10889: bya dang rjod byed kyi dgongas pa mtha' dag kuna
NK093(ge)002:10890: nasa 'dusa pa'i rtsa ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ma
NK093(ge)002:10891: lus pa'i dgongs pa'i zhe phugs dam par gyur ba'i
NK093(ge)002:10892: 'bras bur nges pa 'di ni snga rabas 'adsa pa'i
NK093(ge)002:10893: dus su byon pa'i phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba
NK093(ge)002:10894: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis kyang thugs kyi dgongas
NK093(ge)002:10895: pa la brgyud nas gsungas shing bka' stsal bar mdzad
NK093(ge)002:10904: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:10905: de yang ji skad du nges don mdo bcu las /
NK093(ge)002:10906: a nu yo ga'i a ti ni //
NK093(ge)002:10907: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid de //
NK093(ge)002:10908: rgyu rkyen bral ba'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK093(ge)002:10909: gsang ba'i ye shes rang byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:10910: zhes gsungs pa'i don gyi snying po de nyid /
NK093(ge)002:10911: a ti yo ga'i a nu ni //
NK093(ge)002:10912: rang bzhin ma bcos chos nyid de //
NK093(ge)002:10913: sgrib pa med pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK093(ge)002:10914: dbyings dang ye shes rang byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:10915: zhes gsungs pa'i ngo bo dang gnad mthun par /
NK093(ge)002:10916: a nu yo ga'i la bzlas ni //
NK093(ge)002:10918: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK093(ge)002:10919: chos nyid zab mo rang byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:10920: zhes gsungs pa'i chos nyid don gyi la bzla de nyid /
NK093(ge)002:10921: a ti yo ga'i la bzlas ni //
NK093(ge)002:10922: brjod du med pa'i chos nyid de //
NK093(ge)002:10923: sgro skur bral ba'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK093(ge)002:10924: bde ba chen por rang byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:10925: zhes gsungs pa ltar phyogs med bde ba chen po
NK093(ge)002:10926: rang rig rang grol gyi ngang du la bzlas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:10927: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ma 'dres mtha' bral
NK093(ge)002:10928: yongs rdzogs dbyer med phyogs bral gdal khyab chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:10929: dgongs don zab mo ji bzhin par ston te /
NK093(ge)002:10930: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i
NK093(ge)002:10931: dngos po gnyis kyi chosa thams cad kuna gyi gzhi
NK093(ge)002:10932: dang rtsa ba ni rang gi rig pa byang chub
NK093(ge)002:10933: kyi semas spros pa dang bral ba'i rnam shes dgu
NK093(ge)002:10934: pa 'di nyid kho na la 'dusa shing rdzogs pa
NK093(ge)002:10935: yin pas kun gzhi byang chub sems kyi rang rtsal
NK093(ge)002:10936: semas nyida tshogs brgyad kyi dngos por gyur pa rnams
NK093(ge)002:10937: skabs lnga'am bcur gansa gyur te ye nas ye shesa
NK093(ge)002:10938: lngar gnas pa nyid rig pa la shar zhing snang
NK093(ge)002:10939: ba'i bla dwags su gnas gyur zhes brjod pa ste
NK093(ge)002:10940: / rtogs pa de nyid kyi dona la rang gi
NK093(ge)002:10941: blo yid kyi bya bsam dang rtsol ba med par
NK093(ge)002:10942: nges para bazhaga pasa ma bcos rang grol gyi ngang
NK093(ge)002:10943: la rang bab tu 'dug cing g.yo ba med par
NK093(ge)002:10944: / gnas na / semas nyid ye shes lngar gansa
NK093(ge)002:10945: gyur pa yang de nyid yina pas de kho na
NK093(ge)002:10947: de lta bu'i ye shes lnga yang rig pa gcig
NK093(ge)002:10948: dang du ma bral ba'i chos nyid byang chub kyi
NK093(ge)002:10949: sems rtogs pa de la mtshan nyid rnam lnga ma
NK093(ge)002:10950: 'gags par gsal ba'i tshul gyis yongs su rdzogas pa
NK093(ge)002:10951: yin pasa na ye shes lnga yanga ngo bo tha
NK093(ge)002:10952: dad med par rang rig pa rang byung gi ye
NK093(ge)002:10953: shes gcig pu nyid du 'dus shing rim pa min
NK093(ge)002:10954: par cig char du rdzogs pa yina te /
NK093(ge)002:10956: mi gnas thugs la phyi nang med //
NK093(ge)002:10957: stong pa'i ye shes dngos po med //
NK093(ge)002:10958: me long lta bu'i ye shes ni //
NK093(ge)002:10959: shes bya kun la mngon phyogs med //
NK093(ge)002:10960: mnyam nyid ye shes che chung med //
NK093(ge)002:10961: so sor rtog pa ma 'dres gsal //
NK093(ge)002:10962: bya ba nan tan thugs rje dngos //
NK093(ge)002:10963: rang byung ye shes nyag gcig la //
NK093(ge)002:10964: yon tan cha res du mar bgrangs //
NK093(ge)002:10966: des na rang rig pa'i semas kyi chos nyid ma
NK093(ge)002:10967: bcos ma bslad pa'i ji bzhina pa de kho na
NK093(ge)002:10968: ba de nyid cir yang ma mthong ba'i tshul gyis
NK093(ge)002:10969: yang dag par rtogsa shing rig pa na /
NK093(ge)002:10970: de ltar rtogs pa'i yon tan gyis sems 'phral du
NK093(ge)002:10971: sangs rgyas min pa las yin par bzos ma bsgyur
NK093(ge)002:10972: bar ye nas 'khrul pa med par sangsa rgyas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:10973: don rgyu rkyen gyis bslad pa med par ma nora
NK093(ge)002:10974: ma bcosa para mngon du gyur pa yin pas de
NK093(ge)002:10975: las gzhan du bgrod pa med pa'i phyir sems nyid
NK093(ge)002:10976: gadla ba chen pos chos kun la khyab pas kun
NK093(ge)002:10977: tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i sa mchog de
NK093(ge)002:10978: nyid ched du ma mnan par nona pa yin te
NK093(ge)002:10980: rang gsal nyag gcig dri ma med //
NK093(ge)002:10981: rtsol med nam mkha' bzhin du gnas //
NK093(ge)002:10982: sangs rgyas sems can kun la khyab //
NK093(ge)002:10983: de rnyed rtogs pas 'bras bu'i sa //
NK093(ge)002:10985: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK093(ge)002:10986: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pas //
NK093(ge)002:10987: kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa //
NK093(ge)002:10988: ma sbyangs sems nyid sa dag la //
NK093(ge)002:10989: sa rnams ma lus thams cad 'dus //
NK093(ge)002:10991: kun byed rgyal po'i spyi'i bshad rgyud sde bzhi'i ya
NK093(ge)002:10992: gyal nam mkha' dang mnyam pa yi ge med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:10993: rgyud las / khyab gdal don 'di sus rtogs pa //
NK093(ge)002:10994: rgyal sras bzhin du dbul ba sangs //
NK093(ge)002:10996: mtshan ma ma spangs rang sar grol //
NK093(ge)002:10997: 'khor ba ma bkag gnas su dag /
NK093(ge)002:10998: 'khrul pa ma bsal rtsad nas chod //
NK093(ge)002:10999: dug lnga ma bsgyur chos nyid klong //
NK093(ge)002:11000: rtsol sgrub med par ye sangs rgyas //
NK093(ge)002:11001: yin pa'i don la yin par shes //
NK093(ge)002:11002: dper na gser la gser mthong bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:11003: yid kyi rnam rtog zad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11004: nam mkha' chen po'i klong chen bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:11005: khyab gdal mi 'gyur kun rdzogs grol //
NK093(ge)002:11006: nyi ma sprin med snying po bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:11007: dus gsum sgrib med de bzhin nyid //
NK093(ge)002:11008: brgya byin gtsug gi nor bu bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:11010: ma gi ta yi sman bzhin du //
NK093(ge)002:11011: gang la reg pa sman du 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:11012: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK093(ge)002:11013: de ltar sems nyid ma nor bar rtogs pa la
NK093(ge)002:11014: thams cad rdzogs para rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa
NK093(ge)002:11015: 'dusa pa'i ston pa khyab bdag dam pasa bka' stsal
NK093(ge)002:11016: bar mdzad de nges par gsungas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11017: zhes gsang bdag chen pos lo rgyus su brjod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11019: lta bas thag bcad par gdams pa /
NK093(ge)002:11020: rtogs nas ci yang mi 'geg pa spyad cing blo bzhag thabs bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:11021: bzhag pa bzhin nyams su blang bas kun gyi sgo
NK093(ge)002:11022: dang mthun par dam pa'i dgongs pa myong bar bstan
NK093(ge)002:11023: pa / de ltar dgongs pa rnyed pas pha rol phyin pa drug kyang rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:11024: ma bcos mnyam pa'i ngang las nyams pa'i skyon byung na bcos thabs bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:11025: ting 'dzin ma yengs pa'i ngo bo la rnal 'byor gsum gyi don kun rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:11026: don de shes shing goms pa nyid rgyal ba'i dgongs spyod mthar thug tu nges par gdams pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11031: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11032: rtogs pa'i yon tan de lta bu dang ldan pas
NK093(ge)002:11033: na rjes su 'jug pa po rnams kyis dang por
NK093(ge)002:11034: lta bas thag bcad par gces te /
NK093(ge)002:11035: de'i tshul ni chos nyid ji bzhin pa ji lta
NK093(ge)002:11036: bar shes shing thag chod pa'i gansa skabs kyi dus
NK093(ge)002:11038: de lta bu'i rang rig pa la nyan rang byang
NK093(ge)002:11039: sems ltar yod med kyi mtha'i lta ba rjes bcad
NK093(ge)002:11040: pa dang / gsang sngags spyi'i dgongs pa ltar mathara
NK093(ge)002:11041: thug gi bsgrub bya zab mo gtan la dbab pa
NK093(ge)002:11042: pa dang / dang / tshogs brgyad semas kyi rang
NK093(ge)002:11043: bzhin rnal ma'i dbyings kyi ngo bo chos nyid de
NK093(ge)002:11044: bzhina nyid rang byung ba'i gnas lugs ji ltar yina
NK093(ge)002:11045: pa dang / dang / pa dang / sems nyid
NK093(ge)002:11046: de la yang sems tsam skad cig ma de yi
NK093(ge)002:11047: rgyun yoda med thag bcad de mtshan ma'i tshogs brgyad
NK093(ge)002:11048: dang gsang ba'i dbyings kyi rang bzhin ma 'dres yongs
NK093(ge)002:11049: rdzogs su rtogs pa'i ye shes dam par nges pa
NK093(ge)002:11050: pa dang / dang / pa dang / rnyed para
NK093(ge)002:11051: bya'o // de la'ang gal po'am gtar ka gegs sel
NK093(ge)002:11052: pa dang / dang / pa dang / rnyed para
NK093(ge)002:11053: bya'o // lta bur / gal te lta sgom gyi
NK093(ge)002:11054: ngo bo sems ma bcos pa'i de bzhina nyid la
NK093(ge)002:11055: skabs ganga 'dira tshul ji ltar lta bar bya zhe
NK093(ge)002:11056: pa dang / dang / pa dang / rnyed para
NK093(ge)002:11057: bya'o // lta bur / na / 'di ltar rtsad
NK093(ge)002:11059: sems kyi rang bzhin chos nyid ji bzhin pa de
NK093(ge)002:11060: nyid 'di ltar yong de mngon sum du snang ba
NK093(ge)002:11061: zhig yina nam / gal te med cing mi snang ba zhig tu gyur tam /
NK093(ge)002:11062: 'on te ranga snang ba'i sems nyid ye nas sangsa rgyas pa zhig yina nama /
NK093(ge)002:11063: yang na sangsa rgyas mina par sems can 'ab'a zhig
NK093(ge)002:11064: tu gyur pa zhig yin zhes spros pa gcod pa
NK093(ge)002:11066: sems kyi de kho na nyid 'di lasa sangsa rgyas
NK093(ge)002:11067: chos kyi sku zhes bya ba de nyid gazhana logs
NK093(ge)002:11069: 'on te gzhan na med par 'di nyid kho na yin nam /
NK093(ge)002:11070: zhes tshul 'di ltar rtsad bcad la /
NK093(ge)002:11071: lta ba ji ltar yin pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11072: sgom pas don ji ltar gyur pa'i blo yi nges pa gang la gazhaga pa rnams /
NK093(ge)002:11073: yin don legs par rtogs pa dang snang spyod ye
NK093(ge)002:11074: shes su shar ba'i phyir dang por lhag mthong gi
NK093(ge)002:11075: grosa kyis thag choda para bya ba kho na gal
NK093(ge)002:11076: che ste / kun 'dus rig pa las /
NK093(ge)002:11077: klong yangs nam mkha'i snying po la //
NK093(ge)002:11078: sprin med nyi ma 'bum gyis brdal //
NK093(ge)002:11079: cing snang ci yang ma yin pa //
NK093(ge)002:11080: mi skye mi 'gag ngo bo las //
NK093(ge)002:11081: ji ltar bltas rgu der snang ba //
NK093(ge)002:11082: theg mchog spyi rgya rlabs kyis bcad //
NK093(ge)002:11083: de yang lta ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK093(ge)002:11084: bdag nyid chen po'i rnal 'byor dang //
NK093(ge)002:11085: lhun gyis grub dang klong yangs chub //
NK093(ge)002:11086: gsum rdzogs rang byung gdal ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:11089: kye sems kyi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11090: grub dang ma grub gnyis su lung mi ston //
NK093(ge)002:11091: bde dang sdug bsngal gnyis su rtog mi byed //
NK093(ge)002:11092: 'khor dang mya ngan 'das par re dogs bral //
NK093(ge)002:11093: lhun grub sems kyi rang bzhin cir snang bas //
NK093(ge)002:11094: ma byung stong pa'i don du smra mi byed //
NK093(ge)002:11095: gzhi rtsa snying po rtog dpyod las 'das pas //
NK093(ge)002:11096: grub cing brtan pa'i phyogs su zhes mi byed //
NK093(ge)002:11097: ces gsungs pa ltar ji bzhin pa'i don zab mo
NK093(ge)002:11098: la nges pa legs par rnyed pa'i ched du bshad
NK093(ge)002:11099: pa 'di dag la brtags pa rgyas par bya ste
NK093(ge)002:11100: zhib tu 'phrul gyi me long gi gdams pa bzhin
NK093(ge)002:11105: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11106: lta bas 'di ltar ngesa pa rnyed de gtan la
NK093(ge)002:11107: phebs nasa sgom pas de ltar gdengs dang ldan te
NK093(ge)002:11108: klung du gyur na yanga gzhan gyi don du 'dus
NK093(ge)002:11109: byas kyi dge rtsa'am glo bura gyi las lam dkar
NK093(ge)002:11110: po'i phyogs rnams mi 'gega pa'am mi spang bar nus
NK093(ge)002:11111: tshad thams cad de bzhina du spyad par bya ste
NK093(ge)002:11112: / de nyid spang bya min pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11113: chos nyid de las gzhan pa'ang ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:11114: des na ngang gi rang bzhin ma rtogs par zhen
NK093(ge)002:11115: rtsol gyis byas na chu sas rnyogs pa dang 'dra
NK093(ge)002:11116: yang ngang las mi 'da' ba'i rang bzhin du spyad
NK093(ge)002:11117: na ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su 'gyur ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:11118: de ltar rtogs te thag chod pa des na chos
NK093(ge)002:11119: kuna gyi ranga bzhina la spang blang gang yang med
NK093(ge)002:11120: pa dang thams cad dgongs pa de nyid du gsal
NK093(ge)002:11121: bar 'dus pa yin pas bkol spang gi spros mtha'
NK093(ge)002:11123: de ltar rtogs nas nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK093(ge)002:11124: blangs pa'i tshe thog mar blo bzhag pa'i thabs 'chad
NK093(ge)002:11125: de / snyegs pa'i rtogs pa de dang don gyi
NK093(ge)002:11126: gzhi la ma nor bar rjes su 'jog pa de
NK093(ge)002:11127: de / ni / chos nyid mnyam pa nyid ji
NK093(ge)002:11128: bzhin par rtogs pas blos bsam bya med cing sgom
NK093(ge)002:11129: pas dmigas su meda pa'i ngang dera yid la bya
NK093(ge)002:11130: ba dang gtong 'dzin med de 'du shes gang du'ang
NK093(ge)002:11131: ma zhugs par gyin 'da' bar bzhag pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:11132: bsam pa gang du'ang ma g.yos pas bzhag pa'i ming thob pas thabs dam pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:11134: ji bzhin rtsol bral bde ba chen po la //
NK093(ge)002:11135: sgo gsum mi rtsol bcos shing dmigs mi byed //
NK093(ge)002:11136: yid la mi byed mtshan ma'i rjes mi 'brangs //
NK093(ge)002:11137: rang byung ye shes bde ba'i don la bzhag /
NK093(ge)002:11138: 'di ni rang byung 'od gsal dgongs pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:11139: kun byed rgyal po'i dgongs pa'i phrin las so //
NK093(ge)002:11142: tshe skabs kyi don ni de lta bur rig pa
NK093(ge)002:11143: mi g.yo ba chen por gnas pa la tha snyad
NK093(ge)002:11144: ci snang ji srid kyi chos so cog mtha' dag
NK093(ge)002:11145: thams cad matshana nyid dang bral ba'i chos kyi dbyings
NK093(ge)002:11146: su gsal ba'i ngang spros pa med pa dera dgongs
NK093(ge)002:11147: pa lhun gyis grub par gcig tu grol basa rang
NK093(ge)002:11148: gi ngo bo rgyu las skye ba dang rkyen gyis
NK093(ge)002:11149: 'agga pa med par de kho na nyida du ye
NK093(ge)002:11150: nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:11152: ji ltar snang grags chos rnams thams cad la //
NK093(ge)002:11153: snying po rtogs goms don nyid gcig las med //
NK093(ge)002:11154: snying po mngon du phyung nas gang bstan pa //
NK093(ge)002:11155: rang bzhin skye ba med pa'i don du rtogs //
NK093(ge)002:11156: ma yengs re dogs chad pa'i dgongs pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:11162: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11163: de lta bu'i dgongs pa dam pa de nyid la
NK093(ge)002:11164: 'dzin pa'i rnam pa gang yang med cing yengs bya
NK093(ge)002:11165: yengs byed dang bral te kun tu ma yengas par
NK093(ge)002:11166: gyur pasa na gzhan du ma brtsala na yanga don
NK093(ge)002:11167: gyi ngo bo mtha' bral kun rdzogs su gsal ba
NK093(ge)002:11168: tsam nyid bgrod pa'i gnas mchog mthar thug pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:11169: la gnas pa yin pas rdzogas pa thams cad kyi
NK093(ge)002:11170: spyir ram spyi bor chibas pa'i sa mchog dam pa
NK093(ge)002:11171: nyid gsar du mnan pa ma yin par ye nasa
NK093(ge)002:11172: nona pa nyid mngon du snang ba yin pas da
NK093(ge)002:11173: lta nyid nas 'bras bur mngon byang chub pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:11175: klong yangs 'ub chub gdal khyab sa //
NK093(ge)002:11176: spyir chibs sa bcu 'dus pa'i klong //
NK093(ge)002:11177: gcig las bye brag phye ba'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11178: sa bcu snang ba yon tan yin //
NK093(ge)002:11181: dgos ni khams gsum sems can thams cad kun //
NK093(ge)002:11182: rang sems de bzhin nyid de mthong gyur na //
NK093(ge)002:11183: sangs rgyas tshig gi sa la mi gnas te /
NK093(ge)002:11184: da lta nyid nas shin tu rnal 'byor thob //
NK093(ge)002:11186: de ltar chos nyid byang chub kyi sems de nyid
NK093(ge)002:11187: ji bzhin du rtogs nas blos bsam du med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11188: bsam gtan la yun ring du gnas pas mjug drag
NK093(ge)002:11189: dal gyi goms pa chu dang mtsho gting gi dpes
NK093(ge)002:11190: nyamsa tha ma dang ldan zhing /
NK093(ge)002:11191: drod mchog dam pa thog tu phebs te rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11192: nyamsa su sgrib byed ma dmigs par rang gasla bar
NK093(ge)002:11193: 'gyur la / de ltar na yanga mi mthun pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:11194: gsang mchog theg pa chen po ni chos kun gyi
NK093(ge)002:11195: bdag nyid yin pas 'di nyid la bslab pas snang
NK093(ge)002:11196: stong dbyer med gsum dang ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum
NK093(ge)002:11197: sogs theg pa'i sgo rnams dang mi 'agla zhing mthun
NK093(ge)002:11198: par bstana pa'i phyir ram ched du /
NK093(ge)002:11199: dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med par rtogs pa'i phyogs bral
NK093(ge)002:11200: lhun grub gsum gyi rig pa la stong chen de
NK093(ge)002:11201: bzhin nyid dang kun tu snang ba dang rgyu'i ting
NK093(ge)002:11202: nge 'dzina gsum yang rdzogs par ldana te yongs su
NK093(ge)002:11203: grol bas / rang bzhin stong pa'am de bzhin nyid kyis skye bor gola ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:11204: snang ba dang rgyus byang sems su gol ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:11205: dbyer med dang snying rjes nyan rang du gol ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:11206: gsum char ngang la rdzogs pas sngags phyi nang gi
NK093(ge)002:11207: rtogs pa phyogs ris su gol ba'i sgo rnams bakaga
NK093(ge)002:11208: nasa dgongs pa yongs rdzogs lhun grub chen por gnas
NK093(ge)002:11209: pa yin te / ji bzhin pa nyid ma bslad
NK093(ge)002:11210: par gsal ba ni ril gyi 'byung gnas su gyur
NK093(ge)002:11211: pa yin te / pa'i phyir ro // de lta
NK093(ge)002:11212: bas na dgongs pa 'di la mtha' rnams ma bsal
NK093(ge)002:11213: bral bas gol sgrib tu ltung ba'i gnas rnams ma
NK093(ge)002:11214: spangs la mi 'byung bar yang dag par shes pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11216: rtogs pa de nyid la mtshan ma'i nyams drod brtag tu med na yang /
NK093(ge)002:11217: snga ma'i dgos pa dang bstun te nyams drod dang
NK093(ge)002:11218: nyams drod chena po'i dbye bas phyi nang gsang ba'i
NK093(ge)002:11219: drod mchog g.yo thob brtan pa gsum gyis rgyal ba
NK093(ge)002:11220: rnam 'dren dama pa'i dgongas pa ji lta ba bzhin
NK093(ge)002:11221: du nyams su myong nas ro bstar bar 'gyur ro
NK093(ge)002:11226: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11227: de ltar ji lta ba nyid kyi ro bstar ba'i
NK093(ge)002:11228: tshul des na dgongs pa'i tinga nge 'dzina rnam pa
NK093(ge)002:11229: gsuma gyi nyamsa dus gcig la rnyed pa'i phyir na
NK093(ge)002:11230: rtogs pa de nyid mthar phyin pasa rgyal ba'i yon
NK093(ge)002:11231: tan 'bras bu sku gsum dang rgyu pha rola tu
NK093(ge)002:11232: phyina pa drug po rnams kyang ranga bzhina gyis yongs
NK093(ge)002:11233: su rdzogsa par ci ste bar mi chud de /
NK093(ge)002:11234: dper na nyi ma'i chos nyid gsal ba dang mtshungs par rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK093(ge)002:11235: chos nyid kyi rigs pas shin tu gsal lo //
NK093(ge)002:11237: dgongs pa dang po ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK093(ge)002:11238: bar ma ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11239: tha ma ni sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK093(ge)002:11240: de lta bu la zin chags med par gdal bas sbyin pa'i phar phyin dang /
NK093(ge)002:11241: dri ma gnyis dang bral ba'i don las mi 'da' bas tshul khrims dang /
NK093(ge)002:11242: mnyam pa'i don chen po gang la'ang nyam mi nga zhing mi skrag pas bzod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11243: cir yang mi g.yo bas bsam gtan dang /
NK093(ge)002:11244: dus gsum du yengs bral med pas brtson 'grus dang /
NK093(ge)002:11245: ji bzhin par rig pa rang gsal bas shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11250: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11251: semas kyi chos nyid rtog pas ma bcos pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK093(ge)002:11253: cho 'phrul 'byung ba dang thog ma dang mtha' dbus
NK093(ge)002:11254: bral ba'i chos gsum gyi nam mkha'i dbyings dang mtshungs
NK093(ge)002:11255: pa nyid ni byas pa med par rang rig pa
NK093(ge)002:11256: lhun gyis grub pa'i nganga ste /
NK093(ge)002:11257: don de la de nyid du'ang ma bsam pa ni ngang gnas su bazhaga pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:11259: kye sems dpa' rdo rje ji bzhin nyid sgoms shig /ma bcos ji bzhin nyid la 'jug pa la /
NK093(ge)002:11260: tshad ma mi dgos gnyen pos bcos mi dgos //
NK093(ge)002:11261: rtogs pa'i don la ma bcos de bzhin zhog /ces so //
NK093(ge)002:11262: 'on kyang de ltar sgom pa de yi tshe na
NK093(ge)002:11263: yang drana zhing rtog pa'i rnam pa phra rags ci
NK093(ge)002:11264: zhig byung ste 'phro bar snang na yanga /
NK093(ge)002:11266: ye shes kyi rol par shes nas de bzhina nyid
NK093(ge)002:11267: las ma g.yosa pa'i ngang la bsam pa gang du'ang
NK093(ge)002:11268: 'byung 'jug med par gdeng du chud pa nyid kyis
NK093(ge)002:11269: dran rtog thams cad la bzlas te lta bas thag
NK093(ge)002:11270: bacada pasa dran rtog gi rgyu ba gang yang ma
NK093(ge)002:11271: dmigs te blos ched du ma gtad par rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11272: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bor nganga gisa grol bas
NK093(ge)002:11273: rgyu rkyen nam byed pa pos ma bcosa par rang
NK093(ge)002:11274: bzhin yongsa kyis 'oda gasla ba nyid du ma bkag
NK093(ge)002:11275: la mi ldan par yongs su dag pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:11276: gasnga ba sngags kyi ston mchog rgyal ba'i dgongs pa
NK093(ge)002:11277: kun nas 'dusa shing rdzogs pa rnams kyis sems nyid
NK093(ge)002:11278: don gyi ngo bo ma nor ba yina para ched
NK093(ge)002:11279: du basngagas te yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung gnas
NK093(ge)002:11280: nyid du nges par bstan nas che ba brjod pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11281: tshul gyis bka' stsal pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:11283: ji bzhin ma bcos rgyal ba'i dgongs pa la //
NK093(ge)002:11284: sems dang sems las byung ba ci skyes kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11285: de nyid skye med nyid du gnas shes na //
NK093(ge)002:11286: bya rtsol mtshon ma'i 'du shes kun dang bral //
NK093(ge)002:11287: kye sems dpa' rdo rje ji bzhin nyid sgoms shig /rtogs pa rang sar grol ba'i lta ba la //
NK093(ge)002:11288: ma yengs rang bzhin bzhag pas bya btsal med //
NK093(ge)002:11289: kun kyang rang byung rang sar grol ba yin //
NK093(ge)002:11291: rang byung snying po mchog gi dkyil 'khor la //
NK093(ge)002:11292: sgo gsum lhug pas ji bzhin ngang bzhag na //
NK093(ge)002:11293: kun byed nga yi dgongs par gnas pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:11294: snga rabs 'das pa'i kun byed rgyal pos kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11295: dgongs pa rnal du bzhag pas don rdzogs la //
NK093(ge)002:11296: ma byon dus kyi kun byed rgyal pos kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11297: ma bcos rnal du bzhag pas don rdzogs 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:11298: da ltar bzhugs pa'i kun byed rgyal pos kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11299: dgongs pa rnal du bzhag ste gnas pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:11301: kye ston pa kun byed nga yi ye shes nyid //
NK093(ge)002:11302: bgrang du med la bgrang na mtha' las 'das //
NK093(ge)002:11303: che ba re la ye shes grangs bstan pas //
NK093(ge)002:11304: brjod pas de dag mi rdzogs lung bstan to //
NK093(ge)002:11305: kye kun byed rgyal po nga yi ye shes ni //
NK093(ge)002:11306: rnam par mi rtog spros pa kun dang bral //
NK093(ge)002:11307: rab zhi gdul med mkha' ltar gnas pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:11308: skye ba med pa zhes su bstan pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:11309: rang byung ye shes gcig las ma g.yos kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11310: rnam pa'i khyad par ma bcos so sor gsal //
NK093(ge)002:11311: de ltar gang gis rig cing rtogs pa nyid //
NK093(ge)002:11312: kun byed rgyal po'i sras su lung bstan to //
NK093(ge)002:11313: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK093(ge)002:11317: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11318: de yang rtogs pa'i ngo bo byang chub sems kyi
NK093(ge)002:11319: ngang las gzhan pa'i yul du gyur pa'i chos gang
NK093(ge)002:11320: yang ma dmigs pas phyogs bral ba bde ba chen
NK093(ge)002:11321: po'i don las ma yengas par dang por skye ba
NK093(ge)002:11322: dang tha ma 'agga pa meda pa'i chos nyid rang
NK093(ge)002:11323: gsal ba ni rang byung rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzina
NK093(ge)002:11325: rang rig pa mnyam pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas so //
NK093(ge)002:11328: dmigs pa'i mtha' las 'das pas na //
NK093(ge)002:11329: mi gnas chos sku'i ngo bo nyid //
NK093(ge)002:11330: rgyu rkyen med par rang byung bas //
NK093(ge)002:11331: rang byung ye shes nam mkha' che //
NK093(ge)002:11332: thams cad de ru 'dus pas na //
NK093(ge)002:11333: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs theg pa'i rgyan //
NK093(ge)002:11335: rang rig gdal khyab chen po rtogs nas ngang la gnas pa'i rang bzhin la /
NK093(ge)002:11341: bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor gsuma gyi dona yang
NK093(ge)002:11342: dus gcig tu dbyer med par de yi skabsa na
NK093(ge)002:11343: rig pa la ma 'dres yongs su rdzogas pa yin
NK093(ge)002:11344: no // bdun pa la lnga ste /
NK093(ge)002:11345: ma nor bar shes dgos par gdams pa /
NK093(ge)002:11346: de ltar rtogs pa'i yon tan bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:11347: yengs med du bsgom dgos par gdams pa /
NK093(ge)002:11348: de ltar bsgom pa'i yon tan bstan pa //
NK093(ge)002:11349: tshul de nyid thun mong ma yin pa'i dgongs spyod du bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11354: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11355: dgongs pa mchog gi ting nge 'dzin gyi che ba'i
NK093(ge)002:11356: yon tan la snyegs pa desa na gtan tshigs lta
NK093(ge)002:11358: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi bshesa gnyena ston mchog
NK093(ge)002:11359: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa'i gsang ba'i dbyings kyi
NK093(ge)002:11360: dgongas pa zab mo gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK093(ge)002:11361: nas rig 'dzin dra ma la brgyud pa'i rgyud 'di'i
NK093(ge)002:11362: don ji bzhin du rtogs nasa 'bras bu dama pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11363: dona du nges pa ni dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer
NK093(ge)002:11364: med pa'i rang rig lhun mnyam chen po semas nyida
NK093(ge)002:11365: byang chub kyi sems su ye sangs rgyas pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:11366: du yang dag par shesa para bya ste /
NK093(ge)002:11367: de ltar mthar thug don gyi ngo bo ji bzhin par shes nas bsgom pa gces par bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11372: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11374: rgyud 'di'i don ston pa de nyid rgyal mchog rdo rje semas dapa'a nyid yina te /
NK093(ge)002:11375: 'dul ba'i dbang gis mtshan so sor grags pa'ang ngo
NK093(ge)002:11376: bo la bye brag med pasa na dam pa ganga
NK093(ge)002:11377: zhig gis rgyud kyi dgongs pa ji bzhin pa rdo
NK093(ge)002:11378: rje lta bu'i chos lnga dang ldan pa rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:11379: 'od gsal mtha' bral byang chub sems kyi chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:11380: 'di yi bden pa mthonga na bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK093(ge)002:11381: rdo rje sems dpa' de yi zhal nges par mthonga
NK093(ge)002:11384: ting 'dzin rab la lung bstan pa //
NK093(ge)002:11385: gser ri g.yu yis brgyan pa 'dra //
NK093(ge)002:11386: ye shes gsal la gdugs brdal 'dra //
NK093(ge)002:11387: rdo rje sems dpar de ma thag /sangs rgyas kun gyi snying por 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:11388: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po yin //
NK093(ge)002:11390: nam mkha' che rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK093(ge)002:11391: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK093(ge)002:11392: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK093(ge)002:11393: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11394: ma skyes ma 'gags cir mi dgongs //
NK093(ge)002:11395: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK093(ge)002:11396: dam pa 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NK093(ge)002:11397: 'das dang da ltar byung ba kun //
NK093(ge)002:11398: 'di nyid brnyes nas lhun gyis grub //
NK093(ge)002:11400: rtogs pa'i yon tan ji lta bu snyam pa la /
NK093(ge)002:11401: de ltar nges par mthonga nas don gyi gnad zab
NK093(ge)002:11402: mo khong du chud pa'i dus de nyid phana chad
NK093(ge)002:11403: 'khor bar ltung ba med pa dang rgyal ba dama
NK093(ge)002:11404: pa nyid dang spyod yul gcig pa yina pasa sangs
NK093(ge)002:11405: rgyas nyid de / des na rdo rje sems dpa'
NK093(ge)002:11406: rgyal ba kun gyi ston pa 'gro ba yongs kyi
NK093(ge)002:11407: bshesa gnyena dam pa de nyid yina para rdo rje
NK093(ge)002:11408: gsang ba'i rgyud las gragsa pa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:11410: don 'di tshig tu ma khyer bar //
NK093(ge)002:11411: gnad kyi gdeng du chud pa gang //
NK093(ge)002:11412: dman pa'i lus la dam pa'i sems //
NK093(ge)002:11413: dus gsum sangs rgyas sras gcig po //
NK093(ge)002:11414: 'jig rten dregs pas bcings pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:11415: lha srin sde brgyad thams cad kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11416: jo bo'i tshul du khur bar byed //
NK093(ge)002:11417: sangs rgyas kun dang dgongs pa mnyam //
NK093(ge)002:11418: nam mkha' nyid la nam mkha' spyod //
NK093(ge)002:11421: lus ni gang zag 'jig rten yang //
NK093(ge)002:11422: sems dgongs rdzogs chen sangs rgyas yin //
NK093(ge)002:11423: 'di yis sems can don byas kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11424: don la nor ba nges mi 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:11425: yin pa dag la nor ba med //
NK093(ge)002:11426: nges pa dag la the tshom med //
NK093(ge)002:11427: rdzogs pa chen po'i lung 'di la //
NK093(ge)002:11428: yod med tshig dang ma nges pa'i //
NK093(ge)002:11429: don la 'da' ba mi mnga' bas //
NK093(ge)002:11430: brjod pa'i tshig las 'da' mi mnga' //zhes so //
NK093(ge)002:11435: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11436: de lta'i rnal ma ma bcos pa'i dona mthonga zhing
NK093(ge)002:11437: rtogs pa'i skyes bu dam pa blo yang rab tu
NK093(ge)002:11438: gyur pa ganga dang gang zhig gisa /
NK093(ge)002:11439: bya ba thams cad btang nas ci la'ang mi lta
NK093(ge)002:11440: bar chos nyid de kho na la zhena te bsgom
NK093(ge)002:11441: para bya'o // de ltar goms pa desa ting nge
NK093(ge)002:11442: 'dzin las su rung bar gyur na bya ba thams
NK093(ge)002:11443: cad ma bsgrub par byas zina te mthar phyin cing
NK093(ge)002:11444: don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang la 'bad rtsol
NK093(ge)002:11445: med par rang snang rig pa'i ngo bo dera ngesa
NK093(ge)002:11446: te mi 'gyur bar gnas na rgyu rkyen med pas
NK093(ge)002:11447: ranga byung rang gsal bas ye shesa chen po nyid
NK093(ge)002:11448: bying rmugs rgod 'thor gyi skyon rnams yongas su dag
NK093(ge)002:11449: cing mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i ngo bo snang
NK093(ge)002:11450: ba'am mngon du gyur pa zhes bya ba yin par
NK093(ge)002:11451: bka' zab mo dag las 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:11452: de la bying ba ni ye mi gsal ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:11453: rmugs pa ni rig pa ma stor yang mi gsal ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:11454: rgod pa ni ye g.yo ba /
NK093(ge)002:11455: 'thor ba ni cung zad gsal yang 'thor nas bya bas khrid pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:11457: bying bas rig pa gsal ma thon //
NK093(ge)002:11458: rmugs pas shes bya'i don ma gsal //
NK093(ge)002:11459: shin tu bying na dran pa 'gag /rab tu rmugs na 'du shes spangs //
NK093(ge)002:11460: rgod pa rig pa yul la 'phro //
NK093(ge)002:11461: g.yeng ba bya ba'i las kyis khrid //
NK093(ge)002:11462: rab tu rgod na yid la byed //
NK093(ge)002:11463: shin tu g.yengs na mtshan mar smin //
NK093(ge)002:11469: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11470: de lta bu'i spyod yul la gdeng du chud cing
NK093(ge)002:11471: goms pa'i stobs dang ldan pa desa na chos can
NK093(ge)002:11472: gyi rtog pa dang spyod pa zina chagas ci byas
NK093(ge)002:11473: ci spyad de thogs shing zhen pa dang bde ba
NK093(ge)002:11474: dang sdug bsngal ci zhig ltar byung yanga /
NK093(ge)002:11475: de nyid mi 'gog par thabs spyod pa ma 'gags pa'i bde ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:11476: de la ngo bo ye nas ma dmigs pa yin
NK093(ge)002:11477: pa'i don gsal bas snang ba ma 'gags pa bsod
NK093(ge)002:11478: nams kyi tshogs dang rang bzhin med pa ye shes
NK093(ge)002:11479: kyi tshogs te tshogas gnyis ched du brtsal bas ma
NK093(ge)002:11480: basgas kyang rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par rdzogas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11481: ngo bo yin para dama bca' ba ste zhe bas
NK093(ge)002:11482: 'dod par bya'o // de ltar bsgom pa'i yon tan ci lta bu zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:11483: mos pa las byung ba'i mi dmigs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11484: shin tu mi dmigs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11485: rjes su mi dmigs pa'i rim pa mthar phyin nas
NK093(ge)002:11486: cir yang mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzina dam pa
NK093(ge)002:11487: ji ltar yang mi g.yo bar gsal ba la /
NK093(ge)002:11488: de kho na nyid thob par rtog pa'i matshana ma
NK093(ge)002:11489: yang rnam par daga cing yang dag par bral ba'i
NK093(ge)002:11490: rig pa ni shes rab kyi dbang po dang ye
NK093(ge)002:11491: shes kyi spyan gyis rang rig pa'i chos nyid de
NK093(ge)002:11492: kho na nyid rang snang rig pa'i mngona sum du
NK093(ge)002:11494: de lta bu la ni dper na 'bras legs pas
NK093(ge)002:11495: phub sog zhor la 'byung ba lta bur gnas skabs
NK093(ge)002:11496: dang mthar thug gi che ba'i yona tan rnams kyang
NK093(ge)002:11497: dus kun tu rgyun mi 'achada par 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:11498: de'ang nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib par bsnyad
NK093(ge)002:11499: pa gnyis dang mtshan ma'i spyod yul thams cad byang
NK093(ge)002:11500: zhig dag nas yang dag pa'i spyod yul tshogsa chen
NK093(ge)002:11501: rnam gnyis yongs su rdzogas pasa na /
NK093(ge)002:11502: thob bya sku gsum gyi 'bras bu'ang bzhin dang me
NK093(ge)002:11503: long gi tshul du rang snang ba'i phyir a nu
NK093(ge)002:11504: man chad kyi theg pa ganga gi phyogsa kyi sgo
NK093(ge)002:11505: rnams dang mi 'gal zhing mthuna para /
NK093(ge)002:11507: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK093(ge)002:11508: zhes pa ltar rim gyis min par gcig char gyi
NK093(ge)002:11509: tshul du 'og mas bgrod pa'i sa rnams kyang da
NK093(ge)002:11510: lta nyid du nona pa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:11512: rgyud dang mdo sde bla med sa //
NK093(ge)002:11514: ma chags pad+ma stug po bkod //
NK093(ge)002:11515: tshogs chen yi ge 'khor lo dang //
NK093(ge)002:11516: kun tu dbye ba med pa'i sa //
NK093(ge)002:11517: sa drug sems la bgrangs pa yang //
NK093(ge)002:11518: ma bcos rdzogs pa chen po'i sa //
NK093(ge)002:11519: rtogs pa'i yon tan drug tu bstan //
NK093(ge)002:11520: ma bcos sa la sbyangs pa med //
NK093(ge)002:11521: 'od gsal lhun rdzogs chen po la //
NK093(ge)002:11522: sa yi rim pa gang yang med //
NK093(ge)002:11523: rang byung rig pa rtogs gyur na //
NK093(ge)002:11524: nor bu rin chen lhun grub ltar //
NK093(ge)002:11525: thams cad sems las byung ba'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11526: rang snang byang chub sems kyi sa //
NK093(ge)002:11532: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11533: de ltar skabs 'dir bstan pa'i don 'di ni bde
NK093(ge)002:11534: bar gshegs pa kun gyi dgongs pa 'dusa pa'i bstan
NK093(ge)002:11535: pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas rgyal ba'i dgongas pa
NK093(ge)002:11536: dang mdzad spyod zaba mo shin tu dpag par dka'
NK093(ge)002:11537: ba nyid mngon du phyung ba yina pas /
NK093(ge)002:11538: ganga daga 'og ma kun gyis mi rtogs pas /
NK093(ge)002:11540: phyi pa sogs blo chung dman pa rnams kyi spyod yul du gyur pa ma yina no //
NK093(ge)002:11541: de skad du'ang kun byed las /
NK093(ge)002:11542: dgongs pa rnal du bzhag pa'i don 'di ni //
NK093(ge)002:11543: kun gyis spyod yul min pas mi shes shing //
NK093(ge)002:11544: mnyam par bzhag pas rtogs pa'i yul las 'das //
NK093(ge)002:11545: kun byed rgyal po de la gnas par byed //
NK093(ge)002:11548: sangs rgyas dang sems can gyi khyad par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:11549: theg pas bgrod pa'i sa gong 'og gi khyad par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:11550: stong pa dang ma skyes pa'i khyad par bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11555: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11556: de ltar kun gyi spyod yul min pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:11557: skal pa mchog dang ldan pa'i dam pa ganga gisa
NK093(ge)002:11558: tshul ganga ltara thun mong ma yin pa de yi
NK093(ge)002:11559: dona nyid yang dag par mthonga zhing phyin ci ma
NK093(ge)002:11560: log par chud pa ltar du sems can ganga daga
NK093(ge)002:11561: 'khrul bar gnas pa'i skye bor rang rgyud pa dang
NK093(ge)002:11562: rgyu'i theg pa'i sa la gnas pa'i sems dpa' man
NK093(ge)002:11563: chad dam sngags phyi pa man chad zhes kyang gsungs
NK093(ge)002:11564: te thams cad kun ltos pas nor ba ste /
NK093(ge)002:11565: de rnams kyis gsang sngags theg pa mchog gi ngo
NK093(ge)002:11566: bo ji bzhin pa nyid ma mthong bar ma rig
NK093(ge)002:11567: pa'i rgyud dam cha can du gyur pasa na ye
NK093(ge)002:11568: gdoda ma'am thog ma med pa nas bag chags bsags
NK093(ge)002:11569: pas zhena pa'i mun pa las dang nyon mongs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11570: sgrib pa dag shin tu 'byongs pa dang sangsa par
NK093(ge)002:11571: daka'a ba'i phyir / rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11572: dbang gis sangs rgyas dang sems can du 'jog pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11573: khyad par nges par grub pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11578: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11579: bka' rgyud rnams las byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang
NK093(ge)002:11580: sangs rgyas kyi sa yi khyad par la rgyu dang
NK093(ge)002:11581: 'bras bu'i rim pas mtho dman yoda do cesa su
NK093(ge)002:11582: gsungs pa yang / ji skad du /
NK093(ge)002:11584: theg pa re la gnas sa re //
NK093(ge)002:11585: byang chub lam gyi gzhi rten byed //
NK093(ge)002:11586: rdzogs chen byang chub sems sa la //
NK093(ge)002:11587: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK093(ge)002:11588: sku gsum ston pa bzhugs pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:11589: khams gsum sems can ma lus dang //
NK093(ge)002:11590: snang srid snod bcud gnas pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11591: sa la sbyangs shing bgrod du med //
NK093(ge)002:11594: ma bcos rang snang bla ma'i sa //
NK093(ge)002:11595: sbyangs pas ma yin ye nas grub //
NK093(ge)002:11596: rang byung rnam dag kun bzang sa //
NK093(ge)002:11597: dbyer med che mchog chos kyi sku //
NK093(ge)002:11599: 'dir rig ma rig gnyis ka dbyer med pa'i don gyi snying po mngon du gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:11600: sngags dang 'bras bus mthonga ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:11601: srid pa dang rgyu yis ma mthonga ba gnyis ka
NK093(ge)002:11602: dbyer med chen po rang rig pa'i chos nyid du
NK093(ge)002:11604: gang yang ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas mtha'i
NK093(ge)002:11605: tha snyad yang med par rgyal ba dama pa'i dgongas
NK093(ge)002:11606: pa bla na med pa chos thams cad kyi ngo
NK093(ge)002:11607: bo nyid ye nas lhun gyis grub par ngesa pa'i
NK093(ge)002:11608: gsang ba dam pa yang dag par rtogs pa yin
NK093(ge)002:11609: pas skyed du bya ba dang bral ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:11610: des na kun byed las kyang /
NK093(ge)002:11611: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su ma mthong ste //
NK093(ge)002:11612: de bzhin nyid du thams cad gcig par mthong //
NK093(ge)002:11613: de bzhin nyid la gcig dang du ma med //
NK093(ge)002:11614: ma byung ma skyes pa yi snying po la //
NK093(ge)002:11615: sgros kyis btags pa'i tha snyad ga la yod //
NK093(ge)002:11616: ces sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK093(ge)002:11621: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11622: stong pa dang rang bzhina med pa'i khyad par ni /
NK093(ge)002:11624: nyan thos gang zag gi bdag med dang /
NK093(ge)002:11625: sems tsam pas sems 'khrul pa gzung 'dzin gyis stong pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11626: dbu ma pas rten 'brel gyi snang ba ma grub
NK093(ge)002:11627: pas stong pa sogs phyi nang gnyis ka ma grub
NK093(ge)002:11628: pa tsam ste / don dam par stong pa 'ba' zhig go //
NK093(ge)002:11630: gsang chen sngags kyi mtha' gnyis kyis stong pa'i snang
NK093(ge)002:11631: ba nyid na ngo bo med de bden pa gnyis
NK093(ge)002:11633: ma skyes pa dang mi g.yo ba'i khyad par ni /
NK093(ge)002:11634: ma skyes pa ni chos rnams rgyu rkyen dang bral
NK093(ge)002:11635: bas ngo bo med pa ste rgyu'i theg pa'i don
NK093(ge)002:11636: mthar thug pa mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi spyod
NK093(ge)002:11637: yul du byed pa nyid de sngags phyi pa'ang phyogs
NK093(ge)002:11638: mtshungs so // mi g.yo ba ni gsang sngags de
NK093(ge)002:11639: kho na nyid kyi ye shes spyod yul dang bral
NK093(ge)002:11641: gnyis su med pa dang lhun gyis grub pa'i khyad para ci zhig gis 'byed na /
NK093(ge)002:11642: gnyis su med pa ni mi bden pa ris su
NK093(ge)002:11643: ma chad cing spyod yul dang gnyis tha dad med
NK093(ge)002:11644: de rang rig pa tsam mo //
NK093(ge)002:11645: lhun gyis grub pa ni rgyal ba'i sku dang ye
NK093(ge)002:11646: shes kyi yon tan rgyu med par 'char bas 'phags
NK093(ge)002:11647: te / rgyu 'bras dang bskyed rdzogs las rdzogs chen
NK093(ge)002:11648: che ba'i khyad par du yang 'gyur bas ma h+aa
NK093(ge)002:11649: dang a nus gnyis med dang rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:11650: mtha' bzhi rang grol gi shan 'byed du'ang 'gyur ro
NK093(ge)002:11651: te / // de ni gtar ka gegs sel gyi tshig lta bu'o //
NK093(ge)002:11652: de lta bu'i lhun gyis grub pa'i don ni yoda
NK093(ge)002:11653: meda dang rtag chada dang bya brtsal la sogas pa
NK093(ge)002:11654: mtha' gnyis par bsnyad pa ril ma spangs bral ba'i
NK093(ge)002:11655: ngo bo la gang yang bkol ba med par kun
NK093(ge)002:11656: nasa lhun gyisa grub par ye gsal du gansa pa'o
NK093(ge)002:11658: log pa dang ma log pa'i rgyu dang 'brasa bu
NK093(ge)002:11659: nyid kyi chos cir snang cir srid thams cad kun
NK093(ge)002:11660: kyang gsang ba chen po'i ma skyes pa'i chos nyida
NK093(ge)002:11661: ji bzhin pa snying po de bzhina nyid kyi ngo
NK093(ge)002:11662: bo dang dbyer med par ldan pa'i rang bzhin ma
NK093(ge)002:11663: nor ba'i rgyan du rang snang ba nyid ye nas
NK093(ge)002:11665: de dag kun kyang chos nyida kyi ngang la spangs
NK093(ge)002:11666: yang ma spang bkag kyang ma bakaga par ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:11667: tha dad du rgya chad pa'ang med de ma 'dres
NK093(ge)002:11668: la yongas su rdzogas pa'i tshul du rang grol ba'i
NK093(ge)002:11670: bya bral ngang du kun rdzogs pas //
NK093(ge)002:11671: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyan //
NK093(ge)002:11672: ma spangs rang sar grol ba'i klong //
NK093(ge)002:11673: sangs rgyas sku dang sems can lus //
NK093(ge)002:11674: ji ltar snang ba dbyings kyi rgyan //
NK093(ge)002:11677: chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo gtan la dbab pa /
NK093(ge)002:11678: phabs pa'i don nyid rdzogs chen du la bzla ba /
NK093(ge)002:11679: de ltar rtogs pa'i yon tan bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:11680: de nyid kyi don de ma bcos par sgom tshul /
NK093(ge)002:11681: bsgom pa'i yon tan lhun rdzogs su bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11683: skyon yon kun de bzhin nyid du gcig par dam bca' ba /
NK093(ge)002:11684: de'i gtan tshigs de bzhin nyid las gzhan med par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:11685: de la ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang dmigs su med par bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:11690: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11691: de'i don ji lta bu zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:11692: nyan rang nas gsang sngags mchog gi bar gyi theg
NK093(ge)002:11693: pa gonga 'oga gi rim pa bstan pa'i mtho dman
NK093(ge)002:11694: dang / la sogas pa zhes gzhan bsdu ba'i don
NK093(ge)002:11695: gyis lta spyod dang grub mtha'i khyad par gyis 'og
NK093(ge)002:11696: ma'i skyon dang gong ma'i yon tan gyi rnam pa
NK093(ge)002:11697: gnyisa po ji ltar snang zhing bstan pa dag dang
NK093(ge)002:11698: dang / / de las gzhan yang gol sgrib dang
NK093(ge)002:11699: de dag sel ba'i gnyen po dag gi don gsang
NK093(ge)002:11700: sngags kyis ji lta bar mthonga zhing shes pa dang
NK093(ge)002:11701: dang / / / theg pa 'og mas de ltar
NK093(ge)002:11702: ma mthong zhing ma shes pa'i khyad par bstan te
NK093(ge)002:11703: dang / / / / gang mi shes pa'i byis
NK093(ge)002:11704: pa dag 'bras bu la re zhing semas kyi smon
NK093(ge)002:11705: pas 'bad ba sha thang bar byed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11706: gang shes pa dag gis kyang dam tshig sems dpas ye shes sems dpa' la brten pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11707: dbyer med du sgrub pa'i thabs kyis kun tu rtsol
NK093(ge)002:11708: bar gnas pa'i rkyen tsam gyis sgo nas theg pa
NK093(ge)002:11709: so so'i chos rgyu nges pa dang 'brasa bu nges
NK093(ge)002:11710: pa'i tshul gyis ma 'dres par so sora gasla bar
NK093(ge)002:11711: yod do zhes smra ba yanga /
NK093(ge)002:11712: 'dir de skad zer ba ngag kyang rtog ge'i spyod
NK093(ge)002:11713: yul du snang ba kho nar nges pas rang ngo
NK093(ge)002:11715: ngo bo nyid ji lta bar thag chod na skyon
NK093(ge)002:11716: yon rgyu 'bras kyi chos de dag thams cada til
NK093(ge)002:11717: 'bru dang mar gyi dpe lta bur lhun gyis grub
NK093(ge)002:11718: pa'i chos nyid de bzhina nyid du dbyer med par
NK093(ge)002:11719: gciga tu nges para zada de gnyis su snang ba
NK093(ge)002:11720: ye nas med do zhes dam bca' 'o //
NK093(ge)002:11725: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11726: 'o na ci yang mi snang ba zhig gam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:11728: mi 'gyur gdal khyab pho brang na //
NK093(ge)002:11729: cis kyang mi bskyod sems nyid che //
NK093(ge)002:11731: phyi nang med par gsal khyab la //
NK093(ge)002:11732: phyi nang gsang ba'i sgo phugs med //
NK093(ge)002:11733: yul dang dbang po gdod nas dag /mtshan ma 'jil ba'i sku med pas //
NK093(ge)002:11734: rdo rje sems dpa' mi 'gyur che //
NK093(ge)002:11735: ye shes mkha' gsal kun tu bzang //
NK093(ge)002:11736: bsam med mkha' gsal ye sangs rgyas //
NK093(ge)002:11738: de la zhes snyegs pas gzhir bzhag pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:11739: thams cad de bzhin nyid du gcig pa'i don nyid
NK093(ge)002:11740: la lta sgom spyod pa'i rnam grangs sogs kyis ye
NK093(ge)002:11741: nas tshogs shing 'du ba dang gyes chos kyi 'brala
NK093(ge)002:11742: ba meda pa nyid kyi rang bzhina du dus gsum
NK093(ge)002:11743: du gnas pa las mi g.yo bas na sems can
NK093(ge)002:11744: nam 'og ma 'khrul pas mi manyama pa dang sangs
NK093(ge)002:11745: rgyas sam gong ma ma 'khrul pas manyama pa'i spyod
NK093(ge)002:11746: yula du bzhag pa'i so so'i yul dang shes pa
NK093(ge)002:11747: gang cir snang yanga rung ste ngo bo la dbyer
NK093(ge)002:11748: med pas chos nyid ji bzhina pa'i de bzhin nyida
NK093(ge)002:11749: 'di nyid ma yina pa ganga yanga meda par de
NK093(ge)002:11750: kho na nyid du nges pa'i phyir gtan tshigs thun
NK093(ge)002:11751: mong min par chos nyid kyi rigs pas grub pa
NK093(ge)002:11753: de bzhin nyid la gang zhig su gnas pa //
NK093(ge)002:11754: de yis ma nor ma bcos 'grub par 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:11755: de ni ma nor bzhin ni ma bcos yin //
NK093(ge)002:11756: nyid ni ma nor ngo bo nyid la bya //
NK093(ge)002:11757: de bzhin nyid las sangs rgyas chos med do //
NK093(ge)002:11759: rang byung ye shes gcig gi snying po las //
NK093(ge)002:11760: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK093(ge)002:11761: mi snang ba la mngon du 'byin nus pas //
NK093(ge)002:11762: chos kyi snying po yin par yid kyang ches //
NK093(ge)002:11763: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK093(ge)002:11764: don dam kun rdzob bden rdzun gnyis med par //
NK093(ge)002:11765: ma nor nges pa'i byang chub sems ston pas //
NK093(ge)002:11766: the tshom som nyi med par yid kyang ches //
NK093(ge)002:11767: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK093(ge)002:11768: rgyu la mi brten rkyen las mi sgrub pas //
NK093(ge)002:11769: gzhan la rag ma las pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK093(ge)002:11770: rang 'byung ye shes yin par yid kyang ches //
NK093(ge)002:11771: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK093(ge)002:11772: rgyu rkyen med par lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11773: phrin las btsal zhing bya byed bya mi dgos //
NK093(ge)002:11774: ma btsal lhun gyis grub par yid kyang ches //
NK093(ge)002:11775: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK093(ge)002:11776: rang 'byung ye shes ye nas ma bsgribs pas //
NK093(ge)002:11777: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad gsal //
NK093(ge)002:11778: chos rnams thams cad gtan la 'begs pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11779: ston pa'i sgron ma yin par yid kyang ches //
NK093(ge)002:11782: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos par //
NK093(ge)002:11783: rol pa skye ba ltar snang yang //
NK093(ge)002:11789: rgyu 'bras dbyer med thig le che //
NK093(ge)002:11790: rtsa ba med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK093(ge)002:11791: thams cad rang sems rig pa'i rgyan //
NK093(ge)002:11792: yang dag lam gcig bde ba'i mchog /bde chen lam la 'jug ldog med //
NK093(ge)002:11793: dbyings la dbyings shar rig pa'i stobs //
NK093(ge)002:11794: mi rtog bsgom pa bzang rtog yin //
NK093(ge)002:11795: rnam par rtog dang khyad med de //
NK093(ge)002:11796: gnyis ka zang ngan med par mnyam //
NK093(ge)002:11797: de yang rig pa rang gi stobs //
NK093(ge)002:11800: 'dir ni rang yul bstan pa las //
NK093(ge)002:11802: zang ma nyid dang thal byung du //
NK093(ge)002:11803: yul dang shes pa'i snang cha las //
NK093(ge)002:11804: thad ka so so'i gzhi la grol //
NK093(ge)002:11805: 'dod yon rnams ni rang rdzogs te //
NK093(ge)002:11806: sna tshogs 'gyu ba so so'i gnad //
NK093(ge)002:11807: gcig shes pa yis grol bar gnas //
NK093(ge)002:11808: des na chos nyid rtogs pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:11809: cha shas nyid dang bral ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:11811: de ltar ji bzhin pa de yi ngo bo nyid
NK093(ge)002:11812: rtogs pa'i skabs de kho nar mnyam pa'i dbyings de
NK093(ge)002:11813: la sku gsum dang tshogas gnyis rdzogas te thabsa dang
NK093(ge)002:11814: shesa rab zung du 'brela ba nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:11815: ye nas dbyer med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11816: ril chos nyid kyi rgyan du rdzogs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:11817: cir yang ma 'gags par snang ba dang mi dmigs
NK093(ge)002:11818: pa nyid du gsal ba la spyod yul thams cad
NK093(ge)002:11819: du mi 'gog pa gnyis med rang grol du gyur
NK093(ge)002:11820: pa'i phyir ro // gsum pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:11824: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11825: de ltar byang chub kyi sems chos nyid de bzhin
NK093(ge)002:11826: nyid la yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa desa na
NK093(ge)002:11827: / rgyal ba dama pa mang po 'dusa nas sku
NK093(ge)002:11828: bzhi'am lnga yis gdul bya la bstan pa so sor
NK093(ge)002:11829: ji ltar mtshon te bka' stsal pa'i dgongas pa rnams
NK093(ge)002:11830: ni mthar thug dona dama gyi mchog tu gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:11831: bya ba dang bral bar rang rig pa ye nas
NK093(ge)002:11832: ma bcosa par sangs rgyas pa'i semas kyi chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:11833: thams cad kyi gzhi'i ngo bo de la 'dusa shing
NK093(ge)002:11834: dang gcig tu yongs su rdzogs pa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:11835: ji ltar bstan kyang de nyid kyi yon tan gyi
NK093(ge)002:11836: mtshan gyi rnam grangs tha dad du grags par gyur
NK093(ge)002:11837: pa'i phyiir ro // de ltar bsgom pa'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:11838: tshig phyed ni gtan tshigs lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:11839: semas kyi ngo bo ranga bzhina med kyang mi 'gag
NK093(ge)002:11840: pas ye shes chen po spyod yul dang bral ba
NK093(ge)002:11841: 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi gnas lugs rgyu yis ma
NK093(ge)002:11842: byas rkyen las ma byunga bar yul med rang byung
NK093(ge)002:11843: du grol basa thig le nyag gcig tu shar ba'i
NK093(ge)002:11844: phyir ngang las mi 'da' zhing rang bzhin la brjed
NK093(ge)002:11845: pa med pas na rjes su bsgom pa'i ting nge
NK093(ge)002:11846: 'dzina zhesa a nu man chad lta bu'i yul byas
NK093(ge)002:11847: kyi bsam pas dmigas par bya ba kuna dang bral
NK093(ge)002:11848: te 'du shes thams cad las grol bar rang gsal
NK093(ge)002:11849: ba la blo yi ldang ldon gyi ming yang med
NK093(ge)002:11850: pa kho na'o // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:11851: thams cad rdzogs chen du la bzla ba /
NK093(ge)002:11852: mtha' dbus can mtha' dbus med par la bzla ba /
NK093(ge)002:11853: stong par 'dod pa snang stong gnyis su med par la bzla ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:11858: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:11859: gsang chen a ti'i gzhung chen po'i don phul du
NK093(ge)002:11860: byung ba nyid 'di ltar blo gros zab cing rgya
NK093(ge)002:11861: che bas yang dag par ngesa pa'i skyes bu mchog
NK093(ge)002:11862: gi dgongs pa rang rig byanga chub semsa kyi rang
NK093(ge)002:11863: bzhin rtsol med bde ba chen po'i ngang de nyid
NK093(ge)002:11864: rtogs te de las 'da' ba med pa la /
NK093(ge)002:11865: yul du byas te lam lnga dang sa bcur bgrod
NK093(ge)002:11866: pa lta bur bgrod pa'i gansa kyi grub pa'i 'bras
NK093(ge)002:11867: bu gzhan na med par ngo bo nyid du gnas
NK093(ge)002:11868: pa dang / de bzhin du lta bas shes par
NK093(ge)002:11869: bya ba'i yul dngos po gzugas snang tu gyur ba
NK093(ge)002:11870: dang dngos med stong par lta ba'ang meda pasa yul
NK093(ge)002:11871: logs nas mi tshol bar dngos po dang dngos po
NK093(ge)002:11872: med pa'i chos kyi matshana ma thams cad kuna chos
NK093(ge)002:11873: nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba'i rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:11874: du mkhyen cing rtogs pas na skyon dang yona tan
NK093(ge)002:11875: gyi ris su bsnyad pa gang yang thog ma nyid
NK093(ge)002:11876: nas yonga ye med de ma dmigs pas gdal khyab
NK093(ge)002:11877: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor nyid du 'ub chub
NK093(ge)002:11878: pa dang / pa yin te / klong rab 'byams las /
NK093(ge)002:11880: thams cad 'dus shing rdzogs pas na //
NK093(ge)002:11881: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK093(ge)002:11882: phyi nang sgo phugs bral bas na //
NK093(ge)002:11883: mnyam pa nyid kyi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK093(ge)002:11884: mtha' dbus gnyis su med pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11885: mu mtha' med pa'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK093(ge)002:11887: mtho dman med pa'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK093(ge)002:11888: sgrib pa gnyis dang bral ba'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11889: ma bkod gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK093(ge)002:11890: rig pa phyi nang med pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11891: dbyer med zad thal dkyil 'khor yin /
NK093(ge)002:11892: dgag sgrub gnyis dang bral ba'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11893: rgya chen snang ba'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK093(ge)002:11894: ma spangs rang sar grol bas na //
NK093(ge)002:11895: rang bzhin lhun grub dkyil 'khor mchog /ces dang /
NK093(ge)002:11896: gcig tu 'dus pas mtho dman med //
NK093(ge)002:11897: mtho dman med pas yangs dog med //
NK093(ge)002:11898: mtha' dbus bral bas phyi nang med //
NK093(ge)002:11899: skye 'gag med pas dus gsum med //
NK093(ge)002:11900: dus gsum med pas skye shi med //
NK093(ge)002:11902: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid du gcig /rgyal ba'i dgongs spyod bsam yas kyang //
NK093(ge)002:11903: rang byung ye shes gcig gi klong //
NK093(ge)002:11904: gzhan du g.yos pa rdul tsam med //
NK093(ge)002:11907: thega rtse gsang ba chen po'i don 'dir mdo sngags
NK093(ge)002:11908: kyi lta ba dang tshogs gnyis kyi sgo thams cad
NK093(ge)002:11909: stong nyid dang snying rje dbyer med pa'i ngang klong
NK093(ge)002:11910: du rdzogsa te rgyu 'bras ril lhun gyis grub pa
NK093(ge)002:11911: yin pas rang rig rang grol gyi gzhi la gtan
NK093(ge)002:11912: tshigs tshad mas tha dad phyogs 'dzin gyi the tshoma
NK093(ge)002:11913: za ba'i gegs thams cad bsal nas ched byas dang
NK093(ge)002:11914: rtsol sgrub kyis yul du byed pa'i blo thag kun
NK093(ge)002:11915: bacada cing / thams cad theg mchog bla na meda
NK093(ge)002:11916: pa 'od gsal rdzogas pa chena pora ma 'dres yongs
NK093(ge)002:11917: rdzogs kyi dgongs par shar grol dus mnyam du gyur
NK093(ge)002:11918: pas theg pa'i rgyal po'i dgongs spyod ma yin pa
NK093(ge)002:11919: med pa'i don nyid gdeng chen tshad du 'khyol bar
NK093(ge)002:11920: la bzlas pa yin pa'i phyir mthar thug gi dgongs
NK093(ge)002:11921: pa'i skyel so la nges pa rnyed par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:11922: de skad du'ang snga ma las /
NK093(ge)002:11924: mnyam dang mi mnyam sems kyi stobs //
NK093(ge)002:11925: dbye bsal med do gcig gi klong //
NK093(ge)002:11926: gnyis mtha'i gras thag bcad pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11927: mtshungs med phyogs med gtan tshigs kyis //
NK093(ge)002:11928: yul snang zhen pa kun bkrol nas //
NK093(ge)002:11929: phyogs ris med do ye gdal che //
NK093(ge)002:11930: de don 'gyur med gnad la phebs //
NK093(ge)002:11931: phyogs med rig pa kha yan gyis //
NK093(ge)002:11932: mthar 'dzin spros pa kun bcad nas //
NK093(ge)002:11933: dgag sgrub med par ye nas mnyam //
NK093(ge)002:11934: yul sems ris su mi 'byed pas //
NK093(ge)002:11935: yul med rig pa rang shar gyis //
NK093(ge)002:11936: gtan tshigs zhen pa'i gting phyung nas //
NK093(ge)002:11937: rgyu 'bras med de chos nyid che //
NK093(ge)002:11938: de la phyogs su rtsol 'dod pa //
NK093(ge)002:11939: dag dang ma dag gol sa ste //
NK093(ge)002:11940: rim pa brgyad po lam gyi gnas //
NK093(ge)002:11941: yid ches rang gzhan gnyis kyi lung //
NK093(ge)002:11942: the tshom gol sa shugs kyis chod //
NK093(ge)002:11943: phyi nang med par 'od gsal bas //
NK093(ge)002:11944: mtha' yi mun pa klong du dag /rgyu rkyen gnyen pos mi g.yo bas //
NK093(ge)002:11946: ma rig med pa ye shes klong //
NK093(ge)002:11947: thams cad grol ba nam mkha'i klong //
NK093(ge)002:11949: snang srid skye 'gul yong ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:11950: mi srid med pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK093(ge)002:11951: rang byung ye shes klong dkyil du //
NK093(ge)002:11952: ma rdzogs pa ni med pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11953: rdzogs chen lhun grub bla na med //
NK093(ge)002:11954: mnyam pa nyid du thag chod pas //
NK093(ge)002:11955: kun kyang rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK093(ge)002:11956: dus la snga phyi ma mchis pas //
NK093(ge)002:11957: a ti dus gsum chig chod la //
NK093(ge)002:11958: a nu man chad 'og ma yi //
NK093(ge)002:11959: bskal pa'i grangs dang mi tshe'i grangs //
NK093(ge)002:11961: ma spangs gcig tu 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11962: dus gsum tha dad med pa ru //
NK093(ge)002:11963: rang bzhin gcig pas klong du grol //
NK093(ge)002:11964: de yi ngang la rgyun chad med //
NK093(ge)002:11965: rgyun chad med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK093(ge)002:11967: gzhan du lta ba med pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:11968: ye sangs rgyas pa'i chos nyid yin //
NK093(ge)002:11969: de la rang rang longs spyod pas //
NK093(ge)002:11970: phyogs med gter chen 'bras bu yin //
NK093(ge)002:11972: des na rdzogs pa chen po'i byang chub kyi sems
NK093(ge)002:11973: rang byung rig pa'i ye shes ji bzhin du rtogs
NK093(ge)002:11974: pas 'og ma'i theg pa'i lta ba kun las 'phags
NK093(ge)002:11976: nyan thos kyis gang zag gi bdag med tsam las
NK093(ge)002:11977: ma rtogs par chos bdag gzung 'dzin phra ba don
NK093(ge)002:11978: dam du 'dod pa la ltos na /
NK093(ge)002:11979: rang rgyal gyis de'i steng du chos kyi phyogs gcig
NK093(ge)002:11980: gzung ba rang bzhin med par rtogs pas 'phags la
NK093(ge)002:11981: / de las sems tsam pas gzung 'dzin gnyis med
NK093(ge)002:11982: kyi shes pa rang rig rang gsal du rtogs pas
NK093(ge)002:11983: / 'phags shing / de bas dbu ma pas don
NK093(ge)002:11984: dam par rang rig rang gsal du'ang ma grub ste
NK093(ge)002:11985: / 'phags shing / / chos nyid spros bral nam
NK093(ge)002:11986: mkha' ltar bdag med gnyis ka rtogs pas 'phags la
NK093(ge)002:11988: bas don dam rang sems dag pa mtha' bzhi dang
NK093(ge)002:11990: rdzob de rtogs kyi yon tan rigs gsum gyi dkyil
NK093(ge)002:11992: / de gnyis kyang dbyer med du rtogs pas 'phags
NK093(ge)002:11994: / pa dang / de las yo ga pas don
NK093(ge)002:11995: dam sems nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'am /
NK093(ge)002:11996: skye 'gag med pa'i chos sku rnam snang kun tu zhal dang /
NK093(ge)002:11997: kun rdzob de rtogs kyi byin rlabs thun mong gi rigs lnga'am /
NK093(ge)002:11998: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha so bdun /
NK093(ge)002:11999: de gnyis kyang dbyer med du rtogs pas 'phags shing /
NK093(ge)002:12001: don dam rig pa spros bral snang ba ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa /
NK093(ge)002:12002: kun rdzob rig pa sgyu ma rnam dag chen po /
NK093(ge)002:12003: de gnyis tshig la snga phyi yod kyang don la
NK093(ge)002:12004: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar rtogs pas 'phags
NK093(ge)002:12005: la / de las a nu pas dbyings snang ba rtsal rdzogs kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong /
NK093(ge)002:12006: ye shes 'gag pa med par kun tu bzang po'i rol pa /
NK093(ge)002:12007: de gnyis dbyer med sras bde ba chen po rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK093(ge)002:12008: de yang spyod yul dang bral bar rtogs pas 'phags shing /
NK093(ge)002:12009: a nus de ltar rtogs kyang rgyu 'bras sgo phugs su 'byed pa la /
NK093(ge)002:12012: ji bzhin ma bslad btsal du med pa la //
NK093(ge)002:12013: sgo phugs dkyil 'khor bskyed dang ma bral nor //
NK093(ge)002:12014: 'jug skyed ye bral ngang nyid khyod kyis kyang //
NK093(ge)002:12015: phyogs tsam ma shes rang byung nga nyid 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12016: zhes gsungs pa ltar chos thams cad byang chub kyi
NK093(ge)002:12017: sems skye 'gag gnyis su med pa'i rang byung gi
NK093(ge)002:12018: ye shes sgra ji bzhin ma yin par blo dang
NK093(ge)002:12019: dngos po gnyis med rang grol du rtogs pas khyad
NK093(ge)002:12021: de bas na 'dir theg dgu rdzogs chen du 'dus shing kun las 'phags pa'i tshul ni /
NK093(ge)002:12022: 'jam pa'i dbyangs dngos kun mkhyen kahthoga pa chen pos 'dra mthun khyad par ngang pa'i rgyal po las /
NK093(ge)002:12023: snang ba 'gog tu med pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:12024: sems can dang yang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12025: rang rgyud dngos por mi 'dzin pas //
NK093(ge)002:12027: gang zag bdag med 'dod pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:12028: nyan thos dang yang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12029: rdul phran rdzas su mi 'dzin pas //
NK093(ge)002:12030: nyan thos las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12031: rgyu rkyen dag par 'dod pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:12032: rang sangs rgyas dang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12033: rten 'brel mtshan mar mi lta bas //
NK093(ge)002:12034: rang rgyal las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12035: snang ba sems su 'dod pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:12036: sems tsam dang yang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12037: rig pa rdzas su mi sgrub pas //
NK093(ge)002:12038: sems tsam las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12039: don dam spros bral 'dod pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:12040: dbu ma dang yang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12041: bden pa ris su mi 'byed pas //
NK093(ge)002:12042: dbu ma las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12043: rang bzhin dag par 'dod pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:12044: kri ya dang yang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12045: dag byed dngos por mi 'dzin pas //
NK093(ge)002:12046: kri ya las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12048: u pa ya dang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12050: u pa las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12051: snang sems dbyer med 'dod pas ni //
NK093(ge)002:12052: yo ga dang kyang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12054: yo ga las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12055: blang dor med par spyod pas ni //
NK093(ge)002:12056: ma h+aa dang yang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12057: de nyid dngos por mi 'dzin pas //
NK093(ge)002:12058: ma h+aa las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12059: dbyings dang ye shes 'dod pas ni //
NK093(ge)002:12060: a nu dang yang mthun pa ste //
NK093(ge)002:12061: de nyid rgyu 'bras mi lta bas //
NK093(ge)002:12062: a nu las kyang khyad par 'phags //
NK093(ge)002:12063: shin tu rnal 'byor lta ba ni //
NK093(ge)002:12064: rang bzhin skye ba med pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:12065: rol pa 'gag pa med pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:12066: mtshan nyid dbye ba med pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:12067: rig pa rang sar grol ba yin //
NK093(ge)002:12068: 'khrul chos rang sar zhi ba yin //
NK093(ge)002:12069: 'bras bu rang snang lhun grub yin //
NK093(ge)002:12070: zhes gsungs pa ltar theg mchog rgyal po'i dgongs don
NK093(ge)002:12071: bla na med pa la nges pa rnyed par bya
NK093(ge)002:12073: 'dir gnad tsam bstan pa yin gyi rgyas par spros kyang chog go //
NK093(ge)002:12075: mtha' dbus med par khungs kyis bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:12076: gtan tshigs kyis mtha' gud na med par bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:12081: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:12082: de bas na rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa las che ba'i khyad par yod pa'i phyir te /
NK093(ge)002:12083: 'di ltar gsang sngags bla na med pa'i lta ba
NK093(ge)002:12084: gang yang spong len med pa'i don de ltar yin
NK093(ge)002:12085: pa des na / dbu ma pa sogs gang su
NK093(ge)002:12086: zhig gis dbye gzhi zad pa'i dbyer med chen po
NK093(ge)002:12087: la mtha'a dang dbus su 'byed de mtha' bsal nas
NK093(ge)002:12088: dbu mar mi dmigs pa'i don 'dod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:12089: sems tsam sogs shes pa rang rig rang gsal dang /
NK093(ge)002:12090: bden gnyis dbyer med du sgrubs te shin tu brtag
NK093(ge)002:12091: dka' ba'i ngo bo cha phra ba la blo gnas
NK093(ge)002:12092: par 'dod pa rnams kyang kun bral nyag gcig ci
NK093(ge)002:12093: yang ma yin pa'i don chen po mthong ba las
NK093(ge)002:12095: 'on kyang de dag thams cad theg pa chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:12096: mdo mtha'a dbus su 'dzin pa med pa'i mnyam pa
NK093(ge)002:12097: nyid dbu ma dang dbyer med kyi tha snyad las
NK093(ge)002:12098: kyang grol ba'i klong chen po nyid du kun rnam
NK093(ge)002:12099: dbye med pa gcig tu 'dus pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:12100: dper na phul khyor bre nang du shong ba dang mtshungs pa nyid du nges te /
NK093(ge)002:12101: de bas na gsang sngags theg mchog rgyal po 'od
NK093(ge)002:12102: gsal snying po'i dgongs pa nyid 'og ma kun las
NK093(ge)002:12103: khyad para du 'phagsa pa'i che ba rmad du byung
NK093(ge)002:12104: ba rnams yang dag par rig cing rtogs par bya
NK093(ge)002:12105: ba'i dona gyi ched du dgongs pa kun 'dusa kyi
NK093(ge)002:12106: rgyud mchog chen po 'di lta bu nyid bka' stsal
NK093(ge)002:12107: bar mdzad de gsungsa pa yin par shes par bya'o
NK093(ge)002:12112: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:12113: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyur 'dooda pa rgyu'i theg pa rnams dang /
NK093(ge)002:12114: la sogas zhes dngos po gzhan bsdu ba ni yo
NK093(ge)002:12115: ga phyi pa dag ste de rnams kyis phyi nang
NK093(ge)002:12116: snod bcud kyi yula du snang ba'i dngos po daga
NK093(ge)002:12117: la 'phags pa nyan thos kyis dngos po rnams brtags
NK093(ge)002:12118: na brtags mi bzod de ma brtags na nyams dag'a
NK093(ge)002:12119: ba tsam ste rang bzhin cha med gnyis las ma
NK093(ge)002:12121: sngags phyi pas kun rdzob tu snang ba'i matshana ma
NK093(ge)002:12122: rnams kyang dag pa'i chos nyid du nges pas mtshan
NK093(ge)002:12123: ma med pa tsam dang dbyer med du gnas pas
NK093(ge)002:12124: rtogs na yon tan dang byin rlabs rigs gsum dang
NK093(ge)002:12125: rigs lnga'i lhar snang bas na spyod pa rnam par
NK093(ge)002:12126: dkar ba dang gtsang sbras 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs
NK093(ge)002:12127: la mos pas gansa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:12128: ganga daga rnam rig pa dang rnal 'byor spyod pa'i
NK093(ge)002:12129: dbu ma pas dngos po phyi nang gi chosa rnams
NK093(ge)002:12130: kun gzhi gzung cha dang 'dzin cha 'khrul par snang
NK093(ge)002:12131: ba rab rib can gyis rdzas mthong ba ltar gyur
NK093(ge)002:12132: pas 'khrul par snang ba'i semas su gcig tu 'dusa
NK093(ge)002:12133: pas yul logs na med par 'dod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:12134: dbu ma chen pos kun rdzob tu rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba sgyu ma tsam dang /
NK093(ge)002:12135: don dam par mtha'a gnyis sam bzhi po kun dang
NK093(ge)002:12136: bral ba'i chos nyid ma skyes ba'i ngo bor nganga
NK093(ge)002:12137: gis gasla lo zhesa su 'dod pa'i gzhung so so
NK093(ge)002:12138: la brten te 'bad pas 'bras bu thob pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:12139: rgyu 'bras snga phyi yod par smra zhing grub mtha'
NK093(ge)002:12140: so sor 'dzin pa rnams kyis mtshan nyid theg pas
NK093(ge)002:12141: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu tsam du 'dod pa
NK093(ge)002:12142: dang / gsang sngags kyis sems cho 'phrul dang bcas
NK093(ge)002:12143: pa 'bras bur 'dod de rang rang gi lugs srol
NK093(ge)002:12145: kun zlum thig le nyag gcig gsang sngags mnyam pa
NK093(ge)002:12146: chen po'i ngo bor la bzlas te thag bacada pa'i
NK093(ge)002:12147: snying po don gyi gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin
NK093(ge)002:12148: du rtogs shing mthonga na de dag kun kyang spang
NK093(ge)002:12149: bya min par dbyings la rdzogs pasa gsang sngags su
NK093(ge)002:12150: gcig pa nyid las guda na yonga ye med pa
NK093(ge)002:12151: nyid do // des na klong chen rab 'byams las /
NK093(ge)002:12152: ji bzhin pa dang de las gzhan //
NK093(ge)002:12153: ma nor ba dang 'khrul pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:12154: ma bcos pa dang bcos pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:12155: gzhan ma yin dang rang yin dang //
NK093(ge)002:12156: chos can dang ni chos nyid dang //
NK093(ge)002:12157: dbyings dang dngos po la sogs pa //
NK093(ge)002:12158: bzang ngan bye brag 'byed pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:12160: byang chub sems la dbye ba med //
NK093(ge)002:12161: stong nyid snying po'i klong chen 'di //
NK093(ge)002:12162: skad cig rtogs pa tsam gyis kyang //
NK093(ge)002:12163: byang chub klong du der son pas //
NK093(ge)002:12164: mtshan ma'i chos la rag mi las //
NK093(ge)002:12165: stong pa'i chos la blo mi gnas //
NK093(ge)002:12166: cir yang med las gar yang snang //
NK093(ge)002:12167: mthong ba med par kun tu gsal //
NK093(ge)002:12168: brtags na ma rnyed cir yang 'char //
NK093(ge)002:12169: dngos po med las snying po 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:12170: rang bzhin med par kun la khyab //
NK093(ge)002:12171: dngos gzhi med par thams cad 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:12172: bsgrub tu med par cir yang 'grub //
NK093(ge)002:12173: btang bzhag med par rang la gnas //
NK093(ge)002:12176: ye shes nyi ma rang la shar //
NK093(ge)002:12177: gsang sngags don kun bskyed pa'i gzhi //
NK093(ge)002:12178: gdul bya ma lus 'dul ba'i zhing //
NK093(ge)002:12179: thams cad bdag nyid byang chub klong //
NK093(ge)002:12180: mi mdzad mdzad pa mthar phyin pas //
NK093(ge)002:12181: dus gsum rgyal ba ma lus kyis //
NK093(ge)002:12182: phrin las mdzad pa 'di yis mdzad //
NK093(ge)002:12184: de bas na gsang sngags mchog gi don zab mo de dag gis ji bzhin par ma mthong yang /
NK093(ge)002:12185: gala te ngo bos gsang don la rgya chad nas
NK093(ge)002:12186: logs shig par gyur te gud na yoda para 'doda
NK093(ge)002:12187: pa'i phyogs 'dzin na mtha' bral gsang sngags kyi nges
NK093(ge)002:12188: don mthong du mi ster ba'i skyon chen po bag
NK093(ge)002:12189: chags ngan pas nad kyis zin pa yina pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:12190: te / dper na mdzub mos zla ba mtshon pa
NK093(ge)002:12191: na mdzub rtse la chags pas zla ba sgrib pa
NK093(ge)002:12192: te / bzhin no // gsum pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:12196: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:12197: de ltar gsang sngags kyi don du ril 'dus pa
NK093(ge)002:12198: desa na nyan thos nas sngags phyi pa'i bar gyis
NK093(ge)002:12199: theg pa rnams kyi lta ba dang bsam gtan nam
NK093(ge)002:12200: ting nge 'dzin rim pa so so bar gyur te
NK093(ge)002:12201: theg pa chen po'i khyad par las rang rang gi
NK093(ge)002:12202: ngo la tha dad du cir yang snang ba kun
NK093(ge)002:12203: kyang gsang sngags kyi don chen po la shed ma
NK093(ge)002:12204: bye bas byis pa'i spyod yul rang gi blos brtags
NK093(ge)002:12205: pa'i lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin la zhen pa
NK093(ge)002:12206: de yang dper na byis pa chung ngus khang pa
NK093(ge)002:12207: brtsegs pa byas pa dang mnyam du 'jig pa bzhin
NK093(ge)002:12208: du 'khrul pa nying 'khrul nyid snang ba yina pas
NK093(ge)002:12209: ltos pa'i 'khrul snang kho na yin no //
NK093(ge)002:12211: dam pa gsang sngags theg pa cheen po la gnyis
NK093(ge)002:12212: las sngags phyi pa lta 'phang zhan pa dag dang
NK093(ge)002:12213: damna pa gsang sngags la ltos nas rgyu'i theg pa
NK093(ge)002:12215: lta bas kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du yul rang
NK093(ge)002:12216: rgyud du lta ba ni dper na sgyu mas 'khrul
NK093(ge)002:12217: shes 'dren pa'i bya ba byed kyang dngos po med
NK093(ge)002:12219: ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam pa la zhen pa ni
NK093(ge)002:12220: smig rgyu'i chu'i tshul la ri dwags skom pas bdas
NK093(ge)002:12221: kyang skom pas gdung ba mi 'jil ba bzhin dang
NK093(ge)002:12222: / don dam par ranga bzhina skye 'agga meda pasa
NK093(ge)002:12223: nama mkha'a bzhina du 'dod pa'i skabs desa ni rtogs
NK093(ge)002:12224: par dka' ba'i gsang sngags theg pa chen po ji
NK093(ge)002:12225: bzhin pa'i chos nyid rgyal ba'i dgongs pa kun nas
NK093(ge)002:12226: 'dus pa'i ngo bo chos kuna rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:12227: bden pa rnam gnyis dbyer med pa'i don gyi ngang
NK093(ge)002:12228: la gnas par gyur pa nyid mthonga ba med de
NK093(ge)002:12229: rang gi lta bas sgrib pas so //
NK093(ge)002:12231: mdo sde'i byang chub sems dpas ni /
NK093(ge)002:12232: don dam par ma skyes pa zang ma cir yanga
NK093(ge)002:12233: mi snang ba'am snang ma myong ba nyid mtha' dang
NK093(ge)002:12234: bral ba'i lta ba dam pa skyon med pa yin
NK093(ge)002:12236: de ni gsang sngags don gyi snying po ma mthong
NK093(ge)002:12237: ba'i 'khrul pa nor ba'i yul yin pasa des rgyu
NK093(ge)002:12238: 'bras dbyer med pa'i don ma nor ba nyid rtogs
NK093(ge)002:12239: su btub pa ma yina pa'i phyir te snang stong
NK093(ge)002:12240: dbyer med mtha' bral chen po ma rtogs par stong
NK093(ge)002:12241: pa la dam par 'dzin pas so //
NK093(ge)002:12242: 'o na dbu ma snang med pa'i lugs su de ltar nges kyang /
NK093(ge)002:12243: sngags phyi pa ni de la bskrun du med do snyam na /
NK093(ge)002:12244: 'dir rdzogs pa chen po rang snang ris med kyi dgongs pa la ltos na /
NK093(ge)002:12245: sngags phyi pa gsum gyi 'dod pa yang /
NK093(ge)002:12247: kun rdzob snang ba lha tshigs gsum //
NK093(ge)002:12249: dag pa'i mtha' ru lta ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:12250: rigs bzhi dpon g.yog don dam par //
NK093(ge)002:12251: spros dang bral bar lta ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:12252: snang ba rigs lnga grogs po'i tshul //
NK093(ge)002:12253: dam par rnam snang chen por lta //
NK093(ge)002:12254: zhes gsungs pa ltar mthar thug dbyer med du 'dod pa tsam yod kyang /
NK093(ge)002:12255: bden gnyis kyi khas len can du song bas na /
NK093(ge)002:12256: mtha' bral phyogs ris su gyur pa'i don dam du
NK093(ge)002:12257: bzhag pa de nyid kun rdzoob kyi snang ba dang
NK093(ge)002:12259: rin po che gter gtad pa las /
NK093(ge)002:12260: dag bden gtsang sbra dgos pas 'khrul //
NK093(ge)002:12262: snga phyi gnyis skyon rjes su gnod //
