NK093(ge)002:13764: zhes gsungs pa ltar la bzla ste lta ba'i dam tshig gis chings kyis bcings par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:13769: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:13770: de ltar sgo gsum ched du bsdom ste bsrung ba
NK093(ge)002:13771: med par chos nyid nama mkha'i dgongs par gnas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:13772: dama tshiga chen po 'di yi khyad par las blo'i
NK093(ge)002:13773: rim pa bzhin du gdul bya so sor rang rang
NK093(ge)002:13774: gi 'dul ba'i tshad du ji ltar gragsa pa ltar
NK093(ge)002:13775: snang ba'i rang bzhina la sdoma pa dang dam tshig
NK093(ge)002:13776: rgya mtsho lta bu dang nyis brgya lnga bcu'i tshul
NK093(ge)002:13777: khrimsa la sogs pa nges tshig so sora gasla zhing
NK093(ge)002:13779: 'jiga rten gyi skye bo phal pa rnams la chad mdo dang mna' nyid batsana pa ru snang ngo //
NK093(ge)002:13780: don la shed ma bye bas byis pa nyan thos
NK093(ge)002:13781: rnams la tshul khrims kyi bslab pa spong ba'i shes
NK093(ge)002:13782: pa zhes su grags shing snang ngo //
NK093(ge)002:13783: don phyogs la shed bye bas nar sona pa byang
NK093(ge)002:13784: chub sems dpa' la sdoma pa zhes bya bar gragsa
NK093(ge)002:13785: so // theg pa chen po'i gsang sngags phyi pa
NK093(ge)002:13786: dang bla med nang pa mchoga la rtsa ba dang
NK093(ge)002:13787: yan lag gi dama tshig nyid du nges para snang
NK093(ge)002:13788: so // zhing grags so // de lta bu'i snang lugs de dag rnams ni /
NK093(ge)002:13789: dam tshig chen po nor bu rin po che ltar
NK093(ge)002:13790: dam pa mang po'i dngos gzhir gyur pas rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:13791: gciga gi dona lasa ma g.yos par gnas kyang skye
NK093(ge)002:13792: bo nasa a nu'i bar gyis gdul bya rnams ji
NK093(ge)002:13793: ltar 'dula ba'i snang ngo dang 'tshams par rang rang
NK093(ge)002:13794: la so sora snang zhing gragsa par gyur pa kho
NK093(ge)002:13795: na yin no // drug pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:13799: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:13800: de bas na de kho na nyid chos nyid de
NK093(ge)002:13801: bzhina nyid kyi don rtogs pa dang ldana cing goms
NK093(ge)002:13802: pa can ni dama par nges pa ste dus bzhi
NK093(ge)002:13803: kun tu 'da' ba dang nyams pa med par rnam
NK093(ge)002:13804: rtog kun sreg par byed do //
NK093(ge)002:13805: gal te lta ba dang bral nas don de lasa
NK093(ge)002:13806: 'adsa par gyur na rang gi rgyud tshig ste 'og
NK093(ge)002:13807: tu ltung bar 'gyur bas dam tshig chen po zhes
NK093(ge)002:13808: pa'i nges tshig gis bstan pa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:13810: byang chub sems nyid dam pa'i don //
NK093(ge)002:13811: gnas dang mi gnas khyad par las //
NK093(ge)002:13812: rnam par rtog dang rang rgyud sreg /dam tshig ces su dpa' bos gsungs //
NK093(ge)002:13818: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:13819: nges par chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi don rtogs
NK093(ge)002:13820: nas ris med mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig gcig
NK093(ge)002:13821: bsrung bas don las 'da' nyams gang yang med pas
NK093(ge)002:13822: na bsrung mtshams can gyi dam tshig sdom pa thams
NK093(ge)002:13823: cad la zhig ral lta bur byung yang kun kyang
NK093(ge)002:13824: don la bsrungsa par 'gyur bas skyon dang bral ba'i
NK093(ge)002:13825: dama pa'i dama tshiga chena po 'di ni /
NK093(ge)002:13826: gong du bshad pa'i so sor skye bo nas a
NK093(ge)002:13827: nu man chad theg pa so so kun gyis bsrung
NK093(ge)002:13828: mtshams rnams dang 'gal bar mi bya ba ni 'dir
NK093(ge)002:13829: bre phul gyi tshul gyis tshang ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:13830: rgyal po dang 'bangs lta bu'i tshul gyis theg pa
NK093(ge)002:13831: kun gyi bsrung ba rnams dang du blang zhing ngo
NK093(ge)002:13832: bos dag par gyur pa de /
NK093(ge)002:13833: 'on kyang de dag thams cad dam pa chen po
NK093(ge)002:13834: gang gciga gi rang bzhin gyis rgyas thebs pa'i dona
NK093(ge)002:13835: gyi rang bzhin rtogs nas gdeng du chud de don
NK093(ge)002:13836: las 'gyur ba med par mi nyams par bya ba'i
NK093(ge)002:13837: don te / 'di ni sdom pa gsum ldan gyi lung du'ang drang ngo zhes gsungs so //
NK093(ge)002:13841: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:13842: grogas po daga de daga ni mi 'ad'a ba'i ranga bzhina du shesa par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:13843: zhes thos pa dam pa yongas su dag par bgros te dam tshig gi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:13852: ces pa'i bar gyis bstana te /
NK093(ge)002:13853: kye grogas po daga /ces bos nas lta ba dang
NK093(ge)002:13854: dam tshig bstan pa de ltar 'dir gsang ba mchog
NK093(ge)002:13855: gi rang don gyi spyod pa'i rang bzhina nye bar
NK093(ge)002:13858: las dang po pa'i sa nas lus dang ngaga dang
NK093(ge)002:13859: yid kyi sgo gsum gyi las kyi mtha'a gsum nyes
NK093(ge)002:13860: pas ma gos par yongas su dag pa'i rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:13861: du rdzogas te mthar phyin pa na /
NK093(ge)002:13862: de ni theg pa chen po'i spyod pa rmad du byung ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:13863: skyes bu dam pa lam la zhugs pa'i spyod pa
NK093(ge)002:13864: dam pa yina pasa na rigs ngan du gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:13865: damna pa'i spyod pa mina te /
NK093(ge)002:13866: theg pa chen po'i rgyud 'dzin pa zhes bka' las
NK093(ge)002:13867: gsungs pas gsang sngags dama pa'i rigas can gyi spyod
NK093(ge)002:13868: pa zhesa su ston mchog kun tu bzang pos bashada
NK093(ge)002:13869: de bka' stsal ba yin no //
NK093(ge)002:13873: sems kyi spyod pa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:13875: rdo rje lus kyi spyod pa spyir bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:13881: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:13882: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa so so nas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:13883: khyad par du yang sa lnga pa man chad kyi
NK093(ge)002:13884: yul theg pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa yang dag
NK093(ge)002:13885: pa'i don dang mi phyed pas gsang sngags rdo rje
NK093(ge)002:13886: lta bu'i sgor zhugs pa'i dam pa rnams kyi lusa
NK093(ge)002:13887: kyi spyod pa ni ji ltar spyod zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:13888: thar pa de nyid 'dod gzugs dang gzugs med lta bu min pas /
NK093(ge)002:13889: tshig phyed phyed kyis don dang bya bar 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:13890: yul la dmigs nas ched du byed pa dang bral
NK093(ge)002:13891: bas ril mnyam pa'i ngang la bdag mtho sar phyin
NK093(ge)002:13892: pa med lasa don gyi ngo bor gyur pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:13893: lus kyis tshul mi 'chos pa'am bcos par mi bya
NK093(ge)002:13894: ba dang / chos so cog sems kyi chos nyid du gcig pas bdag kyang /
NK093(ge)002:13895: lus sems dang bya ba'i las dang grogs rnams gang
NK093(ge)002:13896: yang gnyis gnyis thams cad rnam par spang nas gcig
NK093(ge)002:13898: dgon gnas dben pa zhig tu gcig tu gansa te 'dug par bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:13899: de nas tshig phyed phyed kyis don dang bya bar mi sbyor bar /
NK093(ge)002:13900: tsham tshom med par glang po chen po'i lta stangas
NK093(ge)002:13901: ltar ji bzhina pa las ma bcos par bag tsha
NK093(ge)002:13902: ba med de zon bag che ba dang ldan par
NK093(ge)002:13903: bya ba dang / de bzhina du lus kyi spyod
NK093(ge)002:13904: pa bcos bslad med par sems rang lugs su rnal
NK093(ge)002:13905: mas gnas te 'dug para bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:13906: gnas ganga du gansa pa der yang rtogs pa'i ngang
NK093(ge)002:13907: la don dang ldan par rtag tu 'dug ste dben
NK093(ge)002:13908: pa la mi skyo bar bya 'phur ba bzhin min
NK093(ge)002:13909: para gansa te ma nges pa'i skyon med par bya
NK093(ge)002:13910: ba dang / 'o na de la chags sam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:13911: don la gansa pa dang ldan pas rtag par 'dug
NK093(ge)002:13912: pa'i dben gnas de nyid la'ang mi dmigs par shes
NK093(ge)002:13913: nas yul gyi sa la lhag par chagas zhen mi
NK093(ge)002:13914: bya ba dang / 'gro nyal 'dug pa dang longs
NK093(ge)002:13915: spyod byed pa'i spyod lam rnama bzhira ji ltar ganga
NK093(ge)002:13916: dang ldana par gnas pa der yang lus la ched
NK093(ge)002:13917: du bcos pa med par ma bcosa rnal mar rang
NK093(ge)002:13918: lugs su gansa para bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:13919: gos rgyan gyi rnam pa gang yang tsha grang gisa
NK093(ge)002:13920: gdunga basa lus sems mi nyen par byed pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:13921: gnoda pa skyob pa de daga gi rkyen tsam lasa
NK093(ge)002:13922: gzhan lhag par bazanga ba dang mdzes pa'i rgyan gyi
NK093(ge)002:13923: phyir du bcosa par mi bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:13924: gnas ganga du yang lus spyod ji ltar bde ba
NK093(ge)002:13925: ltar bag yangs dang ldan par lus dang 'tshams par
NK093(ge)002:13926: sbyar te don dang ldan par bya ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:13927: las dang po pas rang don du spyod par bya
NK093(ge)002:13928: bar ma zad de kho na nyid klong du gyur
NK093(ge)002:13929: kyang gzhan gyi phyir lus spyod dgu po las mi
NK093(ge)002:13930: 'da' bar bya'o // gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK093(ge)002:13931: bya byed mi bcos par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:13932: kha zas mi bcos par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:13933: mtshams bcad pa'i tshul bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:13934: gnas mi bcos par bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:13939: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:13941: rdo rje theg pa gsang ba sngagsa kyi lus kyi spyod yula ni /
NK093(ge)002:13942: spyir bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor sgom lam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:13943: khyad par du yang mthar lam tha ma bdag nyid chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK093(ge)002:13944: lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK093(ge)002:13945: klong yangs chub pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas pasa bya ba gang gis kyang bstangs su med pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:13946: mchod rten mi brtsig pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:13947: glegs bam mi klog pa la sogs pa dgu po mi bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:13948: rnam pa gzhan du na yang blo chen pos gnas
NK093(ge)002:13949: lugs ma bcos par rang grol bya ba med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:13950: don rtogs nas mnyam pa nyid sgom pa'i rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:13951: pa kun gyis kyang ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:13952: dus su / mchod rten brtsigs pa daga gi las
NK093(ge)002:13953: ched du mi bya la glegsa bama klag pa'am gdon
NK093(ge)002:13954: para yang mi bya zhing bris sku dang dkyil 'khor
NK093(ge)002:13955: gyi bya ba sogs gzugas brnyana brtsam pa'i las kyi
NK093(ge)002:13956: bya ba mi bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:13957: de bzhin du rtsol bas don las g.yeng bar 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:13958: bas lag gi phyag rgya mi bcing zhing ngaga gi
NK093(ge)002:13959: sngags bzlas pa byas pas ting 'dzin de la sgribsa
NK093(ge)002:13960: par 'gyur la / rnal 'byor pas su la'ang lus kyi phyag 'tshal bar mi bya ste /
NK093(ge)002:13961: sgom chen gyi phyag lci bas so //
NK093(ge)002:13962: gal te kha na ma tho bas 'jigs na'ang /
NK093(ge)002:13963: phyag gi gnas gang yin pa'i spyi bor lha'am bla ma gnas par byas la phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:13964: nor rdzas sna tshogs rnyed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:13965: mang pos bkur sti bya ba'i ched du blta ba ma yina zhing /
NK093(ge)002:13966: 'jig rten gyi khe sgrub phyir yang ma yina la
NK093(ge)002:13967: gragsa pa 'dod pa'i phyir yang spyad pa min te
NK093(ge)002:13968: de ltar dagu'o // de'i dgos ched ni /
NK093(ge)002:13969: de dag ci yi phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:13970: las dang po pa dang mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal
NK093(ge)002:13971: 'byor pa yang lus brtan na sems brtan la sems
NK093(ge)002:13972: brtan na ting nge 'dzin stobs su 'gyur bas na
NK093(ge)002:13973: / g.yeng ba drug las phyi rola gyi g.yenga ba 'ba' zhig yin pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:13974: shina tu yang bsam gtan gyi dgrar gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:13975: sgo gsum don las g.yenga bar 'gyur ba yina pa'i
NK093(ge)002:13976: phyir gyi gtan tshigs nges na don mnyam pa'i ngang
NK093(ge)002:13977: du blo mi phebs te de la nye ba ma
NK093(ge)002:13978: yina par don las ring bar byed pasa lus 'di
NK093(ge)002:13979: ma bcos rang gnas su rnal mas gansa par bya'o
NK093(ge)002:13980: // 'di dag kyang lus spyod du 'gyur te bsdoms pa'i rnam grangs bco brgyad do //
NK093(ge)002:13985: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:13986: theg pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa gsang sngags su
NK093(ge)002:13987: rigs ngesa shing rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan te bsgom
NK093(ge)002:13988: par 'dod pa'i bsam gtan pasa sku gsung thugs kyi
NK093(ge)002:13989: rdo rje sgrub cing gsang ba sngagsa kyi yon tan
NK093(ge)002:13990: 'byung ba'i gnas su gyur pa'i kha zasa kyi spyod
NK093(ge)002:13991: pa yang ni / lus kyi gzungsa sam gzung 'dzina
NK093(ge)002:13992: cing gso bar byed pa'i rten gyi ched tsam du
NK093(ge)002:13993: bdag rang la ganga ldan te sngar gyi bsod nams
NK093(ge)002:13994: dang mthun par yo byad gang yod dang 'byora ba
NK093(ge)002:13995: ji ltar ldan pa de las ma gtogs par zhim
NK093(ge)002:13996: pa la sogs pa'i ro la chags pas zas kyi
NK093(ge)002:13997: don gyi phyir ched du gnyer nas bsgrub par mi
NK093(ge)002:13998: pa yang ni / bya ba dang / lus kyi
NK093(ge)002:13999: drod rgyas te matshaga par re ba dang nyamsa bskyed
NK093(ge)002:14000: pa'i phyir kha zas za zhing btsal ba ga la
NK093(ge)002:14002: bsam pa mi dmigs pa'i don dang ma bral bas
NK093(ge)002:14003: kha zas ched du ma bcosa par g.yo sgyu spangs
NK093(ge)002:14004: pas rnal ma rang thad tsam du ji bzhina par
NK093(ge)002:14005: baza'i zhes bza' bar bya yi /
NK093(ge)002:14006: 'tsho ba'i zas kyi ched du chags shing zhen pas
NK093(ge)002:14007: g.yos kyi bye brag sna tshogs kyis bcosa shing bsgyur
NK093(ge)002:14009: zas kyi nang nas ro zhim pa la chagsa pa
NK093(ge)002:14010: dang mi zhim pa la ma chagsa pas spang len
NK093(ge)002:14011: mi bya bar blang dor med par bya ba dang
NK093(ge)002:14012: / gzhan gyis 'tsho ba sbyar ba lta bur rang
NK093(ge)002:14013: la kha zas yod bzhin du lhag par chags pas
NK093(ge)002:14014: blang bar bya ba ma yina zhing bsod snyoms dang
NK093(ge)002:14015: slong mosa 'tsho bar yonga ye mi bya ste /
NK093(ge)002:14016: ci yi phyir na gtan tshigs ni bdag gzhan dang
NK093(ge)002:14017: gnyis ka dang chos kyi dona du mi 'gyur ba'i
NK093(ge)002:14018: phyir te slong ba la mi dga' ba 'ong bas
NK093(ge)002:14019: g.yeng ba skyes na bdag gi don du mi 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:14020: ba dang / rkyen des pha rol po la chags
NK093(ge)002:14021: sdang skyes na kho'i don du mi 'gyur bas na
NK093(ge)002:14022: don gnyis dang bral ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:14023: 'tsho ba yongsa su ma daga pa zhes bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:14024: de ltar bdun kyang rtsa ba'i dbang gis lus spyod du 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:14029: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14031: ji skad du ye gdal ba las phyi nang bdag gzhan med //
NK093(ge)002:14033: chos nyid la mtshamsa meda pa'am yang na sngar mtshams
NK093(ge)002:14034: dang mi ldan pa lasa phyis dgon par nyams pa'am
NK093(ge)002:14035: bsam dgra rnams gcod cing lam pas 'grus par 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:14036: ba'i phyir grong yul na gnas kyang rung ste ma
NK093(ge)002:14037: 'drul bar matshamas gcoda par byed pa 'di ni rnal
NK093(ge)002:14038: 'byor pa lta sgom can gyi las su bya ba
NK093(ge)002:14040: des na phyi'i rtog rgyun bcad de shesa bya dam
NK093(ge)002:14041: pa'i ngo bo nanga gi sems kyi chos nyid la
NK093(ge)002:14042: sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gyi thabs la brten nas nges
NK093(ge)002:14043: pa'i dona du 'juga pa yi dus kyi tshe na
NK093(ge)002:14044: phyi rol yul du gyur pa yi 'du 'dzi dang
NK093(ge)002:14046: bsam gtan mchog gi lam gyi bar du gcoda pa
NK093(ge)002:14047: basla zhing spang ba'i dgos ched kyi phyir du phyi
NK093(ge)002:14048: yi grong yul lam 'gro ba gzhan gyi gnas dang
NK093(ge)002:14049: / nanga gi rang gnas kyi sa mtshamsa su gyur
NK093(ge)002:14050: pa'i bar du rang nyid phyir 'gro ba dang gzhan
NK093(ge)002:14051: rnams nang du 'onga ba'i rgyu 'grul rnams gcad para
NK093(ge)002:14052: bya ba'i rtags tho yang brtsigs par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:14057: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14058: de ltar mtshams bcad pa'i gnas der lus ji ltar spyad zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:14059: gcig char ba'i rnal 'byor mchog su zhig bsgom pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14060: tshe blo che ba gang gi yul ni thams cad
NK093(ge)002:14061: rang rig pa'i ngo bor 'od gsal bar shar ba
NK093(ge)002:14062: la lus sems gansa par bya ba'i gzhi rten ma
NK093(ge)002:14063: dmigs te ngo bo med par rtogs pas lus gnas
NK093(ge)002:14064: kyi rang bzhin ma grub pa'i phyir gnas de yang
NK093(ge)002:14065: ched du bdera zhes bde bar bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14066: chos nyid kyi ngang la lus bcos pas kha na med de /
NK093(ge)002:14067: mkhan po gnyan dpal dbyangs kyis /
NK093(ge)002:14068: lus sems ma skyes gzhi med pas //
NK093(ge)002:14069: mkha' ltar bcos pa'i kha na med //
NK093(ge)002:14071: sgyu ma bzhin du lus shes na //
NK093(ge)002:14073: spyod lam gsum gyis gnas pa gang //
NK093(ge)002:14074: ched du bya med byed pa'ang med //
NK093(ge)002:14076: de bas na lus skyil krung la sogs pa chos drug gis bcos par mi bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:14077: 'o na de dag skyon nam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:14078: gang zhig lus gnas la zhena zhing chags pas gnas
NK093(ge)002:14079: su lus 'chosa pa'i spyod lam ched du spyod par
NK093(ge)002:14081: lus gnas bcos pas yang dag pa'i don la bslad de sel zhugs pa yina no //
NK093(ge)002:14082: de bas na lo ts+aa ba ka ba dpal brtsegs kyis lta rim snang ba bcu bdun pa las /
NK093(ge)002:14083: lus ngag ma skyes gzhi med phyir //
NK093(ge)002:14084: skyil krung smra bcad kha na med //
NK093(ge)002:14085: de bzhin sems kyang dngos bral bas //
NK093(ge)002:14086: rtog spangs sgom pa'i khar mi 'ong //
NK093(ge)002:14087: de ltar rtogs pa'i sgom pa po //
NK093(ge)002:14088: yal bar 'dug pa nam yang med //
NK093(ge)002:14089: ci phyir bdag nyid de phyir te //
NK093(ge)002:14090: rang gi dbyings las g.yos pa med //
NK093(ge)002:14092: blo mchog tu che ba'i sgom pa pos bsam gtan
NK093(ge)002:14093: byed pa'i dus su lus sems kyi dngos po ye
NK093(ge)002:14094: ma dmigs pas dbena pa rang gnas yin pa la
NK093(ge)002:14095: lus su mthong nas ched du bcosa par mi bya'o
NK093(ge)002:14096: // 'on kyang lus sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal
NK093(ge)002:14097: ba de la lus sems kyi dngos po de las
NK093(ge)002:14098: dbena pas ma bcosa ma bslad pa de nyid ye
NK093(ge)002:14099: nasa chos nyid mtha' thams cad las ring bas dbena
NK093(ge)002:14100: pa'i gnas mchog dam pa nyid de 'di ni rnal
NK093(ge)002:14101: 'byor chen po mchog gi spyod yul kho na'o //
NK093(ge)002:14102: der ma zad don chen po spyod pa bas ri
NK093(ge)002:14103: phug dang dgon pa dag mkhar len gyi bya bas
NK093(ge)002:14104: gazhala med khang du bcos par mi bya ste /
NK093(ge)002:14106: ri phug la sogs pa'i ngo bo de nyid sems
NK093(ge)002:14107: kyi rang bzhin ye ji bzhin pa blos dapaga tu
NK093(ge)002:14108: med pa'i gnas lugs ma bcos ma bslad pas chos
NK093(ge)002:14109: nyid zab mo byed pas ma byas pa'i ngang gi
NK093(ge)002:14110: thig le'i ngo bo 'di ni ye gdod ma nas
NK093(ge)002:14111: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad kyi bzhugs gnas
NK093(ge)002:14112: rmada du byung ba'i gzhal med khang chen por /
NK093(ge)002:14113: lam pa'i blos byed pa meda par ranga byung ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:14115: bsam gtan lus ni gtsor byed dang //
NK093(ge)002:14116: gnas bde lus kyi phyag rgya kun //
NK093(ge)002:14117: mtshan mar mngon par zhen las byung //
NK093(ge)002:14118: mtshan med sems la bya brtsal med //
NK093(ge)002:14119: smig rgyu bzhin du lus red na //
NK093(ge)002:14120: gnas dang phyag rgyar dmigs pa med //
NK093(ge)002:14121: byed spyod ched du sten byed cing //
NK093(ge)002:14122: bya med bya ba'i dmigs pa'ang med //
NK093(ge)002:14123: de nyid ma skyes gzhi med pas //
NK093(ge)002:14124: gnas der lus bcos kha na med //
NK093(ge)002:14125: zhen par 'chos lam spyod byed pa //
NK093(ge)002:14126: de nyid gzung 'dzin rnam rtog ste //
NK093(ge)002:14127: bsam gtan lus dben dben ma yin //
NK093(ge)002:14128: mkha' la sems dben dben pa'i mchog /sems nyid dben pa'i gnas yin te //
NK093(ge)002:14130: bla gab ri phug gzhal med min //
NK093(ge)002:14131: sems nyid dpag yas gzhal med mchog /ces gsungs te
NK093(ge)002:14132: gang zhig ri phug 'chos pa la ni dgon par
NK093(ge)002:14133: zhen pa yod pas de dag bsal ba'i ched du'ang
NK093(ge)002:14134: mi 'chos pa'o // 'o na gtan nas dgon pa dang du mi blang ngam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:14135: de ltar thag chod nas dgon par 'byung ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14136: gnas nyams dga' bar bya ba ni 'dzin pa med
NK093(ge)002:14137: pas bya ba dang gang yang spang bya min pas
NK093(ge)002:14138: mi 'gal bar the tshom med do //
NK093(ge)002:14139: de dag gi rnal 'byor mchog gi lus spyod de
NK093(ge)002:14140: rnam grangs bsdoms nas nyi shu rtsa brgyad du 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:14145: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14146: rnal 'byor chen po'i rdo rje ngaga gi spyod yul bstan pa yanga /
NK093(ge)002:14147: bla ma dang grogs dama pa dang chos dang mthun
NK093(ge)002:14148: par bya ba'i dgos ched du snyan par smra ba
NK093(ge)002:14149: dang / de las gazhana du kha gasga la sogs
NK093(ge)002:14150: pa kha gtogs dang ga zha'am ku re dang rta
NK093(ge)002:14151: gad bya ba mina la smra zhing brjod pa thams
NK093(ge)002:14152: cad mi 'gyur par ngesa par bden pa nyid du
NK093(ge)002:14153: dang / smra ba dang / smra ba'i don ji
NK093(ge)002:14154: lta bar rdzun med par drang por 'gyur ba'i gsonga
NK093(ge)002:14155: por smra zhing tshig de las phyis mi 'gyur bar
NK093(ge)002:14156: dang / smra ba dang / bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14157: ngag gis ji ltar brjod pa de bzhina du don
NK093(ge)002:14158: kyang de dang mthun par bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14159: skabs dang dgos ched med par thamsa cad kun tu smra ba ma yin pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14160: ngag gis gang brjod cing rjod byed kyi tshig de
NK093(ge)002:14161: brjod bya'i dona dang 'brel bar don dang ldan par
NK093(ge)002:14162: bya ba dang / gzhan gyis dris pa dang kha
NK093(ge)002:14163: ta lta bu skabas dang dgosa ched yod pa ma
NK093(ge)002:14164: gtogsa par de ltar ma yin pa kun tu ci
NK093(ge)002:14165: thod thod du rnam par 'achala ba'i gtam mang po
NK093(ge)002:14166: smra bar bya ba mina pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14167: smra brjod kuna la dpesa mtshona te don gyi thog
NK093(ge)002:14168: tu dabba nas go nges su 'jal bar byed pa
NK093(ge)002:14169: dang / chos thams cad tshad mas gzhal te don
NK093(ge)002:14170: sgro skur med par smras pas bdag kyang tshad mar
NK093(ge)002:14171: smra ba'i tshig gi rjod pa can du bya ba
NK093(ge)002:14172: dang / dang / spyod pa ched du ma bcosa
NK093(ge)002:14173: par don la nganga gisa gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK093(ge)002:14174: dam pa yis rdo rje ngaga gi spyod pa de
NK093(ge)002:14175: ltar yin par ston pa mchog gis bashada de bka'
NK093(ge)002:14176: stsal ba yin pas rnal 'byor mchog gi ngang gi
NK093(ge)002:14182: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14183: rdo rje gsang ba'i theg pa chen po'i yida kyi spyod yul bstan pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:14184: blo ched du ma bcosa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14185: don gyi ngang las yul la ma g.yosa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14186: don la'ang yid kyis ched du bsam pa dang bral ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14187: rtogs pa'i don las mi g.yenga ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14188: mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin ma rmugsa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14189: rtog pa'i zug rngu dang bral te dgongs pa gasla zhing gansa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14190: 'doda pa'i yul la zhen pa med pas ma chagas pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14191: rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang sems nyid rang la sgro skur gyi bsam pa dang bral ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14192: yon tan la bzang por bltas nas blang ba med
NK093(ge)002:14193: cing skyon la ngan par dmigs te dora ba med
NK093(ge)002:14194: pa dang / chagsa sdang gi sems kyi yid byed med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14195: nyes pa 'achaba sems med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14196: yon tan gyi che bas spyoma pa med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14197: de bzhin du nor rdzas dang rnyed 'byor la tshol
NK093(ge)002:14198: zhing chags pa'i sems dang ldan pa mina pa dang
NK093(ge)002:14199: / rig pa phyogsa ris dang bral bar rtogs pa
NK093(ge)002:14200: dang mu mtha'i snang ba med par bsam pa yongas
NK093(ge)002:14202: don gnyis sgrub pas dam bca' ba'i go cha bgosa
NK093(ge)002:14203: nas sgo gsum gyi gzhung lam nyid drang por srong
NK093(ge)002:14204: ba dang / ma dag pa'i lta ba'i duga bdud
NK093(ge)002:14205: rtsir 'gyur bas ting nge 'dzin gyi sman srel zhing
NK093(ge)002:14206: yang dag pa'i lta ba'i gdeng gis mtshona cha ldana
NK093(ge)002:14207: ba dang / pa dang / gnyis med kyi lta
NK093(ge)002:14208: ba'i ngang las mi 'gyur bas rdo rje'i rdzonga la
NK093(ge)002:14210: byang chub kyi sems yida bzhina nora bu 'chang bar
NK093(ge)002:14211: byed pas zhi lhag gi blo grosa dang ldan pa
NK093(ge)002:14212: dang / lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gdeng du
NK093(ge)002:14213: chud de ganga du yang mi 'gyur bas rkyen ganga
NK093(ge)002:14215: rang rig mnyam pa'i dbyingsa 'dira chos kun dbyer med
NK093(ge)002:14216: pas bdag gzhan thams cad dang ngang gciga pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:14217: du rtogs par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:14218: gdul bya ganga gi blo la mngona par snang zhing gsal ba'i ched dam /
NK093(ge)002:14219: yang na dbyings rtogs pas lta ba brtan pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:14220: spyod pa kun nas yongas su legs pa'am che ba'i
NK093(ge)002:14221: yon tan rang snang bas mdzesa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14222: de ltar mi mthun pa med pas bdud rtsi'i gnas kyi bag yoda dang ldan pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14223: chos kyi de nyid rtogs pa'i dabnga lasa phyin ci
NK093(ge)002:14224: log gi sems med pas khrel yod dang mi 'bral
NK093(ge)002:14225: ba dang / sems nyid de la nga rgyal gyis
NK093(ge)002:14226: rlom pa'am nga bdag tu 'dzin pa meda pasa sems
NK093(ge)002:14227: kun dang mthun pas thams cad la yongsa su ldan
NK093(ge)002:14228: te zhi ba'i sems dang ldan par bya ba dang
NK093(ge)002:14229: ba dang / / chos thams cad ril zhi ba
NK093(ge)002:14230: chen po'i chos nyid de yin par rtogs pasa sems
NK093(ge)002:14231: mchog tu ngesa par bya ba'am don de go bar
NK093(ge)002:14233: gang 'dira chos thams cad stong pa nyid pas bsam pa cira yang mi rtog pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14234: chos nyid rtogs pa'i de kho na nyid kyi zhi
NK093(ge)002:14235: ba dang ldan pasa sems 'khrugsa pa med pa dang
NK093(ge)002:14236: / bdag nyid kyi dbyings las ma gtogs par gzhan
NK093(ge)002:14237: ganga nasa kyang dngos grub dang yon tan ci yanga
NK093(ge)002:14238: mi 'byung basa sems nyid las gazhana du dngos grub
NK093(ge)002:14239: dang yon tan tshol ba'i sems pa meda pa dang
NK093(ge)002:14240: / / zanga zinga la 'dod cing chags pa meda
NK093(ge)002:14241: pasa tshul mi 'chosa te bcos ma'i tshul 'chos mi
NK093(ge)002:14242: / / byed pa dang / 'dod yon gyi yul
NK093(ge)002:14243: la sems chags pas gdunga ba med pasa de dang
NK093(ge)002:14244: phrad par 'doda pa'i bsam pa med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14245: sems ci la'ang ma chagsa pa'i don gyi ye shes
NK093(ge)002:14246: rang 'byung du shar basa chog par 'dzina pa dang
NK093(ge)002:14247: ldan pa dang / dngos po ganga ci la'ang rang
NK093(ge)002:14248: rig par rtogs pa'i phyir mtshan mar rtog cing rnam
NK093(ge)002:14249: par mi 'dzina pasa gatsanga sme meda cinga dus gsuma
NK093(ge)002:14250: la snga phyir lta ba'ang meda pas de bzhina nyid
NK093(ge)002:14251: la dama par bltas nas dang du len pa'ang yoda
NK093(ge)002:14252: pa ma yina par bya ba ste de ltar sum
NK093(ge)002:14253: cu rtsa bdun gyis sems kyi spyod pa yang dag
NK093(ge)002:14254: ldan pa dang / par bstan pa'o // de lta
NK093(ge)002:14255: bas na rang rig pa chos kyi sku semas nyid
NK093(ge)002:14256: nam mkha'i rang bzhin chos nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14257: snying po de la 'gro ba rnams kyis glo bur
NK093(ge)002:14258: du brtags pa'i rtog pa sprin lta bu rnams kyis
NK093(ge)002:14259: gtibsa shing spungsa pasa sgrib nas sems kyi rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:14260: ma rtogs pa de nyid yang dag pa'i shesa raba
NK093(ge)002:14261: kyi rlung gisa chos nyid kyi ngang du rang dengs
NK093(ge)002:14262: par byas nas ma gtora bar skye bo ma grangs
NK093(ge)002:14263: pa ga zha makhana gyi rta gad skyed pa dang
NK093(ge)002:14264: mtshungs pa'i 'jig rten gyi spyod pa bzha' le ba
NK093(ge)002:14265: dang 'dra ba lta bu yisa sgrib pa basla zhing
NK093(ge)002:14266: dag pas chos nyid kyi don gasla bar 'doda pa
NK093(ge)002:14267: nyid ni tshi chad pa'i phyir dpe ji ltar na
NK093(ge)002:14268: chus gshera bar byas pas byis pa dag nyi ma
NK093(ge)002:14269: sprin dang ldana pa'i grib ma yisa shina tu sgrib
NK093(ge)002:14270: para gyur nas grang bas sbrebs pa na byis pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14271: ranga bzhina ci yang mi shesa pas sprin chen 'dusa
NK093(ge)002:14272: pa'i phung po de la rang gi kha yi phu
NK093(ge)002:14273: btab pa'i dbugsa kyis bus par byas nasa sprin basla
NK093(ge)002:14274: ldan pa dang / par bstan pa'o // te /
NK093(ge)002:14275: nyi ma'i 'od snang gasla bar 'doda pa dang 'dra
NK093(ge)002:14280: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14281: grogs po dag /bshad pa de dag ni de ltar
NK093(ge)002:14282: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa'i rang bzhina du shes par
NK093(ge)002:14283: bya'o // zhesa thos pa dam pa phyin ci ma
NK093(ge)002:14284: log par bgros te spyod pa'i ngo bo bstan pa'o
NK093(ge)002:14286: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK093(ge)002:14287: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i gsang sngags kyi lta ba
NK093(ge)002:14288: rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyi rang bzhina gyi rnam grangs
NK093(ge)002:14289: bzhi nges par bstan pa'i le'u zhes bya ste /
NK093(ge)002:14290: lnga bcu rtsa bduna pa nyid rnam par bkrol te
NK093(ge)002:14291: bshad pa'o ////gsum pa ljon shing bskyed par bya ba
NK093(ge)002:14292: la gsum ste / mdor bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:14299: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14300: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK093(ge)002:14301: de nas yang 'khor lang ka'i badga po la sogas
NK093(ge)002:14302: pa byang chub semas dapa'a semas dpa' chen po rnams
NK093(ge)002:14303: kyis ston pa gsang ba pa'i badga po la yongsa
NK093(ge)002:14305: kye gsang ba pa'i badga po /
NK093(ge)002:14306: nyid kyis zhe lnga pa chos kyi rnam grangs bcur bkod pa las //
NK093(ge)002:14309: zhesa dama baca'a bar gsungsa pa de nyid /
NK093(ge)002:14310: rtogs pa dang goms pa'i thabs gang gis tshul ji ltar yongsa su shes par bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:14311: spyod yul gyi dngos po de ganga gi ljon shing lagas /
NK093(ge)002:14312: zhesa dri ba gnyis ni shes par bya ba'i thabs dang spyod yul gnyis te /
NK093(ge)002:14314: ston pa gasnga ba pa'i badga posa lan smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK093(ge)002:14315: kye grogsa po dag /ces bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:14316: shinga gi ngo bo ni byang chub sems kyi ljon shinga zhes bya ba ste /
NK093(ge)002:14317: rims kyis 'phel ba dang 'bras bu lhun rdzogs su rgyas par 'gyur bas so //
NK093(ge)002:14319: gong na med cing rtogs par dka' bas bla na
NK093(ge)002:14320: med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK093(ge)002:14321: go 'phang gi 'brasa bur mchog tu smin par 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:14322: basa ganga sangs rgyas dang sems can chos nyid dang
NK093(ge)002:14323: chos can lam pa dang 'bras bu mtha'a dag gi
NK093(ge)002:14324: ngo bo nyid kyi srog 'dzin pa'i gsos su 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:14325: te sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dang rnam
NK093(ge)002:14326: rol cir yang 'char ba'i phyir te /
NK093(ge)002:14327: de bas na skal pa mchog ldan rnams kyis de
NK093(ge)002:14328: lta bu'i rdo rje ltar gyur ba'i ljon shinga dam
NK093(ge)002:14329: pa de nyid don la 'jug rim bcu tshan gyi
NK093(ge)002:14330: sgo nas bskyed par bya ba la brtson par bya'o
NK093(ge)002:14331: // grogas po dag de'i tshul nye bar bstan pa 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:14332: rdzogs par bskyed pa'i nges tshig gi go nas rim par sbyor ba'i tshul bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14333: chos nyid dbyings kyi rang bzhin chos rnams kyi de
NK093(ge)002:14334: kho na nyid 'dus ma byas pa'i ngo bo rdo
NK093(ge)002:14335: rje lta bu'i chos lnga dang ldan pa'i snyinga po'am
NK093(ge)002:14336: bcud du gyur pa'i rtsa ba chen po de la
NK093(ge)002:14337: / gdod nas 'khor ba'i gzung 'dzin dang lam pas
NK093(ge)002:14338: rtsol ba'i rtog pa ganga gi zug rngu dang 'tshe
NK093(ge)002:14339: ba phra rags kun rnam par byang zhing dag pa
NK093(ge)002:14340: dera 'khor 'das kyi chos ma lus pa mtha' dag
NK093(ge)002:14341: yongas su chub ste lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bor
NK093(ge)002:14342: rdzogsa pa la ni byang chub sems kyi ljon shing
NK093(ge)002:14343: zhes bya ste gsang sngags dam pa 'di nyid do
NK093(ge)002:14344: / // des na rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK093(ge)002:14345: ganga gi dgongas pa mthar thug pa de nyid ngesa
NK093(ge)002:14346: par bskyed de gsal bar 'grel pas don rtogs te
NK093(ge)002:14347: rnam par rtog pa bsal bar byed pa'i thabs kyi
NK093(ge)002:14348: sgo nas don la rim par sbyor ba'i skabas su
NK093(ge)002:14349: rnam grangs bcu tshan gyis bashada pa de dag rnams
NK093(ge)002:14350: / // / de ji lta bar ma nod pa
NK093(ge)002:14351: nyid rigs can dam pa khyod rnams la rnam par
NK093(ge)002:14352: bgro ste yang dag par bshad para bya yis gzhan
NK093(ge)002:14353: du ma yengs par rna ba lhogs la nyon cig
NK093(ge)002:14355: 'dir lam rim gyis pa la don la rim par 'jug tshul du nges la /
NK093(ge)002:14356: cig char ba'ang bgrod pa myur bas rim pa med
NK093(ge)002:14357: pa las don la rtogs rims tshang zhing rdzogs par
NK093(ge)002:14358: mngon no // gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK093(ge)002:14359: sems nyid don la sbyor ba'i skabs bcu bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:14360: de dag gi skabs su 'byung ba'i rig pa byang chub kyi sems bcu bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:14361: de rnams mtshon par byed pa'i dpe bcu bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:14362: de gsum sbyar te shin tu gsal bar bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:14367: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14368: de zhes gdams pa la snyegs pas mtshan ma med
NK093(ge)002:14369: pa'i don la 'jug pa'i lam gyi gzhi la ljon
NK093(ge)002:14370: shing bskyed pa'i thabs kyis skabs rnams rgyu dang 'bras
NK093(ge)002:14372: rgyal ba'i dgongas pa nges par 'grel pa las don
NK093(ge)002:14373: la yang dag par sbyor ba'i skabsa chen po ni
NK093(ge)002:14375: tshogs kyi lam sa dang po la yul chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:14376: rtogs par 'dod de 'duna pa skyed pa'i gnas skabs
NK093(ge)002:14377: dang / sa gnyis pa la de la rtsol ba drag pos sbyor ba'i gnas skabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:14378: sbyor ba'i lam sa gsum pa la mtha' bcu'i bslab par 'jug pa'i gnas skabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:14379: sa bzhi pa la 'du shes chos su 'gyur ba'i gnas skabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:14380: sa lnga pa la don la sbyor nasa sbyong len
NK093(ge)002:14381: la 'jug pa'i gnas skabs te de rnams zag bcas
NK093(ge)002:14382: so // mthong ba'i lam sa drug pa la chos nyid kyi ro tshor ba'i gnas skabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:14383: sgom pa'i lam sa bdun pa la yul chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:14384: rang gi mtshan nyid la 'jug ste goms pa'i gnas
NK093(ge)002:14385: skabs dang / mthar lam sa brgyad pa la don
NK093(ge)002:14386: dam rnam par mi rtog pa'i rtog chen la phebs
NK093(ge)002:14388: sa dgu pa la de kho na nyid gdenga du gyur pa'i gnas skabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:14389: sa bcu pa la mthar phyin te las su runga
NK093(ge)002:14390: ba'i gnas skabs te de rnams ni zag med do
NK093(ge)002:14391: // de ltar rig pa skad cig ma'i ngo bo'i
NK093(ge)002:14392: rgyun dang bacasa pa'i byang chub semas kyi gnas skabsa
NK093(ge)002:14394: don gyi rjes su 'jug pa yang //
NK093(ge)002:14395: don ni chos nyid snying po la //
NK093(ge)002:14396: rjes su 'jug pa sems yin te //
NK093(ge)002:14397: sems nyid chos la sbyor ba'i skabs //
NK093(ge)002:14398: rnam pa bcu zhes 'dren pas bshad //
NK093(ge)002:14399: bcu gnyis gang dang gang zhe na //
NK093(ge)002:14400: 'dun pa skye ba'i gnas skabs dang //
NK093(ge)002:14401: rtsol ba sbyor ba'i gnas skabs dang //
NK093(ge)002:14402: bslab pa la 'jug gnas skabs dang //
NK093(ge)002:14404: sbyor chen la 'jug gnas skabs dang //
NK093(ge)002:14405: ro nyid tshor ba'i gnas skabs dang //
NK093(ge)002:14406: yul la 'jug pa'i gnas skabs dang //
NK093(ge)002:14407: rtog chen nyid la phebs skabs dang //
NK093(ge)002:14408: de nyid gdeng du gyur pa'i skabs //
NK093(ge)002:14409: las su rung ba'i skabs dang bcu //
NK093(ge)002:14411: de ltar rtsa ba ljon shing gi snying po de
NK093(ge)002:14412: daga gi don rnams rgyun du bsam nas 'bad pa
NK093(ge)002:14414: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg pa chen po'i skabs rnams
NK093(ge)002:14415: su gnas te sems dang chos 'phrad pas don la
NK093(ge)002:14416: phebs pa'i rnal 'byor bcu skabsa bcu yisa mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:14417: pa yang gzhan bshad pa'i rnal 'byor gyi rtsa ba
NK093(ge)002:14418: rnam pa lnga yi khyad par lasa snang bar gyur
NK093(ge)002:14419: pa ste / de yang rnal 'byor bcu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14421: byang chub kyi sems bcu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14424: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu ste bcu phrag tshan drug gis /
NK093(ge)002:14425: skar phran nas tshes bcu drug gi bar lta bu'i
NK093(ge)002:14426: rgyun gyis ngesa par zla ba'i dkyil 'khor cha gang
NK093(ge)002:14427: bar snang ba ltar yongs su rdzogas shing mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:14428: pa'o // de ltar bstan pa bzhina du gnas skabs
NK093(ge)002:14429: kyi shesa par bya pa'i yul thams cad kun la
NK093(ge)002:14430: grangs kyi rnam pa rtsa ba bcu yi bye brag
NK093(ge)002:14431: gi khyad par gyis gong 'og gi mtho dman gyi
NK093(ge)002:14432: rim pa skye bo pa dang po sems bskyed pa
NK093(ge)002:14433: yan chad nasa bzung ste mthar 'bras bu yongs su
NK093(ge)002:14434: rdzogsa pa thob pa'i bar du rim pas don la
NK093(ge)002:14435: sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo 'og nas
NK093(ge)002:14436: gong du 'phar bas snga ma snga ma rgyu dang
NK093(ge)002:14437: phyi ma phyi ma 'bras bu'i tshul gyis ye shes
NK093(ge)002:14438: re re skyes te ganga sgrib pa bcu po de
NK093(ge)002:14439: dag re re nub cing sbyong nus pa'i rtsal dang
NK093(ge)002:14442: gang gis gang mthong zhes pa nas /
NK093(ge)002:14444: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14445: rten gyi gang zag sa dang po yan chad nas
NK093(ge)002:14446: bcu pa'i bar la 'og ma gang gis gong ma
NK093(ge)002:14447: dag gi chos nyid kyi don ganga la sems nyid
NK093(ge)002:14448: rjes su 'jug pas yang dag par rtogs shing mthong
NK093(ge)002:14449: ba'i gnas skabs de dag re re'i tshe la yang
NK093(ge)002:14450: rim par rtogs pa'i riga pa byang chub kyi semas
NK093(ge)002:14451: re 'byung bas don gyi rtogs pa je gsal du
NK093(ge)002:14452: gyur pas gnas skabs bcu'i sgrib pa de nyid byang
NK093(ge)002:14453: chub sems kyi ngang gi rnam pa dera nub ste
NK093(ge)002:14454: ye shes bcu 'char ba yang skabs bcur 'dus te
NK093(ge)002:14455: skye bar 'gyur ba gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:14456: las dang po pas 'khor ba'am mtha' gnyis las 'das
NK093(ge)002:14457: par gsang ba'i don la cung zad g.yo ba'i byang
NK093(ge)002:14459: de nyid stobs su gyur pas 'das pa'am sngags don la smon pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK093(ge)002:14460: de las 'phags te 'bras bu'i rnam pa la lan re ldang ba byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK093(ge)002:14461: mtha' bcu la 'bad pas gnyis med la sbyor ba byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK093(ge)002:14462: shes rab gsum gyi sgo nas don la gnyis med du 'juga pa'i byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK093(ge)002:14463: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mngon sum du mthong
NK093(ge)002:14464: bas rab tu dag'a ba byang chub kyi sems dang
NK093(ge)002:14465: / de nyid sgom pas de las mi 'gyur bar gnas pa'i byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK093(ge)002:14466: thams cad rang riga pa'i ye shes su shar ba'i mgo g.yo ba byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK093(ge)002:14467: de'i ngang la gansa shing yon tan thob pa byang
NK093(ge)002:14468: chub kyi sems dang mthar thug tu rdzogsa te spyi
NK093(ge)002:14469: bor chibs pa'i byang chub kyi sems dang rnam grangs
NK093(ge)002:14471: dgu po de dag re re yi //
NK093(ge)002:14472: skabs su sems dang chos phrad pas //
NK093(ge)002:14473: rig pa byang chub sems re 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:14474: byang chub sems ni gang zhe na //
NK093(ge)002:14475: 'di yi grangs kyang rnam pa bcu //
NK093(ge)002:14476: g.yo ba byang chub sems nyid dang //
NK093(ge)002:14477: de bzhin smon pa byang chub sems //
NK093(ge)002:14478: ldang ba byang chub chen po'i sems //
NK093(ge)002:14479: de bzhin sbyor ba byang chub sems //
NK093(ge)002:14480: 'jug pa'i sems dang dga' ba'i sems //
NK093(ge)002:14481: mi 'gyur ba dang rig pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:14482: gnas pa dang ni rdzogs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:14483: byang chub sems zhes grags pas na //
NK093(ge)002:14484: sems bcu dag tu rgyas pas bshad //
NK093(ge)002:14486: de ltar byang chub kyi sems rnam pa bcu'o //
NK093(ge)002:14491: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14492: ganga gi rtogs pa dang goms pa'i khyad par ltar
NK093(ge)002:14493: byang chub sems kyi gzugsa brnyana ganga yin pa rig
NK093(ge)002:14494: pa la snang ba yi rtags dang /
NK093(ge)002:14495: dngosa po med par ngo bo rang snang dang mthun
NK093(ge)002:14496: par sems skye lugs kyi mtshon par 'gyur pa'i dpe
NK093(ge)002:14497: gnyis thun mong gi rnam grangs su bstan pa ni
NK093(ge)002:14498: / dper na skar ma phra mo lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14499: tha mala du gyur ba'i 'bring po lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14500: chena po yi skar ma shar ba lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14501: zla ba tshesa gcig pa lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14502: de bzhin du tshes gnyisa pa lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14505: tshes lnga pa lta bu dang ni /
NK093(ge)002:14506: tshes brgyad pa lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14507: tshes bcu drug pa cha shas yongs su gang ba lta bur snang ba ste /
NK093(ge)002:14509: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin de //
NK093(ge)002:14510: skabs bcu dag tu sbyor ba na //
NK093(ge)002:14511: gzugs brnyan chos nyid ngo la snang //
NK093(ge)002:14512: gzugs brnyan rang bzhin ji ltar snang //
NK093(ge)002:14513: phra mo tsam gyi skar ma dang //
NK093(ge)002:14514: de bzhin skar ma tha mal pa //
NK093(ge)002:14515: skar ma chen po dag dang ni //
NK093(ge)002:14516: zla ba tshes gcig rnam pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:14517: gnyis dang gsum dang bzhi dang lnga //
NK093(ge)002:14518: brgyad dang bcu drug rnam pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:14519: gzugs brnyan dag tu snang ba ste //
NK093(ge)002:14520: dngos por snang ba cang ma yin //
NK093(ge)002:14521: chu zla lta bur gzung du med //
NK093(ge)002:14522: sems kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:14523: chos nyid gsal ba'i nyi ma gnyis //
NK093(ge)002:14524: yul dang dbang po'i tshul lta bur //
NK093(ge)002:14525: dbyings dang ye shes rang bzhin gsal //
NK093(ge)002:14527: bgrod par byed pa'i thabs chen yin //
NK093(ge)002:14529: 'di dag chos nyid kyi don la mi sbyar bar
NK093(ge)002:14530: rang gi sems kyi skye lugs la sbyar te sems
NK093(ge)002:14531: 'phel zhing bogs su dbyung ba'i mtshon dper byas nas
NK093(ge)002:14532: lam bcu tshan gyi go bskyed par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:14534: 'dun pa skye ba'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14535: rtsol bar sbyor ba'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14536: bslab par 'jug pa'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14537: 'du shes 'gyur ba'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14538: sbyor chen 'jug pa'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14539: ro myong ba yi skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14540: yul la 'jug pa'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14541: rtog chen dag pa'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14542: gdeng du gyur pa'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa /
NK093(ge)002:14543: las su rung ba'i skabs kyi sems dpe dang bcas pa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:14548: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14549: gong du rnal 'byor chen po'i skabs bcu yis /
NK093(ge)002:14550: zhes gsungs pas don gyis thun mong ma yin pa'i lam 'ba' zhig tu 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:14551: sa dang po tshogs lam gyi thog mar skye bo'i
NK093(ge)002:14552: sa dang rgyu'i sa gang nas kyang gsang sngags mchog
NK093(ge)002:14553: 'dir sems skyes kyang 'di nyid rten gzhi las dang
NK093(ge)002:14554: po par 'gyur bas thog ma sngon gyi dus nas
NK093(ge)002:14555: rgyu mtshungs pa yod pa nyid bla ma nyid bla
NK093(ge)002:14556: ma dam pa las rgyud chen po thos pa'i rkyen
NK093(ge)002:14557: gyis bslad nas thun mong ma yin pa'i sgo 'dir
NK093(ge)002:14558: mos shing 'bras bu la 'duna pa dang po skye
NK093(ge)002:14559: ba'i gnas skabsa daga gi tshe de kho na la
NK093(ge)002:14560: sa gnyis gang rung nas 'jig rten gyi chos 'di
NK093(ge)002:14561: rdzun pa mi bden pa yin no snyam du bden
NK093(ge)002:14562: pa gnyis spyi'i lam po che'i mtshan nyid tsam du
NK093(ge)002:14563: shes pas don la go ba dngos med kyang dus
NK093(ge)002:14564: dus su mos pa skyes te sems g.yo ba byung
NK093(ge)002:14565: ba ni sa gnyis la med par mun pa'i shes
NK093(ge)002:14566: pa las 'phags pas lhag pa'i byang chub kyi semas
NK093(ge)002:14568: dper na dbyar gyi char sprin 'thibs pas mun pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14569: sprin rum lta bu yi gseb bam mthongs nas zer
NK093(ge)002:14570: 'phro ba'i skara ma phra mo byung ba dang 'dra
NK093(ge)002:14571: bar snang yang yun thung ste /
NK093(ge)002:14572: de ma thag nub par 'gyur bas raba riba tsam du snang ba nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:14573: blo mun pa lta bu'i gseb las byang chub kyi
NK093(ge)002:14574: sems rgyu rkyen gyi dbang gis de tsam skyes pa
NK093(ge)002:14575: yin pas dus der de lta bu dngos su yang
NK093(ge)002:14577: 'on kyang snang ngo snyam nas brtags na mi mngon
NK093(ge)002:14578: pas me khyer rtsa ba nas bltas na yod kyang
NK093(ge)002:14579: rgyang nas bltas na med pa dang 'dra bar sems
NK093(ge)002:14580: de tsam skyes kyang mi rtag ste grogs ngan gyi
NK093(ge)002:14581: stobs kyis kyang mi gsal bar 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:14586: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14587: sa gnyis pa tshogs kyi lam phyi mar de ltar
NK093(ge)002:14588: 'dun pa g.yo ba'i rgyu la brten nas rtsol ba
NK093(ge)002:14589: dang bcas pas / btsal zhing yul gsang sngags la
NK093(ge)002:14590: sbyor te grub pa dang rtogs par 'dod pa'i gnas
NK093(ge)002:14591: skabsa daga la gsang sngags 'bras bu'i don de nyid
NK093(ge)002:14592: la slob cing rtogs par smon pa'i khyad par gyis
NK093(ge)002:14593: sa 'og ma 'dun pa pa la med pas lhag
NK093(ge)002:14594: pa'i byang chub kyi semsa 'byung zhing skye ste /
NK093(ge)002:14595: de'i tshul ni snga ma bas cung zad gsal yang
NK093(ge)002:14596: mi brtan zhing brtags tu mi bzod pas mun pa
NK093(ge)002:14597: nas shina tu mi gsal ba'i skara ma phal pa
NK093(ge)002:14598: 'bring po dag mthong yang ganga la raba riba can
NK093(ge)002:14599: gyi sprin gyis bsgribs pa lta bu nyid du snang
NK093(ge)002:14600: ba tsam ste / da dung gsang sngags de kho na nyid la zhugs pa ni ma yin te /
NK093(ge)002:14601: don la smon pa tsam du gyur ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:14602: de gnyis ni rnal 'byor dang po'i khyad par ro //
NK093(ge)002:14607: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14608: sa gsum pa sbyor lam dang por de ltar rtsol
NK093(ge)002:14609: ba dang smon pa'i rgyu las gsang mchog theg pa
NK093(ge)002:14610: chen po la zhugs nas bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la
NK093(ge)002:14611: yang dag para 'jug cing slob pa'i gnas skabsa kyi
NK093(ge)002:14612: tshe dag la / bla ma'i stobs dang bslab mtha'
NK093(ge)002:14613: bcu'i mthu yis 'og ma la med pas lhag pa
NK093(ge)002:14614: smon pa las gyen du 'phags te bden gnyis dbyer
NK093(ge)002:14615: med kyi don la skabs su ldang ba byang chub
NK093(ge)002:14617: de'i tshul ni rtsa ba ma rtogs kyang 'od snang
NK093(ge)002:14618: bas dpe ji ltar na mtshan mo me yi 'od
NK093(ge)002:14619: zer chen po ltar ram skar ma chen po'i 'od
NK093(ge)002:14620: lta bur brtag tu yod kyang rang gi mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:14621: mi gsal bas raba riba ltar snang ba nyid skye
NK093(ge)002:14626: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14627: sa bzhi pa sbyor lam gnyis par de ltar bslab
NK093(ge)002:14628: pa dang ldang ba'i rgyu la brten nas sngar gyi
NK093(ge)002:14629: spyod yul las 'phags te gsang sngags yang dag pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14630: don du 'du shesa snga bar 'gyur ba'i gnas skabsa
NK093(ge)002:14631: dag la 'bad rtsol gyis yul du byed de rtogs
NK093(ge)002:14632: pa'i rig pas gsang sngags gnyis med kyi don la
NK093(ge)002:14633: sbyor zhing gtan la 'bebs pa 'og ma las lhag
NK093(ge)002:14634: pa'i byang chub kyi semas 'byung zhing skye ste /
NK093(ge)002:14636: dpe ji ltar na magla me'i 'khora lo myur la rgyun mi 'chad pa lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14637: cung zad gsal la skyed du bya bar yod pas
NK093(ge)002:14638: tshes gciga pa'i zla tshes lta bura snang zhing mthong
NK093(ge)002:14639: ba ni rtags te de yang mun nang nas snang
NK093(ge)002:14645: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14646: sa lnga pa sbyor lam tha mar /
NK093(ge)002:14647: drod rtags kyi rnal 'byor zhes 'du shes 'gyur ba
NK093(ge)002:14648: dang don la sbyor ba'i rgyu la brten nas gsang
NK093(ge)002:14649: sngags mnyam pa nyid kyi don mngon du byed pa
NK093(ge)002:14650: la sbyor ba'i shes rab sbyangs nas lhag pa'i sems
NK093(ge)002:14651: chen po des mthong lam la 'juga par 'gyur ba'i
NK093(ge)002:14652: gnas skabsa kyi tshe dag la /
NK093(ge)002:14653: gnyis su med pa'i don la rnal 'byor mngon sum
NK093(ge)002:14654: gyis 'jug par byed pas sngar gyi lta ba las
NK093(ge)002:14655: lhag pa'i byang chub kyi semsa skye zhing 'byung ste
NK093(ge)002:14657: dpe ji ltar na btegs pas gsal yang rlung gis
NK093(ge)002:14658: g.yo ba mun par bltams pa'i sgron me lta bu'am
NK093(ge)002:14659: / zla ba tshes gnyis pa lta bur snang ba 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:14660: rtags dang thun mong ba dang skabs kyi sems de
NK093(ge)002:14661: dag gsal mi gsal gyi khyad par sa gong 'og
NK093(ge)002:14662: ltar sems kyi skyed du 'phar bas phye ba dang
NK093(ge)002:14663: / 'og ma las lhag pa'i sems su gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:14664: bshad pa dang 'chad pa ril rjes su mthun no
NK093(ge)002:14665: / // de gsum rnal 'byor gnyis pa'i khyad par ro //
NK093(ge)002:14670: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14671: sa drug pa mthong ba'i lam du /
NK093(ge)002:14672: shes rab gsum gyis sbyor ba dang 'jug pa'i rgyu
NK093(ge)002:14673: la brten nas gsang sngags ji bzhin pa skye ba
NK093(ge)002:14674: med pa'i sems kyi chos nyid ma nor ba'i don
NK093(ge)002:14675: rtogs te ro myong zhing bden pa mthong ba yi
NK093(ge)002:14676: gnas skabsa daga tu gyur pa la /
NK093(ge)002:14677: sngar de lta bu med pas 'khor bar mi ldog
NK093(ge)002:14678: cing zag med kyi mthong ba mthar phyin par myong
NK093(ge)002:14679: nas longs sku mthong bas shin tu dag'a ba dang
NK093(ge)002:14680: ldan par mchog tu lhag pa'i byang chub kyi semsa
NK093(ge)002:14681: 'byung ste skye zhing rig pa la gsal ba ni
NK093(ge)002:14682: dper na bum pa'i snod kyi sgron ma mi g.yo
NK093(ge)002:14684: zla ba tshes gsum pa lta bur don de yang snang ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:14685: de nyid rnal 'byor gsum pa'i khyad par du gzung ngo //
NK093(ge)002:14686: de dag ni shes pa'i mtshan nyid du'ang 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:14687: rtogs pa bzhi la sogs pa'i yan lag gi rkyen dang ldan pas so //
NK093(ge)002:14692: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14693: sa bdun pa sgom pa'i lam du /
NK093(ge)002:14694: de ltar zag med rang gi mtshan nyid rtogs nas
NK093(ge)002:14695: yul chos nyid mthong ba'i ye shes la goms te
NK093(ge)002:14696: nges par 'jug pa'i gnas skabas daga gi tshe la
NK093(ge)002:14697: / lta ba'i gdengs de dang ldan te gnyis med
NK093(ge)002:14698: de nyid rang rig pa'i mngon sum du sgom nas
NK093(ge)002:14699: mthong ba'i don las mi g.yengs pas tshor ba la
NK093(ge)002:14700: sogs pa'i dbang du mi 'gyur ba'i mchog tu lhag
NK093(ge)002:14701: pa'i byang chuba kyi semsa 'byung zhing skye ste /
NK093(ge)002:14702: de'i dus na drod rtags chen po g.yo ba'i skabs te /
NK093(ge)002:14703: sa dang po'i thoba pa dang gnyis pa dang gsum
NK093(ge)002:14704: pa brtana par gyur la bzhi pa nas bdun pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14705: bar gyis nye ba yina pas chos bzhis lung chen
NK093(ge)002:14706: gsang mchog rgyal po'i dgongs don bla na med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14707: rtogs pa dam pa nyid 'byung ma rag pa ste
NK093(ge)002:14708: / de ni dper na zla ba tshes bzhi pa lta bu'i ranga bzhina du snang ba yin no //
NK093(ge)002:14709: 'dir bshad pa'i rang rig mngon sum ni /
NK093(ge)002:14710: gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi ring lugs ltar /
NK093(ge)002:14712: rang byung rang snang chos 'di dag /gnyis med rang rig ma skyes pa //
NK093(ge)002:14713: gsal bar mngon sum the tshom med //
NK093(ge)002:14714: rtogs pa kun gyi mchog tu bshad //
NK093(ge)002:14716: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba las /
NK093(ge)002:14717: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par gnas pa de yang /
NK093(ge)002:14718: lung dang man ngag dang 'gal ba yang ma yin la /
NK093(ge)002:14719: lung dang man ngag gi tshig tsam la brten pa'ang
NK093(ge)002:14720: ma yin par rang gi rig pas blo'i gting du
NK093(ge)002:14721: yid ches pas mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:14722: zhes gsungs pa ltar dmigs pa zung nas /
NK093(ge)002:14723: rnam grangs rnam par phye na /
NK093(ge)002:14725: dbang po drug gi char snang yang //
NK093(ge)002:14726: spyan la mchog tu brjod pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:14727: shes rab yul la dbyer med pas //
NK093(ge)002:14728: mngon sum rtogs pa rtogs pa'i mchog /rang rig ye shes tshogs gcig pu //
NK093(ge)002:14731: shes dang spyod yul gnyis med pas //
NK093(ge)002:14732: thams cad ma lus gcig pa'i ngang //
NK093(ge)002:14733: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal stong gzugs //
NK093(ge)002:14734: lta dang blta bar byar med par //
NK093(ge)002:14735: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK093(ge)002:14736: gang du'ang ma mthong spyan gyi mchog /khyab gsal rang bzhin go ba'i sgra //
NK093(ge)002:14737: thos pa med par thos pa'i phul //
NK093(ge)002:14738: dwang bas tshim byed chos kyi dri //
NK093(ge)002:14739: snom byed med par tshor ba'i shangs //
NK093(ge)002:14740: don bcud nyams su myong ba'i ro //
NK093(ge)002:14741: myong ba'i bya byed med nyid myong //
NK093(ge)002:14742: yang dag don la reg pa nyid //
NK093(ge)002:14743: reg pa kun dngos reg dang bral //
NK093(ge)002:14744: chos khams sna tshogs kun mkhyen pa //
NK093(ge)002:14745: rang rig rgyal por rang snang ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:14746: de bas bdag 'dzin rang gsal ba //
NK093(ge)002:14747: bdag bcas bdag dang bral ba'i yid //
NK093(ge)002:14748: don dang sems can rtog med gsal //
NK093(ge)002:14749: rang byung ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NK093(ge)002:14751: dam pa snga ma rnams kyis shes rab kyi tshogs drug gi nges gsang dam pa'am /
NK093(ge)002:14752: tshogs brgyad kyi lta bar bzhed pa ltar byas nas
NK093(ge)002:14753: skabs don la sbyar na gzhung gi gsang ba dang
NK093(ge)002:14755: de man chad la grags pa'i rang rig mngon sum dang mi 'dra bar shes dgos so //
NK093(ge)002:14756: 'on kyang grub thob chen po ku ku r+aa dzas /
NK093(ge)002:14757: nges don mdo las rgyun grol ye shes basngagasa //
NK093(ge)002:14758: 'phags pa rigs pa can gyis dngos lta smad //
NK093(ge)002:14760: nges don gyi mdo dang rgyud don zab mo ji
NK093(ge)002:14761: bzhin du gzigs pa'i 'phags bod kyi mkhas grub snga
NK093(ge)002:14762: ma rnams kyis tshad ma'i gsung gi gsang ba bzhed
NK093(ge)002:14763: tshul cung zad mi 'dra ba rnams kyang dgongs gzhi
NK093(ge)002:14764: nyid ma nor ba'i don du gnas pa la gzu
NK093(ge)002:14765: bos blos nges pa rnyed na mthar thug gi don
NK093(ge)002:14766: du so so rang rig pa'i ye shes la dgongs
NK093(ge)002:14772: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14773: sa brgyad pa mthar lam dang por /
NK093(ge)002:14774: de ltar 'jug pa dang mi 'gyur ba'i rgyu la brten nas sgom lam mthar phyin pas /
NK093(ge)002:14775: chos thams cad rang rig yul dang bral bas rang
NK093(ge)002:14776: byung gi ye shes su gsal ba'i rtog pa chen
NK093(ge)002:14777: po dag gi ting nge 'dzin shar ba'i gnas skabsa
NK093(ge)002:14779: chos ji bzhin pa gnyis su med par rang rig
NK093(ge)002:14780: pa'i ting nge 'dzin rang gsal bar sgoms te ting
NK093(ge)002:14781: nge 'dzin bye ba brgya la 'jug cing so sor
NK093(ge)002:14782: chos nyan pa dang mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:14783: par ldan pa yul med par mchog tu lhag pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14784: bdag nyid chen po rang byung gi ye shes yin
NK093(ge)002:14785: par wal gyis gsal te rig pa'i cho 'phrul du
NK093(ge)002:14786: snang ba'i byang chub kyi semas 'byung zhing skye ste
NK093(ge)002:14787: / thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi mgo shar
NK093(ge)002:14788: bas der ni mthar phyin pa'i rtagsa chena dang pora
NK093(ge)002:14789: nye bar bsnyen te thog mar don la rnal du
NK093(ge)002:14790: phebs pa'i ye shes nyid dang ldan pa ni dper
NK093(ge)002:14791: na zla ba tshes lnga pa lta bu'i ranga bzhina
NK093(ge)002:14792: du snang zhing gsal bar mthong ba yin no //
NK093(ge)002:14797: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14798: sa dgu pa mthar lam bar pa la de ltar
NK093(ge)002:14799: goms par 'bad pas rtog chen rig pa dag pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14800: rgyu la brten nas rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin shin
NK093(ge)002:14801: tu stobs dang ldan te gdenga can du gyur pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14802: gnas skabsa kyi tshe dag la /
NK093(ge)002:14803: rang rig pa gnyis med chen po mtha' dag bral
NK093(ge)002:14804: ba'i don nyid dang rnam dbyer med par 'bad pa
NK093(ge)002:14805: mi dgos te ngang gis mi g.yo bar gansa pa
NK093(ge)002:14806: mchog tu lhag pa'i byang chub kyi semsa 'byung bas
NK093(ge)002:14807: yon tan du ma la dbang 'byor bar 'gyur te
NK093(ge)002:14808: / dper na shina tu gsal zhing brtan pa'i sgron
NK093(ge)002:14809: ma nyi mas mun pa gazha bral du byas te
NK093(ge)002:14810: phyogs kun tu gsal ba lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:14811: zla ba tshes brgyad pa lta bu'i ranga bzhina du
NK093(ge)002:14812: gsal zhing snang bar 'gyur ba'i mthong ba dag pa
NK093(ge)002:14813: 'byung ste / thams cad mkhyen pa'i rang byung gi
NK093(ge)002:14814: ye shes phyed mngon du byas pa'i dpe yin ni
NK093(ge)002:14815: 'byung ste / zhes gsungs / de'i dus na ston
NK093(ge)002:14816: pa kun gyi bshes gnyen gyis phyag brkyang nas mngon
NK093(ge)002:14817: sum du lung ston pa'i mtha'i drod rtagsa rnams yang
NK093(ge)002:14819: de ltar thog pa nyid na ye shes lnga nyid
NK093(ge)002:14820: skur smin nas chos nyid mi rtog pa'i ngo bor
NK093(ge)002:14821: nges par grub pa yin no zhes bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:14822: spyir sa bdun pa rnal 'byor bzhi pa'i khyad par dang /
NK093(ge)002:14823: brgyad pa dgu pa bcu pa rnams rnal 'byor lnga pa'i khyad par yin yang /
NK093(ge)002:14825: bdun pa brgyad pa dgu pa rnams rnal 'byor bzhi
NK093(ge)002:14826: pa'i khyad par du gsungs pa lta bur bzhugs pa
NK093(ge)002:14827: ni / lung ston pa'i rtags kyi nges tshig dang
NK093(ge)002:14828: bstan par mngon pas tha snyad de ltar bstan kyang
NK093(ge)002:14829: sgom lam pa dang mthar lam pa lung ston tshul
NK093(ge)002:14830: gyi khyad par dbye na sa bdun pa lung chen
NK093(ge)002:14831: ni / thob pa dang / brgyad pa nas rtsal
NK093(ge)002:14832: chen rdzogs pa'i khyad par du 'gyur bar 'grel pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14833: bab kyis dngos don du gsal lo snyam mo //
NK093(ge)002:14838: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14839: sa bcu pa mthar lam tha mal de ltar gdeng
NK093(ge)002:14840: du gyur te ngang gis mi g.yo bar gnas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14841: rgyu las bsgom mi dgos par ting nge 'dzin lasa
NK093(ge)002:14842: su rung ste gnyis med tsam ma yin par lhun
NK093(ge)002:14843: gyis grub par gnyis med kyi tha snyad las grol
NK093(ge)002:14844: bar rang gsal ba'i gnas skabsa dag tu mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:14845: pa'i tshe la dbyings dang ye shes kyang tshig gi
NK093(ge)002:14846: tha snyad tsam du chud de ting nge 'dzin dang
NK093(ge)002:14847: rig pa ye shes kyi rtsal ma 'dres la yongs
NK093(ge)002:14848: su rdzogs par rtogs pas de las skyed du bya
NK093(ge)002:14849: ba med par rdzogsa pa mchog tu lhag pa'i byang
NK093(ge)002:14850: chub kyi semas dam pa mthar thug pa 'byung zhing
NK093(ge)002:14851: skye ba ste / dper na gnyen po med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:14852: sgron ma me chen po rlung gis ma bskyod pa'am
NK093(ge)002:14853: dus mtha'i mes thams cad sregs te mer snang ba
NK093(ge)002:14854: skye ba ste / dang / tshes bcu drug cha
NK093(ge)002:14855: la rdzogas pa'i zla ba nya gang ba lta bura
NK093(ge)002:14856: de bas skyed du byar med pa'i snang zhing gsal
NK093(ge)002:14858: de'i dus na drod rtags chen po bdud dang mi
NK093(ge)002:14859: mthun pa'i phyogs kyis mi 'phrogs par ye shes mi
NK093(ge)002:14860: 'gyur te brtan para ngesa pas mthar phyin pa'i 'bras
NK093(ge)002:14861: bu grub pa chen po yina pas lam yongs su
NK093(ge)002:14867: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14868: 'o na gsang sngags thams cad mnyam pa nyid la
NK093(ge)002:14869: sems bcu dpe bcu skabs bcus ci zhig bya ste
NK093(ge)002:14871: de ltar min par 'gro ba'i semas nyida ye nasa
NK093(ge)002:14872: sangsa rgyas te chos kyi sku'i ngo bo yin yang
NK093(ge)002:14873: / de nyid la rang gi ngo bo ma rig
NK093(ge)002:14874: pa'i rtog pa dang brtags pasa bsgribsa pas ljon shing
NK093(ge)002:14875: de ru ma shesa te don ma mthong ba nyid
NK093(ge)002:14876: rtogs pa'i thabs dam pa rim par 'jug pa'i tshul
NK093(ge)002:14877: gyis rang rig byang chub sems kyi skabs bcu yi
NK093(ge)002:14878: sgo nas ljon shinga mchog nyid bskyed de gong du
NK093(ge)002:14879: / 'phel ba las / de ltar rdzogs shing mthar
NK093(ge)002:14880: phyin pas bla na med pa'i 'bras bur smin te
NK093(ge)002:14881: lhun gyis grub pa yina pas /
NK093(ge)002:14882: dman pa'i lus can khyed cag gis kyang /
NK093(ge)002:14883: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa byang chub sems kyi ljon shing
NK093(ge)002:14884: de nyid dus thams cad du sgoms par gyis shig
NK093(ge)002:14885: pa'o // de bas rtogs pa'i ye shes nyid 'bab
NK093(ge)002:14886: chu ltar bar ma chad par 'phel bas mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:14888: rgyu mtshan des na srin po blo gros thabs ldan
NK093(ge)002:14889: la sogs pa'i grogas po dama pa dag /ces bos
NK093(ge)002:14890: nas / ljon shing gi mtshan nyid 'chad pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:14891: bde bar gshegs pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dama pa
NK093(ge)002:14892: rnamas kyi byang chub semas kyi shing bu ni dus
NK093(ge)002:14893: gsum kun tu yon tan gyi rgyun dang bcas te
NK093(ge)002:14894: dus bzhi'i phyogs ris kyi char ma chad par snang
NK093(ge)002:14895: ba ste / de ltar snang ba yang skad cig
NK093(ge)002:14896: ma'i rgyun las grol te ngo bo ngos gzung med
NK093(ge)002:14897: par dmigs pa'i yul las 'das pa ni 'khrul snang
NK093(ge)002:14898: gzhi dang bcas pa'i 'jug pa chad de don mchog
NK093(ge)002:14899: tu gyur pa dama pa yina no //
NK093(ge)002:14900: de yi tshig gi lhag ma ni /
NK093(ge)002:14901: gal te de ltar snang ba la ngo bo skad
NK093(ge)002:14902: cig ma'i rgyun las grol kyang skabs bcus skad cig
NK093(ge)002:14903: ma'i rgyun chad na mu stegs chad pa'i phyogs su
NK093(ge)002:14904: ltung bar 'gyur bas dam pa min par bstan pa'o
NK093(ge)002:14905: // de lta bur byang chub sems kyi ngo bo'i
NK093(ge)002:14906: don la lam pas skad cig ma'i rgyun du 'bad
NK093(ge)002:14907: de goms pa nyid kyis ni gong nas gong du
NK093(ge)002:14908: bogs dang ldan par gyur te ngesa par 'bras bu
NK093(ge)002:14909: mchog tu smin pa yang ganga byang chub snying po
NK093(ge)002:14910: nyid du lam rnal 'byor lnga dang sa bcus rim
NK093(ge)002:14911: par smin pa'i yon tan rgya mtsho'i dpag bsam gyi
NK093(ge)002:14912: ljon pa nyid ni skyed shinga de yi ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:14913: ste byang chub dama pa bla na med par gyur
NK093(ge)002:14914: ba'i byang chub sems kyi ljon pa'i shing bu mchog
NK093(ge)002:14915: tu rgyas pas 'bras bu dam pa yang dag par
NK093(ge)002:14916: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid du smin ngesa par gyur
NK093(ge)002:14917: // pa'o // ji ltar bgros pa'i khungs dang 'brel bar grogsa po daga bshad pa de daga ni /
NK093(ge)002:14918: ljon shing dama pa ji ltar bskyed pa'i tshul gyis
NK093(ge)002:14919: rgyal ba'i dgongas pa ma nor ba nyid ngeesa para
NK093(ge)002:14922: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa 'dusa pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK093(ge)002:14923: de kho na nyid gasnga ba dama pa byang chub
NK093(ge)002:14924: sems kyi ljon shing bskyed pa'i le'u ste lnga bcu
NK093(ge)002:14925: rtsa brgyad pa nyid rnam par 'grel te bshad pa'o
NK093(ge)002:14926: ////bzhi pa dam par 'jug par bya ba la gsum
NK093(ge)002:14934: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14935: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK093(ge)002:14936: ljon shing bskyed pa bstan ma thag pa de nasa
NK093(ge)002:14937: yang lang ka'i badga po la sogas pa 'khor gyi
NK093(ge)002:14938: byang chub semas dapa'a semsa dapa'a chena po de daga
NK093(ge)002:14939: gisa / le'u zhe lnga pa'i rnam grangs bcu'i bzhi pa'i dri ba yongas su dris pa /
NK093(ge)002:14940: kye gasnga ba pa'i badga po /
NK093(ge)002:14941: nyid kyis dama pa rnams kyi rjesa su 'juga par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:14942: zhesa dama baca'a bar dgongas pa de la /
NK093(ge)002:14943: dama pa rnams kyi rjesa su ji ltara 'juga para bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:14944: de nyid tshul ji ltar yongsa su shes para bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:14945: zhes de skad ces 'jug pa'i thabs dang shes par bya ba'i thabs gnyis yongsa su dris pa las /
NK093(ge)002:14946: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsang ba pa'i badga pos lan smras te gsungs pa /
NK093(ge)002:14947: kye grogsa po dag /dris pa de ni 'di ltar /
NK093(ge)002:14948: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dama pa rnams kyi rjes sam shul ni /
NK093(ge)002:14949: gang ngesa par sngar sangs rgyas par gshegsa pa'i lam
NK093(ge)002:14950: dama pa gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i snying po
NK093(ge)002:14951: chos kyi dbyings yang dag par rtogs pa la bya'o
NK093(ge)002:14953: log par lta ba lam du gzhug lugs ldem dgongs kyis bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:14954: nges pa'i lam du 'jug lugs ma 'dres yongs rdzogs sems kyi gsang lam du bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:14956: ldem dgongs kyis bstan pa dngos bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:14957: de la the tshom za ba dris tshul bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:14958: lan du drang don gyis khrid pa'i thabs tshul gsungs pa /
NK093(ge)002:14959: chos nyid du shes na log pa nyid nges pa'i lam du bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:14963: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:14965: lam dama pa ganga zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:14966: de ltar de nyid bstan pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:14967: skyes bu nyid kyis byung khungs kyi skabs su phyag
NK093(ge)002:14968: na rdo rje kho bos byin rlabs 'byung ba'i bstan
NK093(ge)002:14969: pa rin po che'i gsang ba zab mo mthong zhig
NK093(ge)002:14970: thos pa'i skabsa gciga gi tshe na /
NK093(ge)002:14971: ston pa bshesa gnyena dama pa sku lnga rnams kyis
NK093(ge)002:14972: ngesa par gsungsa pa gang nyid gsan pa'i lo rgyus
NK093(ge)002:14974: rang rgyud pa ni 'khor ba yin kyang rang bzhin ni chos kyi sku yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:14975: 'dir dbyer med kyi bya ba'i rnal 'byor gzhi'i don
NK093(ge)002:14976: 'khor 'das gnyis med gsang sngags ngo bo nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:14977: sku gnyen po med par rang bzhin ma bcos pasa
NK093(ge)002:14978: thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:14979: ril de nyid kyi phyir dang mi mthun pa med pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:14980: log pa'i rnam para rtog pa thams cad ma spangs par rdzogs pa dang ldana te /
NK093(ge)002:14982: lta ba ngan pa rtag pa nyid dang /
NK093(ge)002:14984: de gnyis ni ldem dgongs kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:14985: rang bzhin mi 'gyur ba dang dngos po med pa la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14986: dngos por skye zhing 'gag pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14987: yul la dmigas pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:14989: skye ba med pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK093(ge)002:14990: rang snang mi 'gag pa la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14992: sred pas kun la zhen pa'i 'doda chagsa pa nyid dang /
NK093(ge)002:14993: mnar sems pas zhe sdang ba nyid dang /
NK093(ge)002:14994: kun nas rmongs pas gti mug pa nyid dang /
NK093(ge)002:14995: sems gyong zhing khengs pas nga rgyal ba nyid dang /
NK093(ge)002:14996: gzhan gyi yon tan sems kyi phrag tu mi shong bas phrag doga pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:14997: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med par chags pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:14998: rtog pa'i cho 'phrul la sdang ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:14999: chos nyid kyi ngang la 'byed pa med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15000: mnyam nyid kyi lta ba gshongs su mi 'bab pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15001: mthar 'dzin gyis sgro skur la phrag dog byed pa dang lnga la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15002: 'doda pa lnga ni chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan sems nyid la tshang bar dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15006: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15007: 'doda pasa log par g.yema pa dang gsum nyid /
NK093(ge)002:15009: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes rang stobs kyis len pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15010: chos dbyings la rig pa chags pas 'khor ba las log pa rnams la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15012: ngo bo dang rnam pa'i rdzun smra ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:15015: tshig 'khyal pa smra ba dang bzhi nyid /
NK093(ge)002:15016: phyogs ris mi bden pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15018: log lta tshar gcod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15019: rang bzhin ma nges pa rnams la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15023: log para lta ba nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:15026: 'khor ba las log pa'i yang dag pa'i don la lta ba gsum la dgongs pa nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:15028: pha ma dang dgra bcom gsod pa /
NK093(ge)002:15029: bder gshegs kyi sku la ngan sems kyis khrag 'byin pa /
NK093(ge)002:15030: dge 'dun 'khor lo'am mthun pa'i dbyen byed pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:15031: ye shes lnga la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15032: de dang nye ba lnga ste /
NK093(ge)002:15034: slob dpon dang byang chub sems dpa' gsod pa /
NK093(ge)002:15035: gtsug lag khang gi dkor 'joms pa'am dge 'dun 'du ba'i sgo phrog pa /
NK093(ge)002:15037: mchod rten bshig pa rnams dam tshig ting 'dzin sogs la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15038: yang na ma yang yin la dgra bcom ma yin pa 'dod log gis sun phyung ba /
NK093(ge)002:15039: phyir mi ldog pa'i byang sems nges gnas gsod pa /
NK093(ge)002:15040: 'phags pa slob pa gsod pa ste gzhan gnyis 'dra'o //
NK093(ge)002:15041: phyi nang gi lci ba bzhi la /
NK093(ge)002:15042: nyams pa'i lci ba bzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:15043: skye bo la mi chos kyi mna' lci /
NK093(ge)002:15045: byang sems la sdom pa lci /
NK093(ge)002:15046: sngags pa la dam tshig lci ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:15047: log pa'i lci ba bzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:15052: smad pa'i lci ba bzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:15053: gti mug gi dbang gis 'phags pa'i sku la smad pa lci /
NK093(ge)002:15054: phyogs ris kyi dbang gis dam pa'i chos la blang dor byas pa lci /
NK093(ge)002:15055: nga rgyal gyi dbang gis bden pa'i tshig la smad pa lci /
NK093(ge)002:15056: phrag dog gi dbang gis grogs kyi yon tan la smad pa lci'o //
NK093(ge)002:15057: skur ba'i lci ba bzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:15058: mnyam nyid chos la khyad 'don lci //
NK093(ge)002:15059: rang bzhin ngan la gal 'dzug lci //
NK093(ge)002:15060: mi dge bcu la log lta lci //
NK093(ge)002:15061: mtshams med lnga la khrag 'byin lci //
NK093(ge)002:15063: lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi'i rang bzhin rtogs na spangs
NK093(ge)002:15064: dang rtogs pa'i yo na tan gyi lci ba la
NK093(ge)002:15065: dgongs pa'am / gsang bdag dga' rab dpa' bos spyod pa'i klong las /
NK093(ge)002:15066: gal te mthun pas bkrir btub la //
NK093(ge)002:15067: shan pa smad 'tshong mtshams med pa //
NK093(ge)002:15068: rang bzhin bcas pa'i ma tho kun //
NK093(ge)002:15069: de yis de drang don la sbyar //
NK093(ge)002:15070: nges par dgongs la sgrib mi gnas //
NK093(ge)002:15071: zhes pa ltar rang gi rtogs pa mthar phyin nas /
NK093(ge)002:15072: mthun pas 'dren pa'i thabs mkhas la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15073: log pa'i spyod pa brgyad de phyi'i log pa bzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:15076: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK093(ge)002:15077: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrug pa rnams dang /
NK093(ge)002:15078: nang gi log pa bzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:15081: mched la gdung sems bskyungs pa /
NK093(ge)002:15082: dkyil 'khor gnyan po 'dral ba rnams te /
NK093(ge)002:15090: dam rdzas rnams ma mthun pa'i phyogs las log pa la dgongs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15091: sngar bshad pa ltar sme sha can sha lnga dang /
NK093(ge)002:15095: khu ba la sogas pa bdud rtsi lnga daga /shugs la blo dman pa la sme ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:15096: lam ma rtogs pa la bsting ba yang sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:15097: de lta bu rtog dpyod ngan pa mang po la
NK093(ge)002:15098: ngesa para spyod pa ni 'dir skyes bu dama pa
NK093(ge)002:15099: rnams kyi thar pa'i lam gyi dama pa mchog tu
NK093(ge)002:15100: bstan pa nyid mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa dang
NK093(ge)002:15101: / 'di dag la dga' ba'i 'du shes mthun pa
NK093(ge)002:15102: rnams de'i sgo nas 'dren zhing don la gzhug pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15103: / phyir dang / lam gzhan du zhen pa dgag pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:15104: rang don dang gzhan don gyi spyod pa rna phrug
NK093(ge)002:15105: brag rtsed kyi 'gros su dgongs pas bka' stsal pa
NK093(ge)002:15107: zhes ston pa gsang ba mchog gi bdag pos ngesa
NK093(ge)002:15108: pa dama para rigs kyi bdag po phyag na rdo
NK093(ge)002:15109: rje nyid la gsungsa pa lasa /
NK093(ge)002:15114: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15115: gsang 'dzin phyag na rdo rje kho bosa de yi
NK093(ge)002:15116: tshe ston pa chen po la zhus pa'i tshig nye
NK093(ge)002:15118: rtogs pa'i phyogs nas ston pa la yon tan mnga' bar ngam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15119: gzhi'i rnam 'byor la ngam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15120: lam log par smra bas don la 'dren pa la ngam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15121: thabs gang yang ma spangs pa la ngam pa yin na yang /
NK093(ge)002:15122: ma smin pa'i 'khor gyi bsam pa dang bstun nas /
NK093(ge)002:15123: ston pas lam log pa rnams lam ma nor ba
NK093(ge)002:15124: yang dag tu gsungs pa la ngam nas 'di skada
NK093(ge)002:15126: zhes ngo matshara ba skyes pas /
NK093(ge)002:15127: don rmad du byung ba'i yon tan gyi mnga' bdag
NK093(ge)002:15128: chos kyi rje btsan tshogs gnyis rdzogas pa'i bdag po
NK093(ge)002:15129: rgyal ba sangsa rgyas bcom ldan 'das chos ston pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15130: smra ba dam pa sku lnga'am dus gsum du gshegs
NK093(ge)002:15131: pa rnams kyi dgongs pa rnam dag yang dag pas
NK093(ge)002:15132: brjod pa tshad ma'i gsung gi bstan pa daga ni
NK093(ge)002:15133: lam 'bras rnam par dkar ba yin pa las /
NK093(ge)002:15134: 'di ltar mi dge ba bcu la sogs pa phyin
NK093(ge)002:15135: ci log gi chos kun ma nor ba'i lam du
NK093(ge)002:15136: bka' stsal bar 'byung ba 'di ci lta bu lagas
NK093(ge)002:15137: / zhes de skada zhu ba 'duna pa'i tshul gyis zhus pa lasa /
NK093(ge)002:15139: drang don du bstan pa dngos bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:15140: thabs de ltar bstan pa'i dgos ched bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:15141: tshul de'i mtshon tshul mthun dpes bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15146: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15147: ston pa gsang ba mchog gi mnga' bdag chen po
NK093(ge)002:15148: bshesa gnyena dama pas lan du bka'a stsal pa ni
NK093(ge)002:15149: / 'di ltar bstan pa gang de nyid /
NK093(ge)002:15150: gdul bya phyin ci log gi las la zhena cing chags pa rnams kyang /
NK093(ge)002:15151: ston pa dam pa theg chen gsang ba rgyal po'i
NK093(ge)002:15152: theg pa bye brag mang la yangs pas thabsa mchoga
NK093(ge)002:15153: dapaga gisa mi langa ba'i sprin phung thams cad mkhyen
NK093(ge)002:15154: pa thabs kyi mnga' bdag lags pasa de nyid min
NK093(ge)002:15155: par gzhan gyis mi 'drongs pas na de ltar bstan
NK093(ge)002:15156: cing khrid nas mthar gsang sngags ngesa pa'i dona gyi
NK093(ge)002:15157: sgo 'di la gzud cing 'jug pa'i dgos ched kyi
NK093(ge)002:15158: phyir du / log par lta ba can dag khrida
NK093(ge)002:15159: pa'i thabas su don gnyis med la dgongs te ldem
NK093(ge)002:15160: dgongs sgra ji bzhin ma yin pas phyin ci log
NK093(ge)002:15161: rnams yang dag pa'i lam du bstan cing gsungs pa
NK093(ge)002:15162: phyir du / yina no // gnyis pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:15166: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15167: 'o na de dag la'ang dang po nas zab mo
NK093(ge)002:15168: bstan na ci ma rung ste rnal ma mi ston
NK093(ge)002:15169: pa de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:15170: loga pa'i spyod pa la zhena cing chags pa dag
NK093(ge)002:15171: la thog ma nas ngesa don zab mo sgra ji
NK093(ge)002:15173: blo dang mi 'tshams pas 'jug para mi 'gyur zhing /
NK093(ge)002:15174: der ma zad slar yang mi mos pas de nyid
NK093(ge)002:15175: 'gegs te spong bar 'gyur zhing de'i skyon gyis ngan
NK093(ge)002:15176: song du ltung ba'i rigs rnams kun kyang theg pa
NK093(ge)002:15177: chen po'i sgo 'dis chud ma zos par loga spyod
NK093(ge)002:15178: de lta bu dang mthun pa'i thabas la mkhas pa
NK093(ge)002:15179: nyid kyis gdul bya de nyid drangsa nas don la
NK093(ge)002:15180: khrid na gzod rims kyis gsang sngags rnal ma'i de
NK093(ge)002:15181: nyid la the tshom med par nges pas yid ches
NK093(ge)002:15183: dper na shed ma bye ba'i byis pa me'i nang
NK093(ge)002:15184: du 'jug pa thabs kyis drang ba'i dpe bzhin no
NK093(ge)002:15185: // de'i phyir don chen po la dgongs te thabs
NK093(ge)002:15186: sna tshogs par rang dang mthun pas btsud nas de
NK093(ge)002:15187: nyid la mi gnas par byed pa ni baslu ba'i
NK093(ge)002:15188: // thabsa te / re zhig par bstan pa de
NK093(ge)002:15189: nyid kyis mthar nges pa'i don la gzuda pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:15190: du gdul bya log pa'i lta ba so so la
NK093(ge)002:15191: zhen pas 'dod cing mosa pa dang mthun par thabs
NK093(ge)002:15192: kyi 'jug sgo sna tshogas pa rnams kyis rang rang
NK093(ge)002:15193: gi log pa'i lta spyod rnams dang sgo bstun pas
NK093(ge)002:15194: mthun 'jug gi tshul du cha 'dra ba'i spyod yul
NK093(ge)002:15195: can du sbyar nasa bstan pas gdul bya brida de
NK093(ge)002:15196: mthar gsang sngags dam pa la gzhug pa'i thabas su
NK093(ge)002:15197: gsungsa te bka' stsal bar mdzad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15202: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15203: de'i mtshon dpe brdal shed ma bye ba dang don la shed ma bye ba gnyis ka sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:15204: dpera na loga par spyod pa'i byis pa rnams /
NK093(ge)002:15205: rang gi dngos kyi pha mas 'jigs pas bsdigsa pa
NK093(ge)002:15206: dang dga' bas brida par byed pa'i thabsa kyis ni
NK093(ge)002:15207: / rung ba dang mi rung ba'i bya ba'i lasa
NK093(ge)002:15208: la gzung de lus ngag gi bya brtsal bzang po
NK093(ge)002:15209: ched du 'dzin par gzhug pa ltar /
NK093(ge)002:15210: ston pa rnam 'dren dam pas nyes pa las bzlog
NK093(ge)002:15211: ste bkri drang gi thabs la brten nas thugs brtse
NK093(ge)002:15212: chen dam pasa gsang ba'i dona la rim par 'drena
NK093(ge)002:15213: par mdzad pa'o // 'o na thabs de nyid la
NK093(ge)002:15214: chags pas nyes pas gos par mi 'gyur ram zhe
NK093(ge)002:15215: par mdzad pa'o // na / de yanga dpe ji
NK093(ge)002:15216: ltar na gang zag la la zhiga chu bo chen
NK093(ge)002:15217: po'i pha mthar 'gro bar 'doda pa na /
NK093(ge)002:15218: chu'i klung der gru bo dag la brten nasa brgal
NK093(ge)002:15219: te 'gro yang pha rol gyi mathara sona pa na
NK093(ge)002:15220: gru bo 'bor bar byed pa bzhina du gdul bya
NK093(ge)002:15221: 'dul ba'i thabsa sama theg pa'i bye brag gi rim
NK093(ge)002:15222: pa rnams dang / 'dir log pa'i spyod pa lam
NK093(ge)002:15223: du bka' stsal pa lta bu de dag la brten
NK093(ge)002:15224: pasa don rnal ma la drang ba'i thabsa chen po
NK093(ge)002:15225: yin yang thams cad du ldan pa ma yin te
NK093(ge)002:15226: gsang sngags zab mo'i dona gyi ngesa pa yanga dag
NK093(ge)002:15227: par rnyed ma thag tu chu bo rgal ba'i gru
NK093(ge)002:15228: bzhina du don de dang thabs de nyid la zhen
NK093(ge)002:15229: pa dang rtsol ba'ang mthar 'dora ba nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:15230: rang gi ngo bo 'dor ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:15231: zhen pa 'dor ba gnyis las 'dir lta spyod ngan
NK093(ge)002:15232: pa rang gi ngo bo yang 'dor ba'i dpe dang
NK093(ge)002:15237: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15238: gsang sngags kyi lam ma yin pa med pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:15239: zhen pa dang ngo bo gnyis la mi gnas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15240: tshul desa na gsang ba mchog gi chos kyi dbyings
NK093(ge)002:15241: gnyis su med pa'i de bzhina nyid ma nor bar
NK093(ge)002:15243: lta ba ngan pa thams cada dang spyod pa ngan
NK093(ge)002:15244: pa thams cad ganga yanga rung ste ril dang rig
NK093(ge)002:15245: pa'i ngo bor rtogs te dama pa'i lam du mthong
NK093(ge)002:15246: bas ma spangs par spyod pa nyid kyis mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:15247: par ngesa pas na lam gzhan na med cing 'bras
NK093(ge)002:15248: bu logs su mi tshol ba'i phyir log pa'i lta
NK093(ge)002:15249: spyod kyang spangs mi dgos par grol bas lam thams
NK093(ge)002:15250: cad kyi nanga na nye lam dam pa rmad du
NK093(ge)002:15252: tshul des na skye ba med pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK093(ge)002:15253: shes na dam pa'i lam du ma gyur pa gang
NK093(ge)002:15255: 'o na spyod ngan de ltar gzugs brnyan tsam yin na yang /
NK093(ge)002:15256: lta ngan de nyid ji ltar yod ce na /
NK093(ge)002:15257: chos nyid kyi don mngon du gyur tsa na lta
NK093(ge)002:15258: ngan gyi gzhi yang rang rig pa'i chos nyid du
NK093(ge)002:15259: dag pa yin pas ched du spangs pa ma yin
