NK093(ge)002:15260: par rang grol ba kho na yin no //
NK093(ge)002:15261: de skada ces ston pa mchog gis gsungsa shing bka'
NK093(ge)002:15262: stsal nas de'i tshe phrin las grub pas cang mi
NK093(ge)002:15265: lam shes pa'i dgos pa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:15266: lam rang gi ngo bo bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15271: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15272: de ltar zhus pa'i yon tan gang snyam pa la /
NK093(ge)002:15273: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsang bdag chen pos /
NK093(ge)002:15274: kye grogsa po dag /ces bos nas yon tan gsungs pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:15275: sngar bshad pa'i tshul de bas na /
NK093(ge)002:15276: rgyal ba dama pa rnams kyi gshegs shul gyis rjes
NK093(ge)002:15277: ltar theg pa chen po'i nye lam dama pa mchog
NK093(ge)002:15278: gi sgo 'dira spyad cing zhugsa te rang gi gzhung
NK093(ge)002:15279: las ma nyams na dus snga ma thams cad nasa
NK093(ge)002:15280: phyi ma thams cad dang da ltar gyi rnam pa
NK093(ge)002:15281: thamsa cad kyi bye brag gi lta ba'i don dang
NK093(ge)002:15282: spyod pa'i khyad par ji snyed pa thams cad du
NK093(ge)002:15283: rang snang gi rig pa de nyid gsang sngags kyi
NK093(ge)002:15284: ngo bor shesa shing rtogs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15285: sems kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:15286: rang gi mtshan nyid so so'i bye brag ma 'dresa par phyed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15287: spyi'i mtshan nyid de nyid kyi ngo bor dbyer med par yongsa su rdzogas pa rtogs par 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:15288: tshig lhag ma ni de lta bu'i gdams par 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:15289: des na chos nyid mnyam pa nyid ma rtogs pa
NK093(ge)002:15290: las 'khor ba nyid las nyon gyi rgyu 'bras can
NK093(ge)002:15291: du snang ba'ang / skye ba med pa'i chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:15292: du yongsa su shes para 'doda pas kyang lam 'di
NK093(ge)002:15294: mya ngana lasa 'adsa pa sangs rgyas kyi mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:15295: lam dang 'bras bu'i rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid du
NK093(ge)002:15296: yongsa su shesa par 'doda pasa kyang lam 'di nyid
NK093(ge)002:15298: de bas chos nyid kyi ngo bo 'khor 'das ris
NK093(ge)002:15299: med yin te de'i phyir mnyam nyid rtogs pas 'khor
NK093(ge)002:15300: 'das shes pa'o // gazhana yang sngar le'u bcu drug par bshad pa'i /
NK093(ge)002:15301: rang bzhin bsam gtan las thugs rje bzhi la yan
NK093(ge)002:15302: lag bcu drug ste cho 'phrul chen po nyi shu
NK093(ge)002:15303: thob para 'doda pasa kyang lam dam pa 'di nyid
NK093(ge)002:15305: de bzhin du mthar lam pas gol sgrib ched du
NK093(ge)002:15306: byas pa'i bzang rtog sngar bshad pa lta bu'i rtog
NK093(ge)002:15307: pa'i ri bo brgyad cu rtsa gcig mi dmigs mnyam
NK093(ge)002:15308: pa'i ngang du gzhila bar 'doda pas kyang lam dam
NK093(ge)002:15309: pa 'di yongsa su shes para bya ste /
NK093(ge)002:15311: dngos gzhi'i rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15312: mtshan ma'i rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15313: rtags kyi rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15314: rkyen gyi rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15315: las kyi rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15316: sbyod pa'i rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15317: bskyed pa'i rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15318: zhen pa'i rtog pa dgu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15320: zhes gsungs pas dgrol bar bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:15321: zag pa dang bcas pa'i lam pas ltung ba'i sgo
NK093(ge)002:15322: dgu chada par 'doda pas kyang lam dam pa 'di
NK093(ge)002:15323: nyid yongsa su shes para bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:15325: bdud chen po'i ris su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15326: mu stegs kyi khams su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15327: srin po'i khams su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15328: gnod sbyin gyi ris su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15329: ru tra chen por ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15330: bgegs chen por ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15331: lha chen po'i ris su lhung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15332: sho gam gcan chen gyi ris su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK093(ge)002:15333: dmyal ba chen por ltung ba'i sgo'o //
NK093(ge)002:15335: so so'i mtshan nyid bstan na /
NK093(ge)002:15336: bdud du ltung ba'i sgo ni /
NK093(ge)002:15338: gzhan gyi bsam sbyor bzang po la //
NK093(ge)002:15339: bar chad byed pa bdud yin te //
NK093(ge)002:15340: gzhan gyi rdzas la ser sna byed //
NK093(ge)002:15341: ma rtogs bdud kyi sgor ltung 'khyams //
NK093(ge)002:15343: mu stegs su ltung ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:15345: ma rtogs nga dang bdag 'dzin pas //
NK093(ge)002:15346: gsang sngags lta spyod log pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:15347: brtse med sdig pa kun spyad pas //
NK093(ge)002:15348: mu stegs sgro skur rtag tu 'khyams //
NK093(ge)002:15351: mnyam nyid chos sku ma rtogs par //
NK093(ge)002:15352: rang rgyud chags sdang pho tshod spyod //
NK093(ge)002:15353: snying rje med par gsod la dga' //srin po'i sgor ltung dmyal bar skye //
NK093(ge)002:15355: gnod sbyin du ltung ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:15356: ma rtogs mthu che tshad med kyang //
NK093(ge)002:15357: nga rgyal dregs pa'i nyon mongs can //
NK093(ge)002:15359: gnod sbyin sgor ltung rtag tu 'khyams //
NK093(ge)002:15362: ji bzhin ma nor ma rtogs par //
NK093(ge)002:15363: log rtog spyod cing sna tshogs spyod //
NK093(ge)002:15364: rang gis mi shes gzhan 'grol ba //
NK093(ge)002:15365: ru tra'i sgor ltung dmyal bar skye //
NK093(ge)002:15368: ma rtogs phrin las ci mkhas kyang //
NK093(ge)002:15369: tshig la dngos por 'dzin pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:15370: rang rgyud dam rdzas mngon zhes pas //
NK093(ge)002:15371: bgegs dang bya rog sgor ltung 'khor //
NK093(ge)002:15373: 'di'i rkang pa dang por dpe la lar /
NK093(ge)002:15374: ma rtogs phra men ci mkhas kyang //
NK093(ge)002:15376: lha chen por ltung ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:15377: thabs lam dbang la khungs phyung ste //
NK093(ge)002:15378: 'dod chags rang dgar rtag spyod pa //
NK093(ge)002:15379: lta bas ma zin bde la zhen //
NK093(ge)002:15380: lha chen 'dod chags mngal sgor ltung //
NK093(ge)002:15382: sho gam can du ltung ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:15383: rang dbang ting 'dzin ma thob par //
NK093(ge)002:15384: sdig pas 'khor dang ris su bcad //
NK093(ge)002:15386: sho gam gcan chen gnas su ltung //
NK093(ge)002:15388: ngan song du ltung ba'i sgo ni /
NK093(ge)002:15390: rang sems chos skur ma rtogs par //
NK093(ge)002:15391: mdo rgyud mang po shes bshad kyang //
NK093(ge)002:15392: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:15393: ngan song gsum gyi sgor ltung 'khor //
NK093(ge)002:15395: de la sogas pa sngar yang bshad pa gzhan 'di dag bsdu ba'i don gyis rngam nyi shu dang /
NK093(ge)002:15397: brjid nyi shu la sogs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las smos pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15401: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa mtha'a yasa pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15402: chos ji snyed pa thams cad nas thams cad du
NK093(ge)002:15403: yongas su rdzogas pa kun shes shing rtogs para 'doda
NK093(ge)002:15404: pa rnams ganga dang gang dag gis kyang gsang sngags
NK093(ge)002:15405: gsang ba dama pa'i lam chen po 'di nyid yang
NK093(ge)002:15406: dag par shes par bya ste /
NK093(ge)002:15407: kun 'dus kyi le'u dang po las /
NK093(ge)002:15408: de ltar chos kyis tshul shin tu mang po rgyas par bka' stsal te mjug tu /
NK093(ge)002:15409: 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs de bas na /
NK093(ge)002:15410: sangs rgyas kyi chos de rnams la spyod par 'dod pas /
NK093(ge)002:15414: klong du gyur bar gyis shig /ces gdams par mdzad do //
NK093(ge)002:15422: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15423: yang dag par shes na dgos pa de lta bu
NK093(ge)002:15424: dang ldan pa'i lam gyi ngo bo ni semas kyi
NK093(ge)002:15425: dkyil 'khor dang rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba dbyer
NK093(ge)002:15426: med mnyam pa chen por rtogs pa de nyida rgyal
NK093(ge)002:15427: ba rnams kyi gshegs shul yin pas rnal 'byor pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15428: yang 'jug ngogs dama pa rnal ma ma nor ba'i
NK093(ge)002:15429: lam mchog rmad du byung ba nyid de dper na
NK093(ge)002:15430: khyung chen nam mkha'a la lding yang bya lam gyi
NK093(ge)002:15432: de lta bu'i rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan pa can
NK093(ge)002:15433: la cis kyang mi gos pas zon chags kyis nyam
NK093(ge)002:15434: nga ba dang log par ltung ba'i bag tsha ba
NK093(ge)002:15435: med par nor ba mi 'byung ba ni dama pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15436: lam mchog tu gyur bar nges pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:15438: 'di gnyis sems nyams kyang yin no //
NK093(ge)002:15440: rang mtshan rtogs nas don la 'da' nyams med pa'i gdengs dang ldan pa la dgongs kyi /
NK093(ge)002:15441: ngo bo ma rtogs par ting nge 'dzin brtan pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15442: spyi mtshan tsam gyis go myong la gnas pas ni mi bstongs te /
NK093(ge)002:15444: dam la mi gnas sngags pa de //
NK093(ge)002:15445: na rag rdo rje'i gtan gzhi ste //
NK093(ge)002:15446: rtogs pa spyi yis de mi skyobs //
NK093(ge)002:15447: sems 'dzin gnas pas chu lon min //
NK093(ge)002:15450: lam mchog shes par bya ba'i phyir tshig gis mtshon dgos par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:15451: lam gyi gol sa nyes dmigs dang bcas pa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:15452: don lam gyi ngo bo dngos bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:15453: de ltar mthong goms kyi drod rtags bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:15454: lam pa de nyid theg pa gzhan gyi lam zhugs las dpag par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:15455: don lam gyi rnal 'byor pa la yon tan thams cad rdzogs par bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15460: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15461: 'di ltar theg pa chen po blang dor med par
NK093(ge)002:15462: gsang don ngesa pa'i lam mchog dam pa 'di yang
NK093(ge)002:15463: skal ba dang ldan pa'i lam pa blo rab 'bring
NK093(ge)002:15464: tha ma kun gyis rim gyis shes shing rtogs par
NK093(ge)002:15465: bya ba'i phyir ram ched du brjod 'byung tshig gi
NK093(ge)002:15466: lam gyis ched du gnyer nas yi ges don mtshona
NK093(ge)002:15469: 'on te de ltar bstan kyang don gyi ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:15470: brjod du meda cing tshig gi yul dang brala ba
NK093(ge)002:15471: nyid brjod tshig gis mi phebs te smrar med pas
NK093(ge)002:15472: / lam dam pa de yi rang bzhina de lta
NK093(ge)002:15473: bu ma nor ba'i mtshan nyid can du nges pa
NK093(ge)002:15474: yina na lam pas 'phral du byas te ranga bzhina
NK093(ge)002:15475: ma bcosa shing bsam pa las 'byung ba ma yin
NK093(ge)002:15476: pas chos nyid de bzhina nyid dam pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15477: 'on kyang tshig tu brjod pas lam mtshon pa'i tshul ni /
NK093(ge)002:15478: chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa'i don de la ming med
NK093(ge)002:15479: cing brjod du med pas ma bcos pa'i ngang las
NK093(ge)002:15480: / gdul bya la ming du btagsa te rnam grangs
NK093(ge)002:15481: tha snyad du bsnyad pa'i rgyus phyin ci ma log
NK093(ge)002:15482: par mthong zhing rtogs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15483: de ltar ma mthong zhing ma rtogs pas theg pa sna tshogs tha dada du gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15484: de yi rgyu lasa so so'i ngo la brjod pa
NK093(ge)002:15485: tha dad pa'i gzhira gyur te rang rang gis lta
NK093(ge)002:15486: ba'i gzhung sgrub cing rtsod pas smra brjod 'phel zhing
NK093(ge)002:15488: tshig lam bstan pa de'i dgos pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:15489: tshig tu smra zhing brjod pasa don gyi ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:15490: de kho na nyid mthonga zhing rtogs par bya'i zhes
NK093(ge)002:15492: tshiga gi lam gyis mtshon thabs ni rnam grangsa kyi
NK093(ge)002:15493: bye brag sna tshogs pa mang por bsdebs pa lasa
NK093(ge)002:15494: tshiga gi lam gyi chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri
NK093(ge)002:15495: bzhi stong la sogs pa mi mthun pa dpag tu
NK093(ge)002:15496: med cing bsam yas par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK093(ge)002:15497: de bas na tshig gi spros pa de dag lasa
NK093(ge)002:15498: shes bya'i don ma nor ba dama pa lkog tu
NK093(ge)002:15499: gyur pa'i mtshan nyid mtshon pas rjesa brjod de rigs
NK093(ge)002:15500: pas dpyad par bya ba'i thabs mchog tu gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:15501: ni / gdul bya'i blo dang bstun te drang ba'i thabs su bka' stsal pa tsam min par /
NK093(ge)002:15502: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dam pa gang gi
NK093(ge)002:15503: thugsa kyi dgongs pa lasa byung nas yang dag pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15504: bka'i tshig tu byung ba'i nges pa'i lung snang gsal
NK093(ge)002:15505: 'od ldan lta bu'i sgron mas yon tan lhun gyis
NK093(ge)002:15506: grub par rang la gnas pa'i don gyi nye lam
NK093(ge)002:15507: 'dzam bu'i chu bo'i gser gyi gter dang 'dra ba
NK093(ge)002:15508: btsal te rtogs par bya ba yang brjod pa tshig
NK093(ge)002:15509: lam dam pa la brten nas mtshon par zad do
NK093(ge)002:15514: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15515: de yang ji ltar rgyud dgrol ba'i bslab pa la
NK093(ge)002:15516: gnas pas dmigs med bsam las 'das par thag chod
NK093(ge)002:15517: nas nye lam byang chub dama pa mchog nyid rnyed
NK093(ge)002:15518: pa na ni / de'i ngang la gnas te sgom dgos pas /
NK093(ge)002:15519: de ltar sgom pa'i dus su de'i rig pa de
NK093(ge)002:15520: dag dran pa ganga dang sgo drug gi mtshan ma'i
NK093(ge)002:15521: byung tshor gyi rjesa su de ltar 'brangsa na /
NK093(ge)002:15522: byung tshor gyi dbang gis g.yengs par gyur pa mar
NK093(ge)002:15523: me rlung gis bskyod pa lta bu'i skyon du song
NK093(ge)002:15524: bas 'jig rten par ltung ste rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK093(ge)002:15526: la skye bo rang ka ma dang sgom pa'i shes
NK093(ge)002:15528: ganga mtshan ma'i byung tshor dang rtog pa g.yo ba'i
NK093(ge)002:15529: rgyu ba la skyon du bltas nas dbang po'i sgo
NK093(ge)002:15530: sdoms pas ganga bakaga nas sgom pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:15531: 'dzin chags kyi dbang gis 'gog par gyur pa khyim
NK093(ge)002:15532: bdag 'jur bu can lta bu'i skyon du song bas
NK093(ge)002:15533: rgyun gyi 'goga pa nyid du ltung bar 'gyur te
NK093(ge)002:15534: / 'di la'ang nyan thos 'gog pa dang sgom pa'i shes pa gol ba gnyis su sbyar ro //
NK093(ge)002:15535: gang dran pa dang byung tshor yang med la don
NK093(ge)002:15536: rtogs pa'i shed kyang ma bye bar gang du'ang mi
NK093(ge)002:15537: rgyu bar 'thom zhing blun po pa yi sgom pa
NK093(ge)002:15538: ni / bying rmugs kyi dbang gis 'thibs par gyur
NK093(ge)002:15539: pa 'ben thim pa'i mda' lta bu'i skyon du song
NK093(ge)002:15540: bas ma rig rmongs pa'i mur 'dzina gyis non pas
NK093(ge)002:15541: mun pa'i lam gyi khrod du ltung bar 'gyur te
NK093(ge)002:15542: ni / / 'di la'ang 'du shes med pa'am byol
NK093(ge)002:15543: song dang sgom pa'i shes pa gnyis su sbyar ro
NK093(ge)002:15544: ni / / // gang zag gi bdag gam sems
NK093(ge)002:15545: snang ba 'di nyid do zhes bdag gis ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:15546: gciga tu ganga la nges par bzung nas sgom pa
NK093(ge)002:15547: ni ther zug gi dbang gis 'thas par gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:15548: skyes bu bya rog gi khu 'phrig can gyis mtha'
NK093(ge)002:15549: la rtog pa lta bu'i skyon du song bas rtag
NK093(ge)002:15550: pa'i matshana ma la rtog pa'i ri bo nyid du
NK093(ge)002:15552: 'di la'ang mu stegs rtag lta ba dang sgom pa'i shes pa gnyis su sbyar ro //
NK093(ge)002:15553: tshe'am rgyu 'bras sam don la dus snga phyi gang
NK093(ge)002:15554: yang med ces mu mtha' bacada de da lta 'ba'
NK093(ge)002:15555: zhig ma khegs par yod pa tsam du mthong nas
NK093(ge)002:15556: sgom na ni / phyal ba'i dbang gis med par
NK093(ge)002:15557: gyur pa khyi 'gron phyogs gnyis pa lta bu'i skyon
NK093(ge)002:15558: sgom na ni / du song bas / de ltar
NK093(ge)002:15559: med pa chad pa'i mu can du ltung ba yina
NK093(ge)002:15560: sgom na ni / du song bas / te /
NK093(ge)002:15561: 'di la'ang mu stegs chad lta ba dang sgom pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15562: shes pa gol ba gnyis su sbyar ro //
NK093(ge)002:15563: de bas na ma bcosa pa'i chos nyid ji bzhin
NK093(ge)002:15564: pa'i don gyi lam nyid rig pa la skad cig
NK093(ge)002:15565: yud tsam zhig gsal nas slar de nyid 'gag ste
NK093(ge)002:15566: blo yi rtog pa cir yang g.yosa pas rnam rtog
NK093(ge)002:15567: gi rjes su 'brangs nas skye 'agga 'byung ba de
NK093(ge)002:15568: la slar yang snga ma'i rjes su dran par byas
NK093(ge)002:15569: pas de las sngar ltar bsgom bya gang de yun
NK093(ge)002:15570: du gsal bar 'byung bas ganga rtogs pa je bas
NK093(ge)002:15571: je 'phela du byung nas sems las bogs su gyur
NK093(ge)002:15572: ba na yang / sa bcu dang rnal 'byor bcu
NK093(ge)002:15573: la sogs pa rim gyis pa ji ltar 'jug pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15574: rnam grangsa kyi lam de nyid 'phel zhing gong nas
NK093(ge)002:15576: gang gcig char du 'jug pa'i dama pa'i lam mchog
NK093(ge)002:15577: nyid du gdengs rnyed de klong du phebs pa ni
NK093(ge)002:15578: ma yin te dran par byed pa nyid kyis bsgribs
NK093(ge)002:15579: pa'o // des mi mthong ba nye bar mtshon pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:15580: dpera na 'gro ba ganga brda la shed ma bye
NK093(ge)002:15581: ba'i byis pa dag gis grib ma la 'bros te
NK093(ge)002:15582: spangsa nas grib ma med pa'i lus gzugs rnam par
NK093(ge)002:15584: grib ma rang rgyu ganga lasa byung ba ma shes
NK093(ge)002:15585: pa de nyid kyis grib ma med pa'i lus gzugs
NK093(ge)002:15586: btsal yanga slar grib ma 'phela zhing de med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15587: lus dang gzugs daga pa ni mi rnyed pa dang
NK093(ge)002:15588: mtshungs par rang gi sgo gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK093(ge)002:15589: kun sems kyi de kho na nyid ye nasa rang
NK093(ge)002:15590: rig pa'i de bzhina nyid dam pa'i lam mchog ma
NK093(ge)002:15591: nor ba yin bzhin du gang de nyid mi shes
NK093(ge)002:15592: par rgyu 'bras dang bcas pa'i lam 'dira sdug bsngal
NK093(ge)002:15593: sna tshogas kyis rtsol ba mang po'i gdung bas chos
NK093(ge)002:15594: nyid kyi don la bya ba'i rnal 'byor pa ltar
NK093(ge)002:15595: sha thang bar ni 'bad de lam gzhan du tshola
NK093(ge)002:15596: ba ni bdag nyid chen po mthong du mi ster
NK093(ge)002:15597: bas dona meda pa'i bduda kyi lasa 'bad pa don
NK093(ge)002:15598: med pa kho na yina no //
NK093(ge)002:15599: des na chos nyid rang gi ngo bo tha snyad
NK093(ge)002:15600: dang bral ba'i don de la lam gzhan du tshol
NK093(ge)002:15601: ba'i gzhung mi mthun pa rnams kyis tshiga tu gang
NK093(ge)002:15602: brjod de bden rdzun la rtsod par byed pa ni
NK093(ge)002:15603: dper na nama mkha'a daga la bgo bsha' byas te
NK093(ge)002:15604: yod med du rtsod par byed pa dang 'dra zhing
NK093(ge)002:15605: mtshungs so // de'i phyir gzhan yang dper na tshig
NK093(ge)002:15606: tu sman dang dpyad bzang po bklag ste bashada kyang
NK093(ge)002:15607: sman ma btang na nada pa'i tshogsa la phan pa
NK093(ge)002:15609: dpe de ltar don gyi ngo bo rang rig pa
NK093(ge)002:15610: de kho na nyid la de bzhina nyid ltar gnad
NK093(ge)002:15611: du chud de rtogs pa mngon du ma gyur na
NK093(ge)002:15612: / tshig lam tsam gyi thabs ji snyed pa mang
NK093(ge)002:15613: po de dag brjod kyang don gyi yin lugs chos
NK093(ge)002:15614: nyid de mthong bar 'gyur ba ma yina no //
NK093(ge)002:15615: 'on kyang don rtogs pa la gal che bar bskul
NK093(ge)002:15616: ba las ji lta ba bzhin ston pa'i tshig bkag
NK093(ge)002:15618: de bas na lam gzhan du tshol ba'ang don med
NK093(ge)002:15619: pa'i phyir ganga 'dira rnal 'byor chen po'i gsang ba'i
NK093(ge)002:15620: lung gi don lam gyi sgor zhugs nas 'khor ba'i
NK093(ge)002:15621: lam ganga yin pa spangsa te mya ngan las 'das
NK093(ge)002:15622: pa'i lam mchog ganga zhig gzhan nas tshol ba ni
NK093(ge)002:15623: / dper na gzugsa spangsa nas ni grib ma tshol
NK093(ge)002:15624: ba dang 'dra ste gzhan gang las mi rnyed par
NK093(ge)002:15625: / nges so // de bas na byang chub kyi sems sgom pa las /
NK093(ge)002:15626: 'khor ba'i lam gsum spongs shing mya ngan 'das lam sgom byed pa yang bdud nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:15627: de nyid rang bzhin ma zhi rang bzhin rtsal spangs gar mi gnas //
NK093(ge)002:15628: 'phags pa kun gyi yul dang gnas kyang 'das sogs lam 'di gzhan na med //
NK093(ge)002:15629: ldang dang mi ldang ched du mi spong sems rten mi 'cha' mngon du min //
NK093(ge)002:15630: 'jam dpal ma yin rdul tsam g.yo ba de nyid de yin der mi gnas //
NK093(ge)002:15631: bsgom pa'i sa mi rnyed phyir sgoms pas rnyed par mi 'gyur te //
NK093(ge)002:15632: sems kyi spyod yul shes pa de dag chos rnams kyi ni chos nyid yin //
NK093(ge)002:15633: rnam bral gang la'ang mchog dang tha ma med par lam mchog 'di bsgom mo //
NK093(ge)002:15636: sems nyid gnyis med dam pa'i lam du bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:15637: sems kyi dkyiil 'khor rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal bar bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:15638: sems la dran rtog shar yang rang byung rang zhir bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:15639: lam de'i yon tan sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i ngo bor bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15644: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15645: 'o na gang nas btsal bar bya zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:15646: gnas lugs ji bzhin pa chos so cog gi rtsa
NK093(ge)002:15647: ba semas nyida rang rig pa chen po ni thar
NK093(ge)002:15648: pa dama pa'i lam mchog ma nor ba nyid yin
NK093(ge)002:15649: pas 'khor ba'i rtsa ba ma rig pa dang rig
NK093(ge)002:15650: pa ye shesa chen po gnyis gser dang gaya'i tshul
NK093(ge)002:15651: tsam las ngo bo tha dad mina par dbyer med
NK093(ge)002:15652: du gnas pa'i don la 'khor ba dang sangs rgyas
NK093(ge)002:15653: kyi ris su mi 'dzin te blang dor med par
NK093(ge)002:15654: gnyis su mi rtog pa yi lam chen po bgrod
NK093(ge)002:15655: du med pa 'dira rang bzhin gciga pa yin pas
NK093(ge)002:15658: lam nyid ji ltar yin zhe na //
NK093(ge)002:15659: ma rig ye shes tha dad min //
NK093(ge)002:15660: ma rtogs rtogs pa lam du gcig /sems 'di sna tshogs par snang bas //
NK093(ge)002:15661: sna tshogs sems su gcig pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:15664: 'o na stong pa phyogs gcig pa zhig go zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:15665: semas rang rig pa de nyid 'khor 'das su 'gro
NK093(ge)002:15666: ba'i mtho dman gyi lam ji snyed pa sna tshogas
NK093(ge)002:15667: para snang basa rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa'i dbang
NK093(ge)002:15668: gis sna tshogas cir yang 'char ba nyid sems kyi
NK093(ge)002:15669: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi lam 'dira dbyer med
NK093(ge)002:15670: du gcig pa yin pas 'khor ba'i lam ma spangs
NK093(ge)002:15671: la 'das pa btsal du med par chos nyid rang
NK093(ge)002:15672: rig rang grol du rtogs pa de nyid ma nor
NK093(ge)002:15674: de nyid nye bar mtshon tshul /
NK093(ge)002:15675: dper na gsera gyi rgyu gciga lasa sku dang chol
NK093(ge)002:15676: zangs la sogs pa dbyibsa dang gzugsa ni tha dada
NK093(ge)002:15677: para byas te so sor snang basa snang tshul de
NK093(ge)002:15678: dag la minga yang de dang der tha dad re
NK093(ge)002:15679: rera gragsa mod / gang ltar gragsa kyang don gsera
NK093(ge)002:15680: gyi ngo bora gciga pa las 'gyur ba med do
NK093(ge)002:15681: rera gragsa mod / // dpe de ltar chos thams
NK093(ge)002:15682: cad semas nyid byang chub kyi sems su ranga bzhina
NK093(ge)002:15683: gcig cing ngo bo rnam las dag pa la /
NK093(ge)002:15684: 'jig rten pa dang 'das pa'i theg pa gong 'og
NK093(ge)002:15685: gis don de mthonga zhing rtogs pa dang ma mthong
NK093(ge)002:15686: zhing ma rtogs pa'i khyad par gyis don phyogs med
NK093(ge)002:15687: la ji ltar bltas pa ltar sems nyid gang ltar
NK093(ge)002:15688: bltas rgu de ltar snang ste /
NK093(ge)002:15689: sna tshogs su gsal zhing snang ba yin yang ngo
NK093(ge)002:15690: bo sems nyid de kho na nyid ma gtogs de
NK093(ge)002:15691: las gazhana du gyur pa ni gang yang mi dmigas
NK093(ge)002:15692: pas sems nyid du ma 'dus pa'i chos med do
NK093(ge)002:15697: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15698: 'o na sems kyi rang bzhin ji lta bu zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:15699: dper na snang byed gsal ba'i sgron ma 'od 'abra ba dang ldan pa'i rina chena dam pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:15700: ji ltar 'dam gyi ngana khung du sbas par gyur
NK093(ge)002:15701: na yanga de yi rang bzhina rang gsal du snang
NK093(ge)002:15702: ba yin pas 'oda ni nam mkha'a la gasla bar
NK093(ge)002:15703: 'gyur ro // dpe de bzhina du rig pa byang
NK093(ge)002:15704: chub kyi semsa nyid ye nas rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK093(ge)002:15705: gsal ba'i rina chen mchog gi sgron ma de nyid
NK093(ge)002:15706: lus ngag yid kyi bag chags ngana pa'i 'adma du
NK093(ge)002:15707: bying ste bsgribs par gyur na yang rang rig pa
NK093(ge)002:15708: ye shes chen po las nyams pa med de /
NK093(ge)002:15709: ji ltar rgyu rkyen bral bar ranga byung zhing spros
NK093(ge)002:15710: pa ma spangs ranga sar zhi ste ril rig pa
NK093(ge)002:15711: nyid du shar zhing de nyid sna tshogs par ma
NK093(ge)002:15712: 'gags te ranga snang bar nus pa yin pas na
NK093(ge)002:15713: blos ched du ma bcosa par sems kyi ranga bzhina
NK093(ge)002:15714: ye nas 'byed pa med par yong gisa 'od gasla
NK093(ge)002:15715: ba ni sus kyang ma byas par byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:15720: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15721: de lta bu'i byang chub kyi semsa 'di ni nam mkha'a ji lta bu'i rang bzhina can te /
NK093(ge)002:15722: ji ltar na kun la khyab pa ngo bo stong
NK093(ge)002:15723: pa mtshan nyid gsal ba chos ji snyed pa sna
NK093(ge)002:15724: tshogas cho 'phrul du 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:15725: ro // de lta bu'i byang chub kyi sems de
NK093(ge)002:15726: bsgom pa'i dus su sems kyi byung tshor dang rnam
NK093(ge)002:15727: rtog gi rgyu 'grul g.yo zhing skye ba dang snga
NK093(ge)002:15728: ma 'gag pa dang gnyis cha 'goga pa thams cad
NK093(ge)002:15729: kun kyang byang chub sems kyi ngang las ranga bzhina
NK093(ge)002:15730: gyis 'byung zhing rang snang ba denyida du nges pas
NK093(ge)002:15731: zin chags med pa'i phyir nganga gisa zhi bar 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:15732: ro // ro // mdor na sems nyid rang rig
NK093(ge)002:15733: pa ni ji ltar brtagsa shing bsam pa ltar de
NK093(ge)002:15734: kho na bzhina du snang bar 'gyur basa chos gang
NK093(ge)002:15735: cir yang snang du btub pa'i phyir chos thams cada
NK093(ge)002:15736: kyi ngo bora byung bas rang rig pa dngos gzhi
NK093(ge)002:15737: thams cad par rang snang ba nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:15738: de bas na blo che bas sems nyid rtogs nas
NK093(ge)002:15739: ye ma bcosa ma bslad pa'i ngang la cir snang
NK093(ge)002:15740: ci srid kyang de nyid las g.yo ba med pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15741: dbyings nyid las dran pa dang rnam rtog sna tshogas
NK093(ge)002:15742: kyi rgyu ba ji ltar 'byung ba yang mtshan mar
NK093(ge)002:15743: mi 'char bas skyon du bya ba med par ngang
NK093(ge)002:15745: ci ste na de rnams sems kyi cho 'phrul yin
NK093(ge)002:15746: pas rtog rgyun cir yang mi 'agga par skyes kyang
NK093(ge)002:15747: ched du mi 'gog par de dag skyes pa gang
NK093(ge)002:15748: la'ang nyam nga ba dang bag tsha ba meda de
NK093(ge)002:15749: / ril de kho na nyid du thag chod pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:15750: de ltar chos nyid ma bcos pas ye ji bzhin
NK093(ge)002:15751: pa la rang rig pa ji bzhina pa nyid du
NK093(ge)002:15752: rang snang bas yul la mi dpyod yul phas mi
NK093(ge)002:15753: snang ste chos nyid dngos nam mkha' lta bu nyid
NK093(ge)002:15754: du rig pa dngos nama mkha'i rang bzhin ltar rang
NK093(ge)002:15755: shar ba la blo rang gsal du bazhaga cing don
NK093(ge)002:15756: las ma yengsa te mi 'dzin pa la bral ba
NK093(ge)002:15757: med pa tsam nyid la blo bzhag ste sgom pa
NK093(ge)002:15758: zhes pa'i ming btags pa kho nara zad do //
NK093(ge)002:15763: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15764: de lta bur gcig char du rtogs pa'i ngang la
NK093(ge)002:15765: ma bcos par bzhag ste sgom pa ma nor ba
NK093(ge)002:15766: la gnas pa ni 'bad pa'i gron tshegas kyi dka'
NK093(ge)002:15767: ba byar med par de nyid du sa non pas
NK093(ge)002:15768: dona chen po rmad du byung ba'i che ba dang
NK093(ge)002:15769: ldan pa grub pa yin pas rim par ma bgrod
NK093(ge)002:15770: par 'bras bur rang snang ba de nyid ni dusa
NK093(ge)002:15771: gsuma du gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cada kyi rnam
NK093(ge)002:15772: grol sangsa rgyas 'byung ba'i gnas kyi ngo bo ma
NK093(ge)002:15773: nor ba rgyu yang yina la lam chen po nyid
NK093(ge)002:15779: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te //
NK093(ge)002:15780: de ltar chos nyid mnyam pa nyid rtogs pa de
NK093(ge)002:15781: yi dona la yun ji snyed par ring du gansa
NK093(ge)002:15782: pas / ji lta ba nyid mthonga zhing rtogs pa
NK093(ge)002:15783: de nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dera gomas par byed
NK093(ge)002:15784: pas / pa'i tshe na / yang dag pa'i lam
NK093(ge)002:15785: rnyed de don lam ma nor ba nyid mthong zhing
NK093(ge)002:15786: rtogs nas goms par byas pas nyamsa drod kyi rtags
NK093(ge)002:15787: pas / pa'i tshe na / ni / drod chung ngu ni sa bzhi par yang 'byung la /
NK093(ge)002:15788: drod chen po rnams skabs brgyad pas g.yos nas dgu
NK093(ge)002:15789: pa dang bcu par 'byung ba'ang thob pa dang brtan
NK093(ge)002:15790: pa'i tshul ni / rgyu chos nyid kyi dona la
NK093(ge)002:15791: blo reg pa'i shugs kyis ngesa par 'byung ba yang
NK093(ge)002:15792: dang po kho nar don ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba
NK093(ge)002:15793: ganga sems nyid kyi don ngos zin pa ma yina
NK093(ge)002:15794: pa rnams la snying rje chen pos nges par zina
NK093(ge)002:15795: pa'i sems 'byung ba nyid pas kun rdzob kyi byang
NK093(ge)002:15796: chub kyi sems dama pa 'byung bar 'gyur ba dang
NK093(ge)002:15797: pa'i tshul ni / / dngos po dang matshana mara
NK093(ge)002:15798: rtog pa'i chos rnams la yid mi ches shing sgyu
NK093(ge)002:15799: ma lta bur mi bden par ngesa pa'i shes rab
NK093(ge)002:15800: kyi blo gros 'byung zhing skye ba yin pa /
NK093(ge)002:15801: chos thams cad kun 'di ltar ye nas de kho
NK093(ge)002:15802: na nyid yina pa la 'gro ba rnams kyis ma
NK093(ge)002:15803: rtogs nas 'khrul pas de ltar mi shes te sa
NK093(ge)002:15804: mchog gnyis med chen por ma mthonga ba de ngo
NK093(ge)002:15806: ji bzhin pa'i don brtag par dka' ba de nyid
NK093(ge)002:15807: lam pas ma 'khrul bar yang dag par mthonga ba
NK093(ge)002:15808: de yanga ngo matshara che ba 'di lta bu zhig
NK093(ge)002:15809: snyams nas ya mtshan pa'i 'du shes skyes te /
NK093(ge)002:15810: e ma'o ji ga snyam du 'byung ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:15811: de ltar de kho na nyid kyi don ma mthonga
NK093(ge)002:15812: ba'i 'gro ba gang su dag rnams rtsol sgrub sna
NK093(ge)002:15813: tshogs kyis sha thang bar 'bad de daka'a ba'i tshegas
NK093(ge)002:15815: byang chub dama pa'i lam gzhan nas tshola mi dgos
NK093(ge)002:15816: pa la rtsol bas gzhan nas tshol ba de nyid
NK093(ge)002:15817: lam thag re ringa ngo snyam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15818: de lta bu la 'bad kyang brgyud pa'i rgyu tsam du 'gyur bas /
NK093(ge)002:15819: de yi dona gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu mtho ris tsam 'grub cing 'byung ba de yoda mod kyang /
NK093(ge)002:15820: yang dag pa'i lam chen po de yi don 'di
NK093(ge)002:15821: dngos su rnyed cing rtogs par ni yong ye 'byung
NK093(ge)002:15822: bar mi 'gyur ro snyam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15823: bde bar gshegs pa rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK093(ge)002:15824: dama pa rnams kyi lam ma nor ba rnal ma
NK093(ge)002:15825: nyid rnyed cing thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:15826: bder gshegs dama pa nyid dang mnyam pa yin pasa
NK093(ge)002:15827: lam dama pa la gnas pa yin par nges pa'o
NK093(ge)002:15828: // de dag ni don mthong ba'i drod kyi phyir
NK093(ge)002:15829: lnga pa dang drug par zag med skye ba la
NK093(ge)002:15830: sbyor ba dang dngos su skye ba'i rigs so //
NK093(ge)002:15835: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15837: de lta bu'i rtogs pa'i drod chen po dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor mchog de ni /
NK093(ge)002:15838: rten du gyur pa'i sku'i gzugs brnyana dang drod de
NK093(ge)002:15839: bral ba rnams yon tan gyi khyad par 'dra zhing
NK093(ge)002:15841: de bas na gzhi la dbyer med yin kyang rten
NK093(ge)002:15842: gyi khyad par las bsod nams kyi yul yin kyang
NK093(ge)002:15843: ye shes kyi yul ma yin pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15845: dngos kyi rgyu ma yin pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15846: rig pa'i ngo bo yin kyang rtogs pas ma khyab pas /
NK093(ge)002:15847: mi mtshungs pa'i gtan tshigs bkod pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:15848: nyan thos zag med zhi ba'i lus can dang rang
NK093(ge)002:15849: rgyal rten 'brel mthar 'goga gi chos nyid mthong ba
NK093(ge)002:15850: gnyis kyis kyang bsgrun du med pas mtshungsa pa mina
NK093(ge)002:15851: te / lang kar gshegs pa las /
NK093(ge)002:15852: ji ltar shing dag rgya mtsho la //
NK093(ge)002:15853: rlabs rnams kyis ni rnam par g.yengs //
NK093(ge)002:15854: de bzhin nyan thos rmongs pa yang //
NK093(ge)002:15855: mtshan nyid rnams kyis rab tu g.yengs //
NK093(ge)002:15856: kun nas ldang dang bral mod kyi //
NK093(ge)002:15857: nyon mongs bag chags rnams dang 'brel //
NK093(ge)002:15858: ting 'dzin myos pas rab myos te //
NK093(ge)002:15859: zag pa med pa'i dbyings na 'khod //
NK093(ge)002:15860: mtha' mar phyin pa de la med //
NK093(ge)002:15861: phyir yang de las mi ldog ste //
NK093(ge)002:15862: ting nge 'dzin gyi lus thob nas //
NK093(ge)002:15863: bskal pa'i bar du de mi sang //
NK093(ge)002:15864: ji ltar skyes bu ra ro ba //
NK093(ge)002:15865: chang dang bral nas sangs 'gyur bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:15866: de na de dag nga yi yang //
NK093(ge)002:15867: chos kyi sku ni thob par 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:15870: rkyen rtogs gzung yul ma grub par //
NK093(ge)002:15872: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'i phyir dang //
NK093(ge)002:15873: rgyu'i byang chub sems dpa' sloba pa'i sa bcu la
NK093(ge)002:15874: gnas pa dag dang yang rnal ma rtogs pa de
NK093(ge)002:15876: sngags kyi mnyam pa nyid ma mthong ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:15878: bden pa ris mos pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:15879: gzhan don la ngar 'dzin yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:15880: theg pa chen po'i rnal 'byor gsang sngags phyi pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15881: rig 'dzin byang chub semsa dapa'a don la rtog cing
NK093(ge)002:15883: kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches /
NK093(ge)002:15886: rtog mtha' kri yar gsungs pas /
NK093(ge)002:15888: ganga lus kyi cha byad dang shes bya tsam mtshungsa
NK093(ge)002:15889: yang rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin de 'dra ba
NK093(ge)002:15890: min pas yon tan de dang mi mtshungsa pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:15891: de sngags phyi pa 'di dag gsang sngags yin kyang
NK093(ge)002:15892: nang pa bla med la mi sleb pa'i phyir te
NK093(ge)002:15894: rang snang mnyam pa nyid ma mthong bas so //
NK093(ge)002:15895: 'o na de dag ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:15896: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:15897: theg pa chen po'i drod rtags mchog dang ldan pa'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:15898: bden pa res mos pa med pa'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:15899: theg chen gsang ba'i don nyid la'ang 'dzin rtog dmigs pa dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:15904: des na rnam dag /ces pa nas /
NK093(ge)002:15906: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15907: desa na yon tan gyi ngo bo de lta bu'i
NK093(ge)002:15908: tshul gyis theg pa mchog gi rnam par daga pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15909: lam chen po'i ngo bo ni /
NK093(ge)002:15910: dper na lus kyi gsang mig gis gzugs mthong gi
NK093(ge)002:15911: de las gzhan gyis min pa ltar 'dir rang rig
NK093(ge)002:15912: pa byang chub semsa kyi gsang ba rtogs par dka'
NK093(ge)002:15913: ba 'di nyid rtogs pa kho nas sangs rgyas pa
NK093(ge)002:15914: yina gyi / gzhan gang gis kyang ma yin pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15915: phyir gyi gtan tshigs de basa na rgyal ba rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:15916: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dgongas pa kun nasa 'dusa pa
NK093(ge)002:15917: yi rtsa ba gasnga mchog sngags kyi rang bzhin sems
NK093(ge)002:15918: nyid ji ltar yin pa'i lam 'di shes shing rtogs
NK093(ge)002:15919: par byas pas 'bras bu rang gsal lhun grub tu
NK093(ge)002:15920: 'byung ba la dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK093(ge)002:15921: 'di las gzhan du 'bad pas batsala bar bya ba'i
NK093(ge)002:15922: rgyu med la btsal yang mi dgos pa nyid de
NK093(ge)002:15923: / sems nyid de kho na nyid kyi lam dag
NK093(ge)002:15924: pa 'di nyid ma nor bar mthonga zhing rtogs pa
NK093(ge)002:15925: de nyid kyis gzhan du daka'a bas btsal ba'i tshegs
NK093(ge)002:15926: chen pos rtsol ba ganga yang med par mchog dang
NK093(ge)002:15927: thun mong gi dngos grub thamsa cad dang ji lta
NK093(ge)002:15928: dang ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes thams cad ngang
NK093(ge)002:15929: gis grub zin te lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK093(ge)002:15930: ma lus pa kun mthar phyin par gyur pa yina
NK093(ge)002:15931: pas dbyer med mnyam pa chen po'i rtogs pa yongs
NK093(ge)002:15932: / su rdzogs pa'o // gnyis pa la bcu ste /
NK093(ge)002:15942: mthong lam rdzogs par bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:15947: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15948: de bas na rtogs par dka' ba'i semas kyi gasnga
NK093(ge)002:15949: ba rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i don mchog ganga
NK093(ge)002:15950: yin pa de nyid skyes bu su yis yang dag
NK093(ge)002:15951: par rtogs pa'i ngang la gansa te blo la 'chang
NK093(ge)002:15952: ba de ni gnyis su med pa'i bdena pa sgro
NK093(ge)002:15953: skur dang bral bas don dama pa'i lta ba mchog
NK093(ge)002:15954: nyid mngon du byas pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:15955: de nyid mtha' thams cad las ring du gyur pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15956: phyir dgona pa chena po'i gnas mchoga dam pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:15957: du gyur par rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongas pa kun
NK093(ge)002:15958: nasa 'dusa pa'i ston pas kyang rig pa 'dzin pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15959: 'khor la bka' stsal te gsungsa par mdzad do //
NK093(ge)002:15964: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15965: des na gnyis bral gyi lta ba thams cad kyi
NK093(ge)002:15966: dngos gzhir gyur pas bya brtsal med la gnas tshul
NK093(ge)002:15967: gyi cha nas 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi gnas su
NK093(ge)002:15968: gyur pa'i byang chub kyi sems de nyid blo yis
NK093(ge)002:15969: dapaga tu med cing rtogs par dka' ba yin pas
NK093(ge)002:15970: / de ltar ma nor bar mthong ba de bzhin
NK093(ge)002:15971: gshegs pa rnams kyi yang bzhugs pa'i gazhala yasa dam
NK093(ge)002:15972: pa mchoga khyad par can yon tan cir yang 'char
NK093(ge)002:15973: bas rmad du byung ba'i rina chen mchog gi yid
NK093(ge)002:15974: bzhina gyi khanga pa yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:15975: de'i ngo bo 'phral du byed pa po'am rgyu rkyen
NK093(ge)002:15976: gyis ma byas shing ma sgrubs par ye nas ranga
NK093(ge)002:15977: byung ba'i ye shes nyid la spyod yul ma dmigs
NK093(ge)002:15978: pas phyi dang nang med de ye shes kyis ma
NK093(ge)002:15979: khyab pa med pas kun tu yang nang du gyur
NK093(ge)002:15980: pa yina no // de bas na gnas gzhan du btsal mi dgos so //
NK093(ge)002:15984: rgyal ba dgyes pa'i mchog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:15985: rnal 'byor pa ganga theg pa chen por nges pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15986: sgo 'dira rdzas dang yo byad ldan pa'i lha mi
NK093(ge)002:15987: mang po ganga 'dus pa ni mchog tu nges pa'i
NK093(ge)002:15988: tshogsa chen po ma yina te /
NK093(ge)002:15989: rang gi rig pa'i chos nyid de kho na nyid
NK093(ge)002:15990: la chos thams cad dang 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga
NK093(ge)002:15991: yang ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i ngang du rtogs
NK093(ge)002:15992: pa de nyid tshogsa chen yongs su 'dus pa'i mchoga
NK093(ge)002:15993: nyid yin pas / 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi chos
NK093(ge)002:15994: so cog kun rang rig par 'ong bsdus med par
NK093(ge)002:15995: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs chen por rtogs pasa tha snyad
NK093(ge)002:15996: gnyis pa ril 'byung 'jug dang bral ba med par
NK093(ge)002:15997: de kho na nyid phyi mo'i mchod par gnas su
NK093(ge)002:15999: de lta bu ni dapaga tu med pa'i rgyal ba
NK093(ge)002:16000: thams cad mnyes shing dgyes pa'i dbyer med rnam dag
NK093(ge)002:16001: gi mchod pa mchoga dam pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16006: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16007: lam chen po'i skabs gang 'dira gzugs sgra dri ro
NK093(ge)002:16008: reg bya la sogs pa 'doda pa'i yon tan lngar
NK093(ge)002:16009: longs spyod pa ni yo byad chen po mina te
NK093(ge)002:16010: / kun rdzob kyi 'byor pa yin pas so //
NK093(ge)002:16011: de bas na sems kyi de kho na nyid mnyam
NK093(ge)002:16012: pa chen po ma nor bar rtogs nas gnyis med
NK093(ge)002:16013: du 'byor ba ni yang dag don gyi yo byad
NK093(ge)002:16014: chen po mchog tu gyur pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:16016: de ni ril gyi rgyu chen po'i phyir te /
NK093(ge)002:16017: dman pa dag la med pas lhag pa'i yo byad
NK093(ge)002:16018: dam pa cir yang 'char zhing dga' ba skyed pa
NK093(ge)002:16020: byang chub kyi sems 'bras bu'i chos kyi yo byad
NK093(ge)002:16021: kun gyi rtsa ba 'khor 'das kyi yon tan thams
NK093(ge)002:16022: cad 'byung ba'i gzhi chen po yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16027: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16028: chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i rjes su blo 'brangs nas
NK093(ge)002:16029: ched du sgom ste mngon du ci 'gyur bar byed
NK093(ge)002:16030: pa ni yang dag pa'i bsgom pa mina par 'dir
NK093(ge)002:16031: chos nyid bya ba bsam bya blo'i yul snang dang
NK093(ge)002:16032: yul can shes pa dbyer med par rtogs pa la
NK093(ge)002:16033: chos nyid du'ang 'du shes kyis dmigsa su meda pa
NK093(ge)002:16035: de ni dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa dama
NK093(ge)002:16036: pa rnams kyi gshegs shul rtogs par dka' ba'i gsang
NK093(ge)002:16037: lam ma nor ba yin pas de ltar rtogs na
NK093(ge)002:16038: 'di ltar sgom shesa na bsgoma pa'i lam ji snyed
NK093(ge)002:16039: pa rnams kyi phul dama pa rim par bgrod pa
NK093(ge)002:16040: las 'das te dmigs rtsol gyis g.yo ba dang bral
NK093(ge)002:16041: ba'i ngang las logs su med pa 'di nyid don
NK093(ge)002:16042: gyi dgongs pa 'khrul pa dang bral ba nyid do
NK093(ge)002:16047: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16048: 'dir bsrung mtshams med par rtogs pa la rtsa ba
NK093(ge)002:16049: dang yan lag gi dam tshig bsrung ngo zhes ched
NK093(ge)002:16050: du srung bar bya ba ci yang mi dmigas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16051: don la nyams pa'ang med de stong nyid chen po
NK093(ge)002:16052: mtha' gnyis ma grub pa'i ngang la bsrung rgyu med
NK093(ge)002:16053: cing yon tan cir yang 'byung ba'i zab don reg
NK093(ge)002:16054: par dka' bas gasnga ba dam pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16055: lam ma nor ba ste 'di ltar sems kyi chos nyid rtsol bral rig pa'i dam tshig go //
NK093(ge)002:16056: de'i don la so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK093(ge)002:16057: dbus mathara phye nas brtags pasa mtha' dbus dang phyogs
NK093(ge)002:16058: ris kyi tha snyad bsregs nas mnyam pa'i dam tshig
NK093(ge)002:16059: gi don ma nor ba shes shing rtogs na dam
NK093(ge)002:16060: tshig ji snyed pa kun srungsa pa'i gasnga ba dam
NK093(ge)002:16061: pa kho na'o // bdun pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16065: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16066: don chen po rtogs pa'i gdengs med na /
NK093(ge)002:16067: tshig gi lam du mnyam pa nyid yin no zhes brjod de smras kyang /
NK093(ge)002:16068: de la mnyam pa'i don gang yang mi dmigas pas mnyam don med do //
NK093(ge)002:16070: gsang sngags gasnga ba dam pa'i ngo bo 'dira thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gcig pa la /
NK093(ge)002:16071: de las gzhan du manyam pa'i don zhesa brjod de
NK093(ge)002:16072: mchog tu lhag pa zhig bzang por blta rgyu ga
NK093(ge)002:16073: la yoda de med pas na /
NK093(ge)002:16074: 'di ltar rtogs na ril rgyal ba'i thugs dang mnyam
NK093(ge)002:16075: par sangs rgyas kyi dgongas pa kun nasa 'dus pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16076: zhe phugs 'di'i don nyid dang mnyam pa yin pa
NK093(ge)002:16077: la blang dor ma dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:16082: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16083: lung chen gsang ba'i rnal 'byor chen po bla na med pa mchog gi skabs 'dir /
NK093(ge)002:16084: gang theg pa gazhana dag gi brtul zhugsa sme sha
NK093(ge)002:16085: la sogs pa spyod pa ni 'di'i spyod pa chen
NK093(ge)002:16086: po dam pa nyid mina no //
NK093(ge)002:16087: des na 'di nyid kyi spyod pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16088: chos nyid ji bzhin pa de la dera rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16089: rig pa gnyis med du gzhola te dbyings rig dbyer
NK093(ge)002:16090: med kyi ngang la gnas pas chos nyid la sems
NK093(ge)002:16091: nyid rol pa'i spyod pa ni 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK093(ge)002:16092: so cog thams cad chos nyid de'i ngang 'dira bcom
NK093(ge)002:16093: pas brtul zhing spyod pa phyogs med kyi don 'dir
NK093(ge)002:16094: bcugs te zhugsa pas blang dor gnyis su med par
NK093(ge)002:16095: ma brtsal don kun grub par byas pa la spyod
NK093(ge)002:16096: pa mi 'gog spyad pa med pa nyid ni brtul
NK093(ge)002:16097: zhugsa bla na med cing mchoga tu gyur ba yin
NK093(ge)002:16098: par bde bar gshegs pa kun nas 'dus pa rnams
NK093(ge)002:16099: kyis kyang gsungsa te bka' stsal pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16104: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16105: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi lam mchog 'di yi skabs
NK093(ge)002:16106: 'dira dngosa grub kyi dam pa de kho na nyid
NK093(ge)002:16107: kun gzhi byang chub semas kyi nges gasnga brjod pa
NK093(ge)002:16108: dang bral ba nyid yin pa'i phyir gzhan nas mi
NK093(ge)002:16109: gnyer te / 'bras bu'i snying por ye nas grub
NK093(ge)002:16110: zina du gnas pa la bya ba byas zin pasa
NK093(ge)002:16111: da gzod lha la re rtsol gyis gsola ba gdab
NK093(ge)002:16112: cing dngos grub gzhan nas thoba par bya ba med
NK093(ge)002:16113: gnyer te / do // de lta bu la sku
NK093(ge)002:16114: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dngosa grub rgyun
NK093(ge)002:16115: mi 'achada cing bar chad med pa zhesa bya bar
NK093(ge)002:16116: dgongas pa dama pa kun nas 'dusa pa'i rgyal ba
NK093(ge)002:16117: rnams kyis gsungsa te bka' stsal pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16122: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16123: de ltara bshad pa bzhin semsa kyi de bzhin nyid
NK093(ge)002:16124: gasnga sngags kyi don ji lta bar mthonga zhing rtogs
NK093(ge)002:16125: na sngona chad ma mthong ba'i chos nyid don gyi
NK093(ge)002:16126: lam chen po yang dag par mthonga zhing rtogs pa
NK093(ge)002:16127: yin pas de la ni dngos po'i ngo bo 'di
NK093(ge)002:16128: 'drar mthonga zhing shes par bya ba ci yanga med
NK093(ge)002:16129: pa nyid de / de nyid lam pa ganga su
NK093(ge)002:16130: zhig gi rig pa la gsal bar snang ste mngon
NK093(ge)002:16131: sum du shar ba ni lam mchog bde ba chen
NK093(ge)002:16133: dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor pa thog mthar las
NK093(ge)002:16134: kyang tha ma chen po pa mthong lam yongs su
NK093(ge)002:16137: de lta bu yi don mthong na //
NK093(ge)002:16138: mtshan mar mthong ba ci yang med //
NK093(ge)002:16139: sgyu ma tsam du tshul shes na //
NK093(ge)002:16140: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i don snang 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:16141: kha cig dag ni de don la //
NK093(ge)002:16142: mthong ba ci yang med gyur na //
NK093(ge)002:16143: snang ba zhes ni ci phyir gdags //
NK093(ge)002:16145: the tshom za 'gyur de dag la //
NK093(ge)002:16146: mthong ba med pa'i don de nyid //
NK093(ge)002:16147: yid kyi ngo la snang 'gyur na //
NK093(ge)002:16148: snang zhes de phyir brjod par bya //
NK093(ge)002:16149: zhes gsungs pa sogs 'di dag thams cad gsal bar bstan no //
NK093(ge)002:16153: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te //
NK093(ge)002:16154: grogsa po daga ji ltar bshad pa de daga ni /
NK093(ge)002:16155: de bzhin gshegs pa dama pa rnams kyi rjesa su
NK093(ge)002:16156: 'jug pa'i lam dama pa rang gi ngo bo zhes
NK093(ge)002:16157: bya ba / 'og min chen por 'di skada du
NK093(ge)002:16158: thos pa'i dgongs pa yongas su bgrosa pa yin par
NK093(ge)002:16159: bya ba / shes par bya'o // zhes gsang bdag
NK093(ge)002:16160: chen pos dam pa'i rigs can la bka' stsal to
NK093(ge)002:16161: bya ba / shes par bya'o // // le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK093(ge)002:16162: sangsa rgyas kuna gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chena po lasa /
NK093(ge)002:16163: skal ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams rgyal
NK093(ge)002:16164: ba'i shul lam gyi rjesa su 'jug pa'i lta ba
NK093(ge)002:16165: dang ting nge 'dzin mchog gi don gyi khyad par
NK093(ge)002:16167: lnga bcu rtsa dgu pa nyid gsal bar bshad pa'o
NK093(ge)002:16168: ////lnga pa sgron ma srel bar bya ba la don
NK093(ge)002:16175: mi shes pa'i gzhi med do //
NK093(ge)002:16176: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16177: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK093(ge)002:16178: rjes 'jug bka' stsal ma thag pa de nas yanga 'khor langa ka'i mang'a badga la sogas pa /
NK093(ge)002:16179: grogsa kyi semsa dapa'a dam pa rnams kyis ston pa
NK093(ge)002:16180: gasnga ba pa'i badga po la yongas su dri ba
NK093(ge)002:16181: drisa pa / kye gasnga ba pa'i badga po /
NK093(ge)002:16182: nyid kyis le'u zhe lnga pa 'dira chos kyi rnam
NK093(ge)002:16183: grangs bcu bkod pa las lnga pa rin po che
NK093(ge)002:16184: 'abra ba'i sgron ma bsrel bar bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:16185: zhesa dam baca'a bar dgongas pa de nyid ji ltar yongas su shes par bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:16186: zhes de skad ces dri ba yongsa su dris pa lasa /
NK093(ge)002:16187: ston mchog 'chad pa'i skyes bu gasnga ba pa'i badga posa lan smras te gsungs pa /
NK093(ge)002:16188: kye grogsa po dag /ces bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:16189: rin po che 'abra ba ni 'oda kyi 'byung gansa lagas te /
NK093(ge)002:16190: 'od de nyid 'thora rlung gi tshogas kyis kyang mi sod pas /
NK093(ge)002:16191: de'i byed las ni muna pa sel bar byed pa
NK093(ge)002:16192: kho na yin pasa de'i phyir nges pa'i tshig gis
NK093(ge)002:16193: mtshon te sgron ma zhesa bya bar grub pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16194: des na dpe de ltar don kyang rjes su sbyar te dpe don mtshungs pa'i ngo bor blta'o //
NK093(ge)002:16195: de ltar nges tshig dang ldan pa de'i rang gi ngo bo bstan pa ji lta bu zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:16196: de ni 'di ltar ma rig pa'am mi shes pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16197: rmongs pa sel ba'i rang rig pa'i shesa rab chen
NK093(ge)002:16198: po ye shes rang gsal ba nyid yina te /
NK093(ge)002:16199: de nye bar mtshon pa ni dper na nyi ma'i
NK093(ge)002:16200: snying po'am rina po che'i sgron ma 'od 'bar ba
NK093(ge)002:16201: la mun pa'i gzhi ngang gis meda pa bzhina du
NK093(ge)002:16202: ganga yang dag pa'i shes rab chen po rig pa
NK093(ge)002:16203: gsal ba'i ranga bzhina de la yang mi shes pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16204: ma rig pa ni gzhi yang med pas 'khrul pa
NK093(ge)002:16205: ming med chen por bstan pa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:16206: gsang bdag dga' rab dpa' bos dbang gi klong las /
NK093(ge)002:16207: de nyid de yi rang bzhin te //
NK093(ge)002:16208: de rig de snang de kho na //
NK093(ge)002:16209: nyi ma'am rin chen 'bar ba bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:16210: 'od dang ngo bo de nyid las //
NK093(ge)002:16211: yul dang gzhan gyis byas pa min //
NK093(ge)002:16212: zhes gsungs pa ltar rang gsal rnam dag chen po
NK093(ge)002:16213: yin yang gsal rkyang rang rgyud pa min par ris
NK093(ge)002:16214: med lhun rdzogs chen po nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:16215: de ltar gsal bar ston pa ni nges pa don gyi lung chen mthar thug pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16223: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16224: de bas na yang dag pa'i shes rab med pa
NK093(ge)002:16225: las lta ba tha dad du byung bar bstan pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16226: phyir / de yanga 'di ltar sprul pa'i sku mchog
NK093(ge)002:16227: sgron ma dama pa thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan
NK093(ge)002:16228: las 'das nas yang dag pa'i shes rab gsal ba
NK093(ge)002:16229: chen po de nyid ma go ba'i dbang gis rang
NK093(ge)002:16230: rig pa'i nyi ma nub para gyur pa'i dus su
NK093(ge)002:16231: phyir / snang ba na / chos rnams kun gyi
NK093(ge)002:16232: de bzhin nyid gsang ba'i dbyings gciga gi ngo bor
NK093(ge)002:16233: dbyer med pa'i de kho na nyid kyi ngang la
NK093(ge)002:16235: chos nyid de rig pa dang ma rig pa'i khyad
NK093(ge)002:16236: par gyis lta ba'i mtho dman dang bzang ngan mi
NK093(ge)002:16237: 'dra ba'i rnam para gyur te tha dad du 'byung
NK093(ge)002:16238: zhing snang bar gyur pa'i tshul nye bar bstan pa
NK093(ge)002:16240: muna pa'i sa pa so so'i skye bo'i shesa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16241: ya matshana can mu stegs byed kyi shes pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16242: byis pa nyan rang rnams kyi shes pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16243: phyogsa su riga pa sems tsam pa'i shesa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16244: mtha'a dbus 'byeda pa dbu ma pa'i shes pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16245: nges pa dama pa gsang sngags nyida kyi shes pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16247: mun pa'i shes pa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16248: log sred can gyi shes pa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:16249: byis pa'i shes pa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16250: phyogs su rig pa'i shes pa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:16251: mtha' dbus 'byed pa'i shes pa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16252: dam pa chen po'i shes pa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16257: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16258: de dag so so nas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:16259: kye grogas po dag /ces bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:16260: dang po gang mun pa'i shes pa nye bar ston pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16261: ganga gnyis su med pa'i de kho na nyid 'di
NK093(ge)002:16262: la brtags zhen gyis bdag gzhan du bzung ba las
NK093(ge)002:16263: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par phyin ci loga para mthong
NK093(ge)002:16264: ba skye bo pa rnams kyi shesa pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16269: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16270: gang loga par lta ba la chags sred can rnams kyi shesa pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16271: lta gzhung mi mthun pa sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa tha dad du smra zhing /
NK093(ge)002:16272: rtsa ba rtag pa dang chad pa gnyisa su 'doda pa mu stegs byed kyi shes pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16277: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16278: gang byis pa rnams kyi lta ba ni nye bar bstan pa 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:16279: mu stegs kyi chos rnams sam snang ba rags pa
NK093(ge)002:16280: gang yin pa dang gang zag gi bdag med para
NK093(ge)002:16281: smra zhing phyi gzung ba'i yul thams cad rdul phra
NK093(ge)002:16282: rab kyi chos tsam dang nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa
NK093(ge)002:16283: skad cig tsam rdzas su yod para 'doda pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16284: de yi tshul rgyas par bsnyad pa yang 'di ltar /
NK093(ge)002:16285: dang po gzugs kyi mtha' rdul phra rab dang /
NK093(ge)002:16287: lcags rdul la sogs par brtsis nas dapaga tshad kyi bar dang /
NK093(ge)002:16288: de las sa'i dkyil 'khor chen po la sogs par
NK093(ge)002:16289: snang ba yang rdul gyi ngo bor 'dod pa dang
NK093(ge)002:16290: / dus kyi tshad kyang dus kyi mtha' skad cig ma dang /
NK093(ge)002:16291: de nyid brgya dang nyi shu la de yi skad
NK093(ge)002:16292: cig la sogs pa nas yar brtsis pas nyin zhag
NK093(ge)002:16293: dang zla ba dang lo dang bskal pa chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:16295: ming gi mtha' yi ge sil bu nas ming tshig
NK093(ge)002:16296: la sogs pa tha snyad sna tshogs par gyur te
NK093(ge)002:16297: skar ma dang nyi zla dang ri bo mchog rab
NK093(ge)002:16298: nas 'khora yug gi bar dang 'gro ba lus can
NK093(ge)002:16299: rnams kyi lus bong che chung dang khru la sogs
NK093(ge)002:16300: nas dpag tshad sogs kyi bar du tshad sna tshogs
NK093(ge)002:16302: sems can de dag gi semas sam shes pa skye ba skad cig ma'i yun dang /
NK093(ge)002:16304: tshe tshad la sogs pa dang longas spyod che chung
NK093(ge)002:16305: gi tshul sogs so so'i tshad kyi rnam par bzhag
NK093(ge)002:16306: pa dang / 'gro ba'i snang tshul dang snod kyi dus bzhi gansa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16309: chags pa la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid las tha dada
NK093(ge)002:16310: kyi bye brag gi rnam grangs sna tshogs su phye
NK093(ge)002:16311: bas thams cad du yang mi rtag pa la sogs
NK093(ge)002:16313: rdul dang skad cig mar bshigas nas don dam du
NK093(ge)002:16314: rags par grub pa meda par smra zhing shes yul
NK093(ge)002:16316: rdul tsam yod do ces su 'doda pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:16317: rang nyid mya ngan las 'das pa la mosa pa
NK093(ge)002:16318: dang shes rab chung bas 'khor ba las nges par
NK093(ge)002:16319: 'byung ba'i 'jug thabs de tsam lasa ma gtogs par
NK093(ge)002:16320: lhag pa'i lta ba yod pa mina no //
NK093(ge)002:16325: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16326: skabs gang 'dira rnam par rig pa dang rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:16327: spyod pa'i kun rdzob pa don gyi phyogsa tsam shes
NK093(ge)002:16328: shing riga pa dag gi spyi'i gzhung ni /
NK093(ge)002:16329: yul du snang ba 'di kun phyi don du grub
NK093(ge)002:16330: pa med par ganga sems kyi bar chags las 'di
NK093(ge)002:16331: ltar snang ba kho na yin pasa sems su nges
NK093(ge)002:16333: phyi rol yul gyi dngosa po logs su ma grub pas gzung 'dzin rang rgyud pa med de /
NK093(ge)002:16334: dper na mig shes rab rib dang tsha ba'i rims
NK093(ge)002:16335: kyis bskyod pa ltar kun gzhi rnama par shes pa
NK093(ge)002:16336: 'khrul pa nyid gzung cha dang 'dzin cha'i yul sems
NK093(ge)002:16337: gnyis kyi rnam pa nyid du snang ba yin pas
NK093(ge)002:16339: dkar dmar gyi rnam pa rnams shes pa'i chos su
NK093(ge)002:16340: bden par smra ba rnam bden pa'am rnam bcas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16341: gzhung ngo // de lta bu'i sems de nyid gnyis
NK093(ge)002:16342: med kyi rang rig shel dag pa lta bur sus
NK093(ge)002:16343: kyang ma bcos ma byas par don dam par de
NK093(ge)002:16344: bzhina nyid du yod par 'dod pasa /
NK093(ge)002:16345: dkar dmar gyi rnam pa 'di dag shes pa'i chos su yang mi bden /
NK093(ge)002:16346: phyi rol gyi don du'ang mi bden par rdzun pa
NK093(ge)002:16347: dngos med kyi snang bar smra ba rnam rdzun pa'am
NK093(ge)002:16349: 'di yis gzhan dbang gi shes pa skad cig ma don dam du 'dod pas /
NK093(ge)002:16350: rnam rig tsam zhig rtag tu rnam par snang ste
NK093(ge)002:16351: chosa kyi sku yang rgyun gyi rtag para 'doda pa
NK093(ge)002:16352: yin no // lnga pa la gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:16355: mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma'o //
NK093(ge)002:16360: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16361: mtha' dbus ngesa para 'byed de mtha' gnyis las nges
NK093(ge)002:16362: par 'byung bar byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa gzhung phyi
NK093(ge)002:16363: mo'i dbu ma rab tu mi gnas pa la la
NK093(ge)002:16365: dngos po yul sems kyi snang ba 'di dag so
NK093(ge)002:16366: so yi rnam pa ganga dang gang dag tu snang
NK093(ge)002:16367: yang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba sgyu ma'i mtshan
NK093(ge)002:16368: nyid tsam dang shing rta bzhin du rgyu rkyen 'dus
NK093(ge)002:16369: bdo ba tsam zhig snang bas kuna rdzob tu mthun
NK093(ge)002:16370: par snang ba'i bya ba dang don byed nus pa
NK093(ge)002:16371: yin no // de la'ang yang dag pa'i kun rdzob
NK093(ge)002:16372: dang log pa'i kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid dang nges
NK093(ge)002:16373: tshig ji ltar 'jig rten na grags pa ltar bar
NK093(ge)002:16374: cha dbye bas tha snyad du'ang rang gi mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:16375: du grub par mi bzhed de /
NK093(ge)002:16376: des na yul du gsal bar 'dod pa'i mdo sde spyod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16377: sems su gsal bar 'dod pa'i rnal 'byor spyod pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16378: kun rdzob gang na gang du 'dod pa'ang blo gnyis
NK093(ge)002:16379: snang gi spyod yul tsam ste ngesa par don dam
NK093(ge)002:16380: du kun rdzob sgyu ma nyid kyang med de ma
NK093(ge)002:16381: skyes pa'i chos nyid du gcig pas bden pa gnyis
NK093(ge)002:16382: su dbye ba med par spros bral mnyam nyid chen
NK093(ge)002:16383: po blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16385: de'ang spros pa dang spros med kyi dbye ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:16386: mtshan nyid dang nges tshig gi rnam par bsnyad nas chos nyid rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16391: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16392: la la rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma pa dag
NK093(ge)002:16393: gi lugs kyis don dam mthar thug tu de ltar
NK093(ge)002:16394: ma skyes pa de kho nar ngesa kyang /
NK093(ge)002:16395: kun rdzob tu sems snang ba yin te /
NK093(ge)002:16396: sems 'khrul pa sgyu ma lta bu'i rang bzhin du
NK093(ge)002:16397: snang ba de lasa ma gtogas par yul sgyu ma
NK093(ge)002:16398: de nyid logs shig na yod cing 'onga ba mina
NK093(ge)002:16399: pas rnam rig pa'i don dam dang mthun pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16401: sems skad cig ma'i snang ba de nyid kyang rdo
NK093(ge)002:16402: rje gzegs ma la sogs pa'i gtan tshigs kyis gzhal
NK093(ge)002:16403: ba desa ni sems tsam gyi dngosa por yang grub
NK093(ge)002:16405: dama pa nyid du ngo bo stong pa nyid yin
NK093(ge)002:16406: pas dngos po'i rang bzhin cir yang grub pa med
NK093(ge)002:16411: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16412: la la mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma pa dag
NK093(ge)002:16413: gis dngos po kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam zhig snang
NK093(ge)002:16414: ba ni / ganga ma zina pa yin pa'i phyir sems kyi gzung cha snang ba ma yin te /
NK093(ge)002:16415: sems 'khrul pa de nyid yul du snang bar ni ganga na rung ste mi rung ngo //
NK093(ge)002:16416: de bas na kun rdzob tu rdul phra rab kyi
NK093(ge)002:16417: sa pa de ni phyi rol gyi don du yod
NK093(ge)002:16418: pa yin pas 'di las brtsams te yul gyi rnam
NK093(ge)002:16419: pa kuna sna tshogs su bkra bar nyan thos dang
NK093(ge)002:16420: dgra bcom pa kyang mkhyen pa nyid pas de ltar
NK093(ge)002:16423: kun rdzob kyi rdul phra rab kyi rnam pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:16424: kyang phyogs chas rnam par dbye bas ma grub pas
NK093(ge)002:16425: na kun rdzob slu ba dang 'drida pa can gyi
NK093(ge)002:16426: chos ltar du yoda pa ma yina pas gnyis su
NK093(ge)002:16427: med par 'dod de stong pa nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:16428: de bas na blo gros mi zad pas bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK093(ge)002:16429: blo gros chen po rdul phra rab kyis gzhig na
NK093(ge)002:16430: ba lang gi rwa la dngos por mi 'dug go
NK093(ge)002:16439: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16440: gsang sngags dama pa bla na med pa nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:16441: lta ba dama pa mchog tu gyur pa ganga gi
NK093(ge)002:16442: bzhed pa ni / chos so cog ye ji bzhin
NK093(ge)002:16443: pa'i chos nyid du ye gdod ma nasa sangsa rgyas
NK093(ge)002:16444: pa yin pa la gdags brjod thams cad dang bral
NK093(ge)002:16445: zhing de nyid kyang mngon du bya zhing don du
NK093(ge)002:16447: 'o na tshig tu btags pa la dgos pa med do bar dogs pa la /
NK093(ge)002:16448: de lta bu'i don rtogs pa mina par gdengs ma
NK093(ge)002:16449: chud pa dag gi gnyis su 'dzin lta ba ngan
NK093(ge)002:16450: pa zlog nas don ma nor ba la gzud pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16451: phyir du ye nas gnyis su med par sangsa rgyas
NK093(ge)002:16452: pa yin no // zhes de skad ces brjod pa
NK093(ge)002:16453: yang tha snyad tsam du btags te brjod para zad
NK093(ge)002:16454: pa yin no // kyi / don gyi ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:16455: nyid la ye gdod nas bkoda pa tshig gi lam
NK093(ge)002:16456: gyi tha snyad yod med gnyis kyi brjod pa dang
NK093(ge)002:16457: bral ba'i thig le chen po chos kyi skur gsal
NK093(ge)002:16458: pa yin no // kyi / ba la / bden
NK093(ge)002:16459: pa gnyis su yod ces sgro 'dogs pa dang med
NK093(ge)002:16460: ces skur pa gdab pa'i tshig gi tha snyad don
NK093(ge)002:16461: la mi gadgas te tshig brjod kyis btsal ba'i 'os
NK093(ge)002:16462: min pas gtan tshigs kyis gtse bas don gyi bzhag
NK093(ge)002:16463: sa tshol ba'i tshig rnams kyis bden pa gnyis kyi
NK093(ge)002:16464: brjod pa'i tha snyada so so'i tshiga lam las 'adsa
NK093(ge)002:16465: te gdags pa dang bral ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:16466: de lta bu la ni bden pa gnyis yod do //
NK093(ge)002:16468: med do zhes pa'i tha snyad gdags su med de
NK093(ge)002:16469: brjod pas mi phebs pas gdags pa las grol ba
NK093(ge)002:16470: kho na'o // de bas na mnyam pa chen po
NK093(ge)002:16471: la bden pa gnyis su rtsod pa ni don mi
NK093(ge)002:16472: mthong ba'i nad yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:16473: de'ang dper na nama mkha'a 'di ni yoda pa'am meda
NK093(ge)002:16474: pa nyid do ces blun po mi mkhas pa rnams
NK093(ge)002:16475: ni phyogs su bzung nas rtsod para 'gyur gyi /
NK093(ge)002:16476: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid la makhasa pa rnams ni de ltar mina pas rtsod pa dang bral te /
NK093(ge)002:16477: gang de ltar rtsod pa la ji ga snyam nas
NK093(ge)002:16478: ngo mtshar cher skye bar byed de mthun pa'i dpe
NK093(ge)002:16479: las don gyi dper blangs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16481: chos nyid de bzhina nyid 'di mtha' yod pa dang
NK093(ge)002:16482: med pa nyid ces bden pa ris su phye nas
NK093(ge)002:16483: gsang sngags pa shed ma bye ba'i byis pa nyan
NK093(ge)002:16484: rang dbu sems rnams ni rtsod para 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:16485: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi don rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16486: skyes bu ganga daga ye gnyis su med pa'i ngang
NK093(ge)002:16487: la de nyid du'ang mi rtog pa ni de ltar
NK093(ge)002:16488: mina te rtsod pa'i tha snyad dang bral ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:16489: de bas na de bzhin nyid la mthar bzung nas
NK093(ge)002:16490: rtsod pa ni shesa raba 'achala bar nges pa kho
NK093(ge)002:16491: nar zada do // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:16492: 'di ltar 'khrul pa'i ngo la snang ba'i snod bcud
NK093(ge)002:16493: la sogs pa'i chosa thamsa cada kun ye nas gnyis
NK093(ge)002:16494: su med pa'am lhun gyis grub pa'i nganga gisa sangsa
NK093(ge)002:16495: rgyas pa yin pa'i don gyis yod med rtag chad
NK093(ge)002:16496: snang stong las grol ba'i chos sku chen po nyid
NK093(ge)002:16498: byis pas 'phrul du brtsal te sngar dngos po la
NK093(ge)002:16499: sangs rgyas pa'i don mchog dam pa min pa zhig
NK093(ge)002:16500: lasa yina par sgrubs pas sangs rgyas par gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:16502: chos rnams kyi mnyam pa nyid ni ngo bo nyid
NK093(ge)002:16503: kyis rtogs rung ma rtogs rung ye nas de bzhin
NK093(ge)002:16505: 'phral du rmongs pa dag gis ye nas sangs rgyas
NK093(ge)002:16506: pa yina zhes bya ba dang mina zhes brjod pas
NK093(ge)002:16507: ci zhig byar yoda de med do //
NK093(ge)002:16508: des na de skad smra ba nyid la da dung
NK093(ge)002:16509: yul du byed pa'i sgrib pa yod pas don yang
NK093(ge)002:16511: dper na nam mkha' ye nas stong pa'i dag pa
NK093(ge)002:16512: chen po la nama mkha'a 'di ni meda do zhes
NK093(ge)002:16513: nam mkha'i don mi shes pa'i blun po ganga zhiga
NK093(ge)002:16514: dngos po med par yid la rtog par byed do
NK093(ge)002:16515: // nam mkha' ganga gi mtshan nyid shes pa dag
NK093(ge)002:16516: ni med do bar bsam par yang mi 'dzin tshig
NK093(ge)002:16517: tu'ang mi brjod de bsam pa cir yang mi skye'o
NK093(ge)002:16518: // // de ltar don ma mthong bas chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:16519: yang dag par mi shes pa'i mun sprul rnams gang
NK093(ge)002:16520: dag gis ni de kho na nyid ni mtha' dang
NK093(ge)002:16521: bral ba'o zhes zhe bas 'dzin zhing rtogs par byed
NK093(ge)002:16522: de tshig tu'ang brjod par byed do //
NK093(ge)002:16523: gang chos nyid ji lta ba'i don mthong zhing shes
NK093(ge)002:16524: pa'i mi chen po rnams ni ye nasa mtha' dang
NK093(ge)002:16525: bral ba nyid du'ang yonga ye mi rtog par yid
NK093(ge)002:16526: la mi byed rjes su mi 'brang zhing mtha' dang
NK093(ge)002:16527: bral ba mina para yang kun nas mi rtog zhe
NK093(ge)002:16528: bas mi 'dzin rjes su'ang mi 'brang ste /
NK093(ge)002:16529: de bas na yod med dang yin min la sogs
NK093(ge)002:16530: pa'i tshig tu'ang mi brjod pa ni don la rnal
NK093(ge)002:16531: du phebs pa'i mi rtog pa nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:16532: de lta bu'i gdeng ma chud pa'i mun sprul pa
NK093(ge)002:16533: dag rang gi zhen phyogs kyi bsam ngan gyi dbang
NK093(ge)002:16534: gis btsal du med cing yul dang bral ba ni
NK093(ge)002:16535: rgyal ba'i spyod yul yin gyi /
NK093(ge)002:16536: gang zag gi spyod yul ma yin no zhes smra
NK093(ge)002:16537: ba dag ni theg pa chen por gcig char du
NK093(ge)002:16538: 'jug pa khas 'ches nas theg pa chung ngu'i lta
NK093(ge)002:16540: rgyal po dmangs su 'bab pa lta bu'o //
NK093(ge)002:16541: zhes gnubs chen mkhyen brtse'i gter mdzod kyis gdams par mdzad do //
NK093(ge)002:16549: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16550: yang dag pa'i shes rab chen po de la yanga
NK093(ge)002:16551: tshul 'di ltara so sora rtog pa'i blo gros kyis
NK093(ge)002:16553: shes rab skyed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK093(ge)002:16561: de ltar re rer byas pas rnam grangs rnam pa brgyad du 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:16563: shes rab mchog gi rgyu bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16565: shes rab dam pa'i rnam grangs bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16567: shes rab zab mo'i nges tshig bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16568: shes rab gsal ba'i ngo bo bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:16569: shes rab nges pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16570: shes rab mchog gi dgos ched bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16575: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16576: 'di ltar rnam grangs dang po 'dira gsang sngags kyi
NK093(ge)002:16577: shes rab 'di nyid ni rtogs par byed pa gang
NK093(ge)002:16578: gi rgyu las ji ltar byung ba yin zhe na
NK093(ge)002:16579: / ranga byung gi ye shes kyi ngo bo ji
NK093(ge)002:16580: ltar yin pa de nyid thos bsam yang dag pa
NK093(ge)002:16581: la brten nas rtsing zhib kyi tshul du rtog cing
NK093(ge)002:16582: dpyod pa dang bacasa pa'i so sor rtog pa'i shes
NK093(ge)002:16583: rab dang ldan pas rnal 'byor pa lta bas ma
NK093(ge)002:16584: 'dres yongs rdzogs su gzhal te don la 'jug pa
NK093(ge)002:16585: ganga dag rig pa'i shes rab chen po gang la
NK093(ge)002:16586: g.yo thob brtan cing mthar phyin pa'i tshul gyis bogs
NK093(ge)002:16587: su skye zhing 'og nas gong du mcheda par 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:16588: pa yin pa'i phyir ji lta ji snyed kyi gnas
NK093(ge)002:16589: la rtog cing dpyod pas so sor rtog pa'i shes
NK093(ge)002:16590: rab gnyis po de ni mi dmigs pa'i shes rab
NK093(ge)002:16591: dang so sor rtog pa'i shes rab chen po 'di
NK093(ge)002:16592: daga nyid kyi rgyu ma nor ba skyed par byed
NK093(ge)002:16593: pa'i thabs dam pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16598: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16599: yang dag pa'i shes rab chen po gang de'i byed lasa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16600: gang gnyis med kyi ngo bo mina par brtags pas
NK093(ge)002:16601: tha dad du gyur pa'i chos ji snyed pa mang
NK093(ge)002:16602: po'i mtho dman gyi khyad para dang rnam pa'i bye
NK093(ge)002:16603: brag ma 'dres pa la tha dada para yang ngesa
NK093(ge)002:16604: par 'byed cing / so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis de dag la shes pa 'jug pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16605: de dag gi 'brela ba bsgrub pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16606: de dag la yang dag pa'i lung dang man ngag tshad ma'i sbyor ba tshang bar dgod cing /
NK093(ge)002:16607: gtan tshigs rgyas pa 'ba' zhig gis sbyor ba byed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16608: chos mthun pa'i dpe yis sbyor ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:16609: mi mthun pa nyid can gyis sbyor ba 'god pa
NK093(ge)002:16610: dang bacasa te chos rtags kyi don dang mi 'gal
NK093(ge)002:16611: ba'i sbyor ba dang ldan pas /
NK093(ge)002:16612: chos nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i ngo bo yang dag
NK093(ge)002:16613: pa'i don de nyid mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyis
NK093(ge)002:16614: ngos 'dzina zhing phyin ci ma loga para gtan la
NK093(ge)002:16615: phabs nas ma nor ba'i don du mthar phyin par
NK093(ge)002:16616: byed pas gsang sngags gnyis med kyi ngo bo dngos
NK093(ge)002:16617: mngona du 'byin cing dona gyi gnas lugs rig pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16618: mngon sum du gsal bar 'doda pa dag gis de
NK093(ge)002:16619: ltar brtson te don gyi lam la gnas par byas
NK093(ge)002:16620: pas rtogs par dka' ba'i shes rab dang don ji
NK093(ge)002:16621: bzhin pa'i ngo bo dbyer med du 'brel ba'i nyag
NK093(ge)002:16622: gcig thig le'i klong du grol bar byed pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16623: 'di ni gol sgrib shan 'byed kyi gnad phyed de gsang ba'i don la 'jug pa'ang yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16628: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16629: yang dag pa'i shes rab de'i rnam grangsa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16630: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab dang /
NK093(ge)002:16631: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab rnam pa gnyis te /
NK093(ge)002:16632: gtan la dbab cing rtogs par bya ba'i yul dona
NK093(ge)002:16633: gyi ngo bo ma 'dres pa dang yongs su rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:16634: pa bzhina du phye nas bstan pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16635: des na shes bya'i yul kun la mtshan nyid ma
NK093(ge)002:16636: 'dres par ngesa para 'byed cing yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16637: chos nyid du rtogs nas thos bsam sgom pa'i shes
NK093(ge)002:16638: rab gsum nyid ldan pas don mngon du byed pa
NK093(ge)002:16639: yin te / chos ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa kun rang gsal lhun rdzogs su bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16644: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16645: shes rab dam pa de nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK093(ge)002:16646: so sor rtog pas ma 'dres pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16647: mi dmigs pas yongsa su rdzogsa par shes pa yin la /
NK093(ge)002:16648: mi dmigs pa de yang chos rnams thams cad kun
NK093(ge)002:16649: ngo bo ma grub pas dngosa po meda par rtogs
NK093(ge)002:16650: shing dngos med de nyid du'ang mi rtog par mi
NK093(ge)002:16651: dmigs pa'i ngang gcig tu yongas su rdzogas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16652: so sor rtog pa de yang /
NK093(ge)002:16653: so sora snang ba'i chos brtags pa tha dad pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16654: 'khrul pa la ngo bo dang btags pa tha dad
NK093(ge)002:16655: pa'i chos bsam gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16656: bye brag ji snyed pa kun de dag ji lta
NK093(ge)002:16657: bar ma 'dres par gsal zhing rig par byed pa'o
NK093(ge)002:16658: // mdor na de ltar gsal la ma 'dres pa
NK093(ge)002:16659: dang de nyid ji bzhina pa'i ngo bor mi dmigs
NK093(ge)002:16660: par gsal la yongs su rdzogs par mngon du byed
NK093(ge)002:16661: pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16666: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16667: 'o na ci'i phyir shes rab ces bya zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:16668: gang 'dir gsang sngags de kho na nyid kyi don
NK093(ge)002:16669: phyina ci ma loga pa nyid ma nor bar khong
NK093(ge)002:16671: shes bya'i don mchog dam pa yongsa su chub cing
NK093(ge)002:16672: shes pas shes byed rnams kyi dam pa mchog gam
NK093(ge)002:16673: phul du gyur pas na shes rab ces brjod pa
NK093(ge)002:16678: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16679: shes rab chen po'i ngo bo nyid ni /
NK093(ge)002:16680: chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid la kun nas ma
NK093(ge)002:16681: rmongsa par thams cada rang gasla sgrib med du gzigs
NK093(ge)002:16682: te / shes bya ganga la yang mkhyen cha ma
NK093(ge)002:16683: 'aggas par thogas pa med par kun shes pa la
NK093(ge)002:16685: ganga sngar gsang don zab mo mi shes pa rnams
NK093(ge)002:16686: shes par byed de ma riga pa dang the tshom
NK093(ge)002:16687: gyi dri ma gcoda cing yid ches pa'i gdengs dang
NK093(ge)002:16688: ldan par byed pa nyid yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16693: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16694: yang dag pa'i shes rab chen po'i 'bras bu ni /
NK093(ge)002:16695: shes rab gsal ba de nyid yang dag pa'i rtog
NK093(ge)002:16696: dpyod kyis skye zhing mcheda de kun tu 'phel zhing
NK093(ge)002:16697: rgyas par gyur pa nyid kyi sgo nas /
NK093(ge)002:16698: gsang sngags mchog gi don gang la rtogs pa'i rig
NK093(ge)002:16699: pa'am ye shes gong 'phel du mcheda pa gang gi
NK093(ge)002:16700: bslab pa'i mtha' kun la mkhas par chub pa'i shes
NK093(ge)002:16701: rab kyis / chos nyid sel med pa'i don gyi
NK093(ge)002:16702: klung du gnyis su med par zhugsa par gyur pas
NK093(ge)002:16703: 'bras bu thams cad mkhyen pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16704: mi dmigs pa'i ye shes ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su thob par 'gyur ba'i /
NK093(ge)002:16705: 'du shes klong du chud pas gsang sngags bla na
NK093(ge)002:16706: med pa'i don mchog gang la makhasa shing gdeng du
NK093(ge)002:16707: gyur pa'i ye shesa tshad meda du rgyas te mu
NK093(ge)002:16708: mtha' med par 'phel bar gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16716: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16717: shes rab de nyid dam pa ganga la bstan pa'i dgos ched ni /
NK093(ge)002:16718: lam pa dang 'gro ba su zhig loga par lta
NK093(ge)002:16719: ba la gnas te ma rtogs pa de nyida rnam
NK093(ge)002:16720: par dag ste / theg pa chen po'i don bla
NK093(ge)002:16721: na med pa de nyid gdeng du chud de phul
NK093(ge)002:16722: du phyin par bya ba'i phyira du /
NK093(ge)002:16723: ma rig pa'i ling tog bsal bar byed pas dmigas
NK093(ge)002:16724: bu yang dag pa'i shes rab mchog tu gasla ba'i
NK093(ge)002:16725: sgron ma yis chos nyid ji bzhin pa gsang sngags
NK093(ge)002:16726: kyi de kho na nyid de la ma nor bar
NK093(ge)002:16729: gzhan sel ba'i dgos pa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16730: don du gnyer ba'i dgos pa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16735: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16736: 'o na de med na skyon ci yod ce na /
NK093(ge)002:16737: yang dag pa'i shes rab kyi sgron ma'i snang ba
NK093(ge)002:16738: mi shes par rmongs pa mi shes pas mdongs par
NK093(ge)002:16739: gyur pa rnams ni shes shing mthonga bar bya ba
NK093(ge)002:16740: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa kun la
NK093(ge)002:16741: yang rang gi ma rig pa'i mun pasa bsgribsa te
NK093(ge)002:16742: yang dag pa'i don mthong du mi ster bas dus
NK093(ge)002:16743: nama du gyur kyang gsang sngags kyi zab don snang
NK093(ge)002:16745: mdongs pa'am longa ba'i grong khyer chena pora ltung ste
NK093(ge)002:16746: khams gsum du 'gro ba'i phyir yang de la dgongs
NK093(ge)002:16752: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16753: shes rab chen po yod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK093(ge)002:16754: de bas na shes rab mchog gi sgron ma 'od
NK093(ge)002:16755: 'abra ba ganga nyid legs par srel te mkhyen rab
NK093(ge)002:16756: dam pa dang ldan pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16757: shes shing mthong bar bya ba'i chos kun la ma
NK093(ge)002:16758: rig pa'i mun pa dag cing sangsa nas blo gros
NK093(ge)002:16759: mchog tu gasla ba'i sgo nas chos nyid ji bzhin
NK093(ge)002:16760: pa rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ma nor ma bcosa pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16761: de bzhina nyid kyi don mthar thug pa yang sgron
NK093(ge)002:16762: ma'i dmigas busa nges par khrid nas yang dag par
NK093(ge)002:16763: mthonga zhing rtogs para 'gyur ba'i phyir dgos ched de
NK093(ge)002:16764: lta bu la dgongs te bstan pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16765: gsum pa zhabs bsdu ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:16769: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16770: bla na med pa'i shes rab kyi tshul ni ji
NK093(ge)002:16771: skad bstan pa de ltar du nges pa yin pas
NK093(ge)002:16772: lang ka la sogs pa dama pa'i grogsa po khyed
NK093(ge)002:16773: rnams kyis kyang yang dag pa'i shes rab nor bu
NK093(ge)002:16774: rina chena mchog gi sgron ma rab tu 'abra ba'i
NK093(ge)002:16775: me 'od gsal ba de nyid sems kyi mun par
NK093(ge)002:16776: snang byed kyi dmigas bura ma srela bar rmongs pas
NK093(ge)002:16778: don ji bzhin pa'i de kho na nyid kyi gnas
NK093(ge)002:16779: lugs rang snang rig pa'i gsera bzang po rmad du
NK093(ge)002:16780: byung ba de nyid ma nor bar mthonga zhing rtogs
NK093(ge)002:16781: par ga la rigas te rigs pa ma yin pas
NK093(ge)002:16782: de la ched du gyis shig par gdams pa ste
NK093(ge)002:16783: thag lta bas bcad par 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:16784: grogsa po dag /bshad pa de dag ni /
NK093(ge)002:16785: sgron ma dam pa srel bar bya'o zhesa sngar dam
NK093(ge)002:16786: bcas pa de yi dgongsa pa dama pa'i ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:16787: nyid yang dag par nor ba med par legsa para
NK093(ge)002:16788: bgrosa te bstan pa yin para shesa para bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:16790: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chena po lasa /
NK093(ge)002:16791: rnal 'byor mchog gi snang byed miga gi sgron mas
NK093(ge)002:16792: shes rab kyi spyan dang ldan par bya ba'i tshul
NK093(ge)002:16793: bstan pa'i le'u ste drug cu tham pa nyid legs
NK093(ge)002:16795: drug pa khyad par du bla mar 'gro ba la gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:16803: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16804: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK093(ge)002:16805: sgron ma bstan ma thag pa de nas yanga 'khor
NK093(ge)002:16806: langa ka'i mang'a badga la sogas pa damna pa dama
NK093(ge)002:16807: pa'i semas dapa'a chena po rnams kyis dgos pa'i don
NK093(ge)002:16808: gyi dri ba yongas su dris pa /
NK093(ge)002:16809: kye gasnga ba pa'i badga po /
NK093(ge)002:16810: nyid kyis le'u zhe lnga par /
NK093(ge)002:16811: khyad par du bla mara 'gro bar bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:16812: zhesa dama baca'a bar dgongas pa de nyid ji ltar yongas su shes para bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:16813: de skad ces gsola te chos kyi rnam grangs drug pa dris pa las /
NK093(ge)002:16814: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gasnga ba pa'i badga pos lan smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK093(ge)002:16815: kye grogsa po dag khyad para du 'gro bar bya
NK093(ge)002:16816: ba zhu bar de ni rang gi don du legas
NK093(ge)002:16817: so // gzhan don du'ang shina tu rab tu legas so //
NK093(ge)002:16818: de bas lan dngos gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:16819: sa yi khyad par 'og nas gong du bgrod par bya ba de ni 'di ltar /
NK093(ge)002:16820: dper na sa gzhi chen po la brten nas lo tog snang ba bzhin /
NK093(ge)002:16821: snga ma la brten nas phyi mar smin par byed pa'i phyir sa'i ming 'thob ste /
NK093(ge)002:16822: de yang ston pa sa makhana dama pa yang dag
NK093(ge)002:16823: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis rnal 'byor pa
NK093(ge)002:16824: lam pa rnams kyi sa yi khyad pa yongas su
NK093(ge)002:16825: snang zhing gsal bar byed pa zhesa bya ba'i mtshon
NK093(ge)002:16826: pa thabs kyi sgron ma legas para bkoda de sgro
NK093(ge)002:16827: skur med par rim par nye bar bstan pa ni
NK093(ge)002:16829: gong ma'i sa dang 'og ma'i sa yi khyad para mtho dman nyid du 'byung ba'i rgyu ni /
NK093(ge)002:16830: sa'i grangs dang lta spyod kyi khyad par kun theg
NK093(ge)002:16831: pa chen po bla na med pa ganga 'dira yongsa
NK093(ge)002:16832: kyis chos nyid du gcig cing don la dbyer med
NK093(ge)002:16833: yin pa la / theg pa chen po'i don gyi
NK093(ge)002:16834: shesa bya nyid gtan la 'bebs pa'i shes rab kyis
