NK093(ge)002:16835: sgro 'dogs gcoda par byed pa'i tshe ji ltar rtogs
NK093(ge)002:16836: pa'i tshul gyi blo rtsal che chung gi khyad par
NK093(ge)002:16837: gyis ranga gi riga pa nyid rtogs pa'i shes rab
NK093(ge)002:16838: che chung dang mthun par mtho damna gyi rima para
NK093(ge)002:16839: snang bar zad kyi de las gzhan pa med pa'o
NK093(ge)002:16840: yin pa la / // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK093(ge)002:16841: sa'i khyad par 'byung ba spyir bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16842: ji ltar 'byung ba'i bye brag so sor bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16844: rgyal po'i dkor mdzod kyi dpes khyad par yod par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16845: skas kyi gdang bu'i dpes khyad par yod par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16846: khang pa sgo mngas kyi dpes khyad par yod par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:16847: ri dang mi'i dpes khyad par yod par bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16852: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16853: de yang sa'i khyad par nye bar mtshon pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:16854: dpera na rgyal po chen po'i dkora mdzoda kyi nang
NK093(ge)002:16855: nasa nor che chung ji tsam zhig dbang ba thabas
NK093(ge)002:16856: kyis blangs nas spyod par 'doda pa ganga su yang
NK093(ge)002:16858: mi rigs bzhi las mnga' 'og tu gyur pa dag ni /
NK093(ge)002:16859: rgyal po'i chos kyis nor srun pa sogs daka'a ba
NK093(ge)002:16860: thub pa dang mi thub pa'i dbang las go chod
NK093(ge)002:16861: pa dang mi chod pa yi 'bangs rigs rang re
NK093(ge)002:16862: phyi 'khor dang nanga 'khor mtho dman gyi khyad para
NK093(ge)002:16863: ltar gyis dkor nor la spyod pa dang sgo so
NK093(ge)002:16864: sor 'juga pa'i skal ba dang bya byed kyi lasa
NK093(ge)002:16865: dang thabas kyi rim pa lasa dbang che chung dang
NK093(ge)002:16866: ngo mtho damna gyi khyad par dang mthun par rang
NK093(ge)002:16867: rang gi rtsal gyis rin po che dang yig tshang
NK093(ge)002:16868: ganga zhig lena pa na yang /
NK093(ge)002:16869: gang las blang bar bya ba'i yul rgyal po gcig gi nor la spyod pa las med na yanga /
NK093(ge)002:16870: gser dngul dang g.yu la sogs pa'i rina chena sna
NK093(ge)002:16871: 'ag'i rnam grangs thob pa'i khyad para las thabs che
NK093(ge)002:16872: chung gang gis thob pa'i rtags de daga dang mthun
NK093(ge)002:16873: par rang skal gang la dbang ba ltar thabsa chena
NK093(ge)002:16874: sgo rgu so sora yig tshang sgo rgu'i rim pa
NK093(ge)002:16876: 'dir rgu zhes pa yod do cog lta bu'i don te /
NK093(ge)002:16877: grangs nges med par don yang theg pa mtha' yas pa dang sbyar /
NK093(ge)002:16879: de ni rims kyis pa'i dpe yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16881: gal te rgyala po chen pora gyur pa zhig na
NK093(ge)002:16882: de ni nor thams cad kun la rang dabnga du
NK093(ge)002:16883: mnga' bsgyur byed pa'i badga po nyid du 'gyur ba
NK093(ge)002:16884: yina no // dpe de bzhin du /
NK093(ge)002:16885: mtshan nyid gang du'ang mi zin pas mi gansa pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16886: gsang ba chos nyid ma bcosa pa'i de bzhina nyid
NK093(ge)002:16887: ni theg pa chen po ste /
NK093(ge)002:16888: shesa bya thams cad de yi ngang lasa gzhan du meda pa la /
NK093(ge)002:16889: gang 'di la rang rang gi rig pa'i shes rab
NK093(ge)002:16890: kyis ji ltar rtogs pa'i blo rtsala gyi nus pa
NK093(ge)002:16891: che chung gi khyad para gyis rims kyis pa la
NK093(ge)002:16892: so so'i lta spyod dang ting nge 'dzin gyi 'juga
NK093(ge)002:16893: sgo mi mthun par sna tshogs su snang la /
NK093(ge)002:16894: gcig char bas ni de kun la rim pa nasa
NK093(ge)002:16895: 'jug mi dgos par rtogs pa rdzogs pa 'gyur ba'i
NK093(ge)002:16896: phyir khyad par so sor spyod pa ni de ltar
NK093(ge)002:16902: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16903: de bas na rtogs par bya ba'i don de yi
NK093(ge)002:16904: ngo bo ni rang rig pa de bzhin nyid chos
NK093(ge)002:16905: nyid dbyings kyi rang bzhin de kho na nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:16906: ngang gciga tu dbyer med mnyam pa chen por gnas
NK093(ge)002:16907: pa la / de nyid rtogs pa'i tshul gyis lta ba'i rtsal 'phang mtho damna gyi khyad para gyis /
NK093(ge)002:16908: theg pa'i rim pa dang sa yi go 'aphanga kyang mtho dman gyi khyad para can du gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:16909: rgyu rim gyis rtsol ba dang 'bras bu cig char ba gnyis su snang la /
NK093(ge)002:16910: der yang rim par bgrod pa'i skabs nyid du dper
NK093(ge)002:16911: na skas kyi gdang bu bzhin du yan lag gi
NK093(ge)002:16912: rima pa yang 'gyur dbang ma nges pa nas rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:16913: pa spyir chibs kyi bar du mtho dman gyi khyad
NK093(ge)002:16914: par de ltar du snang ba yina pas so sor
NK093(ge)002:16920: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16921: ganga gzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi chos nyid 'dira thams
NK093(ge)002:16922: cada kun gnas lugs ji lta ba'i ngang du gciga
NK093(ge)002:16923: pa la tha dad kyi spros pa med na yang
NK093(ge)002:16924: / gnas lugs de nyid mthonga ba dang rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16925: khyad par mi mthun pa de yi dabnga gisa so
NK093(ge)002:16926: sor gyur pa ni dpera na phyoogs kun nas 'byung
NK093(ge)002:16927: zhing mang po gansa pa'i khang pa chen po sgo
NK093(ge)002:16928: mangas kyi dpe bzhina du sa yi rim pa dang
NK093(ge)002:16929: rnam par thara pa'i theg pa rnam grangs so so'i
NK093(ge)002:16930: sgo mang po blo rim dang mthun par gzhi'i chos
NK093(ge)002:16931: nyid kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems gciga gi ngang
NK093(ge)002:16932: la mi mthun pa sna tshogas pa de ltar mthong
NK093(ge)002:16933: stangs tha dad par snang ba ni rims kyis pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16934: / snang tshul lo // 'on te na grub pa'i
NK093(ge)002:16935: mtha' yang tha dad par 'gyur ro bar dogs pa
NK093(ge)002:16936: / snang tshul lo // la / theg pa chen
NK093(ge)002:16937: po gsang sngags gcig char bas ni tshe 'dir sa
NK093(ge)002:16938: dang rnam par thara pa'i sgo ganga dag ji snyed
NK093(ge)002:16939: pa la rgyu mtshan nyid nas rim par 'juga pa
NK093(ge)002:16940: la sogas pas ma sbyangas ma btsal kyang /
NK093(ge)002:16941: theg pa chen po gsang chen nges pa'i snying po
NK093(ge)002:16942: ni kun gyi don gyi yang gzhir gyur pas rtsa
NK093(ge)002:16943: ba chen po 'dira bacada de ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:16944: su rtogs par gyur na gzhan kun kyang rtogs pa
NK093(ge)002:16945: yin pasa gsar du rtogs par bya mi dgos la
NK093(ge)002:16946: / des na kun gyi grub pa'i mtha' yang 'dir
NK093(ge)002:16947: gciga ste theg pa tha dada kyi rim pa sna
NK093(ge)002:16948: tshogs su grub pa ni gnas lugs la yongas kyis
NK093(ge)002:16949: meda pas grub pa'i mtha' chen po 'dir ngang gis
NK093(ge)002:16950: dbyer med cing gcig pa kho na'o //
NK093(ge)002:16955: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16956: der yang ma zad khyad par de ni dper na
NK093(ge)002:16957: ri phal pa'i rtse nas mthong ba mi gsal ba
NK093(ge)002:16958: dang / lhun po mchog rab kyi rtse nas gling
NK093(ge)002:16959: rnams thams cad gsal bar mthong ba lta bu dang
NK093(ge)002:16960: dang / / tshong dpon lta bu kun tu rgyu
NK093(ge)002:16961: ba'i mis yul ji snyed pa bgrod pas thos pa
NK093(ge)002:16962: dang / / che ba dang / gzhona nu na
NK093(ge)002:16963: tshod dar la bab pa rang rtsar gnas par de
NK093(ge)002:16964: lta bu'i thos pa med pa'i khyad par yong ba
NK093(ge)002:16965: dang / / che ba dang / ltar du /
NK093(ge)002:16966: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gzhan gyis sa dang rnam
NK093(ge)002:16967: thar gyi khyad par mthonga thos ston pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:16968: theg mchog 'di'i sa dang rnam par thar pa'i gnas kyi khyad para ni /
NK093(ge)002:16969: rig pa dang ma rig pa'i dona gyis ji lta bar mthong ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:16970: mtshon pa'i tshig thos pa che ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:16971: de ltar ston pa'i khyad par dang sa'i rim pa
NK093(ge)002:16972: dang khyad par yang mtho dman yoda pa yina pas
NK093(ge)002:16973: rim par bstan pa yin no //
NK093(ge)002:16975: sa'i khyad par shes par gdams pa /
NK093(ge)002:16976: khyad par can gyi sa'i rim pa dngos bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:16981: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:16982: sa la khyad par yod pa'i tshul desa na chos
NK093(ge)002:16983: rnams thams cada kun gyi gansa shing rten pa'i sa
NK093(ge)002:16984: chen po nyid ni gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:16985: don bla na med pa byang chub kyi semas mnyam
NK093(ge)002:16986: pa nyid 'di kho na yina pasa /
NK093(ge)002:16987: mthun pa dpe yis mtshon byed nama mkha'a lta bu dpesa nye bar mtshona te /
NK093(ge)002:16988: rang rig pa'i sems nyid kun gzhi kuna gyi sa
NK093(ge)002:16989: chen po 'di nyid yang dag par shes shing rtogs
NK093(ge)002:16990: par bya'o // 'di shes pa'i yon tan gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:16991: 'di ltar byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid rgyud 'dir
NK093(ge)002:16992: bstan pa lta bur ganga shesa pa'i rnal 'byor dam
NK093(ge)002:16993: pa su yin kyang lam khyad par can gyi thabsa
NK093(ge)002:16994: la makhasa pa yi gang zag ste /
NK093(ge)002:16995: des yang dag pa'i lam mun pa'i khams su stor
NK093(ge)002:16996: rlag tu gyur pa nyid slar lam batsala ba na
NK093(ge)002:16997: lam mchog ma nor bar rnyed pa yin pasa gzhan
NK093(ge)002:16998: du btsal bas mi rnyed pa'i phyir nye lam dam
NK093(ge)002:16999: pa bdera zhes bde bar rnyed de sems kyi chos
NK093(ge)002:17000: nyid rtogs nas nges par grub cing thob pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17002: rims kyis pa'i sa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17003: gcig char ba'i sa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17012: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17013: rnal 'byor pa ganga su zhig gis nye lam mchog
NK093(ge)002:17014: nyid rnyed pa yang sems kyi chos nyid kyi don
NK093(ge)002:17015: dera rnyed cing mthong ba ni don chen po der
NK093(ge)002:17016: gansa te 'dug pa'i phyir na skyes bu dam pa
NK093(ge)002:17017: rnal 'byor mchog gi don la spyod pa'i sa pa
NK093(ge)002:17018: yin te / de la'ang spyir rims kyis pa dang
NK093(ge)002:17019: gcig char ba gnyis las cig char ba la sa
NK093(ge)002:17020: yi rim pa kun rang rig pa'i ye shes chen
NK093(ge)002:17021: po gciga tu yongas su rdzogsa shing de la 'dus
NK093(ge)002:17022: yin te / pa yin kyang / rims kyis pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17023: dbang du rnam pa'i khyad par gyi gzhi ston pa
NK093(ge)002:17024: ni rang byung gi riga pa rtogs pa'i shes rab
NK093(ge)002:17025: mchoga gam rab tu gyur pa dang 'bring po dang
NK093(ge)002:17026: tha ma'i rim pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:17027: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems su gciga kyang /
NK093(ge)002:17028: rab la lam lnga la rnal 'byor lngar snang /
NK093(ge)002:17029: 'bring la sa'i khyad para ltar rnal 'byor bcur snang /
NK093(ge)002:17030: tha ma la rnal 'byor sum cu so bzhi'am bzhi bcur dbye ba 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17031: de yang rim par 'jug pa ganga dag gi don
NK093(ge)002:17032: gyi cheda du dang po lnga gzhan na gsal bas
NK093(ge)002:17033: 'dir dang po lnga'i gzhi la brten nas phyi ma
NK093(ge)002:17034: gnyis kyi ngo bo rgyas par bgranga ste bstan para
NK093(ge)002:17035: bya'o zhes dam bca' bar mdzad do //
NK093(ge)002:17036: de ltar dam bcas nas nges tshig gi tshul gyis
NK093(ge)002:17037: bstan pa 'di dag la gansa pa dang 'di dag
NK093(ge)002:17038: gis 'dzina pa dang 'di dag gi don la spyod
NK093(ge)002:17039: pa'i phyir sa gzhi dang 'dra bas na sa zhes
NK093(ge)002:17040: bya ste rnam grangs bstan pa ni bcu phrag gcig
NK093(ge)002:17041: gisa yongs su rdzogas te mthar thug par 'gyur ro
NK093(ge)002:17042: // de la 'dir thun mong byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu dang /
NK093(ge)002:17043: khyad par gsang sngags nang pa'i sa bcu las /
NK093(ge)002:17044: 'dir khyad par du 'phags pa'i sa bcu bsnyad de /
NK093(ge)002:17045: thun mong ma yin pa lung chen gsang sngags mchog gi lam sha stag tu 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:17046: thun mong gi rim par brgyud pa'ang 'gog pa ma yin no //
NK093(ge)002:17047: 'dir gzhung btsan par bya ba'i ched du gsang sngags
NK093(ge)002:17048: rjes su rnal 'byor gyi lam nyid du 'jal bar
NK093(ge)002:17049: sbyar te mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis ka la lan
NK093(ge)002:17050: gnyis bshad do // gnyis pa la bcu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17051: sa bcu lam lngar sdud pa ni tshogs lam sa gnyis kyi bdag nyid du bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17052: sbyor lam sa gsum gyi bdag nyid du bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17053: mthong lam sa gcig gi bdag nyid du bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17054: sgom lam sa gcig gi bdag nyid du bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17055: mthar lam sa gsum gyi bdag nyid du bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17057: 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:17058: brten pa gzhi'i sa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17063: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17064: gsang sngags nges don la 'jug pa'i rgyu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17065: rgyu rkyen rnams kyis nyan rang byang sems thun mong
NK093(ge)002:17066: gi sa dang so so skye bo pa gang yang
NK093(ge)002:17067: rung ba las theg pa chen po gsang ba dam
NK093(ge)002:17069: da dung theg pa chen po la ji lta ba
NK093(ge)002:17070: bzhin spyod pa'i gdengs med pas rkyen dabnga la rag
NK093(ge)002:17071: las shing rigs ma ngesa pa la gnas te rten
NK093(ge)002:17072: pa'ang sa zhes bya bar des gong du skyes pas
NK093(ge)002:17073: ming 'grub ste 'chad pa'ang rjes su mthun pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17074: gzhi 'di la nye ring dang mtho dman gyi bye brag gis rnal 'byor lnga ste /
NK093(ge)002:17075: thog mar blo gyen du 'gyur pa'i rgyus gsang sngags kyi don blo la ma shar yang /
NK093(ge)002:17076: lha bsgom pa dang bsam dpyod rnams gsang ba dam
NK093(ge)002:17077: pa'i tshul du bsgyur nas spyod pa la dga' bas
NK093(ge)002:17078: bcosa ma tsam gyi rnal 'byor don gsal ba med
NK093(ge)002:17079: pa dang / sgo gsum gyi spyod pa gsang ba'i
NK093(ge)002:17080: tshul der 'jug pa dang gzhan 'dren mar spyod cing
NK093(ge)002:17081: bsgom pa'ang rtog pa dang 'dren mar rgyu bas phra
NK093(ge)002:17082: mena spyod pa'i rnal 'byor du ba lta bu dang
NK093(ge)002:17083: pa dang / / gsang sngags la mos pas de'i
NK093(ge)002:17084: tshul rtagsa dang lha'i cha lugs 'dzina pa'i rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:17085: smig rgyu lta bu dang de bas kyang khyad par
NK093(ge)002:17086: du gsang ba'i lha dang sngags don la shin tu
NK093(ge)002:17087: mosa pa'i bsam pa la spyod par sgom pa'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:17089: gsang sngags la som nyi dang the tshom gyi dri
NK093(ge)002:17090: ma dang bral bas legas para 'duna par byed cing
NK093(ge)002:17091: lha bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor mar me lta bu dang
NK093(ge)002:17092: lnga'o // de rnams la ting nge 'dzin yang dag
NK093(ge)002:17093: pa med kyang skabs kyi bsam pa dang lha sgom
NK093(ge)002:17094: pa la gnas pa'ang bya bas yid la byed pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17095: ting nge 'dzin yod pas rnal 'byor gyi ming yang
NK093(ge)002:17097: de dag la ni gsang sngags la 'juga pa'ang yod cing /
NK093(ge)002:17098: zhugs nas slar ldoga pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17099: des dbang las ngan 'gror ltung ba dang bacasa pa
NK093(ge)002:17100: yisa theg pa'i gnas kuna tu 'khora zhing 'khyam ste
NK093(ge)002:17101: rigs ma ngesa pa yin pas las dang po par
NK093(ge)002:17102: gyur pa'i sa 'di'i ming gi nges tshig kyang 'grub
NK093(ge)002:17103: pa'o // 'dir rnal 'byor lnga dang bcu las /
NK093(ge)002:17104: de dag gi don la sgom mo snyam du 'duna
NK093(ge)002:17105: pa semas pa'i rnal 'byor nyid bshad pa'i skabs de
NK093(ge)002:17106: sa 'di la brten pa'i phyir sa pa de la
NK093(ge)002:17108: de bas na de dag la rten nas gansa shing
NK093(ge)002:17109: mos pa spyod pa'i sa zhes bya ba grangs dang
NK093(ge)002:17110: po yin no // 'di la'ang mtshan bcas lha bsgom pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17111: mtshan med chos nyid bsgom pa gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17112: dang po yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa lha bsgom pa'i dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:17114: des na ting 'dzin khyad par yang //
NK093(ge)002:17115: dbyings nyid gcig la sgom mod kyi //
NK093(ge)002:17116: rnal 'byor rtsal gyis khyad par gyis //
NK093(ge)002:17117: bsam pa'i yul ni sna tshogs te //
NK093(ge)002:17118: dang po'i sa la gnas pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:17119: brtsam pa las kyi rnal 'byor pa //
NK093(ge)002:17121: sogs pa'i rnal 'byor rnam drug po //
NK093(ge)002:17122: shes rab rtsal gyi 'phang dmas pas //
NK093(ge)002:17123: ting 'dzin rtsal yang chung ba ste //
NK093(ge)002:17124: don la mthong bar mi 'gyur te //
NK093(ge)002:17125: rang gi mos pa'i lha bsgom na //
NK093(ge)002:17126: lha yi sa bon gang yin pa //
NK093(ge)002:17127: kha dog tshon gyis phye nas ni //
NK093(ge)002:17128: sna yi dbugs la rgyu byas te //
NK093(ge)002:17129: dbugs kyi yul du gyur tshad du //
NK093(ge)002:17130: zung sgril phar 'phro gsal ba las //
NK093(ge)002:17132: rang gi chag tshad dang sbyar ba'i //
NK093(ge)002:17133: sku yi khyon yang de tsam mo //
NK093(ge)002:17135: lung 'di'i mdor bstan thun mong yin kyang /
NK093(ge)002:17136: rgyas bshad nas lha dang sbyar bar gsal bas //
NK093(ge)002:17137: de ltar na 'di la rnal 'byor drug ste /
NK093(ge)002:17139: nyams g.yo ba mi brtan pa lha kha dog tsam
NK093(ge)002:17140: las dbyibs mi gsal bar yid la byed pa tsam
NK093(ge)002:17142: nyams g.yo ba brtan pa lha rab rib tsam la sems bcos pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17143: phra men spyod pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17144: nyams thob pa lha res gsal res mi gsal bar 'dres ma'o //
NK093(ge)002:17146: nyams goms pa lha rgyan chas mi gsal te lha'i tshul 'dzin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17147: mos pa'i rnal 'byor ni nyams brtan pa lha rgyan chas bag re gsal ba la mos pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17149: nyams mthar phyin te ting nge 'dzin la skyon med pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17150: rnal 'byor de tsho'i nyams ni bya ba byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin la sbyor /
NK093(ge)002:17151: 'phro 'du ni dbugs kyi bsnyegs tshad du byed /
NK093(ge)002:17152: khyon ni khru bzhi ste rang gi lus po tsam du sgom /
NK093(ge)002:17153: grangs ni lha gcig /rnam pa'i khyad par ni rtog pa'i lha'o //
NK093(ge)002:17154: gnyis pa mtshan med chos nyid bsgom pa'i dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:17155: sa dang po 'dun pa skye ba'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:17156: g.yo ba byang chub kyi sems dpe skar ma rab rib lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17158: dang po ming tsam 'dzin lta bya byed sgom //
NK093(ge)002:17159: rnam par dkar ba'i spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17161: lta ba ni gsang ba mchog gi de kho na nyid kyi ming tsam du 'dzin pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17162: sgom pa ni bya ba byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK093(ge)002:17163: spyod pa ni bsod nams kyi dpung gis rnam par dkar ba'i spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17164: nyams dang rnal 'byor phra mo kun mtshan bcas kyi
NK093(ge)002:17165: skabs dang thun mong yin kyang 'dir mtshan med kyi
NK093(ge)002:17168: chos nyid kyi ming tsam la mos shing 'dun pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17170: chos nyid ming tsam la bcos pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17171: phra men spyod pa ni ming tsam gyi chos nyid de rang gsal mi gsal 'dres ma'o //
NK093(ge)002:17173: chos nyid mi rtog pa'i ming tsam gyi tshul 'dzin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17175: de nyid la dad cing mos pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17177: chos nyid mi rtog pa'i spyi'i rnam pa tsam la gnas pa la skyon med pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17178: tshul des gzhan yang mtshon no //
NK093(ge)002:17179: thun mong du ni phal pa'i sems brgyad las rnal
NK093(ge)002:17180: 'byor lngas rim par skye zhing thog mar 'dun pa
NK093(ge)002:17181: sems pa'i rnal 'byor dang drug ste /
NK093(ge)002:17183: de la rnal 'byor phra mo bzhi bcu ste //
NK093(ge)002:17184: dang po la drug 'dun pa sems pa nyid //
NK093(ge)002:17185: bsnyung bar gnas pa'i sems dang sa bon ltar //
NK093(ge)002:17186: bcos ma'i snying rje'i gnas gtong sdong lta bu //
NK093(ge)002:17187: phra men dge sbyong la gtong lo ma ltar //
NK093(ge)002:17188: tshul 'dzin lhug par gtong sems me tog ltar //
NK093(ge)002:17189: mos pa khrims srung sems bskyed gsos su 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:17190: dge bar 'dun pa lha mchod 'jig rten lam //
NK093(ge)002:17192: de'ang sa dang po la rnal 'byor drug pas lha
NK093(ge)002:17193: dang mi rtog pa bsgom pa la 'dun pa tsam
NK093(ge)002:17194: du sems pa'i rnal 'byor nyid bsnyung bar gnas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17195: sems te brgyad kyi dang po sa bon lta bu
NK093(ge)002:17196: dang / de nas pha ma dang nye du lta
NK093(ge)002:17197: bu la sbyin pa byed de myu gu lta bu
NK093(ge)002:17198: dang / dang / lta spyod sngags kyi tshul du
NK093(ge)002:17199: bcos ma'i rnal 'byor nyid snying rje'i sbyin gnas la
NK093(ge)002:17200: gtong ba sdong po lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:17201: sngags dang tshul gzhan phra men du spyod pa'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:17202: 'byor nyid bram ze dang dge sbyong dag la gtong
NK093(ge)002:17203: ba lo ma lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:17204: 'di la mos pas de'i tshul rtags 'dzin pa'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:17205: 'byor nyid bla ma dang rol mo mkhan la lhug
NK093(ge)002:17206: par gtong ba me tog lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:17207: de nas gang 'dod pa la gtong bas 'bras bu
NK093(ge)002:17208: lta bu dang drug gi sbyin pa'i bslab pa dang
NK093(ge)002:17209: lha dang mi rtog pa sgom pa la mos pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17210: rnal 'byor nyid sbyin pas rgyu byas nas tshul khrims
NK093(ge)002:17211: srung ba la mos pas sems bskyed de srung ba
NK093(ge)002:17212: gsos su 'gyur ba lta bu dang /
NK093(ge)002:17213: the tshom med par dge bar legs par 'dun pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17214: rnal 'byor nyid de bas kyang lha la mchod pa
NK093(ge)002:17215: phul ba shes stobs can du 'gyur snyam nas tshangs
NK093(ge)002:17216: pa la sogs pa mchod pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:17217: de dag ni 'jig rten phal pa'i sems sam lam brgyad ces kyang bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:17222: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17223: de ltar 'dun pa'i stobs dang sgo gsum gyi rtsol
NK093(ge)002:17224: ba'i las la rten pa yi sgo nas gong ma
NK093(ge)002:17225: rnams kyi yon tan 'byung ba'i gzhi yi ngo bor
NK093(ge)002:17226: gyur pa'i phyir sa zhes bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:17227: gzhi 'di la yang rnal 'byor gsum du 'gyur te /
NK093(ge)002:17228: gzhi'i dang po'i lasa cana gsang sngags la sngar lta
NK093(ge)002:17229: bu gdeng can du ma spyad pa las thog mar
NK093(ge)002:17230: gsang ba mchog gi don spyi'i mtshan nyid shes nas
NK093(ge)002:17231: rang gi mtshan nyid kyi mgo go ba la dpyod
NK093(ge)002:17233: gsang sngags kyi sgo dang por bslaba pa'i mtha' dam
NK093(ge)002:17234: pa bcu la sbyor te spyod pas slob cing lha'i
NK093(ge)002:17235: sku dang mi rtog pa'i yid la dmigs par byed
NK093(ge)002:17237: theg pa chen po'i bslab pa bcu las mi 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:17238: bar bya ba'i bsam pa ngesa pa'i rnal 'byor te
NK093(ge)002:17239: / spyi'i bden pa gnyis la rang gi mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:17240: du go ba'i bsam pas mtho dman gyis bye brag
NK093(ge)002:17241: / gsum mo // tshul de dag gi slob pa yang bsam dpyod dag pas spyod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17242: ma dag pas spyod pa gnyis ka yod pas dge
NK093(ge)002:17243: sdig gisa phyogs dkar ba dang gnag pa gang 'dren
NK093(ge)002:17244: mar spyod pa'o // 'di dag kyang tshogs lam pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17245: phyir dang por rnam par dkar ba'i spyod pa la
NK093(ge)002:17247: 'di dag ni rgyal ba'i bka'a lung dang bla ma'i
NK093(ge)002:17248: bka' la rag las te sdoda cing de dag gi
NK093(ge)002:17249: gnang ba thob nas sa gong ma gong mar rigs
NK093(ge)002:17250: phye nas nges par 'gyur zhing sgo gsum gyi rtsol
NK093(ge)002:17251: bas bslab pa la mi g.yel ba'i lasa can gyi
NK093(ge)002:17252: rnal 'byor te de ltar na sa pa de la
NK093(ge)002:17253: rnal 'byor bzhi ste 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:17254: bye brag gnyis pa la gansa shinga mos pas spyod
NK093(ge)002:17256: 'di dag ni gsang ba la slob kyang rigs nges
NK093(ge)002:17257: par ma gyur te de ni rtsol bas sbyor ba'i
NK093(ge)002:17258: skabs su gyur pas gsang ba la 'bad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17259: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17261: gnyis pa'i sa la gnas pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:17262: bka' sdod las kyi rnal 'byor las //
NK093(ge)002:17263: sogs pa'i rnal 'byor rnam bzhi po //
NK093(ge)002:17264: ting 'dzin rtsal gyi khyad par ni //
NK093(ge)002:17265: sa bon rang bzhin yi ge las //
NK093(ge)002:17267: dri 'byung yul ni tshun chad du //
NK093(ge)002:17269: rang gi chag tshad gnyis bsgyur ba'i //
NK093(ge)002:17270: sku yi khyon yang de tsam mo //
NK093(ge)002:17272: bka' sdod las kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17273: nyams thob pa drod rtags dang rtog pa'i lha de lhag mthong gi don la sbyor ba byed de /
NK093(ge)002:17274: ston pa dang bla ma'i bka' la sdod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17276: nyams goms pa thog mar bslab pa'i las la mgo 'dzug pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17277: bslab pa sbyong ba'am sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor ni nyams
NK093(ge)002:17278: brtan pa bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la mi lcog pa
NK093(ge)002:17279: med par 'dris goms su byed pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17281: nyams mthar phyin pa yengs thub la sems brtan zhing mi bslu ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17282: nyams de tsho rin chen myu gu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK093(ge)002:17283: la sbyar te 'phro 'du ni sna yis dri tshor
NK093(ge)002:17284: tshad du'o // khyod ni khru brgyad de lus gnyis 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:17285: grangs ni yab yum gnyis yan lag gi lha dang bcas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17286: rnam pa ni mtshan ma'i lha'o //
NK093(ge)002:17287: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:17288: sa gnyis pa rtsa bar sbyor ba'i skabs smon pa
NK093(ge)002:17289: byang chub kyi sems dpe skar ma phal pa lta
NK093(ge)002:17290: bu ste / sgom thabs sgron ma las /
NK093(ge)002:17292: yid la byed lta dug 'joms sman ting 'dzin //
NK093(ge)002:17295: chos nyid yid la byed pa'i lta ba dang las
NK093(ge)002:17296: kyi bag chags kyi dug thog mar 'jogs pa'i sman
NK093(ge)002:17298: dag ma dag phra men du spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17300: 'di la rin chen myu gu'i ting nge 'dzin gsungs
NK093(ge)002:17301: te gsang sngags kyi bslab pa mchog gi gzhir gyur
NK093(ge)002:17305: sems brgyad la brten stong sems gzhi la bzhi //
NK093(ge)002:17306: bde gshegs bla ma'i bka' sdod las la brten //
NK093(ge)002:17307: dang po'i las can stong par bdag dag bsgom //
NK093(ge)002:17308: bslab pa sbyong bar byed pas byas par spyod //
NK093(ge)002:17309: nges par rgyu med 'bras bu grub par lta //
NK093(ge)002:17311: sems brgyad la brten nas stong pa nyid kyi sems
NK093(ge)002:17312: skye ba'i gzhi la rnal 'byor bzhi ste bde gshegs
NK093(ge)002:17313: dang bla ma'i bka' la sdod cing sgo gsum gyi
NK093(ge)002:17314: bya ba'i las la brten pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK093(ge)002:17315: thog mar sngags la spyod pas dang po'i las can
NK093(ge)002:17316: gyi rnal 'byor stong pa nyid du bdag dag par
NK093(ge)002:17317: bsgom pa dang / sngags kyi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu
NK093(ge)002:17318: la sbyor bar byed de don yid la byas te
NK093(ge)002:17320: bslab pa'i mtha' de las mi 'gyur ba'i bsam pas
NK093(ge)002:17321: nges pa'i rnal 'byor gyis stong pa'i rgyu'am rgyu med
NK093(ge)002:17322: pa las 'bras bu grub par lta ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17323: lam gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17324: gal chen sbyong ba'i sa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17325: bslab pa rgyun gyi sa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17326: bsod nams gter gyi sa bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17331: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17332: shin tu brtson 'grus dang ldan pas /
NK093(ge)002:17333: gsang sngags kyi don la mchog tu ched che ba'am
NK093(ge)002:17334: gala chena por byas te sgo gsum gyi rtsol bas
NK093(ge)002:17335: bag chags ched du sbyong zhing sbyor bar byed pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17336: sa 'di la gsang sngags dang gsang ba ma yin
NK093(ge)002:17337: pa rnams kyi rigas chen po lung dang mos pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17338: nyams kyis 'byed pa'i rnala 'byor nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:17339: 'di nas slar ldog pa gyen du 'byung ba'i gnas
NK093(ge)002:17340: phyed pa yin pa'i phyir rnal 'byor gyi ming 'grub
NK093(ge)002:17341: ste / rnal 'byor de nyid rten te don la gansa shinga spyod pa'i sa yina te /
NK093(ge)002:17342: sa 'dir yang ya nga ba sdig pa'i las kyi
NK093(ge)002:17343: bag chags dang ya mi nga'i dge ba'i las kyi
NK093(ge)002:17344: bag chags rnamas 'phro 'du gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK093(ge)002:17345: dang bden pa gnyis kyi rtogs pa brtan pas kun
NK093(ge)002:17346: nas gcod cing sbyong ba dang yang dag pa'i don
NK093(ge)002:17347: la sbyor ba'i tshul nyid kyis 'dir brtson 'grus kyis
NK093(ge)002:17348: dge ba'i las dbang du 'byongs na mi 'gyur bas
NK093(ge)002:17350: le lo'i dbang gis ma 'byongs na 'gyur bas las
NK093(ge)002:17351: stobs nyes pa gnyis kyi stobsa chen po 'gyed de
NK093(ge)002:17352: brtson 'grus dang shes rab kyi byed pa 'byung ba'o
NK093(ge)002:17353: // des na brtson 'grus gal che ste so mtshams kyi mkhar dang 'dra'o //
NK093(ge)002:17354: tshul de lta bu'i sgo nas bslab pa la 'jug pa'i skabs so //
NK093(ge)002:17355: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17358: gsum pa'i sa la gnas pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:17359: zhes sogs bzhi pa dang thun mong du gsungs pas rnal 'byor gcig ste /
NK093(ge)002:17360: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor zhes bya ba 'khor 'das kyi rigs 'byed pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17361: nyams de nyid dug 'joms sman gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa dang sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:17362: 'phro 'du ni rna bas thos tshad du'o //
NK093(ge)002:17363: khyon ni khru bcu drug tsam ste lus bzhi 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:17364: grangs ni rigs gcig 'khor dang bcas pa tsam mo //
NK093(ge)002:17365: rnam pa ni lha chu zla lta bu'o //
NK093(ge)002:17366: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:17367: sa gsum pa bslab pa la 'jug pa'i skabs ldang
NK093(ge)002:17368: ba byang chub kyi sems dpe skar ma chen po
NK093(ge)002:17369: lta bu ste / sgom thabs sgron ma las /
NK093(ge)002:17371: de kho na nyid mthong ma rag pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17372: rin chen myu gu brtson 'grus spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17374: de kho na nyid mthong ma rag pa'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17375: gsang ba dam pa'i rigs kyi gzhi rin chen myu gu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK093(ge)002:17376: legs nyes stobs 'gyed pa'i brtson 'grus kyi spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17378: nyon sgrib rags pa'i dug 'joms pas sman gyi ting
NK093(ge)002:17379: nge 'dzin te don 'dra yang 'chad tshul gnyis kar
NK093(ge)002:17380: mkhas pas lam gnad la go skyed che'o //
NK093(ge)002:17382: gal chen rigs chen 'byed de log lta sel //
NK093(ge)002:17383: nyon mongs rags pa 'joms pas rigs chen 'byed //
NK093(ge)002:17385: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor gyis gong gi log
NK093(ge)002:17386: lta de dag sel zhing nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa
NK093(ge)002:17387: rags pa 'joms pas rigs chen po 'byed de gyen
NK093(ge)002:17393: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17394: de ltar rigs phye nas theg pa chen por nges pa'i rigs bstan pa'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:17395: 'dir gzod cig theg pa chen po'i gsang ba mchog
NK093(ge)002:17396: gi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la gnas pa nyid rgyun
NK093(ge)002:17397: gyi bar chad pa med par slob par byed pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17398: sa 'di la yang rnal 'byor drug ste /
NK093(ge)002:17399: de yang rtogs pa'i drod rtags dang bsgom pa'i drod rtags che chung las /
NK093(ge)002:17400: 'dir rtogs pa dang lha bsgom pa'i drod rtags chung ngu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17401: snga ma dag la lha bsgom pa dang rtsol ba
NK093(ge)002:17402: yod kyang rigs ma nges pas gsang sngags rang gi
NK093(ge)002:17403: ngo bo gnyis su med pa'i don gtan nas ma
NK093(ge)002:17405: 'dir bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la sbyangs pas rtogs pa'i drod mgo g.yo ba la gnas pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17406: drod de thob nas mgo ldang ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17407: de yang mi 'gyur bar brtana pa'i drod dang gsum 'byung ngo //
NK093(ge)002:17408: de dag shing la me'i drod ltar thun mong gi dro ba lta bu'o //
NK093(ge)002:17409: de bzhina du rtagsa chen po gtos chen gyi 'jig
NK093(ge)002:17410: rten rang bzhin med cing mi 'jigs pa'i mtshan ma
NK093(ge)002:17413: de nas brtan zhing mi g.yo ba yi rnal 'byor dang gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17414: de ltar rnal 'byora rnam pa drug po de dag rnams kyi bslab pa gang zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:17415: rgyud thos pas dgrol bar bslab pa la sogs pa
NK093(ge)002:17416: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i bslab pa'i mtha'a chen po bcu
NK093(ge)002:17417: dag zag pa dang bcas pas mathara phyin par byed
NK093(ge)002:17418: cing gnas pa'o // de las rig pa skye ba'i tshul ni /
NK093(ge)002:17419: de ltar bslab pas drod rtags skyes nas rtogs pa'i ye shes 'phel ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:17420: dpe ji ltar na zla ba yara gyi ngo la
NK093(ge)002:17421: tshes gcig nas nya yi bar du gasla bar 'phel
NK093(ge)002:17422: te 'gro ba bzhina sa bcu yis sgrubs pas bslab
NK093(ge)002:17423: pa'i ye shesa skyed du gsal zhing 'phel bar 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:17424: te ye shes gcig tu mi sdod pas thun mong
NK093(ge)002:17427: de nas gsang sngags bden pa gnyis mnyam pa chen
NK093(ge)002:17428: po'i dona la bzod pa thob nas mi skrag cing
NK093(ge)002:17429: sngangs pa dang bral ba'i rtogs pa 'byung bas de
NK093(ge)002:17430: la ngo matshara che ba'am ya mtshan skye ba nyid
NK093(ge)002:17432: sa thob 'jigs pa lnga dang bral //
NK093(ge)002:17433: bzod thob ngan song yong mi ltung //
NK093(ge)002:17434: zhes gsungs pa ltar ngan 'gro'i 'jigs pa dang bral ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17435: des na chos mnyam pa'i yul la so sor rtog
NK093(ge)002:17436: cing dpyod pa'i semas kyi shes rab kyis don ji
NK093(ge)002:17437: lta ba nyid la 'jug par 'gyur ba'i tshul gyis
NK093(ge)002:17438: zhugs nas rtogs par byed pa'i semas dapa'a desa chos
NK093(ge)002:17439: mnyam pa la dpyod pa'i shes rab kyis ngana 'gror
NK093(ge)002:17440: 'gro ba'i ya nga ba'i gnas kyi rgyud sbyangs nas
NK093(ge)002:17441: slar ngan song du mi ldog ste /
NK093(ge)002:17442: de ni dgona para dben pa'i gnas su 'jug cing
NK093(ge)002:17443: ye shes tshol bar byed de thun mong gi 'jig
NK093(ge)002:17444: rten pa'i chos kyi mchog la zhugs pa lta bu'o
NK093(ge)002:17445: // de'i tshe bsam pa'i bar chada kyi sems g.yeng
NK093(ge)002:17446: 'khrug dang 'du byed la sogs pa dag kyang de
NK093(ge)002:17447: // la 'byung ste / bdud sa lta bu nye du la 'dzin pa /
NK093(ge)002:17448: chu lta bu grags snyan 'dod pa /
NK093(ge)002:17449: me lta bu 'dod sred skye ba /
NK093(ge)002:17450: rlung lta bu khe grags gnyer ba /
NK093(ge)002:17451: mun pa lta bu bla ma ngan pas dbang las mi shes pa sogs dang /
NK093(ge)002:17452: gzhan yang dkar po'i phyogs kyi bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad rnams 'byung ngo //
NK093(ge)002:17453: de ltar drug kyang bsdu na gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17454: gasnga sngags mtshon pa'i sgo lung gi gnas zab mo
NK093(ge)002:17455: la brten cing gnyis med kyi don la bzod pa
NK093(ge)002:17456: thob kyang da dung drod g.yo ba tsam las ma
NK093(ge)002:17457: thob par sgom pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK093(ge)002:17458: de la goms nas spyod lam bzhir bslab pa 'i
NK093(ge)002:17459: mtha' bcu dang mi 'bral bar gnas pas spyod pa
NK093(ge)002:17460: rgyun gyi rnal 'byor gnyis med kyi rtogs pa g.yos
NK093(ge)002:17461: pa'i ye shes 'phel bar byed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17462: de la rgyun du gnas pas rtogs pa'i matshana ma
NK093(ge)002:17463: la brten nas drod dang rtagsa kyi rnal 'byor dang
NK093(ge)002:17464: gsum ldan te / 'di la g.yo thob kyi cha phye bas rnal 'byor drug go //
NK093(ge)002:17465: de dag kyang de la gansa shing spyod pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:17466: sa zhesa bya ste 'du shes 'gyur ba'i skabs so
NK093(ge)002:17467: // 'di la'ang mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17470: rnal 'byor lung gi bka' sgo las //
NK093(ge)002:17471: sogs pa'i rnal 'byor rnam gsum po //
NK093(ge)002:17473: lha yi sa bon gang yin pa //
NK093(ge)002:17474: rang bzhin yi ger bsgyur byas te //
NK093(ge)002:17476: thos pa'i yul ni tshun chad du //
NK093(ge)002:17478: rang gi chag tshad bzhi bsgyur tsam //
NK093(ge)002:17479: sku yi khyon yang de tsam mo //
NK093(ge)002:17481: gsang sgo lung gi rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17482: nyams thob pa shin tu gsal brtan du 'dod cing lung zab mo la brten nas bsgom pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17483: spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17484: nyams goms pa spyod lam bzhir zag bcas kyi bslab pa la mngon du spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17485: mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17486: nyams brtan pa ting nge 'dzin la rgyun du gnas pas rtags dang mtshan ma 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17487: de la drod g.yo thob brtan pa gsum /
NK093(ge)002:17488: rtags g.yo thob brtan pa gsum ste drug tu phye na rnal 'byor bzhi bcur 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:17489: nyams de tsho ni rtse gcig 'phro ba'i ting nge 'dzin la sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:17490: 'phro 'du ni mig gis gzugs mthong tshad du'o //
NK093(ge)002:17491: khyon ni khru sum cu so gnyis tsam ste lus brgyad 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:17492: grangs ni rigs gsum 'khor dang bcas pa tsam mo //
NK093(ge)002:17493: rnam pa ni gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i lha'o //
NK093(ge)002:17494: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du sa bzhi pa 'du shes bsgyur ba'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:17495: sbyor ba byang chub kyi sems dpe zla ba tshes gcig pa lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17497: bslab pa gcig lta tshogs chen rdzogs pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:17498: rtse gcig pa yi spyod pa bzhi pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:17500: gsang sngags kyi bslab pa'i don la gcig tu lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17501: zag pa dang bcas pa'i tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i ting
NK093(ge)002:17502: nge 'dzin sgom pa dang bya ba rtse gcig pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17505: rtse gcig 'phro ba'i ting nge 'dzin du gsungs pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:17506: dmigs pa rtse gcig gi ngang nas 'phro 'du nus pa dang por thob pa ste don gcig go //
NK093(ge)002:17509: sbyor gnas bslab rgyun la gsum gsang sgo lung //
NK093(ge)002:17510: drod la bslab pas rtse mor 'phel ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:17511: chos nyid don la mi skrag bzod pa thob //
NK093(ge)002:17512: spyod pa rgyun gyis gong nas gong du 'phel //
NK093(ge)002:17513: mtshan ma rtags la sems kyi drod rtags te //
NK093(ge)002:17514: g.yo thob brtan pa'i drod gsum rtags la gsum //
NK093(ge)002:17515: gzhi po gsum dang don dgur gnas pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:17517: sbyor lam la gnas pa'i bslab pa rgyun gyi sa la rnal 'byor gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17518: gsang sgo lung gi rnal 'byor lung zab mo la
NK093(ge)002:17519: brten cing sgoms pas drod g.yo ba tsam thob nas
NK093(ge)002:17520: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la mi 'bral bar bslabs pas
NK093(ge)002:17521: rtogs pa'i ye shes rtse mor 'phel ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17522: chos nyid mnyam pa chen po gsang sngags kyi don
NK093(ge)002:17523: la mi skrag cing bzod pa thob pas ngo mtshar
NK093(ge)002:17524: skye ba'o // spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor gyis
NK093(ge)002:17525: bslab pa bcu la dus rgyun du gnas pas ye
NK093(ge)002:17526: shes gong nas gong du 'phel ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17527: mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal 'byor sems nyid rtogs pa dang goms pa'i drod rtags byung ba ste /
NK093(ge)002:17528: de la dbye na drod la g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor /
NK093(ge)002:17531: rtags la'ang de ltar gsum ste rnal 'byor drug dang /
NK093(ge)002:17532: gzhi po gsum ste don la dagu'o //
NK093(ge)002:17537: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17538: de ltar bslab pa'i ye shes 'phel ba'i bsoda namas
NK093(ge)002:17539: skad cig ma la brten nas zad pa med par
NK093(ge)002:17540: rat+na'i gter gyi yon tan ltar du 'byung ba dang
NK093(ge)002:17541: ldan pa'i phyir sa yi ming yang 'grub bo //
NK093(ge)002:17542: de lta bu'i sa 'di la yang gong du bslab
NK093(ge)002:17543: pa'i mtha' bcu dang ma bral bar gnas te spyod
NK093(ge)002:17544: pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor nyid kyi don dang ma
NK093(ge)002:17545: bral bar mthar phyin pa de yis bsam pa'i mosa
NK093(ge)002:17546: pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyis gzung 'dzin rags pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17547: mi shes pa'i dri ma dag cing mnyam pa'i don
NK093(ge)002:17548: la blo 'dun pa'i sgo nas bde ba cha na
NK093(ge)002:17549: po nam mkha'i ngogs bzhin mthong la ma rag par
NK093(ge)002:17550: gansa pa ni bar chad med pa'i lam ste /
NK093(ge)002:17551: bslab pa la rgyun du gnas nas shin tu gsal
NK093(ge)002:17552: brtan du gyur pas 'phags pa'i sa dang po shes
NK093(ge)002:17553: rab mchog gi rtsal can mthong ba'i lam du 'gro
NK093(ge)002:17554: ba'i blo dang ldan pa yisa drug pa'i stegs lta
NK093(ge)002:17555: bu'i bsti gansa kyi sa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:17557: der ni rtogs par byed pa'i zag pa dang bcas
NK093(ge)002:17558: pa'i bslab pa'i mtha'a bcu nyid mthar skyed du bya
NK093(ge)002:17559: ba med par spyir chib cing khong du chud par
NK093(ge)002:17560: gyur pa'o // de ni spyod chen la 'jug pa'i skabs kyi sa ste /
NK093(ge)002:17561: de yan chad du 'khor bar mi ldog pa ma thob pas ldog pa'ang yod do //
NK093(ge)002:17562: sa de gsum rnal 'byor gcig gi khyad par te /
NK093(ge)002:17564: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17567: de bzhin rnal 'byor rim pa bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:17568: lha yi khyad par gang yin pa //
NK093(ge)002:17569: yi ge'i rim pa bzhin byas nas //
NK093(ge)002:17571: rim pa bzhin du sbyar nas kyang //
NK093(ge)002:17573: sems kyis lcogs tshad tshun chad du //
NK093(ge)002:17574: sku yi khyon gyi khyad par yang //
NK093(ge)002:17575: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas par //
NK093(ge)002:17576: sku yi khyon gyis gang bar bsgom //
NK093(ge)002:17577: zhes sa lnga pa nas bcu pa'i bar thun mong du gsungs pas /
NK093(ge)002:17579: spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor zhes bya ba sa
NK093(ge)002:17580: lnga pa'i spyod pa rgyun la ston nas 'di nyid
NK093(ge)002:17581: kyi bar chad med pa'i bslab pa mngon du spyod
NK093(ge)002:17582: de de la rgyun du gnas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17583: rnal 'byor 'dir ni tshogs rten rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:17584: 'phro 'du ni gling gcig tshun chad du'o //
NK093(ge)002:17585: khyon ni khru drug cu rtsa bzhi tsam ste lus bcu drug 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:17586: grangs ni rigs lnga gtso 'khor du bcas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17587: rnam pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi lha'o //
NK093(ge)002:17588: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:17589: sa lnga pa sbyang chen la 'jug pa'i skabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:17590: 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems dpe zla ba tshes gnyis pa lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17592: bar chad med lta rtse gcig 'phro ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:17593: btang snyoms rgyun gyi spyod pa lnga pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17595: bar chad med par zag med du sbyor ba'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17596: rtse gcig las mi 'gyur bar 'phro ba'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17597: zag bcas kyi bslab pa mthar chib cing de dang
NK093(ge)002:17598: mi 'bral bar btang snyom rgyun gyi spyod pa la
NK093(ge)002:17599: slob pa'o // dka' 'grel dang mchan gzhan las /
NK093(ge)002:17600: tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin du gsungs pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:17601: bslab pa spyir chib pas te don 'dra yang zur
NK093(ge)002:17602: gnyis ka ltar shes pas lam gnad la mkhas par
NK093(ge)002:17603: 'gyur pa'o // des na snga ma las /
NK093(ge)002:17604: bsod nams gter la spyod pa rgyun nyid de //
NK093(ge)002:17605: 'jig rten chos mchog bslab pa mthar phyin yin //
NK093(ge)002:17607: gong gi bslab pa bcu'i spyod pa dang ma bral
NK093(ge)002:17608: ba'i rgyun gyi rnal 'byor nyid de gzung 'dzin gyi
NK093(ge)002:17609: dri ma rags pa dag pas thun mong gi 'jig
NK093(ge)002:17610: rten chos mchog lta bu ste zag bcas kyi bslab
NK093(ge)002:17611: pa bcu skyed du byar med par mthar phyin pa
NK093(ge)002:17612: yin no // gsum pa mthong lam sa gcig gi
NK093(ge)002:17613: bdag nyid sa drug pa rten pas khyad par du
NK093(ge)002:17618: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17619: 'dir gong du bslab pa'i mtha' bcu rtser chib pas
NK093(ge)002:17620: chos nyid zab mo gsang sngags kyi don sgoms te
NK093(ge)002:17621: nam mkha'i ngos bzhin rtogs pas mthong lam ste /
NK093(ge)002:17622: rtogs pa'i don 'di la rten nas mthar thug gi
NK093(ge)002:17623: bar du rtogs pa je gsal du gyur pasa 'di
NK093(ge)002:17624: nyid kyi rgyud mthun pa'i khyad para skyed du 'gro
NK093(ge)002:17625: ba yin pa'i phyir ming gi nges tshig kyang 'grub
NK093(ge)002:17626: bo // sa 'di la yang rnal 'byor gyi bye brag gis bdun te /
NK093(ge)002:17627: dang po ji lta ba'i bden pa mthong bas 'khor
NK093(ge)002:17628: ba'i duhkha dang zag bcas kyi lam du rtsol ba
NK093(ge)002:17629: las thog mar dbugsa chena po 'byin te ngal sos
NK093(ge)002:17630: pa thob pa'i rnal 'byor nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:17631: thun mong byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang po pa lta bu'o //
NK093(ge)002:17632: 'on kyang lta ba mnyam pa ni ma yin no //
NK093(ge)002:17633: der ma zad de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan thos pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17636: lam sbyang ba rnams kyi dbugs 'byin pa'ang 'dir thob bo //
NK093(ge)002:17637: theg pa chen po gsang ba'i don gdeng du gyur
NK093(ge)002:17638: pas de'i rgyud du 'byung zhing 'jug pa mi gtong
NK093(ge)002:17639: ba'i phyir rigas chen 'dzina pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK093(ge)002:17640: blang dor dang bzang ngan mi 'byed pa'i lta ba'i
NK093(ge)002:17641: stobs kyis yon tan ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gsal
NK093(ge)002:17642: bar gyur pas manyama rdzogsa che ba'am chen po'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:17643: 'byor dang / spyod lam ci spyad pa thams cad
NK093(ge)002:17644: gsang ba ji bzhin pa nyid du gdeng can du
NK093(ge)002:17645: ngesa par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK093(ge)002:17646: shes rab kyi gdeng gi rtsala chen por sbyong bas
NK093(ge)002:17647: lhun grub kyi don la sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor dang
NK093(ge)002:17648: / rig pa nyid chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i yul
NK093(ge)002:17649: dang dbyer med par zhugs pas sgom lam la 'juga
NK093(ge)002:17651: thams cad ye shes chen po yul dang bral bar
NK093(ge)002:17652: rtogs pas sgom lam thob la ma rag par chos
NK093(ge)002:17653: nyid riga pa la sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor te /
NK093(ge)002:17654: de dag kyang thun mong gi sa dang po rab
NK093(ge)002:17655: tu dga' ba nas bdun pa ring du song ba'i
NK093(ge)002:17657: spyir mthong sgom gyi lam gnyis ka tshang yang 'dir
NK093(ge)002:17658: mthong lam 'ba' zhig gi khyad par du rigs te
NK093(ge)002:17659: sa bdun po de nyid 'dir rdzogsa para gyur pas
NK093(ge)002:17661: ste zhes tshig lhag ma ni slob ma'i tshul 'byung ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17662: de bas na mi ldog par bslab par bya ba'i
NK093(ge)002:17663: zag pa med pa'i rgyu bcu dang 'brasa bu'i mtha'a
NK093(ge)002:17664: bcu la lobs par gyur pa nyid sa lnga par
NK093(ge)002:17665: gomas para byed pa'i tshul du 'dir sbyor bar byed
NK093(ge)002:17666: pas dbugs chen po 'byin pa'i tshe ngala bso ba
NK093(ge)002:17667: la gnas pa las chos so cog thams cad kyi
NK093(ge)002:17668: rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:17669: par ji lta ba bzhin mthonga zhing rtogs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17670: des na 'khor bar ram mtshan mar mi ldog pa
NK093(ge)002:17671: yang dag pa thob pa la da bslab pa bcu
NK093(ge)002:17672: ka snga ma ltar gomas par byar meda de /
NK093(ge)002:17673: zag bcas kyi skabs ltar slob mi dgos pas 'di'i skabs su ma brjod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17674: de yang spyir lam gyi sgrib pa dag cing ye
NK093(ge)002:17675: shes 'char tshul gyi sa'i rim pa smos pa 'di
NK093(ge)002:17676: daga rnams kyang mi dmigs pa'i don mthar thug pa
NK093(ge)002:17677: snying po byang chub la sbyor ba'i gzhi yi dmigs
NK093(ge)002:17678: gciga pa yin kyang mi mthun pa ni sa 'og
NK093(ge)002:17679: ma so so rang rang gi spyod yul du gong
NK093(ge)002:17680: ma gong mar gyur te thun mong ma yina pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17681: gnas su gyur pa 'og mas gong ma'i don ma
NK093(ge)002:17682: mthong bas sgrib pa ste rten pa dang skyed byed
NK093(ge)002:17683: kyi skabs la sa zhes 'dogs te rtsi bar byed
NK093(ge)002:17684: cing 'og ma rang gi zhen pa spangs nas gong
NK093(ge)002:17685: ma'i don mthong ba'i ye shes re re 'achara te
NK093(ge)002:17686: bogs su 'byung bas na sa'i rim pa bkod pa'o
NK093(ge)002:17687: // tshul desa nasa rnams thams cad snying po byang
NK093(ge)002:17688: chub kyi bslab pa'i mtha'a ru don gcig las med
NK093(ge)002:17689: // pa la / sa drug par 'khor bar mi ldog pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17690: sa brgyad pas mtshan mar mi ldog pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17691: la sogas pa zhes gzhan bsdu ba'i don gyis rdzogsa
NK093(ge)002:17692: pa spyir chibs kyi sa chena po'i bar rnams su
NK093(ge)002:17693: rang rig pa la mnyam par bzhag pa'i ting nge
NK093(ge)002:17694: 'dzin sa lnga pa nas rim pa drug por bying
NK093(ge)002:17695: rgod la sogs pa las ring du gyur pa'i sa
NK093(ge)002:17696: ganga der gong ma'i bdena pa mthong ba'i bogs re
NK093(ge)002:17697: re 'byung ba la skabs de'i sgrib pa re 'joms
NK093(ge)002:17698: pa'i nus pa'i rtsal re 'byung ba dang bcas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17699: ye shes re re 'achara ba ste /
NK093(ge)002:17700: de yang grangs kyi tha ma ranga byung gi ye
NK093(ge)002:17701: shes chen po shar nas skyed du bya ba med
NK093(ge)002:17702: pa nyid kyis rdzogas par gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17703: de dag gi skabs su yang mathara phyin pa sa
NK093(ge)002:17704: bcu pa chos kyi sprin nam rdzogs pa spyir chibs
NK093(ge)002:17705: dang / dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros sam gdal
NK093(ge)002:17706: ba chos nyid kyi sa thob pa dang bdun pa
NK093(ge)002:17707: lung chen thob pa sgom lam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17708: brgyad pa mtshan mar mi ldog pa'am gnas pa mi 'gyur ba'i sa mthar lam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17709: drug pa mthong lam mi ldog pa rnamas la rim pa bzhina du lung bstan pa 'byung ba yang /
NK093(ge)002:17710: drug pa'am brgyad pa la rmi lam du lung bstan pa 'byung ba dang ni /
NK093(ge)002:17711: bdun pa'am dgu pa la de las gsal bar sgra
NK093(ge)002:17712: snyan pa bar snang dang gzhal yas la sogs pa
NK093(ge)002:17713: las byung nas lung ston pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17714: mthar lam bcu pa la rgyal ba'i sku mngona sum
NK093(ge)002:17715: du byung nas ngesa par shin tu gsal bar lung
NK093(ge)002:17717: de ltar ci rigas para yang 'dir rmi lam na
NK093(ge)002:17718: lung ston pa 'byung ba'i tshul gyis rmi ltas kyi
NK093(ge)002:17719: mtshan ma brgyad kyang rnal 'byor gyi skabs skabs su
NK093(ge)002:17720: 'byung bas / sgra brnyan dang mngon sum gyi yang
NK093(ge)002:17721: sprul pa dang longs spyod rdzogs pa so sor snang
NK093(ge)002:17722: bas so so la lung bstan pa sbyar te 'chad
NK093(ge)002:17724: de ltar 'tshams par lung ston pa'i tshul yang /
NK093(ge)002:17725: rnal 'byor de dag rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi rig 'dzin du lung ston pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17726: rdo rje 'chang chen po nyid grub pa'i 'bras bur lung ston pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:17727: de yang ming gi lung gsang ba'i mtshan rdo rje
NK093(ge)002:17728: rnal 'byor pa che ge mo zhes byar bos nas
NK093(ge)002:17729: de nyid dang mthun par rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa
NK093(ge)002:17730: gnas kyi khamas ji snyed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17731: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khamas kun tu bsgragsa te grags
NK093(ge)002:17732: par byas nas 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor dama para mngon
NK093(ge)002:17734: sa 'di dang lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK093(ge)002:17735: rtsa ba gnyis las yan lag mtshan nyid kyi sa
NK093(ge)002:17736: bcur 'gyur pa'o // skabs bcu las ro nyid tshor ba'i skabs so //
NK093(ge)002:17737: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17739: lha'i mtshan nyid mnyam pa nyid du gsal ba'i rnal 'byor gyi rim pa bdun te /
NK093(ge)002:17741: nyams g.yo ba zag bcas kyi rtsol bas dub pa la zag med du slob pas dbugs 'byin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17742: rigs chen 'dzin pa'i rnal 'byor ni nyams thob pa
NK093(ge)002:17743: ting nge 'dzin la grims phyung bas mthong ba'i don
NK093(ge)002:17745: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17746: nyams goms pa mnyam pa nyid kyi lha'i ting nge 'dzin tshad du phyin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17748: nyams brtan pa mthong ba'i don gdeng du byas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17749: rtsal chen sbyong ba'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17750: nyams mthar phyin pa'i thob pa shin tu gdeng du
NK093(ge)002:17751: byas te ting nge 'dzin brgya stong la rtsal sbyong
NK093(ge)002:17752: ba'o // yul la 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17753: nyams mthar phyin pa'i goms pa mthong ba la rtsal 'byongs pas sgom lam la 'jug pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17754: rig par sbyong ba'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17755: nyams mthar phyin pa'i brtan pa sgom lam la sbyor nges par bden pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17756: de tsho'i nyams ni mngon par rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:17757: 'phro 'du ni gling bzhi ri rab dang bcas pa tshun chad du'o //
NK093(ge)002:17758: khyon ni khru brgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad dam yang na gling gcig khengs pa tsam mo //
NK093(ge)002:17759: grangs kyang gling gcig lhas khengs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17760: rnam pa ni rang gi mtshan nyid gsal ba'i lha'o //
NK093(ge)002:17761: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:17762: sa drug pa ro myong ba'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:17763: dga' ba byang chub kyi sems /
NK093(ge)002:17764: dpe zla ba tshes gsum pa lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17766: mngon rtogs pa yi lta ba ting nge 'dzin //
NK093(ge)002:17767: shes rab mthun pa'i spyod pa drug pa yin //
NK093(ge)002:17769: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyi don mngon sum du rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17770: de'i ngang la gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom la
NK093(ge)002:17771: shes rab chen po'i bden pa mthong ba dang mthun
NK093(ge)002:17772: pa'i mi dmigs pa'i spyod pa la slob pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17775: drug pa la bdun dbugs chen 'byin pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:17776: bdag gnyis med rtogs mthong lam sa rab daga'o //
NK093(ge)002:17777: rigs chen 'dzin pas gnyis pa dri ma bral //
NK093(ge)002:17778: mnyam rdzogs bden pa gnyis mnyam gsum pa byed //
NK093(ge)002:17779: nges spyod thugs chud don mdzad bzhi pa 'phro //
NK093(ge)002:17780: rtsal sbyong dbyer med sbyong bas sa lnga pa //
NK093(ge)002:17781: rig pas chos nyid yul la 'jug pas drug /rig par sbyor bas nyon mongs dag pas bdun //
NK093(ge)002:17783: 'khor ba'i duhkha las ngal sos pas dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17784: bdag gnyis med pa'i don ji lta ba bzhin rtogs
NK093(ge)002:17785: pas thun mong byang chub sems dpa'i mthong lam rab
NK093(ge)002:17786: dga' lta bu ste lta ba mnyam pa'ang ma yin
NK093(ge)002:17787: no // gsang sngags kyi rigs chen 'dzin pa'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:17788: 'byor sa gnyis pa dri ma med pa lta bu
NK093(ge)002:17789: no // / mnyam rdzogs chen po'i rnal 'byor bden
NK093(ge)002:17790: pa gnyis mnyam nyid du rdzogs par rtogs pas sa
NK093(ge)002:17791: gsum pa 'od byed pa lta bu /
NK093(ge)002:17792: nges par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor gsang ba ji bzhin
NK093(ge)002:17793: pa nyid thugs su chud nas don mdzad pas sa
NK093(ge)002:17795: rtsal chen sbyong ba'i rnal 'byor shes rab kyi rtsal
NK093(ge)002:17796: chen pos dbyer med kyi don sbyong bas sa lnga
NK093(ge)002:17797: pa sbyang dka' ba lta bu /
NK093(ge)002:17798: rig pas chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i yul la 'jug
NK093(ge)002:17799: pa'i rnal 'byor sa drug pa mngon du gyur pa
NK093(ge)002:17800: lta bu / ye shes chen po yul med du
NK093(ge)002:17801: rtogs pas sgom lam gyi rig par sbyor ba'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:17802: 'byor nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag pas sa bdun
NK093(ge)002:17803: pa ring du song ba lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17804: 'dir mthong lam gyi khyad par du gyur par rig par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:17805: bzhi pa sgom lam sa gcig gi bdag nyid bdun
NK093(ge)002:17806: pa dmigs pas 'bras bu skye ba'i sa bshad pa
NK093(ge)002:17810: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17811: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor sgom lam dngos gang snyam pa la /
NK093(ge)002:17812: de ltar gsang sngags mthong ba'i don la 'jug cing
NK093(ge)002:17813: dmigas te gom pasa mthar lam gyi 'bras bu skye
NK093(ge)002:17814: ba ni skabs bcu las yul la 'jug pa'i skabs
NK093(ge)002:17815: te / bsgom pa'i drod rtags da dung ma thob ste de la nye ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17816: de lta bu rten skyed kyi gnas su gyur pa'i sa 'di la yang dbye na gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17817: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs 'dzin grub pa'i rnal 'byor sgom lam thob pa kri ya dang /
NK093(ge)002:17818: de la goms shing nyams pa med par rnal 'byor che'am chen po u pa ya dang /
NK093(ge)002:17819: mtshan ma las ngesa para 'byung ste mthar lam la
NK093(ge)002:17820: sbyor ba'i rnala 'byor yo ga dang gsuma ste byang
NK093(ge)002:17821: chub sems dpa'i sa brgyad pa nas bcu pa'i bar
NK093(ge)002:17823: de yang 'dir chos nyid ji bzhin par rig pa rnal du 'byor ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17824: de pas kyang skyed du gyur pas ltos nas chen
NK093(ge)002:17825: por 'dogs pa dang mtshan ma gnyis las kyang nges
NK093(ge)002:17827: 'di dag thun mong gi rnal 'byor sgo so so'i kri yog ma yin te /
NK093(ge)002:17828: rgyud gcig gi lam dbang du bzhag pa'i phyir te dag pa'i sa gsum yang de ltar nges so //
NK093(ge)002:17829: rgyal ba rigs lnga la sogs pa'i dbang bskur zhing
NK093(ge)002:17830: thugsa kyi byin rlabs lasa rgyal ba'i sras kyi rgyud
NK093(ge)002:17831: du skyes pas sems dpa' bcu drug lta bur 'byung
NK093(ge)002:17832: zhing / lha'i cha lugs 'dzin pas rgyal ba'i sras
NK093(ge)002:17833: po sems dpa' bcu drug gi sprul pa'i rgyal tshab
NK093(ge)002:17834: byed pas gdung 'tshoba pa rtogs pa dang goms pas
NK093(ge)002:17835: khyad para gyis shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK093(ge)002:17836: rtsal 'aphanga kun rdzogas shing chub par byed de /
NK093(ge)002:17837: yang dag par rdzogs te mthar phyin pa'i sa ganga
NK093(ge)002:17838: la nges pa'i ting nge 'dzina rnal 'byor du sgoms
NK093(ge)002:17839: pas sbyor bar byed cing rigs rgyud 'dzin pa rdo
NK093(ge)002:17841: rgyal ba mang po mthong bas stug po bkod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17842: thun mong ma yin par 'di nyid kyi rtogs pa
NK093(ge)002:17843: kho na'i dbang du na gsang sngags gnyis su med
NK093(ge)002:17844: par mthong nas sgom lam de la shin tu mi
NK093(ge)002:17845: g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor grub pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17846: de la gnas pa rnal 'byor mchog tu che ba'i mi g.yo ba thob pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17847: de nyid brtan pas nges par 'byung ste mthar phyin pa'i lam thob lam rag pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:17848: rgyal ba'i thugs las skyes pa'i rgyal sras su dbang
NK093(ge)002:17849: bskur byin gyis brlabs pa las 'byung zhing gdung 'tshob
NK093(ge)002:17850: pas khyad par rtsal 'phang gi goms pa mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:17851: te bslab pa rdzogs pa'i don gang la ting nge
NK093(ge)002:17852: 'dzin mchog gi rnal 'byor du gnas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17853: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17854: dang po la'ang rnal 'byor gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17855: grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni nyams thob ma thag pa phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin grub pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17857: nyams brtan pa de'i ngang la gnas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17859: nyams mthar phyin pa mthar lam la sbyor nges pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17860: nyams de tsho ni mi zad mdzod kyi ting nge 'dzin la sbyor te /
NK093(ge)002:17861: 'phro 'du ni stong gsum tshun chad du'o //
NK093(ge)002:17862: khyon ni khru nyis brgya lnga bcu nga drug gam yang na stong gsum lhas khengs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17863: grangs kyang stongs gsum lhas gang ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17864: rnam pa ni chos nyid zag med kyi lha'o //
NK093(ge)002:17865: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:17866: sa bdun pa yul la 'jug pa'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:17867: mi 'gyur ba byang chub kyi sems /
NK093(ge)002:17868: dpe zla ba tshes bzhi pa lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17870: bdun pa mi g.yo ba yi lta ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:17871: mi zad mdzod kyi ting 'dzin mi g.yo spyod //
NK093(ge)002:17873: chos nyid mi g.yo ba'i don rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17874: dmigs med kyi don sgom pa'i mi zad mdzod kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK093(ge)002:17875: nang du yang dag 'jog las mi g.yo bar spyod pa rnams so //
NK093(ge)002:17878: bdun pa la gsum grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK093(ge)002:17879: mtshan ma las grol mi g.yor gnas pas brgyad //
NK093(ge)002:17880: legs pa cher ldan rnal 'byor chen po dgu //
NK093(ge)002:17881: nges 'byung gzhir gnas chos kyi sprin chen te //
NK093(ge)002:17882: dam tshig ye shes 'byed pas phyi rgyud gsum //
NK093(ge)002:17884: chos nyid rig pa la grub pa'i don rnal ma la 'byor ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:17885: mtshan ma las grol te cis kyang mi g.yo bar gnas pas sa brgyad pa mi g.yo ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:17886: de bas kyang skyed du gyur te legs pa cher
NK093(ge)002:17887: ldan pa'i rnal 'byor chen po ni sa dgu pa
NK093(ge)002:17890: de nyid chos kyi gzhir gnas pas sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin chen nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:17891: rim pa bzhin dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa
NK093(ge)002:17892: 'byed cing 'phro 'du byed pas phyi rgyud kri ya
NK093(ge)002:17893: u pa yo ga gsum mo //
NK093(ge)002:17894: lam lnga pa la gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17895: gnas pa mi 'gyur ba'i sa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:17896: gdal ba chos nyid kyi sa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:17897: rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi sa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17902: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17903: gnyis su med pa'i don la rig pa rnal du
NK093(ge)002:17904: gansa pa nyid las mi 'gyur ba'i ngang du phebs
NK093(ge)002:17905: pas skabs bcu las kyang rtog chen la phebs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17907: ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa la skyon dbang du
NK093(ge)002:17908: 'gyur ba med pas rtags chen po dang ldan pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17909: sa 'di la yang rnal 'byor gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17910: thams cad kyang rang rig pa'i cho 'phrul snang bar
NK093(ge)002:17911: rtogs pas dbang bsgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin dang
NK093(ge)002:17912: ldan pa ste / sbyor sgrol la sogs pa blang
NK093(ge)002:17913: dor med pa'i spyod pa rmada du byung bar spyod
NK093(ge)002:17914: cing dam rdzas sogs la nyam nga med par rola
NK093(ge)002:17916: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa ci spyad yang tshogs
NK093(ge)002:17917: gnyis su 'gyur bar shes pas tshogsa chen 'dus pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17918: rnal 'byor dang / 'di nas lung chen po'i tshogs
NK093(ge)002:17919: sgrub pas de grub nas tshom bu dang bcas pa
NK093(ge)002:17920: rig 'dzin gyi sar gshegs par yang gsungs so //
NK093(ge)002:17921: mnyam pa chen po'i lta spyod zung du 'brel bas
NK093(ge)002:17922: rig pa'i rtsal chen po dang ldan pas cho 'phrul
NK093(ge)002:17923: bzhi 'thob cing 'chad pa'i skyes bur nus pas yon
NK093(ge)002:17924: tan rdzogas pa'i rnal 'byor dang gsum du rdzogas para
NK093(ge)002:17926: de dag ni cha lugs lha'i sku phyag rgya chena
NK093(ge)002:17927: po nyid du gsal bas sgyu ma lta bu'i sku
NK093(ge)002:17928: can phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la gnas pa
NK093(ge)002:17929: yina no // de ni dper na 'khora losa sgyur
NK093(ge)002:17930: ba'i rgyal po chen po gang gi mtshan dpe dang
NK093(ge)002:17931: longs spyod mthong ba dang 'dra ste bdag nyid chen
NK093(ge)002:17932: po rgyal ba rdo rje 'chang chen po'i zhal mthonga
NK093(ge)002:17933: bas dgongs pa lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang nas dbang
NK093(ge)002:17934: phyug chen po'i gansa kyi 'og min chen po'i 'khor
NK093(ge)002:17935: du 'dus nas sems dpa' bcu drug gi mtshan dpe
NK093(ge)002:17936: thun mong ma yin pa dang ldan te 'bras bu'i
NK093(ge)002:17937: gzhi'i sa mchog rdzogas pa'i 'khor smin pa zhing khams
NK093(ge)002:17938: dag pa'i gansa na thams cad la ma chags par
NK093(ge)002:17939: longas spyod pas pad+ma spyan gyi sa non te dgongs
NK093(ge)002:17940: pa brda'i chos bstan pa la spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17941: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:17942: dang po la'ang rnal 'byor gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17943: rmad byung rol pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17944: nyams thob pa spyod pa blang dor med par zhugs nas slob pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17946: nyams goms pa blang dor med pa la slob pa'i tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17947: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17948: nyams mthar phyin pa tshogs grub nas rig 'dzin gyi rtsal rdzogs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17949: nyams 'di dag ni 'byung chen sprul pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK093(ge)002:17950: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin la sbyor te /
NK093(ge)002:17951: 'phro 'du ni rnam rtog gi sems kyis khyab tshad du'o //
NK093(ge)002:17952: khyon kyang sems kyis khyab tshad do //
NK093(ge)002:17953: grangs kyang sems kyis khyab tshad do //
NK093(ge)002:17954: rnam pa ni lhun grub kyi lha thob pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17955: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du sa brgyad pa rtog chen la phebs pa'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:17956: rig pa byang chub kyi sems dpe zla ba chas lnga pa lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:17958: brgyad pa ye shes rig pa'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17959: 'byung chen sprul pa'i ting 'dzin rtul zhugs spyod //
NK093(ge)002:17961: gnyis med kyi ye shes la rig pa rnal du phebs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:17962: 'byung ba chen po lnga la gzhal yas dang lhar sprul pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK093(ge)002:17963: spang blang med pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa la gnas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17964: rtsa ba'i rgyud las ting nge 'dzin bcu gnyis gsungs
NK093(ge)002:17965: pas 'dir yang dbang bsgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK093(ge)002:17966: sbyar ro // 'di'i rnal 'byor phra mo ni /
NK093(ge)002:17968: brgyad pa la gsum rmad byung rol pa ni //
NK093(ge)002:17969: rnal 'byor chen po bskyed pa'i skyed pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17970: tshogs chen 'dun pas bskyed pa'i rdzogs par rdzogs //
NK093(ge)002:17971: rtsal chen rdzogs pa bskyed pa'i rdzogs pa che //
NK093(ge)002:17973: blang dor med par rmad byung rol par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17974: rnal 'byor chen po bskyed pa'i skyed pa'i rim pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:17975: ci spyad tshogs chen gnyis su shes te 'dun pa'i
NK093(ge)002:17976: rnal 'byor ni bskyed pa'i rdzogs par rdzogs pa yin
NK093(ge)002:17977: la / lta spyod 'brel ba'i rig pa'i rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:17978: bskyed pa'i rdzogs pa chen po ste phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin chen po'o //
NK093(ge)002:17983: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:17984: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:17985: mnyam pa nyid du lhun gyis grub pas thams cad
NK093(ge)002:17986: rig pa'i rtsal du snang bar rtogs pa nyid gdeng
NK093(ge)002:17987: du gyur pas rig pa phyi nang gi chos kun
NK093(ge)002:17988: la gadla bar khyab ste mu med pa nyid du
NK093(ge)002:17989: bsnums pa'i chos nyid dag par gsal bas gdeng du
NK093(ge)002:17990: gyur pa'i skabs su'ang gsungs te /
NK093(ge)002:17991: bsgom pa'i mtha'i rtags chen po 'dir thob pa'i sa mchog 'di la yang rnal 'byor gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:17992: snang ba kun tu bzang mo'i rola par rtogs te
NK093(ge)002:17993: dbyings su spyod pa la 'dod yon lnga chos nyid
NK093(ge)002:17994: kyi rgyan du rdzogs par shes pas longs spyod rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:17995: pa nyid kyi rnal 'byor dam pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:17996: stong pa nyid dang snying rje ro mnyam pas nyon
NK093(ge)002:17997: mongs dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa chos thams cad
NK093(ge)002:17998: bde ba che'am chen po byang chub kyi sems rang
NK093(ge)002:17999: byung gi ye shes kun tu bzang por rtogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18000: rnal 'byor dang / dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su
NK093(ge)002:18001: med par ngang chen po'i thiga lera yongs su rdzogsa
NK093(ge)002:18002: par rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang gsum nyid du ni
NK093(ge)002:18004: chos kyi dbyings kyi yul la sbyor ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18005: snying rje 'byung bas dona mi 'gog pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18006: snying rje che dang chos nyid tha mi dad pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18007: phyir rig pa'i ye shes de nyid dang sbyar ba
NK093(ge)002:18008: ste shes bya ril de ltar shesa para byas pas
NK093(ge)002:18009: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med kyi ngang du 'bras
NK093(ge)002:18010: bu thams cada rdzogas te mthar phyin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18011: 'di dag kyang lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin chen po ste /
NK093(ge)002:18012: spyod yul ye shes 'gag med sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK093(ge)002:18013: skur ye nas rang gsal ba'nga de ltar rnam par
NK093(ge)002:18014: dag pa'i sgyu ma lta bur shar ba yina te
NK093(ge)002:18015: rig pas gnyis su med par gsal ba'i ngang la
NK093(ge)002:18016: gzhan don spyod pa'i mdzad pa yang snang bar 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:18017: bas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18018: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas dang mtshan med gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:18019: dang po la'ang rnal 'byor gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:18020: rol pa rgyan gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:18021: nyams thob pa 'dod yon lnga ma spang par chos nyid kyi rgyan du longs spyod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18022: bde ba chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:18024: nyon mongs pa dang sdug bsngal bde chen du gsal ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18025: thig le rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:18026: nyams brtan pa chos thams cad ye shes kyi thig ler mjal ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18027: nyams de tsho ni rnam dag dbyings kyi ting nge 'dzin la sbyor te /
NK093(ge)002:18028: 'phro 'du dang khyon dang grangs gsum char nam mkhas khyab tshad do //
NK093(ge)002:18029: rnam pa ni lhun grub kyi lha shin tu thob pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18030: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:18031: sa dgu pa gdeng du gyur ba'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:18032: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems dpe zla ba tshes brgyad pa lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:18034: dgu pa gnyis med dbyings kyi lta ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:18035: rnam dag dbyings kyi ting 'dzin dbang bsgyur thabs //
NK093(ge)002:18037: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med chos dbyings brdal ba chen po'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18038: rtog pa rnams lha'i dkyil 'khor du rnam par dag
NK093(ge)002:18039: ste rang bzhin med pa dbyings kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK093(ge)002:18040: sgom pa dang / 'dod yon la dbang bsgyur ba'i thabs kyi spyod pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18043: dgu pa la gsum rol pa rgyan de yi //
NK093(ge)002:18044: rdzogs pa'i bskyed pa rtsol bcas rnal 'byor yin //
NK093(ge)002:18045: bde ba chen po rdzogs pa'i rdzogs pa dngos //
NK093(ge)002:18046: thig ler rdzogs pa rdzogs pa'i ngang gnas pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18048: 'dod yon lnga chos nyid kyi rgyan du spyod pas
NK093(ge)002:18049: rol pa rgyan gyi rnal 'byor de ni rdzogs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18050: bskyed pa ste rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:18051: yin la / nyon mongs dang sdug bsngal bde chen
NK093(ge)002:18052: du gsal bas bde ba chen po'i rnal 'byor ni
NK093(ge)002:18053: rdzogs pa'i rdzogs pa dngos yin cing /
NK093(ge)002:18054: de nyid brtan pas ye shes kyi thig ler rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ni rdzogs pa dngos yin cing /
NK093(ge)002:18055: de nyid brtan pas ye shes kyi thig ler rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:18056: pa'i rnal 'byor ni rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang la
NK093(ge)002:18057: gnas pa'o // 'di dag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin du gsungs pa'ang bzhugs mod kyi /
NK093(ge)002:18059: dang po phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin mthar thug pa /
NK093(ge)002:18060: gnyis pa des lhun grub rig 'dzin la sbyor ba'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:18061: gsum pa lhun grub dngos thob par byas na gzhung gi gsung sgros dang shin tu mthun no //
NK093(ge)002:18066: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18067: sa'i rim pa kun lhun gyis rdzogas pa nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:18068: spyir zhes spyi bor phyin te yongs su chibsa pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18069: sa mchog dam pa 'di ni rnal 'byor bcu yi
NK093(ge)002:18070: grangs kyi tha ma mthar thug cing sangs rgyas kyi
NK093(ge)002:18071: sa la 'jug pa'i gral gyi dang po 'dir las
NK093(ge)002:18072: su rung ste skyed du bya ba gtan med par
NK093(ge)002:18073: mathara phyin par rdzogas pa yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:18074: las su rung ba'i skabs su'ang gsungs te /
NK093(ge)002:18075: des na mtha'i rtags rmad du byung ba ril ma
NK093(ge)002:18076: lus la kun mi 'gyur bar brtan pa nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:18077: sa mchog gang zhig gral gyi yang thog 'dir sa
NK093(ge)002:18078: rnams mthar phyin pa'i rtse mo'i toga chen po yina
NK093(ge)002:18079: te / 'di'i ngo bo ni thams cad kyang rang
NK093(ge)002:18080: byung gi ye shes chen po rang snang ba'i klong
NK093(ge)002:18081: yangsa pa 'ba' zhig la gang yang ma chud pa
NK093(ge)002:18082: med pas nam mkha'i dbyings lta bu'i snying por gyur
NK093(ge)002:18083: pa'i 'bras bu'i bcud chen po la kun yongs su
NK093(ge)002:18085: dper na sprin meda pa'i nam mkha' la nyi ma
NK093(ge)002:18086: 'buma dus gcig tu shar ba ltar gyis ye shes
NK093(ge)002:18087: sgrib med du gsal ba'i ngo bor yongs su rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:18088: par gadla ba de ni ci snang ji srid gang
NK093(ge)002:18089: du'ang mi 'gog la rnam pa gang cir yanga grub
NK093(ge)002:18090: pa ma yina pa ste rang bzhin gang du'ang mi
NK093(ge)002:18091: skye bas mtha'i snang ba mi 'byung zhing gang ltar
NK093(ge)002:18092: snang ba'ang mi 'agga pas tha snyad du mtha' ril
NK093(ge)002:18093: las grol ba'i ngo bo nyid du rdzogs pa lasa
NK093(ge)002:18094: dang rnam par thar pa'i sgo tha dad par ji
NK093(ge)002:18095: ltar bltas rgu de ltar bsam pa dera rang snanga
NK093(ge)002:18096: ba nyid kyang 'dir chub pas gadla khyab chen pos
NK093(ge)002:18097: spyi rgya rlabsa kyis bacada pa kho na'o //
NK093(ge)002:18098: de lta bu'i rdzogs pa chen po de la yanga
NK093(ge)002:18099: lta ba dama pa'i khyad par gyis dbye na rnal
NK093(ge)002:18100: 'byor gsum ste / dbyings dang ye shes kyang tha snyad tsam du rtogs te /
NK093(ge)002:18101: chos thams cad ril badga nyid chen po rig pa
NK093(ge)002:18102: rang byung gi ye shes gnyis med chen po'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:18103: 'byor yul med rang gsal gyi ngang gcig tu rtogs
NK093(ge)002:18104: pa dang / de nyid la'ang rgyu 'bras ril ma
NK093(ge)002:18105: brtsal lhun gyis grub par dgongs pas ma 'dres yongs
NK093(ge)002:18107: de nyid kyi tha snyad la'ang mi gnas te gang
NK093(ge)002:18108: yang ma spangs bkol ba med pas chos nyid kyi
NK093(ge)002:18109: klong yangas par chub ste ma 'dres mtha' bral yongs
NK093(ge)002:18110: rdzogs dbyer med du gsal pa'i dkyil 'khor du dgongs
NK093(ge)002:18112: de ltar gsum po de dag ril lhun gyis rdzogsa
NK093(ge)002:18113: pas gsum gyi tha snyad kyang med par ranga byung
NK093(ge)002:18114: gi ye shes kyi nyi ma 'char nub med par
NK093(ge)002:18115: gadla khyab tu gyur pa ni 'bras bu chen po
NK093(ge)002:18116: mthar thug pa nyid du phyin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18117: 'di nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin chen po rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK093(ge)002:18118: 'di la'ang mtshan bcas lha sgom pa dang mtshan med chos nyid sgom pa gnyis las /
NK093(ge)002:18121: bdag nyid chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:18122: nyams thob pa lha dang chos thams cad rang rig tu gsal ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18123: lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:18124: nyams brtan pa rgyu 'bras thams cad gnyis med kyi ngang du lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18125: klong yangs chub pa'i rnal 'byor ni nyams mthar phyin
NK093(ge)002:18126: pa rtsol ba med par gsal ba la mi mthun
NK093(ge)002:18128: nyams de tsho ni thams cad rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK093(ge)002:18129: snang gsal ye 'phyo'i ting nge 'dzin la sbyar te /
NK093(ge)002:18130: 'phro 'du dang khyon dang grangs gsum gcig char chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab tshad do //
NK093(ge)002:18131: rnam pa ni lhun grub kyi lha brtan zhing mthar phyin pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18132: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi dbang du /
NK093(ge)002:18133: sa bcu pa las su rung ba'i skabs /
NK093(ge)002:18134: rdzogs pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK093(ge)002:18135: dpe zla ba tshes bcu drug pa lta bu ste /
NK093(ge)002:18137: tha ma gza' gtad med pa'i lta ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:18138: snang gsal ye 'phyo'i ting 'dzin lhun grub spyod //
NK093(ge)002:18140: rang byung ye shes 'ba' zhig las sel med pas gza' gtad med pa'i lta ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18141: thams cad mkhyen pas snang gsal ye 'phyo'i ting nge
NK093(ge)002:18142: 'dzin dang bya brtsal med par lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18144: 'dir thams cad rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin yang sbyar ro //
NK093(ge)002:18147: tha ma la gsum bdag nyid chen po ni //
NK093(ge)002:18148: rnal 'byor chen po rdzogs par la bzla ste //
NK093(ge)002:18149: lhun gyis grub pa rjes su 'byor ba nyid //
NK093(ge)002:18150: klong yangs chub pa de yis gshis mthong bas //
NK093(ge)002:18151: de las sems bskyed don la reg 'dod yin //
NK093(ge)002:18153: thams cad rang byung gi ye shes su rtogs pas bdag nyid chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK093(ge)002:18154: rnal 'byor chen po rdzogs chen du la bzla ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18155: de la thams cad ma brtsal bar rdzogs pas lhun
NK093(ge)002:18156: gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni rjes su rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:18157: nyid der la bzla ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18158: tha snyad la mi gnas te klong yangs chub pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18159: rnal 'byor de yis gshis mthong bas lhun grub rig
NK093(ge)002:18160: 'dzi na rang rgyud dag pa 'i sangs rgyas so
NK093(ge)002:18161: // de ltar sems bcu bskyed de rnal 'byor gyi
NK093(ge)002:18162: rim pa rdzogs pa las mthar thug gi don la
NK093(ge)002:18163: reg par 'dod pa ni rjes su rnal 'byor gyi
NK093(ge)002:18164: gzhung gi gsang ba yang dag pa nyid yin no
NK093(ge)002:18165: // // de bas na mthar lam gsum po 'di'i /
NK093(ge)002:18166: dang po gnyis med rig pa'i don la 'byor nges pas chos sku'i sas bsdus la /
NK093(ge)002:18167: gnyis pa ye shes kyi sku thob par nges pas longs sku'i sas bsdus shing /
NK093(ge)002:18168: gsum pa la don gnyis kyi mdzad pa rdzogs nges
NK093(ge)002:18169: pas sprul sku'i sas bsdus par yang gsungs te de
NK093(ge)002:18170: ltar sku gsum dbyer med kyi chos sku chen po
NK093(ge)002:18171: ni ngo bo nyid sku'i 'khor du gyur pas skad
NK093(ge)002:18172: cig la snying po byang chub tu sangs rgyas pa
NK093(ge)002:18173: nyid de / rin po che rgyan las /
NK093(ge)002:18174: dus la thog med mthar mi nus //
NK093(ge)002:18175: gnas lugs skabs bzhin 'dir shes bya //
NK093(ge)002:18176: rgyud dag dus kyi dang po ni //
NK093(ge)002:18177: rang rang grol tshe skabs las sbyar //
NK093(ge)002:18178: zhes gsungs pa sogs rgyud dang man ngag dag las rgya cher 'byung ngo //
NK093(ge)002:18179: mdor na thun mong ma yin pa'i lam 'di dag
NK093(ge)002:18180: gang zag rgyud gcig gi dbang du theg pa ril
NK093(ge)002:18181: rdzogs pa chen por 'dus shing 'bras bu der gcig
NK093(ge)002:18182: pa ni chu bo brgal ba'i thabs mi mthun yang
NK093(ge)002:18183: brgyud nas mthar 'dir son pas na gcig pa dang
NK093(ge)002:18185: spyi nyid gsang sngags nang pa man chad kyis yang
NK093(ge)002:18186: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa rdzogs pa
NK093(ge)002:18187: spyir chibs kyi sa chen po mthong ba la phyin
NK093(ge)002:18188: nas thug pa med par bgrod pa ni ma yin
NK093(ge)002:18189: no // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:18190: mdo sde kun tu 'od dang kri ya rdo rje
NK093(ge)002:18191: 'dzin pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa yan chad rdzogs pa
NK093(ge)002:18192: chen po nyid kyi bsti gnas kyi phyir /
NK093(ge)002:18193: nam gnas 'dir sangs rgyas pa na 'dir rdzogs pa chen po thob ces bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18194: rang re'i sgos mthar thug tu bstan pa ni rgyud so so'i mos dbang du bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18199: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18200: 'dir sa'i rim pa thun mong ma yin par smos pa 'di dag rnams ni /
NK093(ge)002:18201: gsang sngags kyi don la rnal 'byor du byed pa
NK093(ge)002:18202: rnams kyi rim par spyod pa'i sa yi rim pa
NK093(ge)002:18203: yin te / sa'i rim pa la khyad para yod
NK093(ge)002:18204: par snang nas rims kyis 'jug par mos pa gang
NK093(ge)002:18205: la de dang mthun par sa'i khyad para mtho dman
NK093(ge)002:18206: du snang ste rims kyis gsang sngags la 'jug pa'o
NK093(ge)002:18207: yin te / // ganga sa'i rim pa khyed par
NK093(ge)002:18208: can du mthong ba med par gcig char du 'jug
NK093(ge)002:18209: par mos pa rnams la de ltar sa mtho dman
NK093(ge)002:18210: gyi khyad par med par rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyis
NK093(ge)002:18212: des na shes rab kyi rtsal 'aphanga mtho ba rnams kyis sa mchog la gcig char bgrod par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18213: 'on kyang stes dbang ma yin te /
NK093(ge)002:18214: sngar sbyangs pas 'di la sa gzhan ma bgrod par
NK093(ge)002:18215: sa'i tog chen po nyid la 'jug pa mi 'gal
NK093(ge)002:18216: ba dang / sems nyid yin bzhin nor bu rin
NK093(ge)002:18217: po che gang ltar bslab pa ltar 'gyur du btub
NK093(ge)002:18219: skal pa dang shes rab kyi rtsal 'phang zhan te
NK093(ge)002:18220: sa'i rim par mtho damna du 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:18221: pasa mtho damna gyi rim pa'i go 'aphanga ltar 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:18222: dbang ma nges pa'i sa nas yar skas kyi gdangs
NK093(ge)002:18224: 'o na gsang sngags kyi dbang po tha shal rim
NK093(ge)002:18225: 'jug ni mdo sde bas kyang lam rim ste phyin
NK093(ge)002:18226: pa'i dus med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:18227: 'dir ting nge 'dzin dang por dmigs pa brtan pas
NK093(ge)002:18228: gzhan rnams la rtsol ba'i yun med par 'gro zhing
NK093(ge)002:18229: thabs khyad par can gyis skad cig tsam du gnas
NK093(ge)002:18230: pa'i rim pa la sar bsnyad kyi /
NK093(ge)002:18231: bskal pa'i grangs dang yun du thogs pa med pas
NK093(ge)002:18232: de nyid la sbyor ba'i phyir ring ba min pa
NK093(ge)002:18233: dang / rgyu yis bskal par spyad kyang thabs 'di
NK093(ge)002:18234: dag dang 'phrad nas 'di bzhin du grub pas gzod
NK093(ge)002:18235: 'tshang rgya ba'i phyir the tshom med do //
NK093(ge)002:18236: thun mong du bsnyad na dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:18237: 'byor rten pas khyad par du 'gro ba man chod
NK093(ge)002:18238: 'jig rten pa dang rgyu'i theg pa'i sar 'gyur bas
NK093(ge)002:18239: de nas gzod gsang sngags kyi dmigs pas 'bras bu
NK093(ge)002:18240: skye ba'i sa la 'jug go zhes gzhan pa dag
