NK093(ge)002:18241: 'dod do // kho bo ni 'dir bshad pa'i yid
NK093(ge)002:18242: la byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa dang
NK093(ge)002:18244: 'chad pa'i lha'i ting nge 'dzin gyis gsang sngags kyis
NK093(ge)002:18245: 'ba' zhig la the tshom med pa'i phyir 'dir thun
NK093(ge)002:18246: mong ma yin par bsnyad pa la 'gal ba med
NK093(ge)002:18247: do // zhes gnubs chen mkhyen pa'i gter mdzod bstan 'gro'i dpal mgon mchog gis gsungs so //
NK093(ge)002:18248: skabs gang 'dira sdud pas dris te dri bar bya
NK093(ge)002:18249: ba'i mchoga sa'i khyad par rnams lan du gsal bar
NK093(ge)002:18250: bshad pas thun mong min pa'i sa'i don la snang
NK093(ge)002:18252: dri ba'i mchog dri ba'i dama para gyur pa langa
NK093(ge)002:18253: ka'i mnga' badga srin po mgrin bcu zhes sdud pa
NK093(ge)002:18254: po la don gyis bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:18255: lung gi rgyud chen po gang 'dira rnal 'byor gyi
NK093(ge)002:18256: rim pa che chung kun sbyor te rdzogs par bstan
NK093(ge)002:18257: pa yang / gsang sngags kyi don mthar thug ngesa pa'i sa mchog chen po bcu ni /
NK093(ge)002:18258: sa kun gyi yang rtsa ba'i gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18259: des na 'dira bstan pa'i sa'i rim pa 'di ni khyad par gyi lam du 'thad de /
NK093(ge)002:18260: gang de dag gi rtsa ba chen po don ma
NK093(ge)002:18261: nor bar nges pa'i sa bcu 'di nyid kyi yan
NK093(ge)002:18262: lag gi rim pa'i dbye ba las /
NK093(ge)002:18263: rnal 'byor phra mo bcu tshan gnyis te nyi shu
NK093(ge)002:18264: dang bduna phrag gnyis la bcu bzhi ste rnal 'byor
NK093(ge)002:18265: sum cu rtsa bzhir phye bas kun 'dus shing rdzogas
NK093(ge)002:18266: pa nyid de / sa bzhi pa'i rnal 'byor phra
NK093(ge)002:18267: mo drug ni mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal 'byor la
NK093(ge)002:18268: 'dus pas logs su ma bgrang ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18269: de lta bu'i sa bcu por sa gzhan gyi rtsa
NK093(ge)002:18270: ba dang yan lag tu phye ba kun 'dus pa
NK093(ge)002:18272: mdo sde byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu dang /
NK093(ge)002:18273: gsang sngags kyi khyad par 'phags pa'i sa bcu ste bcu phrag gnyis dang /
NK093(ge)002:18274: nyan thos kyi sa bdun dang /
NK093(ge)002:18275: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa gnyis la sogs pa ril rdzogs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18277: de dag kyang gsang sngags kyi sar brgyud nas non par byed pa'i rgyur gyur pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18278: de dag gi mthar gtugs pa'i 'bras bu chen po 'di yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:18279: bre phul gyis tshul gyis bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18280: des na gsang sngags lung gi sa bcu ni sa
NK093(ge)002:18281: yi yon tan gyi khyad para las mchog tu che
NK093(ge)002:18282: ba ste / sa ril gyi rtsa ba yin pas
NK093(ge)002:18283: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa'i sa rgya che ba dang
NK093(ge)002:18284: grangsa manga yanga gzhan la 'jug cing bgrod par mi
NK093(ge)002:18285: ba ste / bya ste / gsang sngags nges don
NK093(ge)002:18286: gyi rnal 'byor rdzogs pa'i sa mchog 'di la skal
NK093(ge)002:18287: bas phye nas sgo 'dira tshul gnyis kyis sbyar bar
NK093(ge)002:18288: bya zhing 'jug par gyis shig pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18291: zhes pa nas skad cig tsam bgrod pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18292: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18293: byang chub sems dpa' dang rig 'dzin rnams kyi sa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18294: sangs rgyas rnams kyi'ang sa yi 'byung gansa kyi gzhir gyur pa /
NK093(ge)002:18295: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po
NK093(ge)002:18296: gang de thams cad kun gyi gnas mchog sa chen
NK093(ge)002:18298: ganga su zhig gisa kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems
NK093(ge)002:18299: kyi sa chen po 'di nyid nona te don mngon
NK093(ge)002:18300: du gyur na gzhan rnams bgrod cing sbyangs mi dgos
NK093(ge)002:18301: pa'i phyir sa rnams kun rig pa'i skad cig tsam
NK093(ge)002:18302: gyis bgroda cing yang dag par non pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18303: des na gcig char 'jug pa'i don ni mchog gi mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18307: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18308: grogsa po dag /de dag ni khyad para bla mara 'gro bar bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18309: zhesa dama baca'a bar mdzad pa'i sa'i rim pa 'og
NK093(ge)002:18310: nas gong du 'phar ba'i tshul dang gcig char du
NK093(ge)002:18311: bgrod pa'i tshul gyis dgongas pa dam pa yongas su
NK093(ge)002:18312: bgrosa te bstan pa yin para shesa para bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18314: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK093(ge)002:18315: ting nge 'dzin gyi rnal 'byor bcu yis sa'i rim
NK093(ge)002:18316: pa gsal bar byed pas sgron ma dam pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:18317: bstan pa'i le'u ste druga cu rtsa gcig pa nyid
NK093(ge)002:18318: rnam par bshad pa'o ////bdun pa yul la 'jug par
NK093(ge)002:18330: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18331: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK093(ge)002:18332: sa'i sgron ma bstan ma thag pa de nasa yanga
NK093(ge)002:18333: langa ka'i badga po la sogas pa 'khor damna pa
NK093(ge)002:18335: ston pa gasnga ba pa'i badga po la dris pa /
NK093(ge)002:18336: kye gasnga ba pa'i badga po /
NK093(ge)002:18337: nyid kyis le'u zhe lnga par chos kyi rnam grangs bcu bkod pa las /
NK093(ge)002:18340: zhesa dama baca'a bar dgongas pa de nyid /
NK093(ge)002:18341: ji ltar yongas su shes par bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:18342: de skad ces yongas su dris pa las /
NK093(ge)002:18343: gasnga ba pa'i badga posa lana smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK093(ge)002:18344: kye grogsa po dag /ces skyes bus bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:18345: yul gyi ngo bo bstan pa shes par bya ba
NK093(ge)002:18346: ni 'di ltar ganga su zhig gi sangs rgyas kyi
NK093(ge)002:18347: zhing yongas su spyod para 'doda pa rnams kyis /
NK093(ge)002:18348: gang du ting nge 'dzin dang ye shes kyi dgongas
NK093(ge)002:18349: pa'i yul chos nyid ji bzhin pa de kho na
NK093(ge)002:18350: nyid dang / ganga la gnyis su med pa'i thugs
NK093(ge)002:18351: rje chen po 'byung ba'i yula mtha' yasa shing bsam
NK093(ge)002:18352: gyis mi khyab pa'i 'gro ba 'khora ba na gnas
NK093(ge)002:18353: pa rnams kyi don dang gnyis la dgongs spyod kyis
NK093(ge)002:18354: nyid dang / 'jug para bya'o // tshul de ni /
NK093(ge)002:18355: dpera na btso blag makhana dag gis rasa sbyangsa pa
NK093(ge)002:18356: ganga du tshon gyi bya ba jena pa ltar du
NK093(ge)002:18357: / ganga 'dira lasa kyi dang po pa'i rnal 'byor pasa /
NK093(ge)002:18358: ganga dera don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi byang
NK093(ge)002:18359: chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis kyi rgyus bdag gzhan
NK093(ge)002:18360: gyi sgrib pa sbyang ba la rab tu brtson pa
NK093(ge)002:18361: shin tu gces shing gal che ba nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:18362: de skad ces smras te bka' stsal pasa /
NK093(ge)002:18366: zhugs pa nyid du rig par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18367: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18368: de la sdud pa po byanga chub semas dapa'a semas
NK093(ge)002:18369: dapa'a chena po langa ka'i badga po desa 'di skad
NK093(ge)002:18371: gasnga ba pa'i badga po zhes ston pa la bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:18372: gang sngar gyi dus thams cada nasa phyis kyi dus thams cad kun tu /
NK093(ge)002:18373: 'khor ba nyid ye nasa sangsa rgyas pa yin pasa
NK093(ge)002:18374: 'phral du ma grub pa nyid grub par byar med
NK093(ge)002:18375: par bka' stsal pa de ltar nges na /
NK093(ge)002:18376: da gdoda sangsa rgyas para byar meda phana chad /
NK093(ge)002:18377: dgongas pa dama pa'i yul de kho na nyid la
NK093(ge)002:18378: blos sbyor ba'i sgom pa dang snying rje'i yul du
NK093(ge)002:18379: byas te don bya rgyu nyid du gyur pa ganga
NK093(ge)002:18380: yanga ma dmigs pas med pa nyid du nges lagas
NK093(ge)002:18381: na / 'dira snying rje'i yul du dgongs te don bya ba'i gnas su gyur pa ganga lagas /
NK093(ge)002:18382: de las kyang khyad par du 'gro ba gang su zhiga snyinga rje'i yul du gyur pa lags /
NK093(ge)002:18383: de skad ces smras te dris pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18384: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gasnga ba pa'i badga posa lan smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK093(ge)002:18387: chos rnams kyi rang bzhin de nyid sngar bshad pa
NK093(ge)002:18388: de ltar kun kyanga ye nas sangsa rgyas pa'i rang
NK093(ge)002:18389: bzhin yin phana chad de kho na nyid du nges
NK093(ge)002:18390: pasa / don dam par snying rje'i yul thugs rjes
NK093(ge)002:18391: bzung bar bya ba'i 'gro ba dang dgongas pa'i yula
NK093(ge)002:18392: sgom par bya ba'i ngo bo nyid gang yanga meda
NK093(ge)002:18394: gang gisa dgongs spyod kyi dngos po ji ltar byas
NK093(ge)002:18395: na yanga de nyid chos nyid mnyam pa che na
NK093(ge)002:18396: po'i don gyi de kho na nyid lasa mi 'ad'a
NK093(ge)002:18397: bar gzhan du ma gyur ba'i tshul gyis dgongs spyod
NK093(ge)002:18398: gang yang theg pa'i sgo gang dang yang 'agla ba
NK093(ge)002:18399: min zhing 'gro ba'i bsam pa kun dang 'agla bar
NK093(ge)002:18400: mi bya ba gnyis su bka' stsal pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18402: 'gro ba sems can rnams sam gdul bya gang dag
NK093(ge)002:18403: gi dona nyid byed pa ni thugs kyi dama tshiga
NK093(ge)002:18405: ye nas sangsa rgyas pa yin pasa dona byar meda
NK093(ge)002:18406: de sems can ril lam yang dag par sbyang bas
NK093(ge)002:18407: bya byed dang bral bar sangs rgyas thob zin par
NK093(ge)002:18408: rtogs pa ni snying rje chena po yina no //
NK093(ge)002:18409: gtan tshigs de gnyis kyi phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:18410: don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems rang gi sems
NK093(ge)002:18411: nyid du nges pas dgongas pa dama pa la 'phral
NK093(ge)002:18412: du 'juga mi dgosa para shes pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:18413: dgongas pa dama pa'i yul yang dag pa nyid rnal
NK093(ge)002:18414: du phebs pa yin pas chos nyid de kho na
NK093(ge)002:18415: nyid la zhugsa zin pa nyid du riga cing shes
NK093(ge)002:18416: para bya'o // zhes gdams pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:18418: dgongs pa'i yul la 'jug pa bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:18419: snying rje'i yul la 'jug pa bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18421: dgongs pa gsang ba'i phyir gsang ba'i yul dang lhan cig mi gnas pa /
NK093(ge)002:18422: bya ba med pas gzhan don bya ba /
NK093(ge)002:18423: nyams pa'i yo byad mi spyad pa /
NK093(ge)002:18424: spyad par gyur na de'i nyes pa /
NK093(ge)002:18425: theg pa'i sgo gang dang yang mi 'gal bar dge ba'i dpung bskyed pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18430: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18431: langa ka'i badga po zhes bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:18432: de nyid shes par bya ba'i thabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:18433: dgos pa nye bar ston pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK093(ge)002:18434: chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i dgongsa pa dama para ganga
NK093(ge)002:18435: su zhig 'jug tu med par shes te zhugsa zin
NK093(ge)002:18436: pa gang gi shes rab thun mong gi zab mo
NK093(ge)002:18437: shin tu zaba pa basa kyang ches khyad par du
NK093(ge)002:18438: blo gros zaba pa de nyid kyi dgongs pasa sems
NK093(ge)002:18439: kyi de kho na nyid ji lta ba'i mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:18440: gting nasa rtogs par bya zhing nges par thaga bacada
NK093(ge)002:18441: de / gsang ba'i rtogs pa 'phel ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18442: dam tshig mi nyams pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18443: gdul bya chud mi za ba'i phyir dang /
NK093(ge)002:18444: gasnga sngags mi bstan pa'i yul bzhi ni /
NK093(ge)002:18447: theg pa chung ngu ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18448: theg pa chen po la gsar du zhugs pa rnams sam /
NK093(ge)002:18451: gsang sngags la gsar du zhugs pa bzhir yang gsungs
NK093(ge)002:18452: te skye bo de rnams dang lhan cig ci la'ang
NK093(ge)002:18453: mi bsdad cing nyal te mi gzims pas mi brnal
NK093(ge)002:18456: bstan pa'i gnas min snod ngan dang //
NK093(ge)002:18457: rnam pa bzhis bsdus bye brag rnams //
NK093(ge)002:18459: shes nas spang bar bya phyir bshad //
NK093(ge)002:18461: zab mor 'jug pa'i sngon logs nas //
NK093(ge)002:18462: sems nyid gting nas tshar gcad phyir //
NK093(ge)002:18463: theg pa dman pa'i skye bo dang //
NK093(ge)002:18464: lhan cig ci la'ang mi brnal lo //
NK093(ge)002:18466: des na 'di nyid ltar na gsang yul bzhi dang
NK093(ge)002:18467: nyan thos kyi nang du mi gnas pa dang sbyar
NK093(ge)002:18473: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18474: de bas na de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:18475: de dag gang yanga chos nyid mnyam pa chen po
NK093(ge)002:18476: lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang la yongas su rdzogas pa
NK093(ge)002:18477: nyid kyi phyir ganga yang ris med par lhan mi
NK093(ge)002:18478: gcig pa'i bya bas so sor 'dug tu med cing
NK093(ge)002:18479: / sangs rgyas lta bu'i phrin las kyis dgongs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18480: yul la 'jug pa dang thugs rje'i yul la 'jug
NK093(ge)002:18481: pa rang bzhin yin pas mtshan ma'i yul la rtsol
NK093(ge)002:18482: bas ched du bya ba meda par gyur na yanga
NK093(ge)002:18483: / / rnal 'byor pa blo che ba de yi
NK093(ge)002:18484: thugs kyi ranga bzhina nyi ma ltar du kun la
NK093(ge)002:18485: snyoms shing phana par byed pas gazhana gyi don mdzad
NK093(ge)002:18486: pa yina pasa yul bzhi po dag gi rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:18487: lta spyod kyi nus pa chung ba ganga yin pa
NK093(ge)002:18488: 'dira yang theg chen gsang ba mchog gi lta spyod
NK093(ge)002:18489: zab mo drang thad du bstan na ji bzhin du
NK093(ge)002:18490: mi go zhing skur pas ltung ba'i phyir lhan mi
NK093(ge)002:18491: gcig par byas te phyi'i spyod pa 'tshams pas thams
NK093(ge)002:18492: cad la phana para don bya ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18497: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18498: rnal 'byor pa ganga su zhig gi gasnga sngags zab
NK093(ge)002:18499: mo'i gzhung dona dang 'agla bar gyur cing dam tshig
NK093(ge)002:18500: nyams pa de lasa byung bar gyur pa'i nor rdzas
NK093(ge)002:18501: la sogs pa'i yo byad dag dper na rus sbal
NK093(ge)002:18502: rang gi mgo la mi phyin brgya la 'ongas na
NK093(ge)002:18503: 'chi ltas yin pas myur du 'dor ba bzhin nam
NK093(ge)002:18504: / ru sbal gyi mgo la yod pa'i nor bu
NK093(ge)002:18505: rin po che ni nyen can dang 'brel bar mi
NK093(ge)002:18506: bya ba yin pa ltara du dam nyams kyi rdzas
NK093(ge)002:18507: ni nyes pa chen po dang 'brel bas rgya mtshos
NK093(ge)002:18508: bar bcad pa ltar rtsal skyed nas mu mtha'a meda
NK093(ge)002:18509: para bshug ste spang bar bya ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18510: de'i dgos pa ci yi phyir na dus kun tu
NK093(ge)002:18511: rnal 'byor mchog dam pa gzhung ma nyams pasa rnal
NK093(ge)002:18512: 'byor dam tshig dang ldan pa nyid dang nang 'grul
NK093(ge)002:18513: te bshes par bya ba lasa ma rtogs pa dang
NK093(ge)002:18514: dam nyams pa rnams dang bshes par bya ba mina
NK093(ge)002:18515: pas spang ste kha tsam yang mi gtam par byed
NK093(ge)002:18517: de las gyur pa'i yo byad dag /rus sbal mgo la 'ongs pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:18518: shin tu 'khrugs pa'i sems chen gyis //
NK093(ge)002:18519: rgya mtshos bshugs te spang bar bya //
NK093(ge)002:18523: nyes pa de 'byung mi 'byung gi khyad par rtogs par gdams pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18528: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18529: brgya la gala te gang zag 'ga' zhig gi don
NK093(ge)002:18530: ma rtogs pa'i dabnga gisa ngo bsrab cing 'dod pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18531: rkyen dbang du gyur nas nyams pa dang 'grul na
NK093(ge)002:18532: gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i gzhung gi dama pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18534: nyams pa de dang 'grul bas bsam pa dang mi
NK093(ge)002:18535: mthuna pa'i nyams pa'i bka' chad kyi nyen chena po
NK093(ge)002:18541: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18542: gala te gang zag nyams pa dang bshes pa'i rnal
NK093(ge)002:18543: 'byor de la bka'i chad pa de nyid byung na
NK093(ge)002:18544: de la skyabs su gyur pa'i mgona btsun ni chos
NK093(ge)002:18545: nyid byang chub sems kyi lta ba rtogs nas de
NK093(ge)002:18546: yi ngang la gnas pa'i mi dmigs pa'i shes rab
NK093(ge)002:18547: de lasa gzhan gang gis kyang skyob par nus pa
NK093(ge)002:18548: meda do // de bas na chos nyid byang chub
NK093(ge)002:18549: sems kyi lta ba de yi don gang gis ma
NK093(ge)002:18550: zina na gnyis ka nyams pas 'gos te dge ba
NK093(ge)002:18551: ci spyad kyang 'abna thag chad de rdo rje dmyal
NK093(ge)002:18554: gal te gang zag dbang gis na //
NK093(ge)002:18555: nyams pa'i chad pa byung ba na //
NK093(ge)002:18556: mgon tshun chos nyid chu phab nas //
NK093(ge)002:18557: skong zlog cho ga rgya cher bya //
NK093(ge)002:18559: 'o na gzhan gyis nyams pa ma nyams pa la 'gos btub bam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:18560: 'di nyid kyi gzhung gi dam tshig gi skabs las /
NK093(ge)002:18561: dper na rte'u rid rngo can gyis yu ma khyu phung ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18562: 'o ma rul ba thigs pa gcig ma rul pa'i nang du blugs na kun rul pa bzhin te /
NK093(ge)002:18563: de nyid kyi dam tshig gsang ba mchog gi le'u las /
NK093(ge)002:18564: de lta mod kyi 'di kun rnams //
NK093(ge)002:18565: rmi lam du yang mthong mi bya //
NK093(ge)002:18566: ci'i phyir 'o ma nyung ngu zhig /rul bas 'o ma kun rul bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:18567: rnal 'byor nyams gyur gcig gis ni //
NK093(ge)002:18569: 'khor ba'i g.yul rgyal byed pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:18570: log pa'i rnal 'byor thams cad kun //
NK093(ge)002:18571: don la mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK093(ge)002:18572: thams cad bsgrims te spang bar bya //
NK093(ge)002:18573: gal te ma spangs log spyod na //
NK093(ge)002:18575: bden pa'i byin rlabs mthu chung 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:18577: de bas na nyams pa dang 'dris pa nyid kyis
NK093(ge)002:18578: kyang rgyal ba'i bka' bcag pa'i las byas pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:18579: ro // lnga pa la gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:18587: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18588: 'o na nyams pa'i don gtan 'dir dgag gam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:18589: rnal 'byor pa ganga gi dge ba'i rtsa ba sna
NK093(ge)002:18590: tshogs nyams pa la sogs pa bdag dang gzhan gyi
NK093(ge)002:18591: dona du gang 'gyur ba'i spyod par nges na dge
NK093(ge)002:18592: ba dkar phyogs phra mo'i phra mo'am chung ngu'i chung
NK093(ge)002:18593: ngur gyur pa'i phra ba yana chad nas /
NK093(ge)002:18594: chen po'i chen po man chad ril thams cad nas
NK093(ge)002:18595: thams cad du ji lta bar mos pa rnams don
NK093(ge)002:18596: chud mi gsan par nana tan gyis ni 'bad de
NK093(ge)002:18597: snying rje chen po dang ldan par dag'a ba dang
NK093(ge)002:18598: ldan nas btang snyoms spangs pas sgrubs par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18599: gnyis pa la bcu gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:18600: theg pa 'og ma pa snying rje'i yul du dmigs te 'degs pa /
NK093(ge)002:18601: chu gtor rgya chen po gtang ba /
NK093(ge)002:18604: chos kyi sbyin pa btang ba /
NK093(ge)002:18612: dge ba sna tshogs bya ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18617: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18618: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor pas /
NK093(ge)002:18619: slongsa mo byas te 'tsho ba'i nyan thos pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18620: de'i rigs su gtogs pa'i slong ba la dag'a bas rang rgyal yang bsdus shing /
NK093(ge)002:18621: mdo sde'i byang sems slong mo la brten pa'i bsod
NK093(ge)002:18622: snyoms kyis 'tsho ba'i chos la tshe gcig tu spyod
NK093(ge)002:18623: pa rnams / rang rig gi sde dang tshana pa dang grwara byas pa'am /
NK093(ge)002:18624: yang na nyan thos kyi sde dang rang rgyal gyi tshan dang byang sems rnams grwar byas te /
NK093(ge)002:18625: mchod gnas su mi bkur bar lhag par yang snying
NK093(ge)002:18626: rje sgo khud pa'i zhing du dgongs te yul du
NK093(ge)002:18627: bya ste / 'jig rten pa bsod nams che chung
NK093(ge)002:18628: gis slong ba'i sa pa dag kyang de bzhin du
NK093(ge)002:18629: bya ste / blta'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:18633: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18634: sman rnam pa lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18636: rtsi tog lnga la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK093(ge)002:18637: snying po lnga la sogs pa bcud kyi rigs dang /
NK093(ge)002:18638: rin po che lnga la sogs pa'i mchoga tu gyur pa dag /zhib tu batagas sama /
NK093(ge)002:18639: phye mara byas te bsres nasa kyang /
NK093(ge)002:18640: chu chen po'i klung ngama snod kyi chu gang dag
NK093(ge)002:18641: gam mtsho chena po la sogs pa nyid du blugs
NK093(ge)002:18642: shing dora te / 'phags pa dang 'gro ba rnams
NK093(ge)002:18643: la tshul bzhin du byin gyis brlabs la chagsa pa
NK093(ge)002:18644: meda par mi dmigs pas zin pas dbul zhing sbyin
NK093(ge)002:18645: shing dora te / para bya ba'o // yang na
NK093(ge)002:18646: lnga po dag gi yul de rnams bsam pas de
NK093(ge)002:18647: ltar gzung la sbyin pa'i dngos po 'di rnams gtang
NK093(ge)002:18648: bar bshad de chu'i sgras mi bshad par 'grel pa
NK093(ge)002:18649: lung bstan las 'byung bar yang gsungs so //
NK093(ge)002:18654: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18655: theg pa chen po bas dge ba'i gnas ganga gi
NK093(ge)002:18656: mchod pa'i rten du dam bcas shing khasa blangsa te
NK093(ge)002:18657: / nye ring med pa'i nad pa gso ba dang
NK093(ge)002:18658: gang chos la slob sbyang byed pa'i bri klog gi
NK093(ge)002:18660: chos spyod kyi grwa bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18661: sgom pa'i grwa btsugsa te bsti gansa mchoga tu bya zhing bkur sti chen po byed pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18662: dusa dus su chos kyi 'khora lo'i grwa gzug pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18663: tshogs kyi mchod pa rgya chen po dang /
NK093(ge)002:18664: 'phags pa mchod par bya ba dang 'gro ba sems
NK093(ge)002:18665: can rnams la sbyin pa rgya chen po btang ba
NK093(ge)002:18671: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18672: gsung sgra rgya mtsho sgrogs pa ganga su zhig la
NK093(ge)002:18673: rgyal ba rnam 'dren dama pa'i lung gi brgyud pa
NK093(ge)002:18674: byung zhing thob pa yod pa des gsunga gi mchoda
NK093(ge)002:18675: rten glegs bam zab mo phyi nang kun bsdus nas
NK093(ge)002:18677: gzhan la brjod cing bshad pa dang bsnyen bkur dang
NK093(ge)002:18678: bsti gansa su bya zhing mchod rdzas sna tshogs kyis
NK093(ge)002:18679: mchod pa dang / de dag gi tshig don la mnyam bsam sgom pa bya ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18681: gzhan la zab don ston pa sogs rgya chera yangsa
NK093(ge)002:18682: pa'i dge ba'i lasa rnam par dkar ba rnams la
NK093(ge)002:18685: gsung sgra rgya mtsho sgrogs pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:18686: glegs bam zab mo kun bsten te /
NK093(ge)002:18687: brjod dang bsnyen bkur bsti gnas kyis //
NK093(ge)002:18688: rgya che yangs pa'i las rnams bya //
NK093(ge)002:18694: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18695: 'o na de la yon tan ci yod ce na /
NK093(ge)002:18696: de ltar glegs bam la brten nas gang de'i shes
NK093(ge)002:18697: rab mchog gi rgyud dama pa gong nas gong du
NK093(ge)002:18699: tshogs mchog ye shes kyi rgyu'o //
NK093(ge)002:18700: des na gsang rgyud 'di ltar ngesa te spyod pa
NK093(ge)002:18701: mi 'gyur ba'i rnal 'byor pa dama pa dag gis
NK093(ge)002:18703: glegs bam sna tshogs legs par sbyin nam /
NK093(ge)002:18704: 'dus shes bsgyur ba'i slob dpon gzhan la bsten nam /
NK093(ge)002:18705: rgyu yi chos kyi rim par drangs nasa khrid par byas na /
NK093(ge)002:18706: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa de yi yang dag
NK093(ge)002:18707: pa'i ye shesa nyid tshad meda par gsal zhing mngon
NK093(ge)002:18710: ye shes tshogs rnams rdzogs bya'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:18711: shes rab tshogs kyi sbyin mchog dag /bstan tam glegs bam la sogs pa'i //
NK093(ge)002:18712: blo mchog ldan pa rnams la sbyin //
NK093(ge)002:18718: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18719: ting nge 'dzin sngar gomas zin pa dang phyis su
NK093(ge)002:18720: gomas shing 'dris para byed pa yisa sgo nas kun
NK093(ge)002:18721: gzhi la yod pa'i sgrib pa'i phung po ganga de
NK093(ge)002:18722: rnams sbyangs shing daga para bya ba'i dgos ched kyi
NK093(ge)002:18723: phyir du bsam bsgom byed pa'i yul ting nge 'dzin
NK093(ge)002:18724: gyi sgo bye ba manga po la 'jug cing blo
NK093(ge)002:18725: mchog dang ldan pas de ltar ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:18726: nyid du ting nge 'dzin gyi yul sna tshogs kyi
NK093(ge)002:18727: don la yang nas yang du rtsal rnams sbyangsa te
NK093(ge)002:18728: grub par gyur pa de ltar kun tu goms par
NK093(ge)002:18729: byed de sgom chen gzhan yang 'degs par bya ste
NK093(ge)002:18731: bsgom dang goms par bya ba yis //
NK093(ge)002:18732: kun gzhi dag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:18733: ting 'dzin bye ba mang po la //
NK093(ge)002:18734: blo mchog yid kyi rtsal de sbyang //
NK093(ge)002:18740: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18741: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dama pa la sogs pa'i chos
NK093(ge)002:18742: kyi 'khora lo chen po raba tu bskor ba'i yon
NK093(ge)002:18743: bdag byas te / bdag gzhan gyi shes rgyud sbyang
NK093(ge)002:18744: ba dang lhag mthong zab mo'i ye shes skyed de
NK093(ge)002:18745: gzhi don rtogs pa'i shes raba mchog tu gsang ba
NK093(ge)002:18746: la yang dag par blta bar bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18751: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18752: sho gamas gcan chen gyi 'phrang dang lam srang ngan pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18753: sho gamsa kyi lam du 'tshe bas mi bde ba'i
NK093(ge)002:18754: gnoda pa de kun basla te tshad med pa'i snying
NK093(ge)002:18755: rje'i 'khora lo chen po bskor te spyod pa rgyun
NK093(ge)002:18757: rdzas dang lus dang skyabs dang chos kyi sbyin pa'i 'khora lo bzhi ste /
NK093(ge)002:18758: de la dang po'ang bu dang bu mo dang yul dang rgyal srid man chad do //
NK093(ge)002:18759: gnyis pa sha dang khrag dang mgo dang rkang lag go //
NK093(ge)002:18760: gsum pa gnod pa'i rgyud las skyob pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18761: srog gi bar chad las skyob pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:18762: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa las skyob pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18763: bzhi pa chos bstan pa dang glegs bam dang mkhan por lung bstan pa ste /
NK093(ge)002:18764: de dag rgyun mi gacada pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:18769: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18771: me'am de bzhina du rlung ste 'byung ba lnga po
NK093(ge)002:18772: rnams la sku gdunga dang mchod rten gyi sats+tsha mang
NK093(ge)002:18773: po btab ste spel ba la yun ring por mchoda
NK093(ge)002:18775: ringa bsrel dang ldan pa'i sku mang po rnams byas
NK093(ge)002:18776: shing btabs na lus ngag gis brtsam pa'i thun mong
NK093(ge)002:18777: gi dge ba'i lasa chena po yin pas de ltar
NK093(ge)002:18778: rgyun gyi 'khora lora bya zhing de dag la ye
NK093(ge)002:18779: shes pa spyan drangs te bstim zhing mchod pa dang
NK093(ge)002:18780: bstod pa sogs par mi bcad par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18785: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18786: mtshamsa med pa lnga'i sdig pa'i las kyis rnam par
NK093(ge)002:18787: smin pas mi gos par zlog para byed pa yi
NK093(ge)002:18788: thabs su rang gi lus ngag dang semas rgyud la
NK093(ge)002:18789: zhen 'dzin rdul du rlagsa par bya zhing /
NK093(ge)002:18790: 'di nyid brtson 'grus kyi don yang yin te /
NK093(ge)002:18791: de bas rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i 'aphagas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18792: sprin tshogsa mang po pho brang du yid kyis spyan
NK093(ge)002:18793: drangs la / bdag gi lus kyang rdul snyed du sprul te /
NK093(ge)002:18794: de dag re re'i spyan sngar gus pa chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:18795: tshul gyis 'dug pas lus ngag dang ba dang bcas
NK093(ge)002:18796: te dngos sam yid kyis mchoda pa phul la /
NK093(ge)002:18797: las ngan pa yang ba spyod pa la 'gyod pa
NK093(ge)002:18798: drag po dang bcas pa'i semas kyis yang yang bashagas
NK093(ge)002:18799: par bya'o // yan lag bdun pa bya bar lung bstan gyis bshad do //
NK093(ge)002:18805: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18806: rgyal ba kun mnyes shing dgyes pa bskyed pa'i phrin
NK093(ge)002:18807: lasa rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas thabs khyad pa can
NK093(ge)002:18808: gyi bud shing bsregsa pa'i sbyin sreg byas pa na
NK093(ge)002:18809: / zhi bas nyon sgrib sbyang zhing rgyas pas shes sgrib sbyang la /
NK093(ge)002:18810: dbang gis lta sgrib sbyang ste /
NK093(ge)002:18811: drag pos las sgrib sbyang ba yin pas /
NK093(ge)002:18812: gsang ba sngags kyi thabsa chen po mchog gis 'bras
NK093(ge)002:18813: bu la sbyor ba'i spyi'i lam chena po nyid lasa
NK093(ge)002:18814: / dad pa rlabs po che'i me dang /
NK093(ge)002:18817: shes rab kyi me ste rnam pa bzhi dang ldan
NK093(ge)002:18818: pas me yi lasa mchoga zhi rgyas dbang drag gam
NK093(ge)002:18819: kun 'dus lhun gyis grub par bya ba desa ni
NK093(ge)002:18820: matshamas med pa lnga'i dbang du mi 'gyur bar bzlog
NK093(ge)002:18821: par byed pa yang yina no //
NK093(ge)002:18826: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18827: thugs rje chen po'am snying rje 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur
NK093(ge)002:18828: pas gsang sngags phyi nang gi dkyil 'khora chen po
NK093(ge)002:18829: de dag rnams rgyud ganga dang gang las 'byung ba
NK093(ge)002:18830: ltar rang gang la goms pa yod pa ltar bzhengs
NK093(ge)002:18831: su gsol te 'bad rtsol gyis mchod pa nana tan
NK093(ge)002:18834: thugs rje 'byung ba'i 'khor lo dag /gang ltar goms ltar 'bad rtsol bya //
NK093(ge)002:18835: bstan pa skyong ba'i tshogs rnams la //
NK093(ge)002:18836: sbyin mchod spel ba'i las rnams bya //
NK093(ge)002:18837: zhes gsungs pa sogs 'di dag gsal bar bstan no //
NK093(ge)002:18842: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18843: mdor na de ltar dge ba'i las rnam grangs so
NK093(ge)002:18844: sor bshad na bcu bdun du 'gyur ba la sogas
NK093(ge)002:18845: pa gtor ma cha gsum dang tha na kham gcig
NK093(ge)002:18846: tsam sbyin pa yan chad kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK093(ge)002:18847: sna tshogs pa dag /snga ma las /
NK093(ge)002:18848: bdag dang gzhan dang gnyi ga dang //
NK093(ge)002:18849: chos kyi don du mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK093(ge)002:18850: skyon bzhi po dag spangs nas ni //
NK093(ge)002:18851: de las bzlog pa'i tshul ldan pas //
NK093(ge)002:18852: rnal 'byor snying dang mig lta bur //
NK093(ge)002:18853: gdung ba'i 'du shes nyer bzhag ste //
NK093(ge)002:18854: ci bzhin 'dod pa nye bar sbyar //
NK093(ge)002:18856: bdag dang gzhan dang gnyis ka dang chos kyi dona
NK093(ge)002:18857: du mi 'gyur ba dang bzhi po kun spangsa shing
NK093(ge)002:18858: bsal te nana tan dang ldan pas bsod nams rgya
NK093(ge)002:18859: mtsho lta bu'i dge ba'i tshogsa kyis dpunga chena po
NK093(ge)002:18860: bskyed par bya ba nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:18865: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18866: de dag gi dgos pa ci zhig snyam pa la /
NK093(ge)002:18867: 'di ltar gzhung 'dir bshad pa bzhin du dge ba'i
NK093(ge)002:18868: lasa kyi stangsa ma bsod nams kyi tshogs rgya chen
NK093(ge)002:18869: po la sogas pa gsogs pa'ang dgos pa gazhana zhig
NK093(ge)002:18870: gi ched du spyod pa ma yina te /
NK093(ge)002:18871: tshe 'di dang khe grags lta bu'i dbang du ma
NK093(ge)002:18872: song bar bsam gtan la sems mnyam pa rtse gciga
NK093(ge)002:18873: tu gnas shing blo mi dmigs pa'i dona dang ldana
NK093(ge)002:18874: pa'i bsam pas yul gnyis su med par yid la
NK093(ge)002:18875: bya ba'i rnal 'byor pa yid gnyis med pa rnams
NK093(ge)002:18876: kyis bsgrub pa'i sngon du bya ba'i las dang bsam
NK093(ge)002:18877: pa la mi gnod pa tsam du bya ba'ang rang
NK093(ge)002:18878: gi shes pa'i rgyud sbyong ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:18879: bdag gzhan gyi dona dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:18880: spyod pa yin pas yon tan 'char bar nges pa
NK093(ge)002:18881: dang / brgya la gala te sgo gsum gyi nus
NK093(ge)002:18882: pa chung zhing shes rab kyi rtsal zhana pas de
NK093(ge)002:18883: dag ma lus pa rnams mi dmigs pa dang ldana
NK093(ge)002:18884: par ma grub na yang sngar dang tshe rabs kyi
NK093(ge)002:18885: dge ba ci spyad cing basgas pa'i stangsa chen yod
NK093(ge)002:18886: do cog kun bsdongas shing bsdoms te don bgrang zhing
NK093(ge)002:18892: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18893: de ltar ganga gi skabs 'dira yang 'gro ba sems can thams cad snying rje'i yul du gzung ste /
NK093(ge)002:18894: tshe rabs kyi dge sdig ci spyad pa dang tshe
NK093(ge)002:18895: 'dir yang sngar ji ltar basgas pa'i dona rnams bgrangsa
NK093(ge)002:18896: shing bsdoms la / dge ba ni mtshams med zlog
NK093(ge)002:18897: par byed pa'i skabs su bshad pa lta bur bsam
NK093(ge)002:18898: la byang chub chen por bsngo'o //
NK093(ge)002:18899: sdig pa rnams ni lus ngag yid kyis gdunga ba'i
NK093(ge)002:18900: shugs chen po phyung zhing mchi ma blags te 'gyod
NK093(ge)002:18901: sems kyis rtsal drag pos bshags par bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18902: de ltar sgo gsum rtsal sprugsa kyis shugs byung nas
NK093(ge)002:18903: nyi ma re re bzhin byas na sgrib pa dag
NK093(ge)002:18905: dper na nyi ma shar ba'i gzugs brnyan chu klung dwangs par gsal ba'am /
NK093(ge)002:18906: de'i nang du zla ba'i gzugs brnyan snang la rang
NK093(ge)002:18907: bzhin med par 'char ba ltar du ye shes rang
NK093(ge)002:18908: gsal gyi dngos grub ranga bzhina shugsa kyis rang dbang
NK093(ge)002:18909: med par 'byung ba yin pas de ltar legs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:18910: las lam la 'bad para byed pa shin tu gcesa
NK093(ge)002:18911: so // gtan tshigs de yi phyir na dge ba
NK093(ge)002:18912: chung ngu phra mo yana chad kyang rang gzhan gyi
NK093(ge)002:18913: rgyud la byang chub dama pa rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi
NK093(ge)002:18914: 'bras bu 'grub pa'i dona du 'gyur ba'i gzhir nges
NK093(ge)002:18915: para dpyod de legs par brtson par bya ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:18917: khams gsum snying rje'i gnas rnams la //
NK093(ge)002:18918: yo byad sbyin tshogs chen po las //
NK093(ge)002:18919: 'dod pa'i bsam pa rangs byas na //
NK093(ge)002:18920: mgu bas skongs pa'i stongs su 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:18921: zhes sogs skong ba'i thabs kyi stongs yang rgya cher 'byung ngo //
NK093(ge)002:18922: 'o na gcig char 'jug pa'i blo mchog gis kyang
NK093(ge)002:18923: thams cad du de ltar spyad cing de la rag
NK093(ge)002:18925: theg chen gsang ba mchog gi sgo ganga 'dira shes
NK093(ge)002:18926: pas zina pa dang ma zina pa'i dngosa po brtan
NK093(ge)002:18927: pa snod dang g.yo ba bcud thams cad ril dang
NK093(ge)002:18928: / la sogas pa zhes bsdu ba'i don gyis mya
NK093(ge)002:18929: ngan las 'das pa'i chos rnams dang bcas pa ma
NK093(ge)002:18930: lus pa kun chos dbyings de bzhina nyid du gnyisa
NK093(ge)002:18931: su med par rtogs pa'i ye shes chen po la
NK093(ge)002:18932: 'khor ba sangs rgyas kyi sar bkod zin pas don
NK093(ge)002:18933: byar med pa'i don la de nyid du'ang 'dzin pa
NK093(ge)002:18934: med par blo bazhaga ste sgom na snying rje chena
NK093(ge)002:18935: po bla na med pas 'gro don ma byas rdzogs
NK093(ge)002:18936: pa'i phyir yul gnyis ka la zhugs zin pas gnyis
NK093(ge)002:18937: su med pa'i de kho na nyid yin te /
NK093(ge)002:18938: de bas na skyes bu mchog gi las la spang blang med do //
NK093(ge)002:18943: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:18945: lang ka'i badga po zhes bos nas /
NK093(ge)002:18946: bshad pa de ltar na dgongs pa dang don bya
NK093(ge)002:18947: ba'i yul ganga gzhan na meda pa'i don de'i tshul
NK093(ge)002:18948: gyis ni spyod yul gyi dngos po gang yang snang
NK093(ge)002:18949: la 'dzin pa med pas bdag las gzhan du snang
NK093(ge)002:18950: ste yul dang yul can gyi dngos por 'jug pa
NK093(ge)002:18951: med par rtogs pa'i lung chen po tha dad du
NK093(ge)002:18952: 'jug tu med pa'i ngo bo nyid lasa mi g.yo
NK093(ge)002:18953: bar de ltar ganga gis yang dag par shes te
NK093(ge)002:18955: chos nyid dang snying rje chen po'i yul la 'jug
NK093(ge)002:18956: pa rnams kyi nang nas mchog dama pa phul du
NK093(ge)002:18957: byung ba ste / dgongs spyod gnyis ka lhun gyis
NK093(ge)002:18958: grub pas rtsol med bde ba chen po kho na'o
NK093(ge)002:18959: byung ba ste / // de skad ces bka' stsal
NK093(ge)002:18960: te tshig smras pas 'khor langa ka'i badga po la
NK093(ge)002:18961: sogas pa damna pa'i lus kyi semas dapa'a rnams kyis
NK093(ge)002:18962: ganga gi rgyun du yula la 'juga pa'i don de'i
NK093(ge)002:18963: the tshom chod de ngesa pa dama pa rnyed para
NK093(ge)002:18965: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK093(ge)002:18966: lam gyi sngon du 'gro ba'i dgongs pa dang snying
NK093(ge)002:18967: rje'i yul dama pa la 'jug pa bstan pa'i le'u
NK093(ge)002:18968: zhes bya ste drug cu rtsa gnyis pa nyid legs
NK093(ge)002:18969: par 'grel pa'o ////brgyad pa me long brtag par bya
NK093(ge)002:18978: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te //
NK093(ge)002:18979: le'u 'dis nges don ston te don dang yi ge'i rnal 'byor gnyi ga'i lta ba gcig yin /
NK093(ge)002:18980: de'ang yi ge'i rnal 'byor gyi shas che'o //
NK093(ge)002:18981: yul la 'jug pa bshad ma thag pa de nasa
NK093(ge)002:18982: yanga 'khor langa ka'i badga po la sogas pa damna
NK093(ge)002:18983: pa'i lus kyi semas dapa'a de daga gisa /
NK093(ge)002:18984: ston pa gasnga ba pa'i badga po la /
NK093(ge)002:18985: le'u zhe lnga par chos kyi rnam grangs bcur bkod
NK093(ge)002:18986: pa'i brgyad pa gsang sngags kyi gzhi bcu dpes mtshona
NK093(ge)002:18987: pa'i don rnams kyi dri ba yongas su drisa pa
NK093(ge)002:18988: / kye gasnga ba pa'i badga po /
NK093(ge)002:18989: nyid kyis sngar gong du me longa brtag para bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:18990: zhes dama baca'a bar dgongas pa de nyid ji ltar yongas su brtag para bgyi /
NK093(ge)002:18991: de skad ces dris pa las /
NK093(ge)002:18992: ston pa gasnga ba pa'i badga posa lan smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK093(ge)002:18993: kye grogsa po daga /ces 'khor la bos nas don
NK093(ge)002:18994: gyi dngos po ganga yang rung ba la de dang
NK093(ge)002:18995: mthun par ganga gisa nye bar mtshona pasa /
NK093(ge)002:18996: bcu ka de kho na nyid du shesa para 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:18997: ba'i mtshon pa dpe'i me longa ni don dang bcas
NK093(ge)002:18998: te rnam grangs bcu phrag gnyis kyis 'di ltara bstan
NK093(ge)002:19002: gsang sngags kyi ming brtagsa pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:19004: spyod pa mi chagas pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:19005: bzlas brjod nus pa 'byung ba dang /
NK093(ge)002:19006: lta ba snang ba med pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:19010: dngos grub don dang mthuna pa rnam pa bcu'o //
NK093(ge)002:19021: gzugs brnyana lta bur mtshon pas me long bcu ste /
NK093(ge)002:19022: bshad pa'i don rnams dang mthun pa'i dpe'i dmigas bcu
NK093(ge)002:19023: yis dpe ris don de rim par mtshona nas rnam
NK093(ge)002:19026: zab mor spyod pa la mos pas //
NK093(ge)002:19027: gang zhig don la 'dris pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:19028: gsang sngags spyod pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK093(ge)002:19029: mthun pa'i dmigs bcu dper bzhag ste //
NK093(ge)002:19030: rnal 'byor can gyis shes par bya //
NK093(ge)002:19031: sgyu ma smig rgyu rmi lam dang //
NK093(ge)002:19032: gzugs brnyan dri za'i grong khyer dang /
NK093(ge)002:19033: brag cha chu zla mig yor dang //
NK093(ge)002:19034: chu bur 'khrul dang mgal mer snang //
NK093(ge)002:19035: sgrub dang gsang sngags spyod pa dang //
NK093(ge)002:19036: grub pa dang ni gnas dag dang //
NK093(ge)002:19037: bzlas pa'i sgra dang phyag rgyar rtog /ting 'dzin lta
NK093(ge)002:19038: ba cho 'phrul brtag /ces gsungs te dpe rnams de
NK093(ge)002:19039: ltar yang shes pas don la nges pa lhag par
NK093(ge)002:19041: de'ang byang chub sems kyi ngo bo nyid mtshan nyid
NK093(ge)002:19042: thams cad dang bral bas dngosa po meda kyang mi
NK093(ge)002:19043: mthun pa gsang sngags kyi dngosa po bcur snang bas
NK093(ge)002:19044: na dngos med kyi ngo bos dngosa pora snang du
NK093(ge)002:19045: btuba pa'i tshul mtshon pa dpe yis ston pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:19047: dpe don sbyar te so sor bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19048: dpes mtshon pa'i don gyi mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK093(ge)002:19050: gsang sngags kyi sgrub pa sgyu ma lta bur snang bar bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19051: ming smig rgyu lta bur btags par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:19052: phyag rgya chu zla lta bur 'byung bar bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19053: spyod pa rmi lam lta bur ma chags par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:19054: bzlas pa sgra brnyan lta bur 'byung zhing grub par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19055: lta ba mig yor lta bur snang yang med par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:19056: ting nge 'dzin chu'i chu lbur lta bur dag par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19057: gnas dri za'i grong khyer lta bur nges pa med par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:19058: cho 'phrul sprul pa lta bur cir yang 'byung bar bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19059: dngos grub gzugs brnyan lta bur skabs dang mthun par bshad pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:19064: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19065: de dag so so nas bstan pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:19066: dpe ji ltar na rgyu rkyen las snang ba'i sgyu ma'i ranga bzhina yang ni /
NK093(ge)002:19067: skyes bu sgyu ma mkhan gang gi lag pas rtsol ba byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK093(ge)002:19068: rde'u shing sogs kyi sman dang she'u re'u i na
NK093(ge)002:19069: ya a mo ka a 'gus sa 'gus sogs kyi
NK093(ge)002:19070: sngagas dang rdzas kyi sbyor ba 'dzom pa las 'gro
NK093(ge)002:19071: ba bzang mo la sogs par snang bas ltad mo
NK093(ge)002:19072: ba'i mig gi dabnga po dang yid 'phrog cing dga'
NK093(ge)002:19073: bar byed pa'i dngos po gang cir snang yang /
NK093(ge)002:19074: rgyu rkyen las snang ba'i sgyu ma'i dngos po de
NK093(ge)002:19075: dag la'ang 'gro 'onga gi ngo bo'i dngosa po med
NK093(ge)002:19076: pa ltar du / dpes mtshon pa'i don ni /
NK093(ge)002:19077: 'di ltar tshul de bzhin du gasnga sngags mchog gi sgrub pa'i ranga bzhina yanga /
NK093(ge)002:19078: ngo bo ci yang med pa'i rgyu yi dang las
NK093(ge)002:19079: dngos grub 'byung ba'i tshul yig 'bru dang cho ga
NK093(ge)002:19080: dang rdzas kyi sbyor ba lasa su rung ba las
NK093(ge)002:19081: sngags kyi dngos grub sna tshogs 'du ba ste ji
NK093(ge)002:19082: ltar snang zhing 'byung na yang de'i ngo bo 'di
NK093(ge)002:19083: 'drar grub pa'i ranga bzhina bstan du med do //
NK093(ge)002:19085: ji ltar sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK093(ge)002:19086: skyes bu dag gi rtsol ba dang //
NK093(ge)002:19087: sman dang sngags kyi sbyor ba las //
NK093(ge)002:19088: dbang po yid 'phrog cir snang yang //
NK093(ge)002:19090: de ltar sgrub pa'i mtshan nyid kyang //
NK093(ge)002:19091: yig 'bru rdzas kyi sbyor ba las //
NK093(ge)002:19092: grub par snang yang rang bzhin med //
NK093(ge)002:19098: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19099: dper na gang 'dira smig rgyu'i ranga bzhina ni /
NK093(ge)002:19100: dpyid drod g.yo ba'i dus nas tsha sgo can du
NK093(ge)002:19101: nyi ma phyed la nye bar rlung gzhol phyogs su
NK093(ge)002:19102: bab pa'i tshe lta ba po rgyang na gnas pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19103: rkyen dang bzhi ldan pas chur snang ste /
NK093(ge)002:19104: nam zla dus bzhi'i 'jig chags bzhi las dgun gyi
NK093(ge)002:19105: grang reg 'jiga cing drod 'byung ba g.yo ba'i dpyid
NK093(ge)002:19106: zla tha chung gi dus dag la bab nas drod
NK093(ge)002:19107: dang nyi ma 'dzom pa sogs kyis rkyen de dag
NK093(ge)002:19108: ldan pa de yi rang bzhina las smig rgyu ba
NK093(ge)002:19109: na byis pa skom gyis gdunga ba'i chur bzung ste
NK093(ge)002:19110: skom sel ba'i 'du shes kyis chu yi 'du shes
NK093(ge)002:19111: skyed cing bsam pa nyer zhes nye bar bazhaga nas
NK093(ge)002:19112: bdag kyang de la chu med pas ngoms shing sim
NK093(ge)002:19113: pa'am tshima pa'i rgyu dera ga la 'gyur te mi
NK093(ge)002:19114: 'gyur ro // dpe de bzhina du gsang sngags theg
NK093(ge)002:19115: pa chen po de yi ming gi ngo bo'i khyad
NK093(ge)002:19116: para yanga chos kun mtshan nyid gdod ma nas rnam
NK093(ge)002:19117: pa kun ldan gyi ranga bzhina stong pa chen po
NK093(ge)002:19118: mi dmigs pa'i ngang la tha snyad mtshon pas matshana
NK093(ge)002:19119: ma'i minga du btagsa pa yin kyang ming sna tshogs
NK093(ge)002:19120: pa de nyid stong pa nyid pas de yi rang
NK093(ge)002:19121: bzhin mi dmigas te ngo bo 'di 'drar med pa
NK093(ge)002:19123: ji ltar smig rgyu'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK093(ge)002:19124: zhing pa'i dus kyi zla ba la //
NK093(ge)002:19125: drod dang nyi ma'i sbyor ba las //
NK093(ge)002:19126: byis pa gdungs pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK093(ge)002:19127: chu yi 'du shes ci bskyed cing //
NK093(ge)002:19128: tshim pa'i rgyur ni ga la 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:19129: gsang sngags ming gi khyad par yang //
NK093(ge)002:19130: rang bzhin mi dmigs stong pa las //
NK093(ge)002:19131: mtshan ma'i tha snyad ming du btags //
NK093(ge)002:19132: de nyid stong pas ming mi dmigs //
NK093(ge)002:19138: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19139: dper na skabs gang 'di chu yi zla ba ni
NK093(ge)002:19140: sprin la sogs pa'i sgrib pa med par dwangs pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19141: nam mkha'a la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor shara ba na
NK093(ge)002:19142: / de'i gzugsa brnyan rnyog pa dwangsa pa'i chu yi
NK093(ge)002:19143: nang du gsal bar snang yang de la zla bar
NK093(ge)002:19144: brtagsa pa'i dngosa po'i ngo bo gang cir yang grub
NK093(ge)002:19145: / pa med do // dpe de bzhina du don
NK093(ge)002:19146: gyi rang bzhin gsang sngags kyi lha'i sku dang phyag
NK093(ge)002:19147: rgya gang yang ched du bkoda pa med para lhar
NK093(ge)002:19148: snang de nyid chos nyid rig pa'i nam mkha'a lasa
NK093(ge)002:19149: snang srid ganga snang thams cad sku dang zhing gi
NK093(ge)002:19150: phyag rgya sna tshogs su gasla bar gdal ba nyid
NK093(ge)002:19151: du phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gang gi rig
NK093(ge)002:19152: pa'i ngo 'dira rang snang ba de nyid de ltar
NK093(ge)002:19153: gsal yang dag pa lhar snang de yi ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:19154: nyid ye gdod nas dngosa po'i rang bzhin du grub
NK093(ge)002:19155: pa meda pas yod med du 'dzina cing rtog pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19156: mtha' dang bral ba nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:19158: ji ltar chu yi zla ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:19159: sgrib med mkha' las zla shar ba //
NK093(ge)002:19160: gzugs brnyan dwangs pa'i chu nang snang //
NK093(ge)002:19161: snang yang gzung ba'i rtog pa med //
NK093(ge)002:19162: de bzhin gzugs snang phyag rgya yang //
NK093(ge)002:19163: sems kyi mkha' las skur gsal ba //
NK093(ge)002:19164: phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin ngo la snang //
NK093(ge)002:19165: de ltar snang yang 'dzin rtog bral //
NK093(ge)002:19171: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19172: dpe ji ltar na rmi lam dag gi ranga bzhina ni /
NK093(ge)002:19173: skyes bu gang zhig gnyida kyis nona pa de'i rmi lam na /
NK093(ge)002:19174: skad cig thang cig yud tsam dang lo dang zla
NK093(ge)002:19175: ba la sogas pa yun ring thung ji snyed pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19176: bar bar du bde sdug gi rnam pa sna tshogas
NK093(ge)002:19177: ji snyed cig myong bar snang na yang gnyid de
NK093(ge)002:19178: nyid sangsa pa'i dus na de gnyis ka ci yanga
NK093(ge)002:19180: don gsang sngags kyi spyod pa yang stong pa nyid chen po ci yang med pa yi ngang la /
NK093(ge)002:19181: spyod pa'i khyad par legs nyes ji ltar spyad kyang /
NK093(ge)002:19182: spyod bzhin pa la yang ma chagsa pa'i shes rab
NK093(ge)002:19183: ji bzhina pa'i ngang las ma g.yos shing zhen pa
NK093(ge)002:19184: dag pasa ma rig pa'i gnyid sad pa dag gis
NK093(ge)002:19185: brtagsa na spyod pa'i ngo bo nyid la dmigas pa
NK093(ge)002:19186: kun dang bral ba nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:19188: dper na rmi lam rang bzhin ni //
NK093(ge)002:19189: skyes bu gnyid kyi dbang gyur na //
NK093(ge)002:19190: thang cig skad cig yud tsam dang //
NK093(ge)002:19191: lo la sogs pa de bzhin du //
NK093(ge)002:19192: bde dang sdug bsngal de bzhin myong //
NK093(ge)002:19193: sangs nas ci yang mi dmigs ltar //
NK093(ge)002:19194: de bzhin sngags kyi spyod pa dag /stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin la //
NK093(ge)002:19195: spyod pa'i rnam pa cir snang yang //
NK093(ge)002:19196: brtags na dmigs pa kun dang bral //
NK093(ge)002:19202: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19203: dper na brag cha'am sgra brnyan 'byung ba'i ranga bzhina ni /
NK093(ge)002:19204: brag gang gi gansa kyi ngos la mi'i sgras rkyen
NK093(ge)002:19205: dang 'phrad pasa ji skad smras pa de kho na
NK093(ge)002:19206: bzhina grags te de ltar sgra brnyan 'byung ba yin
NK093(ge)002:19207: yang / de nyid kyi ngo bo ci yang meda
NK093(ge)002:19208: pa las 'byung pa yina pas rang bzhin dmigs pa
NK093(ge)002:19209: yang / med pa ltar / brag gi ngos dang
NK093(ge)002:19210: mi'i sgra lta bu'i gasnga sngagas gasnga ba'i byin rlabsa
NK093(ge)002:19211: kyi rnam par 'phrul pa dag gdul bya gang gi
NK093(ge)002:19212: dngos grub kyi ched du gsang sngags kyi bzlas brjod
NK093(ge)002:19213: kyi sgra rnams kyis legs par bsgrub na rang bzhin
NK093(ge)002:19214: meda pa'i dbyings la bzlas pa'i sgra'i tshig gi nus
NK093(ge)002:19215: pa mthu can du 'byung ba nyid kyang sgra brnyan
NK093(ge)002:19216: grags pa lta bu'i sgo gsum gyi chos nyid ci
NK093(ge)002:19217: yanga meda cing mtha' snang gang yang ma yin pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19218: ngang lasa bzlas pa'i sgra'i nus pa'i byin rlabs ci
NK093(ge)002:19220: de nyid ci yang med 'byung lta bu'i gzhi'i gnas
NK093(ge)002:19221: lugs mtshan nyid med pa'i rgyu las ji ltar bsams
NK093(ge)002:19222: shing btagsa pa ltar chagas te gang du bltas para
NK093(ge)002:19223: de ltar sgra sna tshogs su snang yang ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:19224: nyid du bstan du med pa nyid de /
NK093(ge)002:19226: brag cha grags pa'i mtshan ma ni //
NK093(ge)002:19227: dper na ngos la sgras rkyen pas //
NK093(ge)002:19228: ci bzhin sgra ltar brag cha 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:19229: byung yang sgrar thos dmigs pa med //
NK093(ge)002:19230: de bzhin sngags tshig bzlas pa'i sgra //
NK093(ge)002:19231: dper na med las yod brtags pa'i //
NK093(ge)002:19232: mtshan ma la brten stong pa'i sgra //
NK093(ge)002:19233: brjod pa tsam du bstan par zad //
NK093(ge)002:19239: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19240: dper na gang 'dira mig yora gyi ranga bzhina ni gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:19241: mig nada can dang rab rib kyis khyer ba sogs
NK093(ge)002:19242: la dung gi ser snang sogs med pa'i rdzas su
NK093(ge)002:19244: 'khrul rgyu yul la yod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:19245: dbang po la yod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:19246: phyi rol gyi rten la yod pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:19247: nang na yod pa'i rgyu bzhis mthong ste 'khrul pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19248: ngo la snang bar gyur pa'i ngo bo tsam du
NK093(ge)002:19249: zad de / de nyid ji ltar snang ba na
NK093(ge)002:19250: yang dbang po mngon sum yi tshad ma ma yin
NK093(ge)002:19251: pas mi yor la ngo bo gang yang meda pa'o
NK093(ge)002:19252: zad de / // de bzhin du gsang sngags kyi
NK093(ge)002:19253: lta ba yang ngan rtog gi mtha' rnams kyi spros
NK093(ge)002:19255: bzang rtog gi yul dbyings dang ye shes la sogs
NK093(ge)002:19256: pa'i tha snyad kyi spros pa tsam yang bral ba
NK093(ge)002:19257: yi / ranga bzhina stong pa nyid kyi ngang lasa
NK093(ge)002:19258: chos so cog ji ltar bltas pa ltar cho 'phrul
NK093(ge)002:19259: gyi rnama pa mtshan nyid cir yang ma nges par
NK093(ge)002:19260: sna tshogs su snang ba yang rang rig pa'i cho
NK093(ge)002:19261: 'phrul nyid du rol pa cir yang snang ba tsam
NK093(ge)002:19262: du nges para zad pas snang ba de dag ganga
NK093(ge)002:19263: la yanga ngo bo meda par mtshan nyid brjod pa
NK093(ge)002:19266: 'khrul pa snang ba'i rang bzhin ni //
NK093(ge)002:19267: spros bral dngos po stong pa las //
NK093(ge)002:19268: srog dang shed can byed pa po //
NK093(ge)002:19269: sems can pa la sogs par snang //
NK093(ge)002:19270: mig nad ngo la rdzas ltar snang //
NK093(ge)002:19271: 'khrul pa kho na snang bar zad //
NK093(ge)002:19272: de bzhin sngags kyi lta ba yang //
NK093(ge)002:19274: snang ba med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK093(ge)002:19275: 'khrul pa sna tshogs snang bar zad //
NK093(ge)002:19276: rnal 'byor can gyis de ltar blta //
NK093(ge)002:19282: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19283: ting nge 'dzin gyi dpe don la'ang gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:19284: dper na chu dwangs pa dang nam mkha'a dwangsa pa
NK093(ge)002:19285: lasa chu lbur dang sprin tshogas mang po tha dad
NK093(ge)002:19286: par 'byung ba yang chu dang nam mkha' nyid las
NK093(ge)002:19287: ranga byung zhing slar yang de nyid du rang sar
NK093(ge)002:19288: zhi'i zhes zhi ba'i ranga bzhina yin pasa chu nyid
NK093(ge)002:19289: dang nam mkha'a nyid ma dmigs pa bzhina du rnam
NK093(ge)002:19291: dpe de ltar gsang sngags theg pa chen po snang
NK093(ge)002:19292: ba mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang
NK093(ge)002:19293: / mi snang ba mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge
NK093(ge)002:19294: 'dzin sogs ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag ji
NK093(ge)002:19295: snyed pa yi mtshan ma thams cad dang mtshan ma
NK093(ge)002:19296: med pa thamsa cad kun rang rig pa byang chub
NK093(ge)002:19297: kyi sems de nyid yin pas rig pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK093(ge)002:19298: 'od gsal ba de kho na nyid las ranga byung
NK093(ge)002:19299: zhing shar nas de nyid kyi ngang du ranga sar
NK093(ge)002:19300: zhi ste dbyer med pa yin pas mdo sems kyi
NK093(ge)002:19301: chos nyid ji bzhina pa nyid rnam para dag pa
NK093(ge)002:19302: nyid du ngesa pa kho na'o //
NK093(ge)002:19303: de skad du'ang de nyid las /
NK093(ge)002:19304: ji ltar char gyi rgyun bzhin du //
NK093(ge)002:19305: chu las chu lbur rnam par 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:19306: de yang gcig gi rnam pa las //
NK093(ge)002:19307: mang po'i rnam grangs du ma 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:19308: sdud cing phyir yang dum bur 'chad //
NK093(ge)002:19309: de bzhin rnal 'byor sgrub pa yi //
NK093(ge)002:19316: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19317: dper na dri za'i grong khyer gyi gansa la ngesa pa med pa yin pasa khyad par gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:19318: dri za de yi gzugsa ni nam mkha'i gnas kyi
NK093(ge)002:19319: gara byung bar grong khyer de yang de kho na
NK093(ge)002:19321: de ltar byung ba nyid na yang dera ma nges
NK093(ge)002:19322: pa yin pas de kho nar mi rtag pas brtan
NK093(ge)002:19324: gsang sngags kyi gzhal yas khang ni chos nyid ji
NK093(ge)002:19325: bzhina pa yi de kho na nyid ji lta ba
NK093(ge)002:19326: de bzhina nyid du blo gansa pasa rang rig pa
NK093(ge)002:19327: nam mkha'i ngang la gansa pa dang ldan bzhin du
NK093(ge)002:19328: lha'i sku phyag rgyar sgom ste gar gansa te gsal
NK093(ge)002:19329: bar 'byung ba der rang snang de nyid gazhala med
NK093(ge)002:19330: khang chen por rig pa'i byin rlabs las shar bar
NK093(ge)002:19331: snang ste / gnas su 'byung ba'i snang ba de
NK093(ge)002:19332: ltar ther zug pa'i gansa rtag pa can ma yina
NK093(ge)002:19333: par sems kyi de kho na nyid rang snang ba
NK093(ge)002:19334: snang ste / nyid de / snga ma las /
NK093(ge)002:19335: dri za gnas pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK093(ge)002:19336: mkha' 'am stong pa'i ngos dag la //
NK093(ge)002:19337: dri za'i gzugs ni gar byung yang //
NK093(ge)002:19338: grong khyer de yang de nas 'byung //
NK093(ge)002:19339: byung nas de yang mi rtag ltar //
NK093(ge)002:19340: gsang sngags grub pa'i gnas dag kyang //
NK093(ge)002:19341: chos sam yid kyi mkha' ngos la //
NK093(ge)002:19342: rnal 'byor gsang bdag gar bskyed par //
NK093(ge)002:19343: de nyid gnas pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK093(ge)002:19344: byung yang de la gnas mi 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:19350: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19351: dpe ji ltar na mgal me'i sprul pa'i ranga bzhina ni gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:19352: dngos po med bzhin du 'khor lo la sogs pa
NK093(ge)002:19353: sna tshogs su 'byung ste mgal me gciga gi rnam
NK093(ge)002:19354: pa lasa kyang dbyibs so sor du mara mang po
NK093(ge)002:19355: 'byung bas / gang dag me nyid bskor te bsgyur
NK093(ge)002:19356: na mgal me'i 'khora lo'i rgyun dang thog ris la
NK093(ge)002:19358: snang ba'i 'byung rgyun bar chada pa ma yin no //
NK093(ge)002:19359: de bzhin du don sngags kyi cho 'phrul yang mi mnyam pa 'khor ba'am sems can dang /
NK093(ge)002:19360: mnyam pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'am sangs rgyas gnyis
NK093(ge)002:19361: kyi ranga bzhina chos nyid gnyis su med pas blang
NK093(ge)002:19362: dor med pa'i ngo bo las /
NK093(ge)002:19363: 'dul bya dag gi bsam pa ji lta ba de
NK093(ge)002:19364: ltara cho 'phrul bltas rgu sna tshogs pa de nyid
NK093(ge)002:19366: ganga 'dira don mdzad pa'i bkod pa mang po'i snang
NK093(ge)002:19367: 'byung ston pa rgyun gyi bar mi chad par shar
NK093(ge)002:19368: kyang ma 'gags par sna tshogs su 'byung ba de
NK093(ge)002:19369: la bri zhing 'grib pas zad pa meda cing 'ong
NK093(ge)002:19370: bsdus kyis dngos por 'phela ba gang yang meda pa
NK093(ge)002:19372: ji ltar mgal me'i rang bzhin ni //
NK093(ge)002:19373: gang dag lag na 'gal me thogs //
NK093(ge)002:19374: bskor na 'khor lo'i rgyun ltar snang //
NK093(ge)002:19375: de la 'khor lo'i rang bzhin med //
NK093(ge)002:19376: de bzhin sngags kyi cho 'phrul yang //
NK093(ge)002:19377: mi mnyam mnyam pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK093(ge)002:19378: ji ltar dmigs pa'i don 'byung ste //
NK093(ge)002:19385: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19386: dper na gang 'dira bzhin gyi gzugsa brnyan ganga snang ba ni gsum ste /
NK093(ge)002:19387: byad bzhina gyi gdong pa dngos dang bzhina snang 'byung
NK093(ge)002:19388: ba'i gzhi me long g.ya' med par dwangsa pa gnyis
NK093(ge)002:19389: 'dzom nas snang ba yod pa gsum dang ldan pa
NK093(ge)002:19390: la brten nasa 'jog pa po'i byad bzhin de nyid
NK093(ge)002:19391: ji lta ba bzhina du gzugsa brnyana gyi snang ba
NK093(ge)002:19392: 'byung ngo // de ltar 'byung yang gzugs brnyan de
NK093(ge)002:19393: nyid dang me long de gnyis dus der tha mi
NK093(ge)002:19394: dad pa yin pa bzhin du /
NK093(ge)002:19395: don gsang sngags kyi dngos grub kyang /
NK093(ge)002:19396: gang 'dira spyir rgyu dang 'bras bu gnyis so so
NK093(ge)002:19397: tha dad par ma mthong basa theg pa chen po'i
NK093(ge)002:19398: don gyi ngo bo mthong na /
NK093(ge)002:19399: dngos grub kyi gazhi'am rgyu sems kyi chos nyid de 'bras bu dngos grub chen po yang yin te /
NK093(ge)002:19400: de nyid 'byung ba'i rgyu yang yin pas don la rgyu 'bras dbyer med pa'i phyir te /
NK093(ge)002:19401: de basa na chos nyid de la sems dang dngos
NK093(ge)002:19402: grub la rgyu 'bras so so de gnyis med de
NK093(ge)002:19403: sems kyi de bzhina nyid do //
NK093(ge)002:19404: des na de kho na dngos grub chen po mthar thug pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:19405: de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK093(ge)002:19406: gzugs brnyan snang ba'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK093(ge)002:19407: dper na gdong dang me long la //
NK093(ge)002:19408: brten nas bzhin gyi gzugs 'byung yang //
NK093(ge)002:19409: reng par gyur pa ga la yod //
NK093(ge)002:19410: de bzhin sngags kyi dngos grub kyang //
NK093(ge)002:19411: sgrub dang ting 'dzin yo byad las //
NK093(ge)002:19412: brten nas dngos grub tshul 'byung yang //
NK093(ge)002:19413: gsol thob dmigs pa ga la yod //
NK093(ge)002:19415: 'di dag kyang mtshan ma'i rnal 'byor bcus shes par bya ba'i mchog ste thag gcad pa'i don to //
NK093(ge)002:19417: de kho na nyid gcig par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19418: de blo dman pa'i yul ma yin par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19419: blo dman pas mi rtogs pa'i dpe don bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:19420: blo dman pa la gcig char mi rtogs pas rim gyis bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19421: bsam du med pa'i don blo dman la mi bstan par gdams pa /
NK093(ge)002:19422: don de mtshon cing brjod du med par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19423: rtogs na mtha' dbus med par bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:19424: don la blang dor med par bstan pa /
NK093(ge)002:19425: ma rtogs pa'i gol sa bshad pa /
NK093(ge)002:19426: rtogs ma rtogs kyi khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:19431: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19432: gtan tshigs kyis yid ches par bya ba ni /
NK093(ge)002:19433: bshad pa'i tshul desa na ji snyed du brjod cing
NK093(ge)002:19434: bstan pa yi mtshan mar snang ba'i chos so cog
NK093(ge)002:19435: thams cad mtshan ma med pa ji bzhina pa'i de
NK093(ge)002:19436: kho na nyid du dbyer med par gciga pa'i phyir
NK093(ge)002:19437: te de bas na sgrub thabs ganga ji ltar yang
NK093(ge)002:19438: snang ba de ltar bsgrub pa las dngos grub cir
NK093(ge)002:19439: snang dang rtags rnams ji ltar byung na yanga chos
NK093(ge)002:19440: nyid mnyam pa chen po mi g.yo ba yi ngang
NK093(ge)002:19441: lasa 'byung snang meda pas byang chub kyi sems las
NK093(ge)002:19443: de bas dpe bcus don mthong tshul gyi ngo bo de bzhin nyid du gcig par bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19445: de phyir mtshan ma'i chos thams cad //
NK093(ge)002:19446: mtshan med ngang du gcig pas na //
NK093(ge)002:19447: rtog pa'i bag chags ci byung yang //
NK093(ge)002:19448: chos kun dbyings su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK093(ge)002:19449: rtog 'jug spros pa'i mtshan ma kun //
NK093(ge)002:19450: ma byung ma skyes dbyings nyid las //
NK093(ge)002:19452: yon tan sna tshogs cher 'byung ba'i //
NK093(ge)002:19453: gter gyi dbyig 'di gang mthong ba //
NK093(ge)002:19454: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan yang //
NK093(ge)002:19455: skad cig gcig la de la 'dus //
NK093(ge)002:19456: de bas yid bzhin rin chen 'di //
NK093(ge)002:19457: ldog pa med pas dang du blang //
NK093(ge)002:19463: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19464: gsang sngags kyi dgongs don zaba mo zab pa'i yang snying gasnga ba dama pa 'di ni /
NK093(ge)002:19465: nam mkha'a la mu mtha' brtags kyang rtog pas mi
NK093(ge)002:19466: rnyed pa dang 'drar zhes 'dra bar gsang sngags mu
NK093(ge)002:19467: mtha' bral ba'i nges don gting dapaga daka'a zhing ji
NK093(ge)002:19468: bzhin du mthong ba dkon pa la /
NK093(ge)002:19469: rnal 'byor chen po shes rab kyi spyan nam lta
NK093(ge)002:19470: ba dang mi ldana pa ganga gis tha snyad kyi
NK093(ge)002:19471: ming mang po btags nas gsang ba'i grub mtha' la
NK093(ge)002:19472: rtog pa ni / brtags su med pa la brtagas
NK093(ge)002:19473: pa yin pasa yang dag par rtogsa para mi 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:19474: te rtog pa nyid kyis mi rnyed pa'i phyir ro
NK093(ge)002:19475: rtog pa ni / // des na snga ma las /
NK093(ge)002:19476: mi dmigs spros bral byang chub sems //
NK093(ge)002:19477: zab mor snang ba'i nges don 'di //
NK093(ge)002:19478: mkha' la mdud 'drar gting dpag dka' //rnal 'byor dmigs ldan blo chung zhing //
NK093(ge)002:19479: gang zhig rtsal zhan de rtog pa //
NK093(ge)002:19480: g.yog mo'i tshul du bdag brtags pa //
NK093(ge)002:19481: brtags kyang rtogs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:19487: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19488: de lta bu'i don de brtags pa'i tshul 'dis mi rtogs par 'chad de /
NK093(ge)002:19489: ji bzhin du rtogs par dka' ba'i tshul mtshon pa /
NK093(ge)002:19490: dpera na nyi ma'i snyinga po la miga gi dabnga posa gtad nas raba tu brtagsa na /
NK093(ge)002:19491: 'od kyi snying po de yanga gang su zhig gis nges par mi rtogsa kyi /
NK093(ge)002:19492: nyi ma 'oda 'abra ba'i zer phog pa'i zila gyis
NK093(ge)002:19493: mig rjira ram rdzil bar byas nas mi mthong bar
NK093(ge)002:19494: 'gyur ro // dpe de bzhina du gsang ba'i don
NK093(ge)002:19495: la shed ma bye ba'i byis pa blo rtsal zhana
NK093(ge)002:19497: gsang sngags snying po'i dona la blos cir brtagsa te
NK093(ge)002:19498: ji lta bar dpyad kyang rtog pa des gasnga ba'i
NK093(ge)002:19499: snying po gnyis su med pa'i sngags kyi don rtogs
NK093(ge)002:19500: par mi 'gyur bar yang dag par mi mthonga gi
NK093(ge)002:19501: / slar btsal ba po blo ngan pa'am zhana pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19502: byis pa de nyid tshi chad cing don la mdongs
NK093(ge)002:19503: te ga chad du brgyal bar 'gyur ba'i phyir de
NK093(ge)002:19504: / nyid las / dper na nyi ma'i snying po la /
NK093(ge)002:19505: mig gi dbang pos rab brtags na //
NK093(ge)002:19506: de brtags don de mi rtogs kyi //
NK093(ge)002:19508: de 'drar byis pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK093(ge)002:19509: zab mo'i don la cir brtags kyang //
NK093(ge)002:19510: yang dag don de mi mthong gi //
NK093(ge)002:19511: blo zhan byis pa ga chad brgyal //
NK093(ge)002:19517: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19518: desa na gsang sngags gasnga ba dama pa 'di ni /
NK093(ge)002:19519: rtogs par dka' ba'i tshul gyis dpesa mtshona par yang
NK093(ge)002:19520: dka' basa shes para mi nus te yul las 'das
NK093(ge)002:19521: pa'o // kyang ni mi mthun pa ste 'on kyang /
NK093(ge)002:19522: blo ldan la brgyud nas mtshon pa'i tshul gyis gang
NK093(ge)002:19523: gsang sngags gnyis su med pa'i don la rmongsa pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19524: mdongs pa dag la don gyi ngo bo phyogsa tsam
NK093(ge)002:19525: mtshon nas shes par bya ba'i dgos ched kyi phyir
NK093(ge)002:19526: du theg 'og pa'am lha'i rnal 'byor sogs dang ldan
NK093(ge)002:19527: pa'i skal ba can la ting nge 'dzin don dang
NK093(ge)002:19528: 'brel ba'am / sku phyag rgya la sogs pas don
NK093(ge)002:19529: la sbyor tshul phyogsa mtshon du bstan pa tsam mo
NK093(ge)002:19530: 'brel ba'am / // de skad du'ang snga ma las /
NK093(ge)002:19531: stong par sbas pa'i don 'di la //
NK093(ge)002:19532: dpes mtshon tshig gi lde mig gis //
NK093(ge)002:19533: mnyam nyid rig pa'i sgo dbye byas //
NK093(ge)002:19534: sbas pa'i don 'byin gsal byed pa //
NK093(ge)002:19535: s+aa lu phub khrod snang me bzhin //
NK093(ge)002:19536: bsal bteg snang rnyed sa ler 'dug /ces so //
NK093(ge)002:19541: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19542: spyod yul ka nas dag pas bsam du meda pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19543: chos nyid 'di la ye nas yid la bya bsam
NK093(ge)002:19544: dang bral te rtog dpyod kyis yul du med pas
NK093(ge)002:19545: de ltar nges pa'i lam pas kyang de nyid du'ang
NK093(ge)002:19546: 'du shes ma zhugs par de bzhina du gazhaga par
NK093(ge)002:19547: byas na rnal du phebs pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:19548: de ltar phebs pa'i ngang la mi rtog par gazhaga
NK093(ge)002:19549: pas ci ltar spyad kyang 'ching ba med pa'i don
NK093(ge)002:19550: gyi chos nyid zab mo 'di ni shin tu rtogs
NK093(ge)002:19551: par dka' bas gsang don la shed ma bye ba'i
NK093(ge)002:19552: byis pa blo chung rnams la ston pa ngasa ma
NK093(ge)002:19553: bstan zhing bka' stsal bar ma mdzad do zhes pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19555: brtag tu med pa'i chos rnams ni //
NK093(ge)002:19556: rtog pa can gyis mi rtogs te //
NK093(ge)002:19557: gang zhig de don mi rtog phyir //
NK093(ge)002:19558: g.yang sar ltung ba ci cha yod //
NK093(ge)002:19559: gdod nas ma thos shin tu dge //
NK093(ge)002:19560: bsam dang bral bas de bzhin gzhag /mi brtags bzhag pa'i chos 'di gang //
NK093(ge)002:19561: byis pa rnams la ngas ma bstan //
NK093(ge)002:19562: bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur ste //
NK093(ge)002:19563: bstan du med cing go bar dka' //zhes so //
NK093(ge)002:19569: gsang ba'i dbyings ji bzhin pa ni tshig tu brjod
NK093(ge)002:19570: pas don la mi phebs pa'i phyir tshig gi mtshona
NK093(ge)002:19571: pa lasa 'adsa te brjod pa dang bral ba yin
NK093(ge)002:19572: pa la bzlas pa'i sgra dang sgrub par gyis shig
NK093(ge)002:19573: ces pa la sogs pa ngo bo nges par brjod
NK093(ge)002:19574: pasa 'di zhes bstan du ga la yoda de med
NK093(ge)002:19575: pa'i phyir ro // des nas de kho na nyid
NK093(ge)002:19576: brjod pa dang bral ba'i phyir phyogs gcig tu grub
NK093(ge)002:19577: pa meda pasa ngo bo nges par mi zin pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19578: chos nyid de de la 'di zhes bstan pa'i dmigas
NK093(ge)002:19579: pa dag gis mi rnyed de mtha' gang du'ang mi
NK093(ge)002:19580: dmigas pa'i chos nyid kyi dbyings la brjod pa'i tshig
NK093(ge)002:19581: lam med par tha snyad thams cad las 'das pa
NK093(ge)002:19582: ni lta ba'i mchog dam pa yin te /
NK093(ge)002:19584: tshig gis brjod pa kun dang bral //
NK093(ge)002:19585: 'di zhes bstan du ga la yod //
NK093(ge)002:19586: med pas bstan pa'i dmigs mi phyed //
NK093(ge)002:19587: mi dmigs chos la blo sbyangs shing //
NK093(ge)002:19588: yid kyi me long gsal byas nas //
NK093(ge)002:19589: nam mkha' dag la rab brtags na //
NK093(ge)002:19590: snang ba med pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK093(ge)002:19591: nam mkha' lta bur de nyid 'gyur //
NK093(ge)002:19597: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19598: chos so cog kun gyi de kho na nyid ni
NK093(ge)002:19599: gsal la mi g.yo ba nam mkha'a lta bu dang
NK093(ge)002:19600: 'dra ba ste / des na chos nyid kyi nam mkha'a la yanga matshana nyid 'di yin no //
NK093(ge)002:19603: chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu ste //
NK093(ge)002:19604: nam mkha' la yang mtshan nyid bral //
NK093(ge)002:19606: de bas na nam mkha'a la dbus mtha'a mi dmigas
NK093(ge)002:19607: pa bzhina du chos kun kyang mtha'a dbus kyi mu
NK093(ge)002:19608: dang bral ba'i rig pa cir yang ma g.yos pa
NK093(ge)002:19609: ni ting nge 'dzin dam pa'i phyir ro //
NK093(ge)002:19614: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19615: dper na nam mkha'a la gang zag gang zhig ming
NK093(ge)002:19616: gi sgo nas yod med du brjod par byed pa
NK093(ge)002:19617: na yang / brjod pa de nyid tshig gi dngosa po yin te /
NK093(ge)002:19618: des na nam mkha' de yi tha snyad yod med
NK093(ge)002:19619: la sogs par minga gis brjod kyang nam mkha'a nyid
NK093(ge)002:19620: ming las mi skye bas de la skye 'agga gi
NK093(ge)002:19621: dngos po yod par mi 'gyur ro //
NK093(ge)002:19622: de bzhin du chos nyid mi rtog pa chen po
NK093(ge)002:19623: 'di la yang rnam par mi rtog pa'o zhes gang
NK093(ge)002:19624: dag don mi rtogs par smra zhing brjod de zhe
NK093(ge)002:19626: 'dod pa dang brjod pa de nyid rnam rtog kho
NK093(ge)002:19627: na ste chos nyid mi rtog pa la reg pa
NK093(ge)002:19628: med do // 'o na rnam par rtog pa spang ba zhig gam zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:19629: gsang ba'i dbyings mnyam pa nyid la rnam par rtog
NK093(ge)002:19630: pa dang rnama par mi rtog pa gang ci zhig
NK093(ge)002:19631: brjod par byas kyang de nyid yin pas ngo bo
NK093(ge)002:19632: la gnyis su med pas 'agla bar yang mi 'gyur
NK093(ge)002:19633: te / cir yang btags pa ltar chags pa'i phyir te /
NK093(ge)002:19634: de bas na de bzhin nyid de ni rgyal ba thams cad kyi bzhugs gnas chen po'i phyir /
NK093(ge)002:19636: nam mkha' gang ming rjod byed pa //
NK093(ge)002:19637: brjod pa de nyid dngos po ste //
NK093(ge)002:19638: dngos po de yi ming brjod kyang //
NK093(ge)002:19640: de bzhin mi rtog brjod byed pa //
NK093(ge)002:19641: brjod pa de nyid rnam rtog ste //
NK093(ge)002:19642: rnam rtog de yi ming brjod kyang //
NK093(ge)002:19644: de 'drar sems kyang de ltar lta //
NK093(ge)002:19645: sems nyid gzhan du ma grub ste //
NK093(ge)002:19646: de bzhin chos kyang grub ma yin //
NK093(ge)002:19647: sems dang chos nyid gnyis med de //
NK093(ge)002:19648: sems nyid gang yin chos nyid de //
NK093(ge)002:19649: chos nyid kyang ni de bzhin no //
NK093(ge)002:19650: chos sems gnyis med ldan gyur pa //
NK093(ge)002:19651: bla med byang chub chen por bshad //
NK093(ge)002:19657: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19658: thig le chen po chos kyi sku'i bdag nyid la
NK093(ge)002:19659: skabs gang 'dira cho 'phrul tha dad gzhi dang snang
NK093(ge)002:19660: ba gnyis su 'doda pa la sogs pa dang /
NK093(ge)002:19661: dbus dang mtha'a 'byed de chos nyid kyi mu tshol
NK093(ge)002:19662: ba thams cad ni nor ba dang gol sar 'phyan
NK093(ge)002:19663: pa'o // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK093(ge)002:19664: mnyam pa nyid la de nyid du'ang brjod cing mngon
NK093(ge)002:19665: du bya ba dang bral ba las mi mnyam pa
NK093(ge)002:19666: la ltos nas mnyam pa nyid ces bya ba de
NK093(ge)002:19667: nyid du btags pa'i tha snyad kyi snang ba nyid
NK093(ge)002:19668: kyang mnyam mi mnyam gnyis dang dbus mathara 'byed pa
NK093(ge)002:19669: las gyur te ltos pa'i dbang las byung ba ste
NK093(ge)002:19670: skyon yin no // de bas na cho 'phrul gyi mtshan nyid dang mtha' dbus ci snang yang /
NK093(ge)002:19671: ye tha snyad dang bral ba la de nyid du 'dod cing mngon du byed pa'ang med pa'o //
NK093(ge)002:19673: kye ma 'di gcig ces pa nas /
NK093(ge)002:19674: nges pa 'di ltar zhog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te //
NK093(ge)002:19675: kye ma'o zhes ngo mtshar ba'i tshig gis bos nas
NK093(ge)002:19676: 'dir gsungs pa ltar mnyam pa'i rang bzhin 'di nyid
NK093(ge)002:19677: gciga tu nges pas chosa kyi spun gyi nges tshig
NK093(ge)002:19678: kyang 'grub ste dngos grub dang bsgrub par bya ba
NK093(ge)002:19679: thams cad ji snyed pa'ang don de kho na nyid
NK093(ge)002:19680: gcig pu de las meda bzhina du rgyu 'bras dang
NK093(ge)002:19681: mtha' gnyis la sogs par snang ba 'di kun gnyis
NK093(ge)002:19682: su 'byed phan chad thams cad ril rnam par rtog
NK093(ge)002:19684: de bas na don bcu dang dpe bcu ril kun
NK093(ge)002:19685: gyis kyang ngesa para brjod pa'i don gyi snying po
NK093(ge)002:19686: dam pa 'di ltar yid la zhog la legs par
NK093(ge)002:19687: zungs shig pa'o // gsum pa ni /
NK093(ge)002:19690: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK093(ge)002:19692: de dag ni dpe yi me long la brtag nas don btsal bar bya'o //
NK093(ge)002:19693: zhes pa'i dgongsa pa ma nor ba'i ngo bo dama
NK093(ge)002:19694: pa nges para bgrosa pa yin par shes par bya'o
NK093(ge)002:19695: // de skad ces smras te bka' stsal pas /
NK093(ge)002:19696: 'khor langa ka'i badga po la sogas pa dman pa'i
NK093(ge)002:19697: lus kyi semas dapa'a chen po rnams kyis kyang de'i
NK093(ge)002:19698: the tshom chod de don yang dag para ngesa pa
NK093(ge)002:19699: de kho na nyid gciga tu gdengs rnyed de chos
NK093(ge)002:19700: nyid kyi ngang du ngesa par mnyam par 'joga para
NK093(ge)002:19702: sangsa rgyasa kuna gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK093(ge)002:19703: dpe la brten nas don nye bar mtshona pa zhes
NK093(ge)002:19704: bya ba'i le'u ste drug cu rtsa gsum pa nyid
